NK029(ha)001:1: // snga 'gyur bka' ma'i chos sde'i glegs bam nyer dgu pa bzhugs so //
NK029(ha)001:3: // dang po phyi dbang gi chu bo las /
NK029(ha)001:4: +aah kri ya'i dbang gi them skas bzhugs so //
NK029(ha)001:5: lnga pa bya ba'i rgyud kyi dbang la gnyis te /
NK029(ha)001:6: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:9: tshad dang ldan pa'i sa stegs la //
NK029(ha)001:10: dri bzang chu yis chag chag gdab //
NK029(ha)001:11: byin brlabs ldan pa'i thig skud kyis //
NK029(ha)001:12: cha chen bcu drug legs par gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13: de nas cha bran gdab pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:14: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK029(ha)001:15: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)001:16: gsum pa bzhi pa dor bar bya //
NK029(ha)001:17: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK029(ha)001:18: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK029(ha)001:19: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)001:20: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab /
NK029(ha)001:21: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:22: cha chen gcig nas lte ba bskor //
NK029(ha)001:23: cha chen gnyis nas rtsibs bzhi bskor //
NK029(ha)001:24: cha chen gsum nas rtsibs bcu bskor //
NK029(ha)001:25: glang gur rdo ra spyi dang mtshungs //
NK029(ha)001:26: zla yab zur thig phrad so nas //
NK029(ha)001:27: pad ra rdo ra me ri la //
NK029(ha)001:28: ci rigs 'tshams pa bskor bar bya //
NK029(ha)001:29: byin brlabs ldan pa'i tshon rtsi yi //
NK029(ha)001:30: mkhas pas re kha legs par bri //
NK029(ha)001:31: dbus kyi lte ba ser po byed //
NK029(ha)001:32: mtshams bzhi'i rtsibs bzhi ser po la //
NK029(ha)001:33: phyogs bzhir gri gug bzhi yang bri //
NK029(ha)001:34: de'i phyi la rtsibs bcu sngo //
NK029(ha)001:35: rtsibs 'chan dmar po gru chad ni //
NK029(ha)001:36: shar dmar lho ljang nub dkar po //
NK029(ha)001:37: byang ser lha rnams phyogs mdog go /
NK029(ha)001:38: rtsigs pa la sogs gong dang mthun //
NK029(ha)001:39: de nas rnam pa bgod pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:40: dbus su rigs gsum mgon po'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:41: rtsibs bzhi la ni gtum po bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:42: rtsibs mchan bzhi la gri gug bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:43: rtsibs bcu la ni khro bo bcu //
NK029(ha)001:44: gsung thugs rten ni gong dang mtshungs //
NK029(ha)001:45: lhag chad gsal zhing zhal gsos mchod //
NK029(ha)001:46: mchod yon la sogs phyi mchod dang //
NK029(ha)001:47: gtor ma bshams pa la sogs dang //
NK029(ha)001:48: bum sogs bsham pa gong dang mthun //
NK029(ha)001:49: de ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:50: de rab gnas kyi don ni /
NK029(ha)001:51: dpon slob rnams gdan la bzhugs shing //
NK029(ha)001:54: byin gyis brlabs la bsngo zhing 'tshams bcad pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:55: mchod pa byin gyis rlabs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:56: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed rnams gong bzhin sngon du song nas /
NK029(ha)001:60: b+h+rum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang pa /
NK029(ha)001:63: rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa'i nang du /
NK029(ha)001:69: dam tshigs sems dpa' bskyed pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:70: ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:78: gtso bo bskyed pa dang 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:79: dang po la gnyis te bskyed pa dang byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:80: dang po ni ye shes kyi tshogs ci yang mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK029(ha)001:81: 'byung ba rims brtsegs ri rab dang bcas pa'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:82: rdo rje'i gur khang yangs shing rgya che ba'i dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:83: de'i phyi rims du 'khor lo rtsibs bcu /
NK029(ha)001:84: 'khor lo'i lte bar rin po che'i khri seng ge brgyad kyis btegs pa'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:87: ram las nyi ma'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:88: h+aum sngo nag gcig gsal ba las /
NK029(ha)001:89: na ma tsan d+ha badz+ra kro d+ha y+aa hu lu
NK029(ha)001:90: hu lu tish+tha tish+tha b+han d+ha b+han d+ha ha na
NK029(ha)001:91: ha na a smri ta h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:92: ces brjod pas bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa sku mdog sngo nag /
NK029(ha)001:93: zhal gcig phyag gnyis zhabs gnyis dor thabs kyi nyi ma'i gdan rdzis pa /
NK029(ha)001:94: shin tu khros nas spyan gsum dmar la zlum pa /
NK029(ha)001:95: bskal pa'i me dpung gi klong na bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:96: mche ba rno dkar zangs yag tu brtsigs pa /
NK029(ha)001:97: ag tshom rma ra kham pa gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK029(ha)001:98: dbu skra kham ser gyen du 'khyil ba'i rtsa bar sbrul dang rdo rje'i 'phreng ba bcings pa /
NK029(ha)001:99: g.yas rdo rje rgya gram bskor tshul gyis 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:100: g.yon pa sdigs 'dzug thugs khar bsgreng ba /
NK029(ha)001:101: sku smad la stag gis sham thabs byas pa /
NK029(ha)001:102: sku stod la dar ljang khu'i chos gos mnabs pa'i 'phel ka rlung gis g.yeng ba lta bu /
NK029(ha)001:103: dbu'i ral chings rgyal rigs dkar po la byas pa /
NK029(ha)001:104: rna brgyan rje rigs khra bo la byas pa /
NK029(ha)001:105: phyag gdub bram ze ser po la byas pa /
NK029(ha)001:106: zhabs gnyis gdol pa nag po las byas pa /
NK029(ha)001:107: klu'i pho nya'i rigs nag po se ral khar thogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:108: dbu la rin po che'i srog zhu dang /
NK029(ha)001:113: 'od skal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i nang na /
NK029(ha)001:114: h+aum h+aum phata kyi sgra 'brug stong ldir ba ltar sgrogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:115: gdug pa can thams cad 'dul ba'i tsha rngam gyi skur sgom /
NK029(ha)001:116: gnyis pa byin brlabs la gnyis te /
NK029(ha)001:118: kha lag byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:121: spyi bor zla ba'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:122: rdo rje dkar po gyis mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:124: mgrin par pad+ma'i steng du rdo rje dmar po +aas /
NK029(ha)001:127: thugs khar nyi ma'i steng du rdo rje mthing nag h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:129: lte bar rin chen zur brgyad kyi steng du rdo rje ser po tram gis mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:131: gsang gnas su e gru gsum gyi steng du rdo rje ljang khu has mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:132: a ta ha sa ni la badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:133: dpung pa g.yas su zla ba'i steng du rdo rje mthing nag h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:135: dpung pa g.yon du zla ba'i steng du rdo rje 'thing nag h+aum gis mtshan pa bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:136: de ni 'bras bu byang chub sems dpa' bdun gyi ngo bo yin /
NK029(ha)001:137: gnyis pa kha lag byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:138: rang gi lce rdo rje rtse gsum pa 'phred nyal du 'dug pa'i bum pa h'u gis mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:139: lag pa rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK029(ha)001:140: bum pa gdu gu ltar 'dug par bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)001:141: de'i g.yas su 'jam dbyangs sku mdog dmar gser zhal phyag gnyis pa /
NK029(ha)001:142: phyag g.yas shes rab kyi ral gri glad la 'phyar ba /
NK029(ha)001:143: g.yon pa pha rol tu phyin pa'i po ti thugs khar bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:144: dar dang rin po che'i brgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:145: zhabs rdo rje dkyil dkrungs gis bzhugs par bsgoms /
NK029(ha)001:146: g.yon du spyan ras gzigs sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
NK029(ha)001:147: phyag gong ma gnyis thugs khar thal mo sbyar ba /
NK029(ha)001:148: g.yas kyi 'og ma shel dkar gyi 'phreng ba brgya rtsa brgyad 'dren pa /
NK029(ha)001:149: g.yon 'og ma na pad+ma 'dab ma drug pa'i yu ba 'dzin cing /
NK029(ha)001:150: snyan gyi thad kar kha gyes pa /
NK029(ha)001:151: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:152: zhabs rdo rje dkyil mo dkrung gis bzhugs par bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:154: tshin d+ha tshin d+ha ma h+aa ki li ki la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:155: byang shar 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su /
NK029(ha)001:156: rdo rje gtum po sku mdog smug nag zhal gcig phyag gnyiis shin tu khros pa /
NK029(ha)001:159: tsu ru tsu ru tsan d+ha li badz+ra ki li ki la ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:160: shar lhor rdo rje phur bu sku ser nag g.yas rdo rje rtse gcig /
NK029(ha)001:162: b+han d+ha b+han d+ha kro ta ki li ki la ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:163: lho nub du rdo rje be con sku mdog da mar nag g.yas dbyug pa g.yon sdig mdzub /
NK029(ha)001:164: tra sa ya tra sa ya badz+ra ki li ki la ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:165: nub byang rdo rje khro bo sku mdog nag po g.yas tho ba g.yon sdig mdzub /
NK029(ha)001:166: 'tshams bzhir gri gug bzhi bsam pa yum du mos /
NK029(ha)001:167: khro bo de rnams ni zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK029(ha)001:169: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'khyil ba /
NK029(ha)001:171: klu chen brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:172: skal pa'i me dpung gi nang du bzhugs pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:173: skad cig gis rdzus skyes su bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:174: de'i phyi rol 'khor lo rtsibs bcur nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bcu'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:178: nub smad du stobs po che /
NK029(ha)001:180: shar du rnam par rgyal ba /
NK029(ha)001:182: shar lhor dbyug pa sngon po /
NK029(ha)001:186: lho nub du mi g.yo mgon po /
NK029(ha)001:187: ha ra d+ha ra ya badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:189: d+ha ru na d+ha ru na badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:190: nub byang du gzhan gyis mi thub pa /
NK029(ha)001:194: byang shar du khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba /
NK029(ha)001:195: khro bo de dag thams cad sku mdog mthing nag /
NK029(ha)001:196: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa /
NK029(ha)001:200: nyi ma'i gdan la brkyang skum gyis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:201: stags lpags kyi sham thabs can /
NK029(ha)001:202: klu chen po brgyad dang rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:203: bskal pa'i me ri 'bar ba'i dbus na /
NK029(ha)001:205: chems rngams gyis sgra dang bcas te bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:206: de'i phyi rol 'khor yug gi steng du mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:207: bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:208: sgo ba bzhi mos pa'am cung zad gsal bar bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:209: de yan ni dam tshig sems dpa' bskyed pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:210: gnyis pa spyan drangs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:211: lha tshogs thams cad kyi spyi bor /
NK029(ha)001:213: h+aum las 'od 'phros pas byang phyogs lcang lo can
NK029(ha)001:214: nas rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i lha tshogs rnams
NK029(ha)001:216: rdo rje dril bu dang bcas pas 'di skad du /
NK029(ha)001:217: h+aum ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing /
NK029(ha)001:218: bdud sde dpung bcas mi bzad 'joms mdzad lha /
NK029(ha)001:219: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:220: bcom ldan 'khor bcas gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:221: e h+ya hi b+ha ga ban /
NK029(ha)001:222: ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha hohdzahh+aum bam ho /
NK029(ha)001:223: zhes mdun gyi nam mkha' nas byon par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:224: gsum pa zhal bsil dbul ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:225: yang dag nyid du bdag med kyang /
NK029(ha)001:226: 'jig rten srid zhu'i tshul gyis ni /
NK029(ha)001:227: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil mdzod la /
NK029(ha)001:228: 'di nyid du ni bzhugs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:229: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho sarba d+harma swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho ham bzhi pa gdan dbul ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:230: mya ngan mi 'da' thugs rje'i ngang //
NK029(ha)001:231: nyon mongs ma spangs gos pa med //
NK029(ha)001:232: ma chags rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK029(ha)001:233: pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:234: tish+tha badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)001:236: rnam dag sku mnga' mchog tu gzugs bzang ba //
NK029(ha)001:237: ye shes rgya mtsho gser gyi lhun po 'dra //
NK029(ha)001:238: grags pas 'jig rten gsum na lham me ba //
NK029(ha)001:239: mgon po mchog nyid la ni skyabs su mchi //
NK029(ha)001:240: h+aum bcom ldan rnam par 'joms pa'i gtso //
NK029(ha)001:241: gdug pa 'dul phyir khro rgyal kun gyi gtso //
NK029(ha)001:242: sku yi 'od zer bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:243: gzigs mdangs sdang gzigs nyi ltar 'bar ba'i brjid //
NK029(ha)001:244: spyan gsum bsgrad pas sdang mig zlum zhing 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:245: log 'dren bgegs 'dul mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:246: nyon mongs dug 'joms mdzad pa'i sku nyid du //
NK029(ha)001:247: nor bu rna chas brgyan cing klu chen brgyan //
NK029(ha)001:248: sbrul gdugs gzugs kyi tshogs 'dzin rnams kyis spras //
NK029(ha)001:249: zhe sdang dug 'joms mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:255: drug pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:257: badz+ra dz+wa la a na la ha na da ha pa tsa ma tha b+hany+tsa ra na h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:259: tram las rin po che'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du /
NK029(ha)001:260: +aahh+aum 'od du zhu ba las byung ba'i lha rdzas las grub pa'i mchod yon /
NK029(ha)001:266: rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas /
NK029(ha)001:267: nam mkha' bar snang thams cad yongs su gang ba'i
NK029(ha)001:268: mchod sprin bsam gyis mi khyab pa rang bzhin thogs
NK029(ha)001:270: na ma sar+b+ba ta tha ga ta argam pra ti dza ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:278: rgyal ba'i sku la dri ma mi mnga' yang //
NK029(ha)001:279: sems can dri ma'i bag chags bsal slad du //
NK029(ha)001:280: sku gsung thugs la khrus chab 'di gsol bas //
NK029(ha)001:281: khams gsum gnas pa'i bag chags dag gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:282: ma h+aa ra a ha ra sarba b+hi d+ha ra
NK029(ha)001:283: argam pu tsa me ga sa mun+ta s+pha ra na
NK029(ha)001:285: tshul khrims dri ldan spos mchog dam pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:286: ting 'dzin sngags dang phyag rgyas byin brlabs nas //
NK029(ha)001:287: sangs rgyas zhing du spos dri ngad ldan pas //
NK029(ha)001:288: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams mnyes gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:289: na mahsarba ta th+aa d+hu pe pu tsa me ga
NK029(ha)001:290: sa mu tra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum
NK029(ha)001:291: / dkyil 'khor kun tu rgyal ba mnyes mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:292: rin chen dbyibs legs lha rdzas me tog 'di //
NK029(ha)001:293: nam mkha' gang bar yid kyis mngon sprul te //
NK029(ha)001:294: gzhal yas khang du sprin bzhin gtibs gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:297: nyon mongs dug sregs ma rig mun sel ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:298: shes rab gzi mdangs dpal gyi sgron me 'di //
NK029(ha)001:299: sprin med mkha' la nyi shar ji bzhin du //
NK029(ha)001:300: ye shes snang bas phyogs bcur gsal gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:302: stong gsum kun tu dri ngad ldan pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:303: spos mchog rnams kyi thub dbang rgyal ba'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:304: gser mdog btso ma byi dor byas 'dra ba'i //'od chags 'dra ba de la byug par bgyi //
NK029(ha)001:307: rgyal ba'i sku la bkres pa mi mnga' yang /
NK029(ha)001:308: 'gro ba'i don du lha rdzas bdud rtsi'i bshos //
NK029(ha)001:309: dag cing gtsang mar sbyar te 'bul lags na //
NK029(ha)001:310: ye shes thugs rjes dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:313: dril chen bsil snyan rnam grol tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK029(ha)001:314: bsam dag ngag gis bstod de 'bul lags na //
NK029(ha)001:315: sa bcu rim gyis bgrod nas sangs rgyas par //
NK029(ha)001:316: tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas chos kyi rgyal por shog /
NK029(ha)001:319: bcom ldan rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i lha tshogs la //
NK029(ha)001:320: mchod pa bla na med pas mchod //
NK029(ha)001:321: sangs rgyas dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //'gro la phan phyir gtso chen gyis //
NK029(ha)001:322: sman par dgongs te bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:323: dkon mchog rin chen dpal zhing du //
NK029(ha)001:324: yid du 'ong ba'i mchod sprin dang //
NK029(ha)001:325: rol mo bsil snyan 'phan gdugs dang //
NK029(ha)001:326: bla re rgyal mtshan lhab lhub dang //
NK029(ha)001:327: me tog 'phreng ba bdug pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:328: mchod sprin sna tshogs phyogs bcur 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:329: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bden pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:330: nam mkha' mdzod kyi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK029(ha)001:331: sangs rgyas zhing khams rab 'byams su //
NK029(ha)001:332: bla med mchod pa sprin 'byung zhing //
NK029(ha)001:333: yon tan brgyad ldan thams cad kyi //
NK029(ha)001:334: zhabs la spyi bos gtug gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:335: bdun pa bstod pa bya ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:336: chos dbyings ye shes rnam rtog 'joms //
NK029(ha)001:337: nyon mongs dgra de ye shes sku //
NK029(ha)001:338: rtogs pa dri ma sel mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:340: me long ye shes gzung 'dzin spongs //
NK029(ha)001:341: zhe sdang dri ma 'joms mdzad cing //
NK029(ha)001:342: rdo rje gtum po ye shes sku //
NK029(ha)001:343: nga rgyal rnam gsum 'joms mdzad cing //
NK029(ha)001:344: tshe ring dbang bskur mchog thob mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:345: phyag 'tshal rdo rje phur bu la'o //
NK029(ha)001:346: so sor kun rtog ye shes kyis //
NK029(ha)001:347: lta ba ngan pa 'joms mdzad cing //'dod chags rnam dag shes rab rgyas //
NK029(ha)001:348: mun pa 'joms phyir be con la'o //
NK029(ha)001:349: bya ba rjes bsgrub ye shes kyis //
NK029(ha)001:350: sems can kun la mchog rtsol cig /
NK029(ha)001:351: gdon bgegs 'joms phyir shin tu khros //
NK029(ha)001:352: ye shes sku 'joms khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:353: h+aum dbus su rdo rje rnam 'joms ni //
NK029(ha)001:354: sku mdog mthing kha nag po'i zhal //
NK029(ha)001:355: phyag 'tshal sna tshogs rdo rje la //
NK029(ha)001:356: dngos gcig yu ba brten mdzad cing //
NK029(ha)001:357: ye shes lus can sku yi mchog /
NK029(ha)001:358: tshe 'phel yon tan mthar phyin mdzad //'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:359: gnyis med sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:360: byang shar rdo rje khro bo ni //
NK029(ha)001:361: sku mdog smug nag drag po'i zhal //
NK029(ha)001:362: phyag mtshan rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:363: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK029(ha)001:364: shar lhor rdo rje phur bu ni //
NK029(ha)001:365: sku mdog ser nag drag po'i zhal /
NK029(ha)001:366: phyag na rdo rje rtse gcig bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:367: de la bstod lho nub rdo rje be con ni //
NK029(ha)001:368: sku mdog dmar nag drag po'i zhal //
NK029(ha)001:369: phyag na rdo rje be con bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:370: de la bstod de nub byang rdo rje khro bo ni //
NK029(ha)001:371: sku mdog nag po shin tu khros //
NK029(ha)001:372: phyag mtshan rdo rje tho ba bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:373: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK029(ha)001:374: h+aum stengs phyogs khro rgyal h+aum ka ra //
NK029(ha)001:375: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK029(ha)001:376: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:378: h+aum shar phyogs khro bo rnam par rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:379: zhal gcig phyag zhabs gnyis dri za 'dul la /
NK029(ha)001:380: shar lhor khro rgyal dbyug sngon can //
NK029(ha)001:381: zhal gcig zhabs gnyis me lha 'dul la lho phyogs khro rgyal gshin rje bshed /
NK029(ha)001:382: zhal gcig zhabs gnyis gshin rje 'dul la lho nub khro rgyal mi g.yo mgon //
NK029(ha)001:383: zhal zhabs srin po 'dul la nub phyogs khro rgyal rta mgrin ni //
NK029(ha)001:384: zhal zhabs klu gdon 'dul la nub byang khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:385: zhal zhabs rlung lha 'dul la byang phyogs khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK029(ha)001:386: zhal zhabs gnod sbyin 'dul la byang shar khro bo khams gsum rnam par rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:387: zhal zhabs 'byung po 'dul la /'og phyogs khro bo stobs po che //
NK029(ha)001:388: zhal zhabs sa bdag 'dul la h+aum lha chen 'dod chags gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:389: nang gi lha mor sku sprul pa //
NK029(ha)001:390: sgeg mo 'phreng ba de bzhin glu //
NK029(ha)001:391: gar mdzad lha mo phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:392: bde gshegs dgyes pa bskyed pa'i phyir //'phags pa mchod cing sku sprul pa //
NK029(ha)001:393: bdug spos me tog mar me dang //
NK029(ha)001:394: dri yi lha mor phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:395: bde gshegs mngon par sangs rgyas tshe //
NK029(ha)001:396: bkra shis rtag tu sku sprul pa //
NK029(ha)001:398: rgyal mtshan gdugs dang bum pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:399: dung dang gser nya la sogs te //
NK029(ha)001:400: bkra shis lha mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:401: bde gshegs dgyes pa bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:402: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrogs dril //
NK029(ha)001:403: sgo skyongs bsrungs ma'i tshogs rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:404: dad pas brgyud te phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:405: de nas ye shes pa stim mo //
NK029(ha)001:407: rang gi thugs khar sna tshogs rdo rje rgya gram gyi lte bar /
NK029(ha)001:408: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h+aum mthing nag rab tu 'bar ba'i mtha' skor du /
NK029(ha)001:411: de rgyab gzungs ring gis bskor bar bsams la /
NK029(ha)001:412: sngags las 'od zer spro bsdu kha dog rnam pa bzhi dang sbyar /
NK029(ha)001:413: sngon du bsnyen pa tshad du bskyol ba'i brgya rtsa brgyad la sogs gang 'grub bazla'o //
NK029(ha)001:417: h+aum dus gsum sangs rgyas gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin cing /
NK029(ha)001:418: khro bo'i rgyal bo ye shes rdo rje can //
NK029(ha)001:419: sku yi sprul pa rdo rje rnam par 'joms //
NK029(ha)001:420: rdo rje rigs kyi khro rgyal phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:421: gdug pa 'dul phyir khro rgyal skur ston pa //'gying bag tshul bzhugs 'jigs pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK029(ha)001:422: rigs bzhi khro bo bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:423: h+aum bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK029(ha)001:424: rigs sngags rgyal po bsrungs pa'i khro bo bcu //
NK029(ha)001:425: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten bgegs kyi tshogs bcom pa //
NK029(ha)001:426: khro bo chen po bcu la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:427: bsod nams ye shes tshogs gnyis rab rdzogasashinga //
NK029(ha)001:428: legs pa'i don ldan bkra shis lha mo brgyad //
NK029(ha)001:429: yid 'ong lha yi rgyan gyis rab tu mdzes //
NK029(ha)001:430: bkra shis lha mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:431: bcom ldan rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bka' nyan cing //
NK029(ha)001:432: bstan pa bsrungs phyir 'jig rten skyongs pa'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:433: tshangs pa chen po la sogs bka'i 'khor //
NK029(ha)001:434: rdo rje rigs kyi bsrungs ma rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:437: spyi don gnyis pa bum bskyed la brgyad kyi dang
NK029(ha)001:438: po dam tshig sems dpa' bskyed pa la gnyis te
NK029(ha)001:442: lag pa 'khor lo'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK029(ha)001:443: bum pa mi dmigs pa'i ngang las /
NK029(ha)001:445: rang gi thugs kha nas b+h+rum gcig spros pa las /
NK029(ha)001:446: rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:447: phyi bum pa'i dbyibs su 'dug pa /
NK029(ha)001:449: 'og bzhi 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:450: mtshams bzhi gri gug bzhi langs te 'dug pa /
NK029(ha)001:452: de'i phyi rol du 'khor lo rtsibs bcu /
NK029(ha)001:453: phyi'i lha rnams dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:457: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan gsum brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:458: rtsibs bcu la nyi ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:460: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK029(ha)001:462: na mo rat+na tra ya y+aa /
NK029(ha)001:463: na mo tsan d+ha badz+ra krod+ha y+aa /
NK029(ha)001:464: ki li ki la ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:465: ces rnam par 'joms pa 'khor bcas bdag bskyed ltar bsgoms /
NK029(ha)001:466: lha rnams la mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:467: bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:468: sgo ba bzhi dang bcas pa bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:473: bstod pa'i rjes su bsnyen pa byed pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:474: thugs khar sngags 'khor bsgom pa gong dang 'dra ba la /
NK029(ha)001:475: h+aum de'i zhabs kyu'i khug par bsgrubs bya bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:478: mdo'i phan yon dang bcas bskor ba bsgoms //
NK029(ha)001:479: dmigs pa gsal po yun ring du gtad pa lha'i rnam 'byor ro //
NK029(ha)001:480: gnyis pa gzungs 'don pa'i dmigs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:481: gzungs thags thugs khar gzung la /
NK029(ha)001:482: rang gi thugs kha'i h+aum dang /
NK029(ha)001:483: bum bskyed kyi thugs kha'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:484: 'phags pa'i tshogs la mchod pa 'bul zhing /
NK029(ha)001:485: gnyis su med pa'i zag med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi 'byung bas bdag la thim /
NK029(ha)001:486: bdag gis thugs kha nas mu tig star la rgyus pa ltar gzung thag la brten nas /
NK029(ha)001:487: bum bskyed kyi thugs khar bsgrub bya la phog pas lus ngag yid gsum gyis sdig sgrib dag /
NK029(ha)001:488: rnam 'joms kyi skur gyur nas bdud rtsi lhag mas bum pa gang bar bsam /
NK029(ha)001:489: gzungs kyi yig 'bru yang de ltar bsams nas klag pa'i tshul du 'don no //
NK029(ha)001:490: gzungs kyi cho ga las bzhi dang sbyar ba zhal shes mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:491: lag pa g.yas pas yungs dkar gzung /
NK029(ha)001:492: g.yon pas gzungs thag gzung la /
NK029(ha)001:493: thon nas yungs kar de la sngags te bum par blugs /
NK029(ha)001:494: ngo bo bdud rtsi las rnam pa khro chung rdul
NK029(ha)001:495: phra rabs kyis bsgrub bya'i lus bltams nas bum pa
NK029(ha)001:496: gang bar bsam / spyi don gsum pa mdun bskyed la brgyad kyi dang po /
NK029(ha)001:497: dam tshig sems dpa'i bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK029(ha)001:502: rdul tshon mi dmigs pa stong pa'i ngang las /
NK029(ha)001:504: ri rab dang bcas pa'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:505: rdo rje'i gur khang yangs shing rgya che ba'i dbus
NK029(ha)001:506: su b+h+rum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub
NK029(ha)001:507: pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:508: rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:509: 'og gzhi 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:510: mtshams bzhir gri gur langs te 'dug pa /
NK029(ha)001:512: de'i phyi rol du 'khor lo rtsibs bcu /
NK029(ha)001:513: phyi'i lha rnams dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:515: dbus su seng ge'i khri nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan gsum brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:516: rtsibs bcu la nyi ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:517: lha rnams la zla ba re gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK029(ha)001:519: na mo rat+na tra ya y+aa /
NK029(ha)001:520: na mo tsan d+ha badz+ra krod+ha ya ki li ki la ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:521: ces rnam par 'joms pa 'khor bcas bdag bskyed ltar bsgoms /
NK029(ha)001:522: lha rnams la mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:523: bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:524: sgo ba bzhi dang bcas pa bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:534: dbang rdzas la sogs la nas 'bru gtor zhing /
NK029(ha)001:536: 'grub na sbyin sreg kyang ci rigs par bya'o /
NK029(ha)001:537: gnyis pa 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la gnyis te /
NK029(ha)001:538: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:539: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:540: dang po slob dpon 'jug cing dbang len pa ni gong dang mtshungs so //
NK029(ha)001:541: gnyis pa slob ma 'jug cing dbang bskur ba la gnyis te /
NK029(ha)001:542: dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:544: khrus nas tshogs yon 'bul ba yan chad bco lnga po gong dang mthun la /
NK029(ha)001:545: bye brag du bco lnga pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:546: 'o mdun 'di na yod pa'i kri ya'i dkyil 'khor rten dang brten pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:549: de'i nang du gzhal yas kyi khang pa /
NK029(ha)001:552: rgyan rta babs dang bcas ba /
NK029(ha)001:554: 'khor lo rtsibs bcu 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba
NK029(ha)001:555: dang bcas pa mngon sum du mthong ba'i mos pa
NK029(ha)001:556: mdzod / 'khor lo'i lte bar bcom ldan 'das rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa phyag na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:559: de'i phyi rol rtsibs bzhi la gtum po lha bzhi
NK029(ha)001:560: rtsibs mchan bzhi la yum bzhi'i ngo bo gri khug
NK029(ha)001:561: bzhi / de'i phyi rol lha rnams la mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:562: bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:563: sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa sku snang la rang
NK029(ha)001:564: bzhin med pa me long nang gi gzugs brnyan bzhin
NK029(ha)001:565: mngon sum du mthong ba de khyed rang rnams kyi
NK029(ha)001:566: yi dam gyi lha skal yin ang snyam pa'i mos
NK029(ha)001:567: pa mdzod cig / tshogs dang yon ni gong lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:568: spyi don gnyis pa dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)001:572: dang po ni gong dang mthun no //
NK029(ha)001:573: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)001:574: phyi phan pa'i dbang la brgyad dang /
NK029(ha)001:575: nang nus pa'i dbang la lnga dang /
NK029(ha)001:576: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:578: bum pa'i dbang la sogs dgu po gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:579: bye brag du phyag rgya'i dbang bskur ba la /
NK029(ha)001:596: mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad bkra shis lha mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:597: sgo ma bzhi 'khor dang bcas pa byon nas khyed
NK029(ha)001:598: rang rnams la thim nas khyed rang rnams kyi phung
NK029(ha)001:599: po khams skye mched rnams dang gnyis su med par
NK029(ha)001:600: bsgoms mdzod cig / bsgrags tshigs ni /
NK029(ha)001:601: chos dbyings ye shes rnam rtog 'joms //
NK029(ha)001:602: nyon mongs dgra ste ye shes sku //
NK029(ha)001:603: rtog pa'i dri ma sel mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:604: rdo rje rnam 'joms dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:605: na mah tsan+da badz+ra kro d+ha ya hu lu hu lu tish+tha tish+tha ban+d+ha ban d+ha /
NK029(ha)001:606: ha na ha na a mri ta h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:608: gzhon nu'i cha lugs 'chang ba po //
NK029(ha)001:609: ye shes sgron mes rab brgyan cing //'jig rten gsum
NK029(ha)001:610: gyi mun sel ba //'jam dpal dbyangs kyi dbang bskur
NK029(ha)001:611: ro // wa gi shwa ri mum /
NK029(ha)001:613: skyon gyis ma gos sku mdog dkar //
NK029(ha)001:614: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi dbu rgyan can //
NK029(ha)001:615: thugs rje can gyis 'gro la gzigs //
NK029(ha)001:616: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:619: yum chen sangs rgyas sbyan ma dang //
NK029(ha)001:620: bcom ldan yum chen ma ma ki /
NK029(ha)001:621: bcom ldan yum chen gos dkar mo //
NK029(ha)001:622: bcom ldan yum chen dam tshig sgrol //
NK029(ha)001:623: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:625: me long ye shes gzungs 'dzin spongs //
NK029(ha)001:626: zhe sdang dri ma 'joms mdzad cing //
NK029(ha)001:627: rdo rje gtum po ye shes sku //
NK029(ha)001:628: rdo rje gtum po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:629: tshin+d+ha tshin+d+ha ma h+aa ki li ki la ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:631: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes sku //
NK029(ha)001:632: nga rgyal rnam gsum 'joms mdzad cing //
NK029(ha)001:633: tshe ring dbang bskur mchog thob mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:634: rdo rje phur ba'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:635: bin+d+ha bin+d+ha kro d+ha ma h+aa ki li ki la y+aa s+w+aah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:636: a so sor kun rtog ye shes kyi //
NK029(ha)001:637: lta ba ngan pa 'joms mdzad cing //'dod chags rnam dag shes rab rgyas //
NK029(ha)001:638: rdo rje be con dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:640: tsan ti ka li ki la ya s+w+aa h+aa //
NK029(ha)001:642: bya ba rjes grub ye shes kyis //
NK029(ha)001:643: sems can kun la mchog stsol cig /
NK029(ha)001:644: gdon bgegs 'joms phyir shin tu khros //
NK029(ha)001:645: ye shes sku 'joms dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:646: tra sa ya tra sa ya ma h+aa ki li ki la y+aa s+w+aa h+aa //
NK029(ha)001:648: h+aum stengs phyogs khro rgyal h+aum ka ra //
NK029(ha)001:649: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK029(ha)001:650: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:651: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:652: ha ra ha ra badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:653: h+aum shar phyogs khro bo rnam par rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:654: zhal cig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK029(ha)001:655: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:656: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //

NK029(ha)001:660: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK029(ha)001:661: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:662: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //

NK029(ha)001:666: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:667: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //

NK029(ha)001:671: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK029(ha)001:672: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:673: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:676: h+aum nub phyogs khro rgyal rta mgrin ni //
NK029(ha)001:677: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK029(ha)001:678: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:679: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:680: d+ha ra ya d+ha ra ya badz+ra /

NK029(ha)001:684: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK029(ha)001:685: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:686: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:687: d+ha ru na d+ha ru na badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:689: byang phyogs khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK029(ha)001:690: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
