NK029(ha)001:692: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:695: h+aum byang shar khro bo khams gsum rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:696: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK029(ha)001:697: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:698: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:699: b+hin+d+ha b+hin d+ha badz+ra h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:701: h+aum 'og phyogs khro rgyal stobs po che //
NK029(ha)001:702: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ldan //
NK029(ha)001:703: zhabs gnyis nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:704: skal ldan bu la dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:709: phung po khams skye mched la stims //
NK029(ha)001:712: rtogs tshogs rang kha mar 'dzin pa'i dri ma dag nas //
NK029(ha)001:713: phung po khams skye mched thams cad rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK029(ha)001:714: 'khor du lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK029(ha)001:715: par gyur cig / gnyis pa kri ya'i dbang la bkra shis nyi shu rtsa drug ni /
NK029(ha)001:716: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa ri rab kyi
NK029(ha)001:717: zoms la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dus su
NK029(ha)001:718: / dpal phyag na rdo rje la rin po che
NK029(ha)001:719: sna lnga'i ri rab kyi dbang bskur bas mthu stobs
NK029(ha)001:720: phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan te /
NK029(ha)001:721: mi 'gyur ba'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:722: de dang rjes su ma thun par rin po che
NK029(ha)001:723: sna lnga'i ri rab kyi dbang bskur bas mthu stobs
NK029(ha)001:724: phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan te /
NK029(ha)001:725: mi 'gyur ba'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:726: gzi brjid lhun sdug ri rab mchog gi sku //
NK029(ha)001:727: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i dbang rim mchog /
NK029(ha)001:728: thams cad gnas pa'i ri bo chen po la /
NK029(ha)001:729: mthu stobs mi 'gyur sku rnams rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:730: skye bzhi 'gro drug khams gsum yongs kyi srogs //
NK029(ha)001:731: kha dog mdzes ldan rin chen sna tshogs gzhi //
NK029(ha)001:732: phyogs bzhi dbus dang ri rab skur bstan pa //'di
NK029(ha)001:733: ni ri rab dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste nyi
NK029(ha)001:735: sngon bcom ldan 'das mdzad pa bcu gnyis rdzogs pa'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:736: u dum 'bar ba'i me tog dang sbyar nas /
NK029(ha)001:737: dpal phyag na rdo rje la rang bzhin gyi mchod rten dang /
NK029(ha)001:738: sprul pa'i mchod rten la sogs pas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:739: rnam par mi rtog pa'i chos sku thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:740: de dang rjes su mthun par mchod rten chen pos
NK029(ha)001:741: dbang bskur bas chos kyi sku thob pa'i dbang dang
NK029(ha)001:743: dran pa nye bar bzhag pa'i bang rim dang /
NK029(ha)001:744: skye 'gag med pa'i bum pa zlum po dang /
NK029(ha)001:745: chos kyi 'khor lo ma 'dres tog la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:746: rnam par mi rtogs chos kyi sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:747: lta ba'i sa dang mngon par byang chub mtshungs mi mnga' //
NK029(ha)001:748: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor dang cho 'phrul ston la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:749: lha yul gnas gshegs ston pa mya ngan gar 'das
NK029(ha)001:750: pa'i //'di ni stobs bcu byin brlabs mnga' ba'i sa
NK029(ha)001:751: // mchod rten dbang gi bkra shis le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:752: sngon bcom ldan 'das yul gyad kyi nye 'khor na bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:753: dpal phyag na rdo rje la dpag bsam kyi shing gis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:754: dgongs pa'i don yid bzhin du 'grub par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:755: de dang rjes su mthun par dpag bsam gyi shing gis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:756: slob ma rnams dgongs pa'i don yid bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:757: gang la gang 'dod dpag bsam shing lta bu //
NK029(ha)001:758: yon tan yid bzhin du zag med gter dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:759: brten pa'i rgyu dang 'bras bu tshul yin te //
NK029(ha)001:760: dgongs pa'i don rnams yid bzhin 'grub par shog /
NK029(ha)001:761: lha yi re skong dpag bsam ljon shing ltar /
NK029(ha)001:762: 'phags pa'i yon tan brjod kyis mi langs pa'i re ba yid bzhin phun sum tshogs pa'i rdzas /
NK029(ha)001:763: 'di ni dpag bsam shing gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u rtsa gsum pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:764: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgya mtsho chen po'i gling la gshegs pa'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:765: dpal phyag na rdo rje la rgya mtsho chen pos dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:766: chos skye ba med pa zab cing rgya che ba'i
NK029(ha)001:767: don rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to
NK029(ha)001:768: // de dang rjes su mthun par chos skye med
NK029(ha)001:769: zab cing rgya che ba'i don rtogs pa'i dbang dam
NK029(ha)001:771: gting dpag zab cing rgya mtsho yangs pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:772: kun tu snyoms pa'i yon tan chen po te //
NK029(ha)001:773: skye 'gags med pa'i rgya mtsho chen po la //
NK029(ha)001:774: zab cing rgya mtsho chos don rtogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:775: chos nyid rgya mtsho lta bur thugs chud cing //
NK029(ha)001:776: zab cing gting dpag dka' ba'i rgya mtsho la //
NK029(ha)001:777: yid bzhin nor rnams kha dog mdzes pa'i tshul //'di
NK029(ha)001:778: ni rgya mtsho dbang gi bkra shis le'u rtsa bzhi
NK029(ha)001:779: pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gdan drung na bzhugs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:780: dpal phyag na rdo rjes zhing chen po gnas kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:781: bkra shis la byin chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:782: de dang rjes su mthun par slob bu rnams la sa gzhi skye gnas kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)001:783: bkra shis la byin chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:784: rab tu dben pa'i gnas mchog dam pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:785: me tog dri gsung mang po skye ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:786: yon tan ma lus tshangs par kun rdzogs te //
NK029(ha)001:787: dben pa'i bkra shis chen po'i gnas su shog /
NK029(ha)001:788: me tog mdzes ldan yid 'ong brgyan pa'i gnas //
NK029(ha)001:789: bkra shis skad snyan bya skad sna tshogs sgrogs //
NK029(ha)001:790: yon tan lta ba ston pas bslab pa'i gnas //'di
NK029(ha)001:791: ni sa gzhi gnas kyi dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)001:792: rtsa lnga pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das ba ra na si na bzhugs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:793: dpal phyag na rdo rje la bdud rtsi'i chu'i dbang
NK029(ha)001:794: bskur bas skye shi mi mnga' ba'i sku thob bo
NK029(ha)001:795: // de dang rjes su mthun par //
NK029(ha)001:796: bdud rtsi'i bum chu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:797: skye shi med pa sku yi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:798: bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun 'gro ba'i gsos kyi mchog /
NK029(ha)001:799: nyon mongs sdug bsngal nad du che ba sel //
NK029(ha)001:800: ma rig dag pa'i bdud rtsi'i chu mchog te //
NK029(ha)001:801: skye shi med pa dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:802: bum pa'i kha brgyan dpag bsam shing //
NK029(ha)001:803: dbang bskur bum par spyi blug pas //
NK029(ha)001:804: bdud rtsi dam pa 'dir stsol cig /'di ni bdud
NK029(ha)001:805: rtsi dam pa dbang gi chu rgyun gyi dbang gi
NK029(ha)001:806: bkra shis le'u rtsa drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:807: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi zoms la bzhugs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:808: lha'i dbang po rgya byin gyis chos zhu ba'i phyir dar bu khad kyi za ra tsags phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:809: chos sgra chen po byin gyis brlabs pa dang ldan par gyur te /
NK029(ha)001:810: de dang rjes su mthun par rdzas 'dis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:811: chos kyi sgra chen po sgrogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:812: chos kyi rgyal srid chen por mnga' rnyes shog /
NK029(ha)001:813: ma rig mun pa ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:814: brgya byin shes pa ma lus grol ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:815: chos rnams thams cad gong bzhin sgrogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:816: gnyen 'jam reg bde dar gyi za ra tsag /
NK029(ha)001:817: rigs kyi kha dog sna bdun shin tu mdzes /
NK029(ha)001:818: yid 'ong legs par brgyan pa'i bkra shis rdzas //'di
NK029(ha)001:819: ni dar gyi za ra tsags kyi dbang gi bkra
NK029(ha)001:821: sngon bcom ldan 'das la sum cu rtsa gsum gyi
NK029(ha)001:822: gnas su lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis chos kyi
NK029(ha)001:824: rin po che'i khri rkang phul nas zhus pas chos
NK029(ha)001:825: shes pa'i rgyud la go bar sgrogs par gyur to
NK029(ha)001:826: // de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che khri rkang gis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:827: chos go bar sgrogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:828: rin chen gser gyi khri stengs su //
NK029(ha)001:829: chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa yis //'gro ba rnams kyi mi shes grol //
NK029(ha)001:830: chos rnams go ba sgrogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:831: tshad med bzhi ldan 'degs par gser gyi khri //
NK029(ha)001:832: yon tan tshogs rdzogs rin chen sna tshogs spras //
NK029(ha)001:833: yon tan yid bzhin zad med dgos 'dod skongs //'di
NK029(ha)001:834: ni rin chen gser khri'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)001:835: rtsa brgyad pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba la /
NK029(ha)001:836: lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis me tog chun pos
NK029(ha)001:837: sbrees pas sems can 'khor ba las slu zhing 'brid
NK029(ha)001:838: pa'i mchog dam par gyur te /
NK029(ha)001:839: de dang rjes su mthun par me tog gi chun pos dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:840: 'khor ba las slu bar byed pa'i brgyan mdzes pa'i
NK029(ha)001:841: brgyan mchog dam pa dang ldan pa'i dbang mchog dam
NK029(ha)001:842: pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:843: sdug cing mdzes pa'i me tog dam pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:844: kha dog ma 'dres so sor gsal ba'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:845: sems can kun gyi blta bar 'os pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:846: mdzes pa'i brgyan mchog dam pa ldan par shog /
NK029(ha)001:847: me tog chu skyes thang skyes dam pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:848: shing dang nags skyes 'bru mchog dam pa 'dis //
NK029(ha)001:849: rin chen 'phreng ltar mkha' la char 'bebs pa'i //'di
NK029(ha)001:850: ni me tog chun po'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)001:851: rtsa dgu pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab
NK029(ha)001:852: kyi rtse khang bu brtsegs pa'i khang bzang na bzhugs
NK029(ha)001:853: rtsa dgu pa'o // pa'i dus su / sum cu
NK029(ha)001:854: rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu 'od dam pa zhes bya
NK029(ha)001:855: rtsa dgu pa'o // pa'i dus su / bas / rnga yab kyi g.yabs pas /
NK029(ha)001:856: dgyes pa chen po'i gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:857: de dang rjes su mthun par rnga yab kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:858: gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:859: snyan pa'i sgra rnams myur du sgrogs pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:860: nyon mongs sdug sngal dri ma myur du sel //
NK029(ha)001:861: thams cad myur bar go ba'i dbang thob nas //
NK029(ha)001:862: bkra shis gzi mdangs mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK029(ha)001:863: rgyal ba'i sku la nyes pas mi gos kyang //
NK029(ha)001:864: dag cing gsal bar bya phyir rnga yab 'dis //
NK029(ha)001:865: sku yis ljan ljin dri ma phyags dar phyir 'di
NK029(ha)001:866: ni rnga yab dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste sum
NK029(ha)001:867: cu pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs pa la //
NK029(ha)001:868: sum cu rtsa gsum lha'i bu 'od zer kun nas 'byung bas /
NK029(ha)001:869: rdul g.yab kyi rdul g.yabs pas //
NK029(ha)001:870: chos nyid la skyon gyis ma gos so //
NK029(ha)001:871: de dang rjes su mthun par lha'i rdul g.yab kyi rdzas kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:872: chos nyid zab mo'i don la 'jug pa'i dbang dam
NK029(ha)001:873: pa thob par gyur cig nyon mongs rdul rnams ma
NK029(ha)001:875: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa bzhugs pa'i gnas /
NK029(ha)001:876: bag chags skyon gyis dri ma bsal ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:877: chos nyid zab mo'i don la 'jug par shog /
NK029(ha)001:878: rgyal ba'i sku la dri ma mi mnga' yang /
NK029(ha)001:879: log rtogs rdul gyi bag chags bsal ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:880: bkra shis gtsang ma'i ras kyi sku phyis pas /
NK029(ha)001:881: 'di ni rdul g.yab dbang gi bkra shis le'u so gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:882: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal dgon pa na bzhugs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:883: sum cu rtsa gsum lha'i bu zhig gis /
NK029(ha)001:885: sems can 'dzin chags kyis skyon grol /
NK029(ha)001:886: de dang rjes su mthun par sbrang g.yab kyi rdzas 'di'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:887: 'dzin chags kyi skyon las grol ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:888: nyon mongs sems can ma rig bsal ba dang //'bras bu thar pa'i go 'phang thob pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:889: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhabs drung 'khor ba'i phyir //'dzin chags skyon gyi dri ma dag par shog /
NK029(ha)001:890: drang srang chen po bsam gtan gnas pa la /
NK029(ha)001:891: srog chags bdug pa'i gzugs can gsal ba'i phyir //'di
NK029(ha)001:892: ni sbrang g.yab dbang gi bkra shis le'u so gnyis
NK029(ha)001:893: pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:894: 'khor rnam bzhis bla res sgrengs pas /
NK029(ha)001:895: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:896: de dang rjes su mthun par bla res kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:897: nyon mongs pa'i sdug bsngal gyis mi gos par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:898: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor phyir bla res sgrengs //
NK029(ha)001:899: mi'i rgyal po seng ge bzhugs pa'i sa //
NK029(ha)001:900: dbang phyug dam pa'i mnga' bdag chen po ste //
NK029(ha)001:901: nyon mongs rdul gyi dri ma med par shog /
NK029(ha)001:902: dpag bsam ljon shing lo 'dab rgyas //
NK029(ha)001:903: nyi zla mang po'i sprin gseb nas //
NK029(ha)001:904: bkra shis bya mang 'phur zhing lding //'di ni dar
NK029(ha)001:905: zab bla res dbang gi bkra shis le'u so gsum
NK029(ha)001:906: pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das bya rgod phung po'i ri la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe /
NK029(ha)001:907: 'khor rnam bzhis rgyal mtshan chen po gtsugs pas che ba'i yon tan nub pa med par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:908: de dang rjes su mthun par bkra shis pa'i rdzas 'di'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:909: che ba'i yon tan rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo ltar nub pa'i dus med par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:910: dpa' brjid mdzes pas 'jig rten yongs kyi rgyan //
NK029(ha)001:911: lhun grub sku mnyes rdzogs pa'i rgyal mtshan des //
NK029(ha)001:912: nub pa'i dus med zad pa med pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:913: yon tan che bas khyad par kun las 'phags //
NK029(ha)001:914: che ba'i yon tan nub pa med par shog /
NK029(ha)001:915: dpa' brjid mdzes pas 'jig rten yongs kyis rgyan //
NK029(ha)001:916: lhun grub sku mnyes rdzogs pa'i rgyal mtshan des //
NK029(ha)001:917: bdud dang mu stegs mthu dpung 'joms par byed //
NK029(ha)001:918: rgyal ba'i sku dang dbyer med mtshungs shig pa'i //'di
NK029(ha)001:919: ni rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis le'u so bzhi
NK029(ha)001:920: pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das skyed mos tshal du bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK029(ha)001:921: 'khor rnams kyis tsha ba'i gdung ba las /
NK029(ha)001:922: gdug kab pas tsha ba'i gdung ba'i sdug bsngal zhi bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:923: de dang rjes su mthun par gdugs kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:924: tsha ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad zhi ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:925: gdugs kyi tsha ba'i gdung ba kun sel zhing //
NK029(ha)001:926: drang zhing bsil ba'i gdug mchog dam pa ste //'gro ba kun gyi nyon mongs tsha ba'i gsos /
NK029(ha)001:927: rims dang tsha ba'i sdug bsngal las thar bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:928: ji ltar nyon mongs tsha bas gdung ba las //
NK029(ha)001:929: gdugs kyi tsha ba'i sdug bsngal skyobs pa ltar //'khor
NK029(ha)001:930: ba nyes pa'i sdug bsngal skyob pa'i phyir //'di ni
NK029(ha)001:931: gdugs kyi dbang gis brjod nas bkra shis le'u so
NK029(ha)001:932: lnga pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das kyi yangs pa can gyi grong khyer /
NK029(ha)001:933: spre'u rdzing gi 'gram khang bu brtsegs pa'i khang bzang na bzhugs pa de'i tshe /
NK029(ha)001:934: bram ze kham pas bso sngon gyi nyes pa 'das nas /
NK029(ha)001:935: nya pa rnams kyis zin pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)001:936: nya pa rnams kyis 'gyod pa rjes su dran nas //
NK029(ha)001:937: nya rgya 'jug pa che chung phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:938: nya pa lnga brgya sangs rgyas par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:939: de dang rjes su mthun par nya rgya'i rtags dar gyi lda ldis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:940: ngan song du skyes nges pa cig yod na yang /
NK029(ha)001:941: de las thar te sangs rgyas pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:942: dar gyi lnga ldis nyon mongs kun spangs te //
NK029(ha)001:943: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus tshogs rdzogs nas /
NK029(ha)001:944: ma rigs 'khrul pa'i shes pa blo dag cing //
NK029(ha)001:945: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i gnas las thar par shog /'khor ba'i nyes pa dag bya'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:946: sdug bsngal brgya mo bkra shis rdzas //
NK029(ha)001:947: sdug bsngal bag chags sbyang slad du //'di ni lda ldi dbang gi bkra shis le'u so drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:948: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyed mos tshal du gshegs pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:949: khyim bdag lha'i bu mo bzang ldan mas ras a ba se'i sku reg gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:950: sku bstan pa'i mchog dang ldan par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:951: de dang rjes su mthun par bkra shis sku regs rdzas kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:952: lung bstan pa'i mchog dam pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:953: dri ma dag pas sku regs gtsang ma'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:954: khyim bdag dad pas phul ba'i sku reg 'di //
NK029(ha)001:955: sku la bcings shing rab tu gdams pas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:956: mi 'gyur brtan pa'i sku mchog thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:957: thar pa mchog gi legs pa gang gsungs pa //
NK029(ha)001:958: mi dmigs dag pa'i ye shes chen po yis //
NK029(ha)001:959: nyon mongs dri med bde ba'i sku rten pa //'di
NK029(ha)001:960: ni sku reg dbang gi bkra shis le'u so bdun
NK029(ha)001:961: pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kha ba can na bzhugs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:962: gnod sbyin rnams kyis spos rnam pa lnga phul te /
NK029(ha)001:963: tsan dan dang ga bur dang /
NK029(ha)001:967: dbang po lnga tshim zhing bkra shis par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:968: de dang rjes su mthun par spos rnam pa lnga'i dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)001:969: dbang po tshims pa'i don gyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:970: dbang po tshim byed bdug pa'i spos mchog ste //
NK029(ha)001:971: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa mchod pa dang //'gro ba ma lus dbang po kun tshims zhing //
NK029(ha)001:972: dri zhim 'phags pa'i sku dang ldan par shog /
NK029(ha)001:973: dri zhim ngad ldan yon tan phun sum tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:974: mkha' la sprin phung mchod pa stim pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:975: yongs su khyab pa'i bdug pa dam pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:976: 'di ni dbang po dam pa tshims byed dbang gi bkra shis le'u so brgyad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:977: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal chen po bzhugs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:978: klu'i rgyal po rnams kyis snying po rnam pa lnga phul te /
NK029(ha)001:984: snying po mi zad pa'i mdzod du zhugs par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:985: de dang rjes su mthun par snying po rnam pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:986: tshe mi zad pa'i mdzod du bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:987: snying po lnga ni gsos gyis mchog /
NK029(ha)001:988: mi zad pa'i dbyig thob te /
NK029(ha)001:989: legs pa'i yon tan mthar phyin zhing /
NK029(ha)001:990: tshe dang longs spyod 'phel bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:991: snying po lnga ni kun gyis dbyig yin te //'gro kun mi zad gter la spyod pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:992: don gyi snying po yang dag rtogs pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:993: snying po lnga'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u so dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:994: sngon bcom ldan 'das yul gru 'dzin gyi ril bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:995: gnod sbyin gter 'chang la sogs pas rin chen lnga phul ste /
NK029(ha)001:999: dkon nor mi zad pa'i mdzod dang ldan par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:1000: de dang rjes su mthun par rin chen sna lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:1001: skor nor mi zad shes pa'i mdzod dam pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:1002: rin chen gser dang dngul mchog ste //
NK029(ha)001:1003: lcags dang zangs dang g.yu la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:1004: mi zad med pa'i nor mchog ste //
NK029(ha)001:1005: zad pa med pa'i nor mchog dam par shog /
NK029(ha)001:1006: dgos pa'i don 'byin rin chen sna tshogs mchog /
NK029(ha)001:1007: zad pa med pa'i gter dang ldan pa te /
NK029(ha)001:1008: sdug bsngal dbul 'phongs kun las thar /
NK029(ha)001:1009: 'di ni dgos 'dod re ba skongs pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u bzhi bcu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1010: sngon bcom ldan 'das yul am ga ma ga d+ha na bzhugs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:1011: rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis 'bru sna rnam pa lnga phul te /
NK029(ha)001:1017: mu ge'i sdug bsngal zhi ste bkra shis par gyur te /
NK029(ha)001:1018: de dang rjes su mthun par 'bru rnam pa lnga'i dbang bskur bas bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:1019: rin chen 'bru mchog 'gro ba'i gsos lags te /
NK029(ha)001:1020: mu ge'i sdug bsngal kun las thar pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:1021: sbyin pa longs spyod rtag tu 'phel ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:1022: zas sogs mi zad gter dang ldan par shog /
NK029(ha)001:1023: longs spyod tshogs ldan 'byor pa kun tshangs pa //
NK029(ha)001:1024: gang la ci 'dod 'dod pa'i gter 'byung ba //
NK029(ha)001:1025: phun sum tshogs ldan dge ba'i 'bru skyed pa //'di
NK029(ha)001:1026: ni longs spyod ldan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)001:1027: zhe gcig pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das tsan dan nags tshal du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK029(ha)001:1028: gcan gzan stag gis sman bya khri phul bas bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK029(ha)001:1029: slob ma rnams la stag tshal pas dbang bskur bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:1030: bya khri sman mchog stag gis phul ba ste /
NK029(ha)001:1031: bcom ldan thugs rje chen pos byin rlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)001:1032: byol song gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:1033: sman mchog nad rnams kun kyang sel bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:1034: sems can gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:1035: thabs kyi cho 'phrul kun las cir yang ston //
NK029(ha)001:1036: thugs rjes chen pos gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //'di
NK029(ha)001:1037: ni cho 'phrul ston pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)001:1038: zhe gnyis pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das seng lding gi shing gseb du gshegs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:1039: gcan gzan gyis rgyal po seng ges seng khri phyag
NK029(ha)001:1040: tu phul bas sman gyis mchog tu bkra shis par
NK029(ha)001:1041: gyur to // de dang rjes su mthun par seng ldeng gi tsher mas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:1042: sman mchog dam pa'i yon tan kun tu bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:1043: seng khri sman mchog seng ges phul ba ste /
NK029(ha)001:1044: bcom ldan thugs rje chen pos byin brlabs kyis //
NK029(ha)001:1045: byol song gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:1046: sman mchog nad rnams kun tu sel bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:1047: gzi brjid 'gro mkhas 'gying ba'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK029(ha)001:1048: gling bzhir 'gying pas byol song rgyal po ste //
NK029(ha)001:1049: sgra skad mtsher bas sder chags zil gyis non /
NK029(ha)001:1050: 'di ni mu stegs 'dul ba'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u zhe gsum pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1051: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri btang bzung chen por klu'i
NK029(ha)001:1052: rgyal po 'jogs pos 'bri has ti phyag tu phul
NK029(ha)001:1053: bas / sman mchog rnam pa lnga ru bkra shis par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:1054: de dang rjes su mthun par shu dag dkar pos dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:1055: sman mchog dam pa'i bkra shis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:1056: shu dag sman mchog klu yis phul ba ste /
NK029(ha)001:1057: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK029(ha)001:1058: klu yi gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:1059: sman mchog nad rnams kun las sel bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:1060: rig pa'i cha ldan byang chub sems dpa'i ngang //'gro ba'i don bskongs gtsug na rin chen mchog /
NK029(ha)001:1061: thabs kyis don mdzad mthu dpung che ba'i klus //'di
NK029(ha)001:1062: ni nad rnams sel ba'i dbang gi le'u ste bzhi
NK029(ha)001:1064: sngon bcom ldan 'das la rgyal bu rgyal byed gyi
NK029(ha)001:1065: tshal du lha'i dbang po brgya byin ha sa de
NK029(ha)001:1066: ba phul bas / sman dang mchog snying po bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK029(ha)001:1067: ming 'di zhes bya ba la dbang po lag pas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:1068: sman mchog dam pa'i don gyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:1069: dbang po lag pa brgya byin phul ba ste /
NK029(ha)001:1070: bcom ldan 'das thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK029(ha)001:1071: brgya byin lha yi sems kyang go bar mdzad /
NK029(ha)001:1072: sman mchog nad rnams kun las sel bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:1073: sum cu rtsa gsum lha yi gnas mchog nas //
NK029(ha)001:1074: longs spyod ldan pas lha dbang brgya sbyin mchog /
NK029(ha)001:1075: sum cu rtsa gsum lha las rnam rgyal ba'i //'di
NK029(ha)001:1076: ni longs spyod dbang gis le'u zhi bcu zhe lnga
NK029(ha)001:1077: pa'o // sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal chen po'i shing gseb du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK029(ha)001:1078: shing gi lha mo 'od 'chang mas kan d+ha ka ri phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:1079: sman mchog snying po bkra shis par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:1080: de dang rjes su mthun par kan d+ha ka ris dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:1081: snying po lnga'i don du bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:1082: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)001:1083: shing gi lha mo'i sems kyang go bar mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:1084: kan d+ha ka ri lha mos phul ba ste //
NK029(ha)001:1085: sman mchog nad rnams kun las sel bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:1086: nags tshal chen po'i shing gseb nas //
NK029(ha)001:1087: bde ba dgos pa'i re ba skongs //
NK029(ha)001:1088: dad pa chen pos rab phul bas //'di ni legs
NK029(ha)001:1089: par rdzogs pa'i dbang gi bkra shis kyi le'u ste
NK029(ha)001:1091: gnyis pa nus pa'i dbang la lnga ste /
NK029(ha)001:1096: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:1097: dbang de lnga ni cho ga yang gong dang mthun no //
NK029(ha)001:1098: gsum pa gsang ba zab mo'i dbang la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)001:1099: gsang dbang dang shes rab ye shes dbang dang /
NK029(ha)001:1100: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:1101: dbang de gsum gyi cho ga'i don ni /
NK029(ha)001:1102: lam khyer bzhi ldan du bya ste /
NK029(ha)001:1103: theg pa lam khyer la gsang sngags kri ya /
NK029(ha)001:1104: lha lam khyer la rigs gsum mgon po snying po lam khyer ni wa gi shwa ri mum /
NK029(ha)001:1107: dbang lam khyer kri ya'i dbang mchog nyi shu rtsa drug go /
NK029(ha)001:1108: mched rdo rje'i spun rnams lus lha'i khyer so //
NK029(ha)001:1110: sems chos nyid kyi khyer so //
NK029(ha)001:1111: khyer so gsum la gnas par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:1112: lta ba ni don dam dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dang bral ba /
NK029(ha)001:1113: kun rdzob rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'dod /
NK029(ha)001:1114: bsgom pa ni cho ga yan lag bcu gcig bsgoms /
NK029(ha)001:1115: spyod pa ni khrus dang gtsang sbra la spyod /
NK029(ha)001:1116: 'bras bu rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob /
NK029(ha)001:1118: rang gi spyi bor thig le dkar dmar mthing gsum brtsegs sgom /
NK029(ha)001:1119: theg le dkar po las 'od 'phros pas sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs te /
NK029(ha)001:1120: de bzhin gshegs pa la phog pas sku mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:1121: 'od de tshul 'dus nas spyi bor thim pas sku'i
NK029(ha)001:1122: lha 'jam dpal sku mdog ser po zhal gcig phyag
NK029(ha)001:1123: gnyis pa / ral gri dang ut+pa la 'dzin pa gcig bsgoms /
NK029(ha)001:1124: de nas thig le dmar po gsung /
NK029(ha)001:1125: mthing kha thugs khar thim pas 'dres /
NK029(ha)001:1126: de ltar lus ngag yid gsum de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor bsgoms nas /
NK029(ha)001:1132: spyod pa dbang chags pa'i rten yin no //
NK029(ha)001:1133: krii ya'i gag drug sbyar na /
NK029(ha)001:1134: gang du gsungs pa'i gnas ni sngon 'byung ba ran ser gsungs la /
NK029(ha)001:1135: rjes 'jug du pad ma me tog 'ja' tshon gyi gling du dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)001:1136: gang gis bskur ba'i ston pa ni sngon 'byung bcom ldan 'das kyis dbang bskur la /
NK029(ha)001:1137: rjes 'jug du slob dpon chen po shan tis bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:1138: gang la bskur ba'i yul ni /
NK029(ha)001:1139: sngon byung du byang chub sems dpa' phyag na rdo rje la skur /
NK029(ha)001:1140: rjes 'jug du slob dpon zla b+har rtsal la bskur //
NK029(ha)001:1141: gang bskur ba'i dbang ni ri rab dang /
NK029(ha)001:1143: dpag bsam shing la sogs pa dbang nyi shu rtsa drug bskur /
NK029(ha)001:1144: ci'i phyir na sngon 'byung du phyag na rdo rje la /
NK029(ha)001:1145: bcom ldan 'das kyis thugs rjes gzung pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:1146: rjes 'jug du snod bcud 'dzom pa'i dus su bstan /
NK029(ha)001:1148: bla ma sbyangs pa'i yon tan dang ldan pas /
NK029(ha)001:1149: slob bu snod dang ldan zhing las 'phro yod bas /
NK029(ha)001:1150: zab ma'i don la mos pa zhum pa med pa'i brtson 'grus kyi gdams pa zhu nus pa /
NK029(ha)001:1151: sho mas len la 'grim pa yid ches pa'i dam tshig dang ldan pa'i ste /
NK029(ha)001:1152: de'i rjes su 'jug pa'i phyir dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:1154: rin po che ri rab kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:1155: mthu stobs khyad par dang ldan pa'i dgos pa yod cing /
NK029(ha)001:1156: mchod rten gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:1157: chos sku thob pa'i dgos pa yod la /
NK029(ha)001:1158: dpag bsam gyi shing la sogs dbang bskur bas dgos
NK029(ha)001:1159: 'dod yid bzhin du 'grub pa'i dgos pa yod pa
NK029(ha)001:1160: la sogs pa nyi shu rtsa drug po de rang
NK029(ha)001:1161: yin no // gsum pa rjes ni yon dang man+dala phul la /
NK029(ha)001:1163: bkra shis brjod tshogs dang dga' ston rgya chen bya /
NK029(ha)001:1166: rjes chog ni mchod pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:1171: bkra shis brjod la dkyil 'khor bsdu /
NK029(ha)001:1172: de ni kri ya'i dbang gi them skas rdzogs so //
NK029(ha)001:1175: // // dang po phyi dbang gi chu bo las /
NK029(ha)001:1176: yo ga'i dbang gi them skas bzhugs so //
NK029(ha)001:1177: drug pa yo ga'i dbang la gnyis ste /
NK029(ha)001:1178: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:1181: tshad dang ldan pa'i sa stegs la //
NK029(ha)001:1182: dri bzang chu yis chag chag gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1183: byin rlabs ldan pa'i thig skud kyis //
NK029(ha)001:1184: cha chen bcu drug legs par gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1185: de nas cha bran gdab pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:1186: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1187: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1188: gsum pa phyi'i cha gcig gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1189: bzhi pa lha snam phyed du gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1190: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1191: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1192: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1193: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK029(ha)001:1194: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:1195: cha chen gsum nas pho brang bskor //
NK029(ha)001:1196: nang du cha bran nyer bzhi yod //
NK029(ha)001:1197: brgyad kyi dbus kyi ling tshe yin //
NK029(ha)001:1198: drug drug phyogs bzhi'i ling tshe la //
NK029(ha)001:1200: dbus dang phyogs bzhi ling tshe la //
NK029(ha)001:1201: pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa'am //'khor lo rtsibs bzhi re res bskor //
NK029(ha)001:1202: glang gur rdo ra spyi dang mtshungs //
NK029(ha)001:1203: mda' yab zur thig phrad so nas //
NK029(ha)001:1204: pad 'dab rdo ra me ri la //
NK029(ha)001:1205: ci rigs mtshams pas bskor bar bya //
NK029(ha)001:1206: byin brlabs ldan pa'i tshon rtsi yis //
NK029(ha)001:1207: mkhas pas re kha legs par bri //
NK029(ha)001:1209: dbus kyi lte ba dkar po bya //
NK029(ha)001:1210: phyogs bzhi sngo ser dmar dang ljang //'dab ma bzhi ni phyogs kyi mdog /
NK029(ha)001:1211: mu khyud gdung bzhi nag po byed //
NK029(ha)001:1212: mtshams kyi ling tshe mdzes tshon la //
NK029(ha)001:1213: gru chad bzhi ni phyogs las log /
NK029(ha)001:1214: lha snam shar sngo lho phyogs ser /
NK029(ha)001:1215: nub dmar byang ni ljang khu byed //
NK029(ha)001:1216: rtsigs pa la sogs gong dang mthun //
NK029(ha)001:1217: de nas rnam pa dgod pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:1218: dbus su rnam snang yum bzhi dgod //
NK029(ha)001:1219: shar du mi skyod sems dpa' bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:1220: lho ru rin 'byung sems dpa' bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:1221: nub du mtha' yas sems dpa' bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:1222: byang du don grub sems dpa' bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:1223: mtshams kyi ling tshe bzhi pa la //
NK029(ha)001:1224: sgeg mo bzhi'i tsag li dgod //
NK029(ha)001:1225: gru chad bzhi la gdugs sogs bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:1226: blo 'bur bzhi la sgo ba bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:1227: lha snam skal bzang sems dpa' stong //
NK029(ha)001:1228: gsung thugs rten ni gong dang mtshungs //
NK029(ha)001:1229: lhag chad gsal zhing zhal gsos mchod //
NK029(ha)001:1230: mchod yon la sogs phyi mchod dang //
NK029(ha)001:1231: gtor ma bshams pa la sogs dang //
NK029(ha)001:1232: bum sogs bsham pa gong dang mthun //
NK029(ha)001:1233: de ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1234: de nas rab gnas kyi dod ni /
NK029(ha)001:1235: dpon slob rnams gdan la bzhugs shing /
NK029(ha)001:1236: sngon 'gro gtor ma cha bzhi'i cha gcig bsham la /
NK029(ha)001:1237: byin gyis rlabs la bsngo zhing /
NK029(ha)001:1239: mchod pa byin gyis rlabs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:1240: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bsrung 'khor bsgom pa rnams gong du song nas /
NK029(ha)001:1243: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum yam /
NK029(ha)001:1244: h+aum las rdo rje'i mtshan pa'i rlung gi dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)001:1245: de'i steng du h+aum bam h+aum las 'o ma'i tsho
NK029(ha)001:1246: de'i steng du h+aum lam h+aum las gser gyi sa
NK029(ha)001:1247: gzhi de'i steng du h+aum bam h+aum las rgya mtsho
NK029(ha)001:1248: chen po bsam / de'i steng du h+aum sum las
NK029(ha)001:1249: ri'i rgyal po ri rab zur bzhi pa rin po
NK029(ha)001:1250: che sna bzhi'i rang bzhin can /
NK029(ha)001:1251: rin po che sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:1252: 'og gzhi de rnams sna tshogs rdo rje'i rang bzhin du byin gyis rlabs /
NK029(ha)001:1254: b+h+rum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:1256: rta babs dang bcas pa'i rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)001:1257: nor bu rin po che las byas pa /
NK029(ha)001:1258: dbus rnam snang gi gnas su ahsim ahls seng ge'i khri /
NK029(ha)001:1260: h+aum las glang po che'i khri /
NK029(ha)001:1263: nub du hrihmam hrihls rma bya'i khri /
NK029(ha)001:1264: byang du ahgamahahlasa nam mkha' lding gi khri /
NK029(ha)001:1265: lha gzhan thams cad kyi gnas su hrih las pad+ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:1266: gtso bo lnga'i pad+ma'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:1268: dbus kyi seng ge pad zla'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:1269: rnam snang dkar po rdo rje dkyil dkrungs gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:1270: phyag gnyis byang chub mchog gi phyag rgyas de bzhin
NK029(ha)001:1271: gshegs pa'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa bsnams pa zhal
NK029(ha)001:1272: bzhi pa zhal dang po shar du gzigs pa /
NK029(ha)001:1273: rnam snang gi mdun gyi pad 'dab la /
NK029(ha)001:1274: sems ma rdo rje ma'i ngo bo rdo rje rtse lnga pa dmar po /
NK029(ha)001:1275: g.yas su rin po che rdo rje ma'i ngo bo yid bzhin nor bu rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:1276: rtse mo rdo rje lnga pas mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:1277: rgyab du rdo rje chos ma'i ngo bo pad ma dkar dmar 'dab ma bcu drug pa la /
NK029(ha)001:1278: 'dab ma brgyad mthur du gyes shing kha bye ba /
NK029(ha)001:1279: 'dab ma brgyad steng du bltas pas /
NK029(ha)001:1280: kha ma bye ba'i nang na /
NK029(ha)001:1281: dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa chud pa /
NK029(ha)001:1282: g.yon du rdo rje las ma'i ngo bo sna tshogs steng rdo rje bcu gnyis pa lte ba dkar /
NK029(ha)001:1284: g.yas kyi ser g.yon gyi ljang /
NK029(ha)001:1286: shar gyi dbus su glang po che'i khri dang /
NK029(ha)001:1287: pad zla la mi skyod pa sngon po sa gnon
NK029(ha)001:1288: gyi phyag rgyas de ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdo
NK029(ha)001:1289: rje rtse lnga pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:1290: mdun gyi pad 'dab la rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:1291: phyag g.yas pa'i sor mo gsum sbreng ba'i rtse mo
NK029(ha)001:1292: la dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa rang gi
NK029(ha)001:1293: thugs khar stod pa'i tshul gyis 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:1294: g.yon na rdo rje khu tshur gyi dril bu kha nang du bstan pa /
NK029(ha)001:1295: snyan pa'i tshul gyis skur brten pa /
NK029(ha)001:1296: g.yas su rdo rje rgyal po gser mdog phyag gnyis
NK029(ha)001:1297: rdo rje lcags kyus de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK029(ha)001:1299: g.yon du chags pa dmar po rdo rjes mtshan pa'i
NK029(ha)001:1300: mdas ut+pa la dmar po kha bye ba'i made'u can
NK029(ha)001:1301: / rdo rje gzhu rna ba'i bar du bkang nas /
NK029(ha)001:1302: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la 'bigs par mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:1303: rgyab tu legs par ljang khu dang po'i rdo rje
NK029(ha)001:1304: rtse lnga pa gnyis bsnams nas legs so sbyin pa'i
NK029(ha)001:1305: tshul gyis de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mnyes par mdzad
NK029(ha)001:1306: pa / lhor rta'i khri la pad zla la rin 'byung ser po /
NK029(ha)001:1307: mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgya rdo rje rin po che
NK029(ha)001:1308: bsnams pa mdun gyi pad 'dab la rin po che
NK029(ha)001:1309: ser pos phyag g.yas rin po che rang gi dbang
NK029(ha)001:1311: g.yon rdo rje khu tshur gyis dril bu kha nang
NK029(ha)001:1312: du bstan nas snyem pa'i tshul gyis skur rten pa
NK029(ha)001:1313: / g.yas su nyi ma nyi ma'i mdog can phyag
NK029(ha)001:1314: g.yas kyi nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi lte ba na
NK029(ha)001:1315: / / rdo rje rtse lnga pa yod pa'i 'od
NK029(ha)001:1316: kyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad snang bar mdzad
NK029(ha)001:1317: pa thugs khar 'dzin cing g.yon pa gdan la rten
NK029(ha)001:1318: / / pa'o // g.yon du rdo rje rgyal mtshan
NK029(ha)001:1319: sngon po phyag g.yas pa'i dang po rdo rjes mtshan
NK029(ha)001:1320: pa'i yid bzhin nor bu'i tog can gyi rgyal mtshan
NK029(ha)001:1321: dar dang mu tig gi chun 'phyang la sogs pa'i
NK029(ha)001:1322: brgyan gyis spras pa phrag pa'i phyogs su sbreng ba'i
NK029(ha)001:1323: tshul gyis 'dzin pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK029(ha)001:1324: sbyin pa'i pha rol du phyin pa la nges par
NK029(ha)001:1325: sbyor bar mdzad pa g.yon pa gdan la rten pa'o
NK029(ha)001:1326: / / pa'o // // g.yon du gzhad pa dung dang pad+ma'i rtsa ba ltar dkar ba /
NK029(ha)001:1327: g.yas kyi dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa gnyis
NK029(ha)001:1328: kyi dbus su chud pa'i so'i 'phreng ba gnyis kha
NK029(ha)001:1329: 'gram g.yas su 'dzin pas de pa thams cad 'dzun
NK029(ha)001:1330: pa smad du byung ba la /
NK029(ha)001:1331: nges par sbyor ba g.yon pa gdan la rten pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1332: nub du rma bya'i khri dang pad zla la 'od
NK029(ha)001:1333: dpag med dmar po mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgyas rdo
NK029(ha)001:1334: rje pad+ma la chos dkar dmar phyag g.yon snyem pa
NK029(ha)001:1335: dang bcas pas rdo rje pad+ma'i gdong bu skur rten
NK029(ha)001:1336: cing g.yas pa'i rdo rje khu tshur gyis theb 'dzug
NK029(ha)001:1337: gyis snying khar rdo rje pad+ma'i 'dab ma kha 'byed
NK029(ha)001:1338: pa'o // g.yas su rnon po sngon po phyag g.yon
NK029(ha)001:1339: pa'i rdo rje khu tshur gyis thugs kar shes rab
NK029(ha)001:1340: kyi pha rol du phyin pa'i po ti bsnams shing
NK029(ha)001:1341: pa'o // / g.yas pa rdo rje ral gri de
NK029(ha)001:1342: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la 'debs pa'i tshul du
NK029(ha)001:1344: rgyu gser gyi mdog can phyag g.yas pa'i gung mo'i rtse mo na /
NK029(ha)001:1345: dang po'i rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i dbyibs can gyis
NK029(ha)001:1346: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa bskor ba'i tshul du 'dzin
NK029(ha)001:1347: zhing g.yon pa gdan la rten pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1348: rgyab du smra ba zangs gyi mdog can phyag g.yas
NK029(ha)001:1349: pa dang po'i rdo rjes mtshan pa'i lce bsnam nas
NK029(ha)001:1350: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la smra bar mdzad
NK029(ha)001:1351: cing / g.yon pa gdan la brten pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1353: mkha' lding gi khri dang pad zla la don 'grub
NK029(ha)001:1354: ljang khu skyabs sbyin gyis phyag rgyas sna tshogs rdo
NK029(ha)001:1355: rje bsnams pa / mdun gyi pad 'dab la /
NK029(ha)001:1356: las zhal dang byin pa gnyis nas zhabs kyi bar dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:1357: zhal gyi 'og nas skyed pa'i bar dmar skya /
NK029(ha)001:1358: skyed pa'i bar dang phyag gnyis sngo skya /
NK029(ha)001:1361: phyag g.yas pa sna tshogs rdo rje rtse bcu gnyis pa thugs khar gtod pa'i tshul gyis 'dzin cing /
NK029(ha)001:1362: g.yon snyems pa dang bcas pas sna tshogs rdo rjes
NK029(ha)001:1363: yu ba byas pa'i dril bu kha nang du bstan
NK029(ha)001:1364: bskur rten pa'o // g.yas su bsrung ba gser gyi
NK029(ha)001:1365: mdog can phyag gnyis kyi mtha' gnyis su rdo rje
NK029(ha)001:1366: rtse lnga pas mtshan pa'i rdo rje go cha bsnams
NK029(ha)001:1367: nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la go dkon
NK029(ha)001:1369: g.yon du gnod sbyin nag po lto ba yangs pa
NK029(ha)001:1370: zhal mche ba gtsigs pa khro bo rdo rje rtse
NK029(ha)001:1371: lnga pas lte bar mtshan pa'i mche ba zhal gyi
NK029(ha)001:1372: grwa gnyis su 'dzin pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK029(ha)001:1373: cad la sdig pa'i tshul du mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1374: rgyab du khu tshur ser po dam tshig gi rdo
NK029(ha)001:1375: rje khu tshur gyis dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga
NK029(ha)001:1376: pa'i 'tshir ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:1377: shar lho'i ling tsher sgeg mo ma dkar mo phyag
NK029(ha)001:1378: gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse lnga pa gnyis skems pa'i
NK029(ha)001:1379: tshul gyis 'dzin cing g.yon du cung zad 'dud pa'o
NK029(ha)001:1380: // lho nub kyi ling tsher 'phreng ba ser mo
NK029(ha)001:1381: rdo rje rin po che'i 'phreng ba'i de bzhin gshegs
NK029(ha)001:1382: pa thams cad la dbang bskur bar mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1383: nub byang gi ling tsher glu ma dkar dmar phyag
NK029(ha)001:1384: gnyis rdo rjes mtshan pa'i pi wang brdung ba la
NK029(ha)001:1385: brtson pa'o // byang shar gyi ling tsher /
NK029(ha)001:1386: gar ma sna tshogs mdog phyag gnyis rdo rje rtse gsum pa gnyis bsnams nas gar stabs byed pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1388: bdug pa ma dkar mo phyag gnyis rdo rje rtse
NK029(ha)001:1389: lnga pas mtshan pa'i spos snams pas de bzhin gshegs
NK029(ha)001:1390: pa thams cad tshim par mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1391: lho nub kyi grar me tog ma ser mo phyag
NK029(ha)001:1392: g.yon rdo rje me tog gi snod 'dzin cing g.yas
NK029(ha)001:1393: me tog gis char 'bebs par mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1394: nub byang gi grar mar me ma dkar dmar phyag
NK029(ha)001:1395: gnyis rdo rje mar me'i sdong bu bsnams te de
NK029(ha)001:1396: bzhin gshegs pa rnams snang ba'i tshogs kyis tshim par
NK029(ha)001:1397: mdzad pa'o // byang shar gyi grar /
NK029(ha)001:1398: byug pa ma sna tshogs mdog phyag g.yon rdo rjes
NK029(ha)001:1399: mtshan pa'i dri'i dung phor bsnams ste phyag g.yas kyi
NK029(ha)001:1400: dri'i sprin gyis de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mchod par
NK029(ha)001:1401: mdzad pa'o // shar gyi blo 'bur la /
NK029(ha)001:1402: lcags kyu dkar po phyag gnyis kyis rdo rje'i mtshan
NK029(ha)001:1403: pa'i lcags kyu bsnams nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK029(ha)001:1405: lhor zhags pa ser po phyag gnyis rdo rje zhags
NK029(ha)001:1406: pas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams 'jug par mdzad pa'o
NK029(ha)001:1407: // nub la lcags sgrogs dkar dmar phyag gnyis rdo
NK029(ha)001:1408: rje lcags sgrogs de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'ching
NK029(ha)001:1409: // bar mdzad pa'o // byang rdo rje 'bebs pa
NK029(ha)001:1410: sna tshogs mdog phyag g.yas rdo rje dril bu bsnams
NK029(ha)001:1411: nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'bebs par mdzad
NK029(ha)001:1412: pa g.yon gdan la rten pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:1413: gong gi rigs sngar lnga po la /
NK029(ha)001:1414: nyi ma'i 'od kyi rgyab yol mnga' ba /
NK029(ha)001:1415: lha rdzas kyi dar la'i stod g.yogs smad g.yogs mnabs pa /
NK029(ha)001:1416: rin po che'i cod pan dang dar dpyangs kyi dbang bskur ba dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:1417: rdo rje sems dpa' man chad rab dgyes pas /
NK029(ha)001:1418: spyan gdangs pa sgeg pa'i nyams can 'dzum bag dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:1419: sangs rgyas lnga'i cod pan dang dar dpyangs kyi dbang bskur mdang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:1420: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:1421: dar dkar pa'i stod g.yogs dang smad g.yogs bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:1422: pad zla'i gdan la sems dpa'i dkyil mo dkrungs gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:1423: zla ba'i rgyab yol can no //
NK029(ha)001:1424: de nas lha rnams la bskal bzang stong du bzhis ma tshang ba /
NK029(ha)001:1425: phyogs rer nyis brgya bzhi bcu rtsa dgu dgu sems
NK029(ha)001:1426: dpa' dang po bzhi dang 'dra pa la khyad par
NK029(ha)001:1427: rdo rje rin po che cod pan gyi dbang bskur
NK029(ha)001:1433: mun pa nges par 'joms pa'i blo gros /
NK029(ha)001:1440: bzang skyong grwa ba can gyi 'od /
NK029(ha)001:1441: byang du rdo rje snying po /
NK029(ha)001:1444: kun tu bzang po rnams sems dpa' dang po bzhi dang 'dra ba la /
NK029(ha)001:1445: khyad par rdo rje rin po che cod pan gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:1446: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi gong bzhin sgom /
NK029(ha)001:1447: lha tshogs de rnams kyi spyi bor +amo /
NK029(ha)001:1450: rang bzhin gnas nas ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab cing spyan drangs /
NK029(ha)001:1451: de nas spyan drangs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:1453: ma lus sems can kun gyi dbang gyur ba /
NK029(ha)001:1454: bdud sde dpung bcas ma lus 'joms mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:1455: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:1456: bcom ldan rnam snang 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:1457: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha ho sa ma ya stam /
NK029(ha)001:1458: bcom ldan 'di ni byon pa legs /
NK029(ha)001:1459: bdag ni bsod nams skal par ldan /
NK029(ha)001:1460: bdag gi mchod yon bzhes nas kyang /
NK029(ha)001:1461: thugs rjes thugs dbag mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:1463: badz+ra ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:1464: ji ltar ltams pa tsam gyis kyang /
NK029(ha)001:1465: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ba /
NK029(ha)001:1466: lha'i chu ni dag pa yi /
NK029(ha)001:1467: de bzhin bdag gis sku khrus gsol //
NK029(ha)001:1468: mo badz+ra sarba de ba sa ta ya tsa ha ti ya mi te ta ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:1469: bdag dang 'gro la thugs rtse'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:1470: nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul mthu yis ni /
NK029(ha)001:1471: ji srid mchod pa bdag 'bul na /
NK029(ha)001:1472: ji srid bcom ldan bzhugs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:1473: pad+ma ka ma la ye h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:1474: me tog dam pa 'di dag dang /
NK029(ha)001:1475: de bzhin chu skyes thang skyes dang /
NK029(ha)001:1476: mchog du dad pas bdag 'bul na /
NK029(ha)001:1477: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:1478: +amo na ma sarba ta tha ga ta pus pa
NK029(ha)001:1479: pu tsa me ga sa mun tra pa ra na
NK029(ha)001:1481: lhan cig skyes dang sbyar bas mchog /
NK029(ha)001:1482: bdug spos dam pa 'di dag ni /
NK029(ha)001:1483: mchog du dad pas bdag 'bul na /
NK029(ha)001:1484: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:1486: mun pa'i tshogs rnams 'dzoms mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:1487: phyogs kun gsal byed mar me 'di //
NK029(ha)001:1488: kun mkhyen dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:1489: mchog du dad pas bdag 'bul na //
NK029(ha)001:1490: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:1492: yang dag par ni sbyar ba'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:1493: dri mchog dam pa 'di dag ni //
NK029(ha)001:1494: mchog du dad pas bdag 'bul na //
NK029(ha)001:1495: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:1497: kha dog dri dang ro ldan pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:1498: bza' dang bca' bar yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:1499: thams cad sbyar ba'i bshos 'di dag /
NK029(ha)001:1500: mchog du dad pas bdag 'bul na //
NK029(ha)001:1501: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:1503: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //'khor lo rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:1504: srid pa'i 'khor lo rgyun chad nas //
NK029(ha)001:1505: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:1506: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa rat+na tsakra pu tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:1507: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK029(ha)001:1508: nor bu rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:1509: bkres shing 'phongs pa rgyun chad nas //'byor pa phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:1510: ma h+aa rat+na pu tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:1511: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK029(ha)001:1512: btsun mo rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:1513: shes rab dbyings kyi don rtogs nas //
NK029(ha)001:1514: shes rab thabs dang 'brel bar shog ba ti rat+na /
NK029(ha)001:1515: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK029(ha)001:1516: blon po rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:1517: phyi nang gsang gsum theg par ldan //
NK029(ha)001:1518: bsam yas bstan pa rab 'dzin cing //
NK029(ha)001:1519: yon tan thams cad ldan par shog /
NK029(ha)001:1520: ma h+aa rat+na pu tsa h'u /
NK029(ha)001:1521: bde bar gshegs par thams cad la //
NK029(ha)001:1522: glang po rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:1523: lta ba ngan pa rab spangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:1524: bla med theg pa rab zhon nas //
NK029(ha)001:1525: thams cad mkhyen pa'i grong khyer du //
NK029(ha)001:1526: da ni rab tu 'jug par shog /
NK029(ha)001:1528: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK029(ha)001:1529: rta mchog rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:1530: srid pa'i sreg lam yongs grol ste //
NK029(ha)001:1531: rdzu 'phrul mchog gi shugs thob nas //
NK029(ha)001:1532: sangs rgyas zhing du 'gro gyur shog /
NK029(ha)001:1533: ma h+aa rat+na na ru rang sha /
NK029(ha)001:1534: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK029(ha)001:1535: dmag dpon rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:1536: phas kyi rgol ba tshar bcad nas //
NK029(ha)001:1537: nyon mongs dgra las rgyal gyur nas //
NK029(ha)001:1538: snyems bral mchog ni thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:1540: kha dog dbyibs legs yid 'ong rgyan 'phreng ldan //
NK029(ha)001:1541: phyogs dus kun na gzugs mchog ci mchis pa //
NK029(ha)001:1542: mos blos mchod gnas rnams la bdag 'bul na //
NK029(ha)001:1543: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:1544: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ru pa bu tsa me
NK029(ha)001:1545: ga sa mu tra sma ra sa ma ye h+aum
NK029(ha)001:1546: / phyogs dus kun nas zin dang ma zin pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:1547: yon tan tshig brjod sgra snyan yid 'ong ldan //
NK029(ha)001:1548: mos blos mchod gnas rnams la bdag 'bul na //
NK029(ha)001:1549: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:1551: phyogs dus kun na tsan dan sbrul snying dang //
NK029(ha)001:1552: a kar la sogs tshim byed dbang po rnams //
NK029(ha)001:1553: mos blos mchod gnas rnams la bdag 'bul na //
NK029(ha)001:1554: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:1555: gan+d+ha pu tsa me ga sa /
NK029(ha)001:1556: phyogs dus kun na ro dang bcud ldan pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:1557: lus sems brtan par byed pa'i ro mchog kyang //
NK029(ha)001:1558: mos blos mchod gnas rnams la bdag 'bul na //
NK029(ha)001:1559: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:1561: phyogs dus kun na 'jam mnyen sprin chags pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:1562: reg bya'i khyad par lus sems tshim byed pa //
NK029(ha)001:1563: mos blos mchod gnas rnams la bdag 'bul na //
NK029(ha)001:1564: ci bde bar ni bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:1565: pa ri sha badz+ra pu dza /
NK029(ha)001:1566: badz+ra sat+wa su sam tra ha /
NK029(ha)001:1570: badz+ra karma ka rod b+ha wa /
NK029(ha)001:1580: h+aum snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK029(ha)001:1581: chos dbyings rnam dag rdo rje'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:1582: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:1583: phyag 'tshal rnam par snang mdzad la'o //
NK029(ha)001:1584: me long ye shes byin rlabs las /
NK029(ha)001:1585: sems ma rdo rje'i phyag rgya ste //
NK029(ha)001:1586: rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga ma //
NK029(ha)001:1587: mchod cing gus pas phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK029(ha)001:1588: mnyam nyid ye shes byin rlabs las /
NK029(ha)001:1589: rat+na'i sems ma'i phyag rgya ste //
NK029(ha)001:1590: rat+na ser po zur brgyad pa //
NK029(ha)001:1591: bstod cing gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:1592: kun rtog ye shes ngang nyid las //
NK029(ha)001:1593: chos kyi sems ma'i phyag rgya ste //
NK029(ha)001:1594: pad+ma dkar dmar bcu drug la //
NK029(ha)001:1595: bstod cing gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:1596: bya grub ye shes byin brlabs las //
NK029(ha)001:1597: las kyi sems ma'i phyag rgya ste //
NK029(ha)001:1598: rdo rje rgya gram ljang khu la //
NK029(ha)001:1599: bstod cing gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:1600: gzung 'dzin rdo rje brtan pa'i sa /
NK029(ha)001:1601: me long ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:1602: rdo rje sa non phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:1603: phyag 'tshal rdo rje mi skyod la'o //
NK029(ha)001:1604: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK029(ha)001:1605: rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa kun //
NK029(ha)001:1606: rdo rje dang po kun tu bzang //
NK029(ha)001:1607: phyag 'tshal phyag na rdo rje la //
NK029(ha)001:1608: rdo rje rgyal po sangs rgyas mchog /
NK029(ha)001:1609: rdo rje lcags kyu de bzhin gshegs //
NK029(ha)001:1610: don yod rgyal po de bzhin mchog /
NK029(ha)001:1612: rdo rje chags pa bde chen po //
NK029(ha)001:1613: rdo rje mda' ni dbang byed pa //
NK029(ha)001:1614: bdud kyi 'dod pa rdo rje cha //
NK029(ha)001:1615: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gzhu khyod la //
NK029(ha)001:1616: rdo rje legs pa sems dpa' mchog /
NK029(ha)001:1617: rdo rje mgu pa dga' ba che //
NK029(ha)001:1618: rab skyes rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK029(ha)001:1619: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dgyes khyod la //
NK029(ha)001:1621: mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:1622: rdo rje mchod sbyin phyag rgya mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:1624: rdo rje rin chen rdo rje'i don //
NK029(ha)001:1625: rdo rje nam mkha' nor bu ni //
NK029(ha)001:1626: nam mkha'i snying po rdo rje phyug /

NK029(ha)001:1726: shugs kyi kun skyod don yod thogs //
NK029(ha)001:1727: tshogs gnyis yong bsags blo mi bzang //
NK029(ha)001:1728: stobs bcu yongs gnon spobs pa rtsegs //

NK029(ha)001:1775: bi shud+he ma h+aa ya na pa ri wa re

NK029(ha)001:2015: phyag mtshan phyag na me tog bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:2016: push+pe ma yi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:2017: badz+ra push+pe a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:2018: nub byang lha mo a lo ke //
NK029(ha)001:2020: phyag mtshan phyag na mar me bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:2021: a lo ke'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:2022: badz+ra a lo ke a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:2023: byang shar lha mo gan+d+he ma //
NK029(ha)001:2025: phyag ma tshan phyag na dri chab bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:2026: gan+he ma yi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:2027: badz+ra g+han+te a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:2028: shar phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK029(ha)001:2030: phyag mtshan phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:2031: shar gyi sgo ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:2032: badz+ra ang+gu sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:2033: lho phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK029(ha)001:2035: phyag mtshan phyag na zhags pa bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:2036: lho yi sgo ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:2037: badz+ra pa sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:2038: nub phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni /
NK029(ha)001:2040: phyag mtshan phyag na lcags sgrogs bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:2041: nub kyi sgo ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:2044: byang phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK029(ha)001:2046: phyag mtshan phyag na dril bu bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:2047: byang gi sgo ma'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:2051: stim gnas ni phung po khams dang skye mched la stim /
NK029(ha)001:2052: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK029(ha)001:2053: phung khams skye mched dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i dri ma dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:2054: phung po khams skye mched rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK029(ha)001:2055: lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK029(ha)001:2056: cig / yo ga'i dbang gi bkra shis drug cu rtsa gnyis las /
NK029(ha)001:2057: dang po thugs rje gzung kyi dbang bcu gcig /
NK029(ha)001:2058: dang po sku gzugs phyag rgya'i dbang ni //
NK029(ha)001:2059: sngon ri rab ri'i rtse mor rin po che dang /
NK029(ha)001:2061: dpal kun rig rnam pa snang mdzad kyi 'khor gyis
NK029(ha)001:2062: byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad grub pa la
NK029(ha)001:2063: sogs ba la / phyag rgya chen po lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2064: rigs lnga ye shes lnga ru mthar phyin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2065: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya chen po
NK029(ha)001:2066: lnga'i dbang bskur bas ye shes lnga mthar phyin nas
NK029(ha)001:2067: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2068: byang chub mchog dang sa gnon ni //
NK029(ha)001:2069: mchod sbyin mnyam pa'i phyag rgyar ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2070: skyabs kyi phyag rgya la sogs lngas //
NK029(ha)001:2071: mi 'da' phyag rgya'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2072: rgyal po phyag rgya mchog gi rgyas //
NK029(ha)001:2073: phyag rgya'i dbang mchog mi 'da' ba //
NK029(ha)001:2074: ye shes lnga dang rigs lnga'i dbang //
NK029(ha)001:2075: dbang gnyis rdzogs pa'i bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu zhe bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2076: gnyis pa gsung gi gzungs yig 'bru'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2077: sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor
NK029(ha)001:2078: rnams la snying po sngags kyis dbang bskur ba ni
NK029(ha)001:2079: / rtog pa'i ye shes phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2080: de dang rjes su mthun par de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK029(ha)001:2081: thugs ye shes kyi byin gyis rlabs pa'i snying po
NK029(ha)001:2083: rtog pa ye shes phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2084: thugs kyi sa bon 'bru mchog ste //
NK029(ha)001:2085: sngags kyi byin rlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK029(ha)001:2086: ye shes thugs kyi sa bon mchog /'bras bu sngags kyi bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2087: snying po rigs lnga sangs rgyas gsung gi mchog /
NK029(ha)001:2088: gsung mchog sngags kyi phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK029(ha)001:2089: byin rlabs chen po gzhan na med pa yis //'di
NK029(ha)001:2090: ni dbang rnams thob pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)001:2095: a mi ta ba h+r+aih a mo g+ha sad+hi a /
NK029(ha)001:2096: gsum pa thugs kyi gzungs gser thur ni /
NK029(ha)001:2097: sngon ri rab ri'i rtse mor rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)001:2098: kyi 'khor rnams la gser gyi thur mas dbang bskur
NK029(ha)001:2099: bas / ma rig pa'i ling thog byang nas shes rab kyi mig gsal bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2100: de dang rjes su mthun par gser gyi thur mas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2101: ma rig pa'i ling thog byang nas shes rab kyi mig gsal bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2102: gser gyi thur ma thogs byas ste //
NK029(ha)001:2103: mig mkhan rgyal pos dbang bskur bzhin //
NK029(ha)001:2104: bu khyod ma rig mi shes pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:2105: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyi bsal //
NK029(ha)001:2107: rin chen gser gyi thur ma yis //'bar ba'i ye shes gsal phye nas //
NK029(ha)001:2108: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK029(ha)001:2109: shes rab mchog gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste bzhi bcu zhe dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2110: bzhi pa me long gi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2111: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la me long gis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2112: chos thams cad gzugs rnyan rten 'brel sgyu ma tsam du mthong par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2113: chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin med par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2114: de dang rjes su mthun par me long gi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2115: chos thams cad gzugs rnyan lta bu ste //
NK029(ha)001:2116: rten 'brel mthu las snang ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:2117: brjod med rang bzhin dag pa'i don //
NK029(ha)001:2118: chos nyid sgyu ma lta bur gsal zhing ston par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2119: snang gsal dri ma sel ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:2120: mi mngon dbang po gsal ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:2121: ye shes gsal ba'i me long gis //'di ni me
NK029(ha)001:2122: long gsal gyi bkra shis le'u ste lnga bcu pa'o
NK029(ha)001:2124: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la 'khor los dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2125: 'gro ba'i don la thag thog med par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2126: de dang rjes su mthun par 'khor los dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2127: 'khor ba'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan nas /
NK029(ha)001:2128: khams gsum gyi gnas thams cad du 'gro ba'i don
NK029(ha)001:2129: la thag thog med par 'gro bar gyur cig /'og
NK029(ha)001:2131: brjod pa med don 'bru bkod nas //
NK029(ha)001:2132: gzhan gyi don la phan pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:2133: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:2134: nyon mongs me'i gzhom pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:2135: legs pa'i yon tan rdzogs pa dang //'bras bu kun tu 'phags pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:2136: des ni dbang rnams bkra shis le'u ste nga gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2138: sngon bcom ldan 'das la lha'i rgyal po dbang po
NK029(ha)001:2139: brgya byin gyis dung gtsug g.yas su 'khyil ba phul
NK029(ha)001:2140: bas rdo rje spo la gshegs ste chos sgra chen
NK029(ha)001:2141: pos gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu dang ldan pa'i
NK029(ha)001:2142: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i rdzas 'dis /
NK029(ha)001:2143: ngas slob ma rnams la sbyin pas /
NK029(ha)001:2144: tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs shing /
NK029(ha)001:2145: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i don gyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2146: dung gi chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i tshul //
NK029(ha)001:2147: yon tan rgya mtsho bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK029(ha)001:2148: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:2149: bkra shis des ni tshig la longs spyod shog /
NK029(ha)001:2150: chos sgra chen po phyogs bcur grags pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:2151: rgyal ba'i gsung mchog dung gi sgra bus ste //
NK029(ha)001:2152: ma lus rgyal ba kun gyi rgyud 'grol ba //'di
NK029(ha)001:2153: ni 'phags pa'i gsung gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)001:2155: bdun pa me tog 'phreng ba'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2156: sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:2157: me tog gi 'phreng bas dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)001:2158: tshul khrims kyi 'phreng ba yongs su rdzogs par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2159: de dang rjes su mthun par /
NK029(ha)001:2160: me tog gi 'phreng bas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2161: tshul khrims gyi 'phreng bas yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK029(ha)001:2162: ngan song las ldog pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2163: sdug cing mdzes pa'i me tog brgyan //
NK029(ha)001:2164: dgos pa'i don rnams myur bar 'byin //
NK029(ha)001:2165: thams cad kun gyi yid du 'ong //'byor ba'i longs spyod brgyan du shog /
NK029(ha)001:2166: kha dog dbyibs legs rin chen me tog 'di //
NK029(ha)001:2167: nam mkha' gang zhing sa gzhi khebs pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2168: mchod pa'i phrin phung dus su char 'bab pa'i //'di
NK029(ha)001:2169: ni me tog mdzes pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u
NK029(ha)001:2171: brgyad pa 'phrin las rdo rje'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2172: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:2173: phyag rgya bzhi la rdo rje res dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2174: thugs rdo rje rigs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2175: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya bzhi la rdo rje res dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2176: thugs ye shes rdo rje lta bu'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2177: sku yi phyag rgya rtags brtan pa //
NK029(ha)001:2178: ye shes rdo rje lta bu de //
NK029(ha)001:2179: rdo rje thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK029(ha)001:2180: me tog lta bu'i ye shes thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2181: rdo rje rigs mchog rdo rje sems dpa' che //
NK029(ha)001:2182: dkar la dag pa shar phyogs sangs rgyas zhing //
NK029(ha)001:2183: bde ba chen po'i brgyan du bstan pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2184: thugs kyi bkris le'u ste lnga bcu nga bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2186: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)001:2187: 'khor rnams la phyag rgya chen po bzhi'i rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2188: yon tan rin po che'i rigs dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2189: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2190: yon tan rin po che lta bu dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2191: sku yi phyag rgya rtags rtan nas //'gro ba kun gyi re ba bskongs //
NK029(ha)001:2192: yon tan rin chen rang bzhin ste //
NK029(ha)001:2193: mnyam nyid ye shes thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2194: rin chen rigs mchog sems dpa' ste //
NK029(ha)001:2195: sngo la dag pas lho phyogs sangs rgyas zhing //
NK029(ha)001:2196: bde ba chen po'i bstan pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:2197: yon tan bkra shis le'u ste nga lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2199: sngon ri rab rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis //'khor rnams la pad+ma'i dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)001:2200: pad+ma gsung gi rigs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2201: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya chen po bzhi la pad+ma'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2202: 'gro ba'i don mdzad pas nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma
NK029(ha)001:2203: gos pa'i gsung dam pa lta bu dang ldan pa'i
NK029(ha)001:2204: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2205: sku yi phyag rgya rtags bstan pa //
NK029(ha)001:2206: pad+ma dbang gi rang bzhin ste /
NK029(ha)001:2207: gsung gi rang bzhin 'byung ba'i mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:2208: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2209: pad+ma rigs mchog chos kyi sems dpa' ste //
NK029(ha)001:2210: dmar la dag pa nub phyogs bde chen zhing //
NK029(ha)001:2211: bde ba chen po'i brgyan du bstan pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2212: gsung gi bkra shis ste nga drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2213: bcu gcig pa rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2214: sngon ri rab ri yi rtse mor dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:2215: phyag rgya bzhi las rdo rje brgya gram gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2216: thugs rdo rje rigs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur te /
NK029(ha)001:2217: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag rgya chen po bzhi las rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2218: thugs ye shes rdo rje lta bu dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2219: sku yi phyag rgya rtags bstan pa //
NK029(ha)001:2220: ye shes rdo rje lta bu ste //
NK029(ha)001:2221: rdo rje thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK029(ha)001:2222: me long ye shes thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2223: rdo rje rigs mchog rdo rje sems dpa' ste //
NK029(ha)001:2224: dkar la dag pas shar phyogs sangs rgyas zhing //
NK029(ha)001:2225: bde ba chen po'i brgyan du bstan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2226: thugs dbang bkra shis le'u nga bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2227: lnga pa khyad par gdan gyi dbang la gsum las /
NK029(ha)001:2228: dang po zil gnon seng ge'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2229: sngon ri rab ri yi rtser dpa' rnam par snang
NK029(ha)001:2230: mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la seng ge'i dbang bskur bas
NK029(ha)001:2231: / log pa'i phyogs zil gyis non pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2232: de dang rjes su mthun par seng ge'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2233: gsung rabs rgya mtsho'i sgras log pa'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis mnan nas /
NK029(ha)001:2234: skad cig la stong spyi phud kyi sems can mngon
NK029(ha)001:2235: par rdzogs par sangs rgya bar byed pa'i bcom ldan
NK029(ha)001:2236: 'das dpal kun tu bzang po zhes bya bar gyur
NK029(ha)001:2237: cig / gdug bzang sems can kun gyi gtso bo ste //
NK029(ha)001:2238: zil gnon sgra 'byin sder chags skrag par byed //
NK029(ha)001:2239: phyogs rnams kun bskyed seng ge dpal dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2240: zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2241: seng ge nga ro sgra chen thog med pas //'jigs med 'joms pa'i sgra rnams bsgrag nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:2242: bdud kyi dpung rnams zil gyis gnon mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:2243: mthu dpung che ba'i bkra shis nga brgyad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2244: gnyis pa mun sel nyi ma'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2245: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la nyi ma'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2246: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2247: de dang rjes su mthun par nyi ma'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2248: skye 'gro ma lus pa'i sems kyi rgyud la ye
NK029(ha)001:2249: shes kyi 'od zer chen po'i dus mtha' med par
NK029(ha)001:2250: 'char ba'i skal ba dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2251: nyi ma mun sel shes rab sgron //
NK029(ha)001:2252: kun las gsal bas rin po che //
NK029(ha)001:2253: thams cad kun gyi dpal du shar //
NK029(ha)001:2254: ma rig sel ba'i sgron mar shog /
NK029(ha)001:2255: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcur khyab par dro //
NK029(ha)001:2256: thugs rje che bas mun sel byed //'od gsal dra bas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pas //
NK029(ha)001:2257: shes rab bkra shis le'u nga dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2258: gsum pa zla ba'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2259: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la zla bas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2260: mun pa sel zhing tsha ba'i sdug bsngal sel ba'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2261: de dang rjes su mthun par zla ba lag tu
NK029(ha)001:2262: byin pas stong khams thams cad kyi mun pa dus
NK029(ha)001:2263: cig tu byang nas kun tu gsal bar byed par
NK029(ha)001:2264: gyur cig / thams cad kun gsal chu shel lta bu ste //
NK029(ha)001:2265: dgongs pa'i don 'byin dkar la dag pa'i tshul //
NK029(ha)001:2266: tshad med thabs kyi zla ba rin po che //
NK029(ha)001:2267: ma rig mun sel dbang mchog bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2268: dkar la dag pa zla ba dri med pas //
NK029(ha)001:2269: thabs kyi mtshan nyid skyon gyis ma gos ste //
NK029(ha)001:2270: yongs su dag pas mun sel bsil ba'i sman //
NK029(ha)001:2271: thabs dbang bkra shis le'u drug cu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2272: bzhi pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ni //
NK029(ha)001:2273: sngon dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis bdud rtsi bum pa'i 'khor rnams la dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2274: rnam par rtog pa sel bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2275: de dang rjes su mthun par de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK029(ha)001:2276: thugs rjes byin gyis rlabs pa'i bdud rtsi bum pas
NK029(ha)001:2277: dbang bskur bas lus dang khong mi bde ba'i nad
NK029(ha)001:2278: rnams bkrus nas dag cing byang bar gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2279: spros med spros bral chos kyi dbyings //
NK029(ha)001:2280: bum pa zlum po yum gyi gter //
NK029(ha)001:2281: phan byed sman pa'i mchog yin ste //'gro ba'i nad sel bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2282: bum pa zlum po spros med chos kyi dbyings //
NK029(ha)001:2283: thugs rje chen pos phan mdzad yum gyi tshul //'khor ba'i gnas skyob dri ma dag mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:2284: sgrib sel bkra shis le'u re gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2285: drug pa rgyal srid rin po che'i dbang la bcu drug las /
NK029(ha)001:2287: 'khor los bsgyur 'khor lo rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhes na /
NK029(ha)001:2288: rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2289: gso sbyong gi nyi ma bco lnga la dbu khrus byas la /
NK029(ha)001:2291: steng gi 'khyams btsun mo'i 'khor na gnas pa'i tshe /
NK029(ha)001:2292: shar phyogs nas 'khor lo rtsibs stong yod pa /
NK029(ha)001:2293: lte ba dang mu khyud gser las grub pa /
NK029(ha)001:2294: 'gar gzos ma byas shing rang byung ba /
NK029(ha)001:2295: gnam 'phangs su rta la bdun gyi srid tsam zhig
NK029(ha)001:2296: rgyal po'i phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du rang babs ste
NK029(ha)001:2297: / de'i tshe rgyal po'i bsam pas rtags 'di dang
NK029(ha)001:2298: sbyar na bdag ni 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po
NK029(ha)001:2299: yin nges so snyam nas lag pa g.yas pas 'khor
NK029(ha)001:2300: / lo bskor ste / rdzu 'phrul gyi nam mkha' la 'gro zhing phyag du 'khor lo gnas ste /
NK029(ha)001:2301: rgyal ba gsung gi tshogs dang bcas pa yang gnas pa ru 'khod de /
NK029(ha)001:2302: gling bzhi la gnas pa'i rgyal rigs thams cad kyis mdun bsu zhing gnas pa'i tshe /
NK029(ha)001:2303: mi thams cad dge bcu'i lam la 'khor cing 'dzud par byed la /
NK029(ha)001:2304: nang par khes su sus la dga' ba nyams su myong bar byed do //
NK029(ha)001:2305: de dang rjes su mthun par 'khor lo rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2306: ming 'di la chos kyi 'khor lo rin chen bskor
NK029(ha)001:2307: te 'jig rten gsum gyi 'gro ba mus pa rnams
NK029(ha)001:2308: rnam par grol ba'i lam la 'god cing so so'i
NK029(ha)001:2309: skal pa ci lta ba bzhin du sems kyi rgyud
NK029(ha)001:2310: la yongs su smin par byed cing /
NK029(ha)001:2311: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal srid kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2312: dus gsum rgyal bas bskor ba'i 'khor lo 'di //
NK029(ha)001:2313: mi kho ma rgyun chad rgyu dang 'bras bur ston //'khor los bsgyur ba'i dbang phyug rin po chen //
NK029(ha)001:2314: bla med 'khor lo dam pa bskor gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2315: stong nyid ye shes gsal ba'i 'khor lo la //
NK029(ha)001:2316: chos nyid dbyings las 'phrin las cir yang ston //
NK029(ha)001:2317: sems can kha lo gyen du bsgyur mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:2318: chos 'khor bskor ba'i bkra shis le'u ste re gnyis pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2319: gnyis pa rta mchog dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2320: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rta mchog rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK029(ha)001:2321: mdog rin chen in tra ni la ltar sngon por gnas pa /
NK029(ha)001:2322: rngog ma ljang lor gnas pa /
NK029(ha)001:2323: zhon nas gus par byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:2324: gser gser gyis brgyan pa gser gyi dra bas g.yogs
NK029(ha)001:2325: pa rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig nam mkha' la
NK029(ha)001:2329: rgyal pos nyi ma shar bar rta la zhon ste /
NK029(ha)001:2330: gling bzhi'i rgya mtsho mtha' bskor ste /
NK029(ha)001:2331: slar log pa dang khye'u gzugs kyi dga' ba nyams su myong /
NK029(ha)001:2332: de dang rjes su mthun par rta rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2333: ming 'di zhes bya ba rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan de /
NK029(ha)001:2334: bzhon pa dang ldan nas thams cad dga' 'gu 'gro
NK029(ha)001:2335: ba la thogs pa med par gyur cig /'khor ba'i
NK029(ha)001:2336: chu bo 'jig pa bzhi las grol //
NK029(ha)001:2337: brtson 'grus myur bas rdzu 'phrul shugs kyi 'gro //
NK029(ha)001:2338: cang shes sprin gyis shugs 'chang rin po che //
NK029(ha)001:2339: mi gnas yid bzhin spyod par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2340: rdzu 'phrul thogs med kun tu myur ba'i shugs //
NK029(ha)001:2341: gar yang 'gro ba'i don la myur ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:2342: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs kun tu ston pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:2343: thogs med dbang gi bkra shis le'u re gsum pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2345: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po glang po rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu ldan zhes na /
NK029(ha)001:2346: kha dog shel cag pa'i 'phro bzhin du dkar ba /
NK029(ha)001:2347: yan lag bdun du shin tu gnas pa /
NK029(ha)001:2348: rin po che gtsug gis shin tu brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:2349: gser gyi dra bas shin tu brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:2350: rdzu 'phrul dang ldan shing nam mkha' la 'gro ba /
NK029(ha)001:2351: lha dang lha ma yin gyis g.yul rab tu 'gyed pa na /
NK029(ha)001:2352: g.yul de dag la rab tu rgyal ba'i mthu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2353: de dang rjes su mthun par glang po che 'di byin pas /
NK029(ha)001:2354: rdo ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyi gnon pa'i mthu dang ldan zhing rgyal bar gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2355: theg pa'i don de bla med bstod pa'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:2356: yan lag bdun mdzes u mu ta'i mdog /'dul dka' stobs chen glang po rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:2357: khyu mchog rlabs chen stobs lnga rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2358: stobs mchog pha rol gnon pa'i stobs mnga' ba //
NK029(ha)001:2359: gdug pa chen po gzhan gyis mi non pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:2360: pha rol gzhan gyi rdzu 'phrul non mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:2361: mthu stobs dbang gi bkra shis ste le'u re bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2362: bzhi pa nor bu rin po che'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2363: nor bu rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhes na /
NK029(ha)001:2364: thams cad du sngon bee t+aur+ya'i rang bzhin du gnas pa /
NK029(ha)001:2366: yon tan stong dang ldan pa byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:2367: shin tu sbyang ba de nam gyi gung la mun pa rab tu gnag pa la /
NK029(ha)001:2368: nyams sad pa'i phyir rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags te /
NK029(ha)001:2370: skyed mo 'tshal du gzigs mo'i rnam pa thams cad lta bar 'dod na yang /
NK029(ha)001:2371: nor bu rin po che'i 'od kyi dpung gis tshogs
NK029(ha)001:2372: yan lag bzhi yan chad dpag tshad gcig tshun chad
NK029(ha)001:2373: gang dgar mthong par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2375: de dang rjes su mthun par non bu rin po che 'di byin pas /
NK029(ha)001:2376: shes rab rnam par dag pa dang ldan ste /
NK029(ha)001:2377: kun nas nyon mongs par gyur pa'i mun pa thams
NK029(ha)001:2378: cad gsal ba'i sgron me dang ldan nas lhag mthong
NK029(ha)001:2379: gi ye shes rin po che dang ldan par gyur
NK029(ha)001:2380: cig / dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan yid bzhin
NK029(ha)001:2381: gter //'khor ba'i mun sel bde ba'i snying po 'byung
NK029(ha)001:2382: cig / // dgongs pa mchod sbyin nor bdun phun sum tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:2383: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen spyod par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2384: dgos 'dod bskong ba'i nor bu rin po che //
NK029(ha)001:2385: thams cad kun gyis yid dang mthun par shog che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2386: yid bzhin bkra shis le'u ste re lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2387: lnga pa blon po rin po che'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2388: blon po rin po che'i tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhes na /
NK029(ha)001:2393: dpag tshad tshun chad du rin po che'i gter yod pa mthong ste /
NK029(ha)001:2394: rin po che'i gter chu'i nang na yod pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:2396: ring ba na yod pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:2398: bdag po med pa thams cad mthong ste /
NK029(ha)001:2399: des 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po la gsol pa /
NK029(ha)001:2400: lha dkon nor la thugs khral chung bar mdzod cig /
NK029(ha)001:2401: dkor nor ci bzhed par ni ci bzhed pa bka' stsol cig /
NK029(ha)001:2402: de skad ces gsol pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:2403: rgyal po'i dgongs pa thams cad bsgrub po /
NK029(ha)001:2404: de dang rjes su mthun par blon po rin po che 'dis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2405: ming 'di zhes bya ba la lha'i mig rnam par 'phags pa'i nor bdun dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)001:2406: bdag dang gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs pa'i dgos pa thams cad mthar phyin pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:2407: shes bya la thog pa med pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2408: gang la ci 'dod dpag bsam shing lta bu //'gro la snying brtse tshogs gnyis rdzogs par smon //
NK029(ha)001:2409: dbang phyug blon po'i nor bu rin po che //'khor
NK029(ha)001:2410: los bsgyur ba'i rgyal thabs thob par shog /'dzangs pa'i
NK029(ha)001:2411: phul phyin blon po rin po che //
NK029(ha)001:2412: legs nyes kun mkhas spyod pa'i don la mkhas /
NK029(ha)001:2413: yo khal do srong 'dzangs pa'i 'phrul bag can //
NK029(ha)001:2414: blon po dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste re drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2415: bdun pa btsun mo rin po che'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2416: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i btsun mo rin po che tshul ji lta bu zhe na /
NK029(ha)001:2417: rgyal po rgyal rigs su skyes pa /
NK029(ha)001:2423: mi'i mdog las 'das nas tshul lha'i mdog thob ste /
NK029(ha)001:2424: lpags pa'i mdog kyang spri yang ku ltar 'dug pa /
NK029(ha)001:2425: lus ran cing dbyibs legs pa /
NK029(ha)001:2426: sha ran cing ba spu'i bu ga nas tsan dan dri bsung dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:2428: kha nas u dpal gyi ngad ldang ba /
NK029(ha)001:2429: lus kyang bya ka tsha li ka ltar reg na bde ba /
NK029(ha)001:2430: drang ba'i dus na reg na dro ba /
NK029(ha)001:2431: tsha ba'i dus na reg na bsil ba de ni sngon du bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:2432: phyi nas ci bya ba'i lung ma nor ba yid du 'ong bar byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:2433: snyan par smra ba la mkhas te /
NK029(ha)001:2434: yid kyi dgu la yang 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po yid dang 'gal bar mi byed na /
NK029(ha)001:2435: lus dang ngag gi dang ga la byed de /
NK029(ha)001:2436: des ni bud med thams cad kyi skyon sel ba ste /
NK029(ha)001:2437: dpen na skar ma spa ba sangs kyi skar ma thams cad zil gyis non pa bzhin no //
NK029(ha)001:2438: de dang rjes su mthun par btsun mo rin po che 'di byin pas /
NK029(ha)001:2439: ming 'di zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin zhi ba'i chos la dbang 'byor ste /
NK029(ha)001:2440: 'phags pa'i 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam spyod /
NK029(ha)001:2441: yul yongs su dag pas bdag dang gzhan gyi don bden par sdud pa la yid bzhin 'du /
NK029(ha)001:2442: 'byor ba la dpal dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2443: pha rol phyin bcu skyob pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:2444: shes rab gzung 'dzin btsun mo rin mo che //
NK029(ha)001:2445: bsdu ba rnam bzhi tshad med bzhi po yi //
NK029(ha)001:2446: tshe dang longs spyod gter rnams spyod par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2447: shes rab dbyings las sprul pa'i lha //
NK029(ha)001:2448: dgos pa'i don 'grub btsun mo ste /
NK029(ha)001:2449: mthu dang dad pas 'brel pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2450: btsun mo'i bkra shis le'u re bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2451: bdun pa dmag dpon rin po che'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2452: dmag dpon rin po che'i tshul ci lta bu zhes na /
NK029(ha)001:2457: rgyal po bsam pa bzhin byed nus pa /
