NK029(ha)001:2459: sgra thams cad kyi sbyor ba la mkhas pa /
NK029(ha)001:2460: bsdo ba thams cad zil gyi non pa'i go cha bgos pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2461: de dang rjes su mthun par dmag dpon rin po
NK029(ha)001:2462: che 'di byin pas ming 'di zhes bya ba thabs
NK029(ha)001:2463: dang shes rab gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa mthar
NK029(ha)001:2464: phyin nas / 'jigs tshogs kyi lta ba thams cad
NK029(ha)001:2465: legs par spyod pa'i ye shes phun sum tshogs pa
NK029(ha)001:2467: gnod pa'i dpung 'joms brtson 'grus go bgos ste //'jigs pa'i skyabs byed 'gro la ma 'jigs sbyin //
NK029(ha)001:2468: thabs dang shes rab bstan pa'i dmag dpon 'di //
NK029(ha)001:2469: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul dpung gis bsrungs bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:2470: drag shul dreg pas pha rol 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:2471: nyon mongs mi shes g.yul ngo sel ba yis /
NK029(ha)001:2472: rnam par rtog pa cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:2473: gnyen po 'dul ba'i le'u ste re brgyad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2474: brgyad pa ral gri'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2475: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la ral gris dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2476: nyon mongs pa'i dra ba gcod pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2477: de dang rjes su mthun par ye shes kyi gral du phyin pas //
NK029(ha)001:2478: sdug bsngal gyi rgyu 'khrul pa bcad pas bag chags thams cad yongs su byang bar gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2479: sgrib pa'i dra ba bcad nas kyang /
NK029(ha)001:2480: mi shes dra ba gcod tshul du rnon pos bag gcod pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:2481: thams cad kun las rgyal bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:2482: sgrib pa sdig pa'i dra ba gcod mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:2483: ye shes rnon po gar yang thog pa med //
NK029(ha)001:2484: ye shes bag chags rtsad nas gcod mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:2485: sdug bsngal gcod pa'i bkra shis le'u ste re dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2487: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la 'da' gzhu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2488: thabs dang shes rab kyi dbang thob po //
NK029(ha)001:2489: de dang rjes su mthun par 'da' gzhus dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2490: thabs dang shes rab rnam par thar pa'i rgya mtsho myur du bgrod par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2491: bsdo ba'i phyogs 'joms myur ba'i shugs 'chang ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:2492: thabs kyi 'dul la nyes pas ma gos ste /
NK029(ha)001:2493: dngos po kun 'joms pha rol 'bigs pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:2494: thabs kyi 'dul ba'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2495: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med gcig pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2496: thugs rje myur ba'i thabs kyis 'gro la 'byung /
NK029(ha)001:2497: yang rab brtsal mchog blo yi rnon po ste //
NK029(ha)001:2498: shes rab thog med bkra shis le'u bdun cu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2499: bcu pa rnam ral gri dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2500: sngon dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la rnam ral rin po che'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2501: bar du 'joms pa'i bdud dpung 'joms pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2502: stobs ldan dbang phyug mthu stobs che mnga' ba //
NK029(ha)001:2503: bdud dpung phas kyi sdo ba kun btul nas //
NK029(ha)001:2504: che ba chen pos kun la rgyal ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:2505: thams cad mthu stobs kun las dbang byed shog /
NK029(ha)001:2506: rin chen brgyad mdzes rnam ral rin po che //
NK029(ha)001:2507: log pa'i phyogs dang bsdo ba zil gnon pa //
NK029(ha)001:2508: thabs la mkhas pa'i bdud dpung che ba ste //
NK029(ha)001:2509: kun las rgyal ba'i bkra shis le'u don gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2510: bcu gcig pa shan gri'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2511: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)001:2512: kyis 'khor rnams la bshan gri nye ba'i rin po
NK029(ha)001:2514: 'khor ba'i sgrib pa gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2515: de dang rjes su mthun par bshan nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2516: 'khor ba'i sgrib pa'i dra ba gcod pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:2517: dngos po mtshan ma gzhom pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:2518: mi shes rnam rtog ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:2519: bdug pa 'joms pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2520: rin chen mdzes pa'i bshan mchog rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:2521: legs par rno la pha rol nyes pa gcod //
NK029(ha)001:2522: ye shes rnon po kun gyi yid du 'ong //
NK029(ha)001:2523: sdug bsngal gcod pa'i bkra shis le'u ste don gnyis pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2524: bcu gnyis pa zhwa'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2525: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)001:2526: 'khor la zhwa'i nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2527: bgegs dang logs 'dre med pa'i tshe'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2528: de dang rjes su mthun par zhwa nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2529: bgegs dang leg 'dre cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i tshe'i g.yu drung gi dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2531: gdung ba sel ba'i dbang mchog ste //'bras bu thar
NK029(ha)001:2532: ba thob pa'i phyir //'jigs pa bzhi yi skyabs su
NK029(ha)001:2533: shog / rin chen brgyan mchog dbu zhwa rin po
NK029(ha)001:2534: che //'jigs pa bzhi skyobs log pa'i skyon las bsrung
NK029(ha)001:2535: shog / // mi 'gyur g.yu drung tshe'i dbang thob pa //
NK029(ha)001:2536: g.yu drung bkra shis le'u ste don gsum pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2537: bcu gsum pa khab skud dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2538: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis
NK029(ha)001:2539: 'khor la tshang pa'i kha bskud kyi dbang bskur bas
NK029(ha)001:2540: / legs pa'i yon tan 'dod pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2541: de dang rjes su mthun par tshangs pa'i khab skud kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2542: legs pa'i yon tan grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2543: tshangs pa'i kha bskud nye ba'i bkra shis ste /
NK029(ha)001:2544: legs pa'i yon tan tshangs par rdzogs pa'i dpal //
NK029(ha)001:2545: nyes pa kun skyobs phyir na bkra shis ste //
NK029(ha)001:2546: thams cad rdzogs pa'i dbang mchog bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2547: tshangs pa'i khab skud legs pa'i yon tan 'grub //
NK029(ha)001:2548: gang la yid 'cham legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK029(ha)001:2549: don la thugs rje chen po che ba'i rtags //
NK029(ha)001:2550: legs pa tshangs pa'i bkra shis le'u ste don bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2551: bcu bzhi pa na baza'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2552: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)001:2553: kyis 'khor rnams la na bza' nye ba'i rin po
NK029(ha)001:2555: grang ba'i sdug bsngal skyob pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2556: de dang rjes su mthun par na bza' nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2557: 'di dang pha rol gnyis kar grang ba'i nyon mongs
NK029(ha)001:2558: pa zhi ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK029(ha)001:2559: / nyes pa kun skyob na bza' rin po ches bde mchog yid bzhin zad pa med pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:2560: yon tan tshangs pa'i na bza' dam pa 'di //'di dang pha rol gnyis su gon par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2561: rin chen na bza' ji ltar blta bar gdug /
NK029(ha)001:2562: che chung dbyibs ran 'gro la mdzes par snang //
NK029(ha)001:2563: yon tan bla med 'phags pa'i sku dang mtshungs //
NK029(ha)001:2564: chos nyid rtags kyi bkra shis le'u ste don lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2565: bco lnga pa chags kyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2566: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)001:2567: chags nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2568: thugs rje 'gro ba'i don la chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2569: de dang rjes su mthun par chags nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur pas /
NK029(ha)001:2570: 'gro ba'i don la zhabs kyis 'chags dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2571: rin chen chags kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2572: kun la snyoms pa'i thugs rje yis //
NK029(ha)001:2573: sems can don la thogs med de //'gro ba 'dren pa'i dpal du shog /
NK029(ha)001:2574: rin chen mdzes pa'i tshogs mchod dam pa rnams //
NK029(ha)001:2575: gar yang thogs med phyogs bcur bsgrod nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:2576: don rnams ma lus rdzogs par bya ba yi //
NK029(ha)001:2577: yongs la khyab pa'i bkra shis le'u ste don drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2578: bcu drug pa khri snyan sa le'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2579: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:2580: khri gnyan sa le'i lpags pa nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2581: snying rjes sems can 'dren pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2582: de dang rjes su mthun par khri gnyan sa le'i
NK029(ha)001:2583: lpag pa nye ba'i rin po ches dbang bskur bas
NK029(ha)001:2584: / thugs rjes sems can gyis don byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2585: khri gnyan sa le'i lpags pa bkra shis ste /
NK029(ha)001:2586: thams cad snyoms pa'i bkra shis dam pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:2587: yon tan tshang bar rdzogs pa'i bkra shis pa //
NK029(ha)001:2588: snying rjes don byed dbang mchog bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2589: snying rje chen pos sems can don la mkhas //
NK029(ha)001:2590: nyams thag 'phongs pas kun gyi don bya ste //
NK029(ha)001:2591: sems can 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //'gro don rdzogasapa'i bkra shis le'u ste don bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2592: bdun pa bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang la bcu drug las /
NK029(ha)001:2593: dang po yung dkar gyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2594: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis yungs dkar 'thor byed kyi /
NK029(ha)001:2595: rgyal bo bgegs gyi gnyen por byin gyis rlabs pa'i rdzas ni /
NK029(ha)001:2596: rdo rje slob dpon ngas byin pas /
NK029(ha)001:2597: slob ma'i lus sems kyi rgyud la /
NK029(ha)001:2598: bgegs stong phrag brgya bcu'i bsam sbyor ngan pas mi tshugs shing /
NK029(ha)001:2599: bgegs thams cad 'dul ba'i mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa'i don gyi bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2600: yungs dkar rdo rje gsang mchog chen po ste //
NK029(ha)001:2601: rtogs bral mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje yis //
NK029(ha)001:2602: rtogs pa'i bgegs rnams rab tu zhi mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:2603: bkra shis des kyang bgegs rnams rab tu zhi bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:2604: yungs dkar rdo rjes bgegs mchog 'dul //
NK029(ha)001:2605: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i mthu stobs ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2606: dgra bgegs kun las rgyal ba'i byin rlabs bkra shis le'u ste don brgyad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2607: gnyis pa zho phor gyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2608: sngon bcom ldan 'das la khyim bdag bzang skyong gis zho phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:2609: gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i rdzas 'di /
NK029(ha)001:2611: slob ma khyod la sbyin pas /
NK029(ha)001:2612: khyod kyis ting nge 'dzin gyi bcud dang bsod nams
NK029(ha)001:2613: gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i don gyi bkra shis par
NK029(ha)001:2614: gyur cig / zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:2615: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs ste //
NK029(ha)001:2616: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2617: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir zhi bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:2618: bkra shis byin ldan rdzas mchog zho mchog 'dis //'dod don mchog ldan 'dod 'jo ba'i zho //
NK029(ha)001:2619: nyon mongs 'phongs pa 'grangs zhing tshims byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:2620: gzi mdags ldan pa dbang gis bkra shis le'u don dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2621: gsum pa rtsa dur ba'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2622: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bram ze kun d+ha lis r+ts+wa dur ba phul ste /
NK029(ha)001:2623: dur ba ji ltar chung ngu las yal ga dang lo 'dab mang po 'phel ba bzhin du /
NK029(ha)001:2624: rgyu dge ba'i rtsa ba chung ngu las 'bras bu
NK029(ha)001:2625: bsod nams mang po 'phel ba'i byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK029(ha)001:2626: rdzas 'di slob ma la byin pas /
NK029(ha)001:2627: chos rgyu 'bras la ma rmoongs shing dge ba'i rtsa
NK029(ha)001:2628: ba chung ngu la rten nas bsod nams 'bras bu
NK029(ha)001:2629: phun sum 'phel ba'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur
NK029(ha)001:2630: cig / dur bas tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:2631: rdo rje tshe ni rab bsgrub pas //
NK029(ha)001:2632: skye shi'i sdug bsngal rgyun bcad de //
NK029(ha)001:2633: dur bas bkra shis des ni tshe brtan shog /
NK029(ha)001:2634: dur ba'i r+ts+wa mchog bsod nams mang pos 'phel //
NK029(ha)001:2635: bkra shis lo 'dab me tog 'bras bu rgyas //
NK029(ha)001:2636: yid la ci bsam 'dod pa'i bkra shis pa //'dod 'byung bkra shis le'u brgyad bcu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2638: sngon bcom ldan 'das la sa'i lha mos 'tshal li khri phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:2639: ji ltar li khri dmar po chags pa zhen pa'i ngo bo na gnas pa de bzhin du /
NK029(ha)001:2640: thugs rje chen pos sems can thams cad mi btang bar byin gyis brlabs pa'i rdzas 'di /
NK029(ha)001:2641: ngas slob ma khyod la byin pas khyod kyis sems
NK029(ha)001:2642: can thams cad kyi don byed cing 'khor ba'i chos
NK029(ha)001:2643: thams cad la spyod pa'i chos thams cad la sbyod
NK029(ha)001:2644: bzhin ma chags pa'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur
NK029(ha)001:2645: cig / li khri dmar ba dbang gi rang bzhin ste //
NK029(ha)001:2646: chos kun ma lus dbang du gyur pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:2647: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu bstan gyur pa //
NK029(ha)001:2648: bkra shis des kyang rgyal srid bstan gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2649: kha dog dmar po nub phyogs dbang gi pad+ma'i rigs /
NK029(ha)001:2650: chags pa gnyis ldan bdag don gzhan don 'grub //
NK029(ha)001:2651: gsung gi bdag nyid don ston bkra shis rdzas //
NK029(ha)001:2652: tshe yis bkra shis le'u ste gya gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2653: lnga pa me long gi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2654: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis rnam par shes pa gnas
NK029(ha)001:2655: lan gsum du gar pa me long lta bu'i ye
NK029(ha)001:2656: shes bsnyes nas mngon par rdzogs pa'i rdzas 'di slob
NK029(ha)001:2658: khyod kyi bag chags gyi sgrib pa bag la nyal
NK029(ha)001:2659: cha phra mo yan chad rdo rje lta bu'i ting
NK029(ha)001:2660: nge 'dzin gyis bcom nas kun gzhi'i rnam par shes
NK029(ha)001:2662: me long ye shes mthong nas mngon par rdzogs par
NK029(ha)001:2663: sangs rgyas pa de'i don gyis bkra shis par gyur
NK029(ha)001:2664: cig / me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan ste //
NK029(ha)001:2665: ye shes rgyal mtsho'i bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK029(ha)001:2666: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pas //
NK029(ha)001:2667: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir sgriib pa dag gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2668: me long gdong bstan bzhin gyi dri ma sel //
NK029(ha)001:2669: de bzhin nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib pa sel //
NK029(ha)001:2670: gsal la rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK029(ha)001:2671: ye shes gsal ba'i bkra shis le'u ste gya gnyis pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2673: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la dung gis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2674: tshangs pa'i sgra sgrogs par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2675: de dang rjes su mthun par dung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2676: tshangs pa'i dbyangs lta bu sgrog pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2677: chos dung rgyal bas bus nas ni //'jig rten sems can skal ldan la //
NK029(ha)001:2678: rnam gsal sdig byang chos thob pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:2679: tshangs pa'i sgra skad sgrogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2680: skyob pa mgon po tshangs pa'i dbyangs //'phags pa'i gsung
NK029(ha)001:2681: mchog 'gro la sgrog /'jig rten gsum du rgyas pa
NK029(ha)001:2682: yis // gsung gi bkra shis le'u ste gya gsum pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2683: bdun pa g+hi hang gi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2684: sngon bcom ldan 'das la glang po che sa bsrungs gis sman g+hi hang phul ste /
NK029(ha)001:2685: bee d+aur+ya dang ldan pa'i sman mchog bdud bzhi las grol bar byin gyis brlabs pa'i rdzas 'di /
NK029(ha)001:2686: ngas slob ma la byin pas slob ma'i bdud bzhi
NK029(ha)001:2687: las thar zhing nad thams cad sel bar byed pa'i
NK029(ha)001:2688: mthu phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa'i don gyis
NK029(ha)001:2690: g+hi hang dug gsum 'joms pa'i sman yin ste //
NK029(ha)001:2691: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs 'gyur te //
NK029(ha)001:2692: nyon mongs zung ngu med par gyur pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2693: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2694: yon tan ldan pas bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi sel //
NK029(ha)001:2695: sman mchog skye 'gro ma lus kun gyis gsos //
NK029(ha)001:2696: byin gyis rlobs pa'i bkra shis tshe yis gsos //
NK029(ha)001:2697: tshe ring nad med bkra shis le'u ste gya bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2699: sngon bcom ldan 'das la shing bil ba phyag du
NK029(ha)001:2700: phul te ji ltar shing bil ba smin cing 'bras
NK029(ha)001:2701: bu sa'i ngo bor gnas pa bzhin du /
NK029(ha)001:2702: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis sku dang ye shes
NK029(ha)001:2703: dang stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa 'bras
NK029(ha)001:2704: bu'i chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs par byin gyis
NK029(ha)001:2707: khyod la stobs bcu mi 'jigs pa bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)001:2708: ma 'dres pa bco brgyad dang ldan par sku dang
NK029(ha)001:2709: ye shes dang mtshan dang dpe byad la sogs ste
NK029(ha)001:2710: / 'bras bu'i chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs par
NK029(ha)001:2711: sangs rgyas pa'i don gyi bkra shis par gyur cig
NK029(ha)001:2712: / / bil ba rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i
NK029(ha)001:2713: mchog /'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun
NK029(ha)001:2714: / / // byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2715: bkra shis des kyang 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2716: yal ga lo 'dab me tog g.yu lor 'khyiil //'bras bu yid 'ong 'byor pa'i longs spyod ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2717: kun gyi don dang mthun par spyod pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2718: phun tshogs bkra shis le'u ste gya lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2719: dgu pa thugs dpal be'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2720: sngon bcom ldan 'das la byang chub kyi shing drung du /
NK029(ha)001:2721: bdud kyi brgal ba'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:2722: bkra shis pa'i rtags brgyad dang ldan ste /
NK029(ha)001:2723: thugs dpal be'usa bkra shis pa de bzhin du slob
NK029(ha)001:2724: ma'i thugs dpal be'u ru bkra shis par gyur cig
NK029(ha)001:2725: / dpal be'u thugs kyi sa bon ste //'dren pa rnams kyi thugs lags pas //
NK029(ha)001:2726: bla med thar lam drangs pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:2727: thugs kyi dpal be'u bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2728: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2729: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:2730: thugs kha nyid las gsal ba mngon par ston //'di
NK029(ha)001:2731: ni dpal be'u dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste gya
NK029(ha)001:2732: drug pa'o // ston la bdud kyi sdos pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)001:2733: thugs kyi dpal be'u bkra shis 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:2734: de ring khyod la byin byas pas //
NK029(ha)001:2735: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2736: thugs dpal be'u bkra shis pas //
NK029(ha)001:2737: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2738: bcu pa phyag zhabs tsakra'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2739: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis rgal ba'i dus su bkra shis pa'i rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:2740: phyag dang zhabs kyi mthil 'khor los bkra shis pa /
NK029(ha)001:2741: de bzhin du ming 'di zhes bya ba la 'khor los dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2742: phyag dang zhabs kyi mthil 'khor los bkra shis par
NK029(ha)001:2743: gyur cig /'khor los bkra shis phyag dang zhabs mthil
NK029(ha)001:2744: la // skyobs pa'i sangs rgyas 'dren pa lha'i lha //
NK029(ha)001:2745: nyon mongs sems can sman pa'i gsos //
NK029(ha)001:2746: phyag zhabs 'khor los bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2747: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2748: sdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK029(ha)001:2749: phyag zhabs mthil la mngon par gsal bar ston //'di
NK029(ha)001:2750: ni 'khor lo dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste gya
NK029(ha)001:2751: bdun pa'o // ston la bdud kyi bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)001:2753: de ring khyod la byin rlabs pas //'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2754: phyag zhabs 'khor los bkra shis pa //'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang rnams thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2755: bcu gcig pa ljag pad+ma'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2756: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis brgal ba'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:2757: bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad 'byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:2758: ljag pad+mara bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK029(ha)001:2760: ming 'di zhes bya bas ljag pad+mara bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2761: gsung mchog pad+ma chos kyi rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:2762: nyon mongs ma gos pad+ma'i gsung //
NK029(ha)001:2763: thams cad sgrol ba'i gsung lags ste //
NK029(ha)001:2764: ljags mchog pad+mara bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2765: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2766: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK029(ha)001:2767: ljags kyis mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //'di
NK029(ha)001:2768: ni pad+ma dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste gya brgyad
NK029(ha)001:2769: pa'o // ston la bdud kyis bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)001:2771: de rings khyod la byin rlabs pas //
NK029(ha)001:2772: thogs pa med pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2773: ljags nyid pad+ma'i bkra shis pa /
NK029(ha)001:2774: ljags pad ma'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2775: bcu gnyis pa sku rgyal mtshan gyi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2776: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis brgal ba'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:2777: bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:2778: sku rgyal mtshan du bkra shis pa de bzhin du rgyal mtshan gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2779: ming 'di zhes bya ba sku rgyal mtshan du bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2780: mi nub rgyal mtshan 'dren pa'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:2781: thams cad bdud kyi sde btul nas //
NK029(ha)001:2782: dpung bcom sangs rgyas sku bstod de //
NK029(ha)001:2783: sku mchog sangs rgyas bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2784: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2785: sdo ba'i chos rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK029(ha)001:2786: sku yi mchog la brtson par gsal bar ston //'di
NK029(ha)001:2787: ni rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis kyi le'u ste
NK029(ha)001:2788: gya dgu pa'o // ston la bdud kyis bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)001:2789: sku nyid rgyal mtshan bkra shis 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:2790: di rings khyod la sbyin pas bdud bzhi pham byed dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2791: sku nyid rgyal mtshan bkra shis pa /
NK029(ha)001:2792: sku rgyal mtshan gyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2793: bcu gsum pa mgur bum pa'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2794: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyi brgal ba'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:2795: bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:2796: mgur bum par bkra shis pa de bzhin du bum pas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2797: ming 'di zhes bya ba la mgur bum par bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2798: bkra shis bum pa dam pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:2799: bcom ldan 'das kyi mgur lags ste //
NK029(ha)001:2800: mgur mchog bkra shis 'di byin pas //
NK029(ha)001:2801: bum pa'i bkra shis thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2802: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2803: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun la khyad par 'phags //
NK029(ha)001:2804: mgur gyis mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //'di
NK029(ha)001:2805: ni bum pa'i dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste dgu
NK029(ha)001:2806: bcu pa'o // ston la bdud kyi bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)001:2807: mgur nyid bum par bkra shis 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:2808: de rings khyod la byin rlobs bas //
NK029(ha)001:2809: snying rjes 'dzin pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2810: mgur gyi bum par bkra shis pa //
NK029(ha)001:2811: mgur bum pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2812: bcu bzhi pa dbu skra gdugs kyi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2813: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyi brgal ba'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:2814: bkra shis pa'i rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:2815: dbu skra gdugs su bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK029(ha)001:2817: ming 'di zhes bya ba dbu skra gdugs su bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2818: gdugs kyis tsha ba'i sdug bsngal kun sel te //
NK029(ha)001:2819: nyon mongs ma lus kun las rgyal ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:2820: che ba'i yon tan ma lus rgyas pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:2821: log pa'i phyogs rnams zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2822: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2823: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK029(ha)001:2824: dbu skra'i mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston //'di
NK029(ha)001:2825: ni gdugs kyi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste go
NK029(ha)001:2826: gcig pa'o // ston la bdud kyi bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)001:2827: dbu skra gdugs kyi bkra shis 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:2828: de rings khyod la byin rlabs pas //
NK029(ha)001:2829: gdung ba sel byed dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2830: dbu sgra gdugs kyi bkra shis pa //
NK029(ha)001:2831: dbu skra gdugs kyi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2832: bco lnga pa tshems dung gi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2833: sngon bdud kyi brgal ba'i dus su //
NK029(ha)001:2834: bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad byung ngo //
NK029(ha)001:2835: gsung du bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK029(ha)001:2837: ming 'di zhes bya bas gsung dung du bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2838: snyan pa'i sgra rnams phyogs bcur sgrogs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:2839: mu stegs log pa'i phyogs rnams skrag pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:2840: sems can kun gyi shes pa dgrol ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:2841: gsung mchog dung gi rgyal por bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2842: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan /
NK029(ha)001:2843: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags /
NK029(ha)001:2844: gsung gi mchog la mngon par gsal bar ston /
NK029(ha)001:2845: 'di ni gsung gi dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste go gnyis pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2846: ston la bdud kyi bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)001:2847: gsung nyid dung gi bkra shis 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:2848: de rengs khyod la byin brlabs pas //
NK029(ha)001:2849: rgol ba dpa' skum dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2850: gsung nyid dung gi bkra shis pa //
NK029(ha)001:2851: gsung dung gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2852: bcu drug pa phyag zhabs nya yis bkra shis kyi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2853: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdu da kyis brgal ba'i dus su bkra shis kyi rtags brgyad byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:2854: phyag dang zhabs kyi nya bkra shis kyi nyar bkra shis pa de bzhin du /
NK029(ha)001:2855: ming 'di zhes bya ba la nyas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2856: phyag dang zhabs kyi nyar bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2857: phyag zhabs gnyis shar bkra shis te /
NK029(ha)001:2859: nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:2860: nya sha bkra shis nyar ni shog /
NK029(ha)001:2861: gzhan gyis mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:2862: bsdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK029(ha)001:2863: nya sha bzhi las mngon par gsal bar ston //'di
NK029(ha)001:2864: ni nya'i bkra shis dbang gi le'u ste go gsum
NK029(ha)001:2865: pa'o // ston la bdud kyi bsdod pa'i tshe //
NK029(ha)001:2866: nya bzhi gser nyas bkra shis 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:2867: de rings khyod la byin rlabs pas //'khor bar nyams nga med par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2868: nya bzhi gser nya'i bkra shis pa //
NK029(ha)001:2869: bkra shis nya'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2870: brgyad pa shes bya la ma rmongs pa'i dbang la bdun las /
NK029(ha)001:2871: dang po rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2872: sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis ri
NK029(ha)001:2873: rab ri'i rtser 'khor rnams la rdo rje rgya gram
NK029(ha)001:2876: de dang rjes su mthun par rdo rje rgya gram gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2877: phyogs bcu na sngags 'chang rnams kyis rtag tu bsrung bar gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2878: dgos dang som nyid med pa la /
NK029(ha)001:2879: gtsug du rgya gram dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2880: rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams kyis kyang //
NK029(ha)001:2881: bsrungs ba mdzad pa nyid du shog /'phrin las thogs pa med pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2882: bya ba nan tan ye shes las //
NK029(ha)001:2883: dgos pa'i don rnams kun 'grub pa'i //'di ni sngags
NK029(ha)001:2884: 'chang dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste go bzhi pa'o
NK029(ha)001:2885: // gnyis pa dar gyis cod pan kyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2887: dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor la dar dpyangs kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2888: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad la dbang byed par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2889: de dang rjes su mthun par dar dpyangs kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2890: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad dbang bsgyur ba gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2891: dar dpyangs gyen la 'phur ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:2892: chos kyi sku dang gnyis su med //'phred dang 'thur gnyis sku gnyis ste //
NK029(ha)001:2893: longs spyod rdzogs dang sprul sku thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2894: dmar po yar 'phur chos nyid gyen du rtogs //
NK029(ha)001:2895: sngon po 'phred 'phur 'phrin las rnam bzhi mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:2896: mthing kha mar 'phur klu gdug zil gyis non //
NK029(ha)001:2897: dar dpyangs bkra shis le'u ste go lnga pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:2898: gsum pa mchod pa lnga'i dbang //
NK029(ha)001:2900: dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)001:2901: 'khor rnams la pu tsa rnam pa lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2902: rdo rje rgyas thebs dang las kyi kar ma'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2903: de dang rjes su mthun par mchod pa lnga'i rdzas kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)001:2904: rdo rje rgyal thebs dang las mtha' dag byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2905: thabs chen stobs ldan mchod yon dam pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:2906: dmigs pa lnga dang ting 'dzin cha sbyar ste //
NK029(ha)001:2907: rkyen dang mtshams pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK029(ha)001:2908: dri chab dri gsung me tog mdzes par bkram //
NK029(ha)001:2909: bdug spos yid tshim a rga bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK029(ha)001:2910: lha bshos bro ldan 'od gsal mar me ste //
NK029(ha)001:2911: mchod pa rnam lnga'i bkra shis le'u go drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2913: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:2914: nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas theg pa mtha' dag nyan pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2915: de dang rjes su mthun par ka pa li'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2916: gsang sngags kyi rgyud mtha' dag nyan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2917: gdung ba'i sems bskyed dad pa'i shugs phyung nas /
NK029(ha)001:2918: brtson 'grus shugs kyi thams cad thob pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:2919: dad pa'i shugs kyi kun tu nyan pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:2920: shes rab stobs kyi thams cad shes par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2921: shes rab rgya che nyan pa phyogs med byed //
NK029(ha)001:2922: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' bzhin yongs su slob //
NK029(ha)001:2923: sems dang chos nyid gnyis su med pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:2924: nyan dbang bkra shis le'u ste go bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2925: lnga pa chags shing gi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2926: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)001:2927: 'khor rnams la chags shing gis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2928: theg pa mtha' dag 'chad pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2929: de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che 'chad pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2930: theg pa mtha' dag 'chad pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2932: ma lus gnas su 'dren par byed //
NK029(ha)001:2933: skyes mchog sman pa'i rgyal po ste //
NK029(ha)001:2934: ma rig rmongs pa 'dren par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2935: gti mug rmongs pa shes pa bsgral nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:2936: ma rig log par rtog pa grol bar mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:2937: thugs rje che bas shes pa'i rgyud grol ba //
NK029(ha)001:2938: theg rnams 'chad pa'i bkra shis le'u ste go brgyad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2939: drug pa po ti'i dbang ni //
NK029(ha)001:2940: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:2941: d+harma po tis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2942: chos kyi sgo la mkhas shing rtog par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2943: de dang rjes su mthun par d+harma po tis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2944: chos kyi sgo mo thams cad la mkhas shing rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par cig /
NK029(ha)001:2945: gsung rab po ti chos kyi gzugs rnyan te //
NK029(ha)001:2946: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus skyes mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:2947: thams cad kun gyi dbang po sgrol ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:2948: chos rnams thams cad 'chad pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2949: gsung rab chos 'chad pa'i glegs bam la /
NK029(ha)001:2950: chos nyid sgra sgrogs yig ge'i 'phreng ba bkod //
NK029(ha)001:2951: blo'i rab 'bring ji ltar mtshams par ston //
NK029(ha)001:2952: d+harma'i bkra shis le'u ste go dgu pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2953: bdun pa rdo rje dril bu'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2954: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)001:2955: kyis 'khor rnams la rdo rje dang dril bus dbang
NK029(ha)001:2956: bskur bas / ye shes lnga dang chos kyi dbyings kyi don rtogs ste /
NK029(ha)001:2957: chos kyi sku thob nas 'gro ba'i don byed par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2958: de dang rjes su mthun par rdo rje dang dril bus dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2959: ye shes lnga dang chos nyid kyi don rtogs nas //
NK029(ha)001:2960: chos kyi sku thob nas 'gro ba'i don byed par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2961: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med chos kyi sku //'du
NK029(ha)001:2962: 'bral med pa kun gyi dbang mchog ste //'bras bu'i
NK029(ha)001:2963: stobs ldan phyag rgya chen po yis //
NK029(ha)001:2964: rdo rje dril bu 'chang ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2965: rig pa ye shes rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NK029(ha)001:2966: ye shes lnga po rtags kyi ngo bo mchog /
NK029(ha)001:2967: g.yon pa dril bu gsung rab rgya mtsho'i sgra chen sgrags /
NK029(ha)001:2968: gsung rabs rdor dril bkra shis le'u ste brgya tham pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2969: dgu pa mdzes pa brgyan gyi dbang la drug las /
NK029(ha)001:2970: dang po dbu brgyan gyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:2971: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rigs rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:2972: rin po che'i dbu ba rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2973: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po brnyes pa'i dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2974: de dang rjes su mthun par dbu brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2975: chos kyi rgyal srid la mnga' mnyes par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2976: mya ngan 'das pa thugs kyi dpal //
NK029(ha)001:2977: drin can dbu brgyan chos kyi rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:2978: dbang dang byin rlabs sbyin pa'i byin //
NK029(ha)001:2979: chos kyi rgyal srid byed par shog /
NK029(ha)001:2980: rin chen sna tshogs mdzes pa dbu brgyan mchog /
NK029(ha)001:2981: legs pa kun gyi chos kyi rgyal srid mthud //
NK029(ha)001:2982: phyag rgya rigs lnga mthun dang ldan byed pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:2983: dbu rgyan bkra shis le'u ste rgya gcig pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:2984: gnyis pa dbu brgyan gyi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:2985: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)001:2986: kyis 'khor rnams la dpung rgyan gyis dbang bskur bas
NK029(ha)001:2987: / mi 'jigs pa la mnga' mnyes par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2988: de dang rjes su mthun par dpung brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2989: mi 'jigs pa bzhi la mnga' mnyes par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:2990: de dang rjes su mthun par dpung brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2991: mi 'jigs pa bzhi la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:2992: mi 'jigs phas kyi bsdo ba thub pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:2993: mdzes pa'i brgyan mchog shes par thob pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:2994: mnga' mdzes phung po rtags kyi dam pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:2995: brgyan mchog dam pa ston pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:2996: rin chen dpung brgyan shar bu brgyan gyis brgyan //
NK029(ha)001:2997: chos nyid don rtogs mthun pa bstan pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:2998: dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin legs par bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:2999: dpung brgyan dbang gi bkra shis le'u brgya gnyis pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3000: gsum pa zhabs gdub kyi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:3001: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)001:3002: 'khor rnams la zhabs gdub kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3003: stobs bcu la mnga' mnyes pa'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:3004: de dang rjes su mthun par zhabs gdub kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3005: stobs bcu la mnga' mnyes par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:3006: brgyan gyi bye brag rgyal po'i tshul //
NK029(ha)001:3007: rdo rje zhabs kyi chas rab 'di //
NK029(ha)001:3008: khyod kyi zhabs la dbang bskur bas //'gro ba'i don la chags par shog /
NK029(ha)001:3009: rin chen zhabs gdub dam pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:3010: legs par mdzes pa'i yon tan 'dis //
NK029(ha)001:3011: nyes pa legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK029(ha)001:3012: zhabs dub dbang gi bkra shis le'u brgya gsum pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:3013: bzhi pa phyag gdub kyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:3014: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)001:3015: kyis 'khor rnams la phyag gdub kyi dbang bskur bas
NK029(ha)001:3016: / tshul 'khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:3017: de dang rjes su mthun par phyag gdub kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3018: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:3019: sil snyan mdzes pa'i brgyan lags pas //
NK029(ha)001:3020: yid 'ong snyan pa'i phyag gdub 'di //'bras bu thob pa'i dbang mchog ste /
NK029(ha)001:3021: 'gro ba yid 'ong dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:3022: rin chen phyag gdub dam pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:3023: legs par mdzes pa'i yon tan gyis /
NK029(ha)001:3024: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK029(ha)001:3025: phyag gdub dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya bzhi pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3026: lnga pa do shal gyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:3027: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal kun rig rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:3028: rin po che do shal gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3029: che ba'i yon tan rgyal ba'i dbang thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:3030: de dang rjes su mthun par rin po che'i do shal gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3031: legs pa'i yon tan rdzogs shing mthar phyin pas //
NK029(ha)001:3032: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i dbang dam pa thob par cig /
NK029(ha)001:3033: rin chen 'phreng pas 'gro ba'i re 'dod bskongs /
NK029(ha)001:3034: phreng ba do shal 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:3035: yon tan tshangs pa'i brgyan mchog dam pa 'di /
NK029(ha)001:3036: 'bras bu yid bzhin bkra shis thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:3037: rin chen 'phreng ba'i do shal dam pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:3038: sku yi brgyan mchog yon tan sku la brgyan //'phreng ma chad cing rgyun ma chad mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:3039: rin chen 'phreng dbang bkra shis le'u ste brgya lnga pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3040: drug pa dar gyi cod pan gyi dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:3041: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rnam par snang mdzad kyi
NK029(ha)001:3042: 'khor rnams la dar gyi cod pan gyis dbang bskur
NK029(ha)001:3043: bas // rdul gyis bag chags dang bral bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:3044: de dang rjes su mthun par dar gyi cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3045: sbyor bas khams gsum na gnas na yang /
NK029(ha)001:3046: rdul gyi bag chags dang bral bar gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:3047: bkra shis rtags ldan dar gyi cod pan 'di //
NK029(ha)001:3048: dbang gi rang bzhin dmar po 'bar ba te //
NK029(ha)001:3049: dbang bskur spyi bor rtags pa'i yon tan gyis //
NK029(ha)001:3050: dbang gi bkra shis dam pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:3051: chos nyid dar dang 'dra bar mtshungs pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:3052: don dam nyid du rtogs pa mngon phyung zhing //'di nyid legs pa'i chos nyid don rtogs pa //
NK029(ha)001:3053: byin rlabs dbang gi bkra shis le'u ste brgya drug pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3054: bcu pa ming gi dbang la gnyis las /
NK029(ha)001:3055: dang po rgyu'i ming gi dbang la /
NK029(ha)001:3056: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser dpal rnam par snang mdzad
NK029(ha)001:3057: kyis 'khor rnams la rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur
NK029(ha)001:3058: bas / rigs nges pa'i sras su gyur nas rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur to //
NK029(ha)001:3059: de dang rjes su mthun par rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3060: mi 'gyur ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:3061: rdo rje ming mchog mkhas pa dpe la drangs //
NK029(ha)001:3062: thugs las gsung du byung nas rtags pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:3063: dag cing tshul du khyed la bskur ba yis //
NK029(ha)001:3064: thams cad ston pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:3065: ston pa thugs rjes nges pa'i ming btags pas //
NK029(ha)001:3066: thugs kyi ngang nas nges pa'i sras su mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:3067: rdo rje mchog gi gral thob ming gi dbang //
NK029(ha)001:3068: rdo rje ming dbang bkra shis le'u brgya bdun pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3069: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i ming gi dbang /
NK029(ha)001:3070: sngon ri rab ri'i rtser rgyal bu don thams cad
NK029(ha)001:3071: grub pa la rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi mngon par
NK029(ha)001:3072: shes pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3074: rin po che'i khang bu 'bar bar rnam par snang
NK029(ha)001:3075: mdzad mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur to
NK029(ha)001:3076: // de dang rjes su mthun par mngon par byang chub pa lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3077: 'bras bu ri rab ri'i rtser mngon par sangs rgyas par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:3078: mngon shes lnga ldan 'bras bu sa bcu 'das /
NK029(ha)001:3079: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen sa la gnas /
NK029(ha)001:3080: 'bras bu dam pa sangs rgyas te /
NK029(ha)001:3081: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:3082: dbang mchog thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa yi //'bras bu thams cad ma lus thob pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:3083: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang mchog der rdzogs pas //'di
NK029(ha)001:3084: ni phyi dbang rdzogs pa'i bkra shis le'u ste brgya
NK029(ha)001:3085: rtsa brgyad pa'o // ab+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:3086: dbang don rgyas pa'i dbye ba ltar sbyar ba yin no //
NK029(ha)001:3087: spyir phyi dbang la brgya rtsa brgyad yod do /
NK029(ha)001:3088: ka smad nyan rang gi dbang ma rtogs so /
NK029(ha)001:3090: gnyis pa nus pa'i dbang la lnga ste /
NK029(ha)001:3095: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ngo /
NK029(ha)001:3096: dbang de lnga'i cho ga yang gong dang mthun no //
NK029(ha)001:3097: gsum pa gsang ba zab mo'i dbang la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)001:3099: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang dang /
NK029(ha)001:3100: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:3101: dbang de gsum gyi cho ga'i dod la /
NK029(ha)001:3103: lha lam khyer lha tshogs sum cu rtsa bdun //
NK029(ha)001:3104: snying po lam khyer bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na //
NK029(ha)001:3108: a mo g+ha sid d+hi a /
NK029(ha)001:3110: theg pa lam khyer yo ga'i theg pa /
NK029(ha)001:3111: dbang lam khyer yo ga'i dbang mchog drug cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK029(ha)001:3112: de la dbang chags pa'i rten du 'debs gcig byas na /
NK029(ha)001:3113: rang gi snying gi dkyil na dngas ma chen po lnga gnas pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3114: rang bzhin gyi rigs lnga dang ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gdod ma nas gnas pa yin te /
NK029(ha)001:3115: de la rang gi spyi bor thig le dkar po ril ma tsam gcig bsam /
NK029(ha)001:3117: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thil pa shar /
NK029(ha)001:3119: thig le dkar po de yas mas babs pas /
NK029(ha)001:3120: snying gi dkyil du dngas ma lnga'i rigs lngar gnas pa dang gnyis su med par 'dres pa bsam /
NK029(ha)001:3121: de ni don dam mtshan ma med pa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK029(ha)001:3122: rigs lngar gnas shing rigs lnga rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gyi lhar snang ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:3123: kun rdzob ye shes snang ba ste //
NK029(ha)001:3124: de dag gnyis su med pa'i ngang las /
NK029(ha)001:3125: blo rang bzhin gyi gnas pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3126: dbang chags pa'i rten yin gsung nga //
NK029(ha)001:3127: de la yo ga'i gags sbyar na /
NK029(ha)001:3128: gang du bskur ba'i gnas ni /
NK029(ha)001:3129: lha bya skad snyan ljon shing gi tshal rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du /
NK029(ha)001:3130: gang gis bskur ba'i ston pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3131: slob dpon chen po kun ma tis bskur /
NK029(ha)001:3132: gang la bskur ba'i yul ni /
NK029(ha)001:3133: rdo rje khyung grags rtsal la sogs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3135: yo ga bkra shis drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dbang bskur ste /
NK029(ha)001:3136: rgyu mtshan ni bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK029(ha)001:3137: bcom ldan 'das che ba'i yon tan smos pa'i phyir ro //
NK029(ha)001:3138: dgos pa ni gang gis thob pa'i bkra shis par bya ba'i phyir dgos pa yod do //
NK029(ha)001:3143: tshogs dang dga' ston rgya chen bya /
NK029(ha)001:3148: bstod pa ci rigs pa bya /
NK029(ha)001:3150: de ltar bdag nyid chen po khyed rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:3151: bsnyen cing sgrub pa dang ci 'byor ba'i /
NK029(ha)001:3152: yo byad rnams kyi mchod pa la ci 'byor ba'i mchod pa grangs ji snyed pa phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:3153: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad /
NK029(ha)001:3156: bla na med pa'i byang chub chen po thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:3158: gang yang bdag brtsod pa'i dus su snyigs ma'i sems can du gyur nas /
NK029(ha)001:3159: gzhung bzhin du yo byad ma tshogs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:3161: de dag thams cad bdag nyid chen po 'khor dang
NK029(ha)001:3162: bcas pa khyed rnams kyis bzod pa chen po mdzad
NK029(ha)001:3163: du gsol / gzhan yang bdag cag las dang po pa'i sems can du gyur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3164: ting 'dzin la dbang ma thob te /
NK029(ha)001:3165: cho ga'i yan lag la bying ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:3167: 'dod chags la sogs pa nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis /
NK029(ha)001:3171: cho ga nyams pa de dag thams cad bdag nyid
NK029(ha)001:3172: chen po 'khor dang bcas pa khyed rnams kyis bzod
NK029(ha)001:3174: gang yang bdag blo gti mug pas //
NK029(ha)001:3175: legs byas 'di la nyes bya gang //
NK029(ha)001:3176: gang phyir lus can skyabs gyur pas //
NK029(ha)001:3177: de ni mgon pos bzod par gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3178: rtsol ba'i nus phan ma mching shing //
NK029(ha)001:3179: ma rnyed pa dang ma tshang ba dang //'dir ni bya ba gang 'gyis pa //
NK029(ha)001:3180: de dag thams cad bzod par gsol /
NK029(ha)001:3182: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:3183: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:3184: rtag tu gshegs pa ma lags kyang //
NK029(ha)001:3185: sems can don la dgongs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:3186: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3187: badz+ra muh bkra shis brjod pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3188: ston mchog dam pa lha mi mchod 'os pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:3189: ces sogs kyi bkra shis brjod /
NK029(ha)001:3191: de ni yo ga'i dbang gi them skas rdzogs so //
NK029(ha)001:3195: // gnyis pa nang dbang gi chu bo las /
NK029(ha)001:3196: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dbang gi cho ga lags so //
NK029(ha)001:3197: gnyis pa nang dbang gi chu bo la /
NK029(ha)001:3198: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la /
NK029(ha)001:3199: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bya /
NK029(ha)001:3202: zhi ba'i dbang bskur ba dbang /
NK029(ha)001:3205: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:3210: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:3211: rab gnas sbyin bsreg ces gsungs pas bdun ste /
NK029(ha)001:3216: sku gsung thugs kyi rnam pa bgod pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:3220: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la /
NK029(ha)001:3222: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la /
NK029(ha)001:3223: sor bzhi dang 'dzub gang gi tshad do //
NK029(ha)001:3224: bum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chung tshad khru gang dang /
NK029(ha)001:3226: 'bring tshad la khru bcu ganya sa dang bcu drug /
NK029(ha)001:3230: de dag kyang gnas khang yangs dog dang /
NK029(ha)001:3231: sbyin bdag 'byor ba che chung gis dbang gis ji ltar rigs par bya'o /
NK029(ha)001:3232: phyag len la sngar las dang bya bas sbyangs pa'i skabs su bya ba nyid do //
NK029(ha)001:3233: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la /
NK029(ha)001:3236: rab nam mkha'i dbyings bsam yas pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3237: de dag kyang slob dpon dgongs pa zab mi zab dang /
NK029(ha)001:3238: slob bu las dag tshabs che chung gi dbang gis
NK029(ha)001:3239: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK029(ha)001:3241: gnyis pa thig la bdun las /
NK029(ha)001:3248: thig lta gon gyi skabs su zin la gdab pa'i thabs dang /
NK029(ha)001:3251: thogs mar 'debs pa'i phyag len ni /
NK029(ha)001:3252: nang par snga bar langs la /
NK029(ha)001:3253: be kra sa ma yam zhes pa'i sngags dang /
NK029(ha)001:3255: mdang lhag par gnas pa'i rten dang brten par bcas
NK029(ha)001:3256: pa'i dkyil 'khor mdun gyi nam mkha' la bteg nas
NK029(ha)001:3258: 'bru'i tshom bu rnams kyang bsdus la /
NK029(ha)001:3259: tsha khang la sogs pa 'gong yugs mi 'gro ba'i sar blug la /
NK029(ha)001:3260: dkyil 'khor gyi sa gzhi dri bzang po'i chus byug cing /
NK029(ha)001:3263: dbang phyug kun bzang gi ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK029(ha)001:3264: ye shes kyi thig skud thog nas shar du 'dug /
NK029(ha)001:3266: slob bu kun tu bzang mor bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:3267: badz+ra badz+ra zhes gtad cing nub du 'dug /
NK029(ha)001:3268: thig byang byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin dkar brengs kyis bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:3270: bdag rdo rje slob dpon che ge mo la sogs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:3271: dbang bskur ba'i ched du de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK029(ha)001:3272: cad kyi sku gsung thugs gsang ba las ches gsang
NK029(ha)001:3273: ba / yang gsang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK029(ha)001:3274: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs pa'i thig 'debs pas /
NK029(ha)001:3275: bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:3278: rdo rje ye shes kyi thig gdab du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:3279: phyogs bcu ma lus dus gsum gyi /
NK029(ha)001:3280: rgyal ba sras bcas thams cad kun /
NK029(ha)001:3281: thig gi sgra 'dis rab bskul nas /
NK029(ha)001:3282: byin gyis brlabs par mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:3283: badz+ra pu tra sa ma ya ma ti kra ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:3285: gsang gnas kyi thad kar shar nub kyi tshang thig gdab //
NK029(ha)001:3286: de nas thig 'gros dang bcas pas /
NK029(ha)001:3288: slob ma byang du phyin la /
NK029(ha)001:3289: tshig bcad dang sngags gong ltar gyis /
NK029(ha)001:3291: de nas slob dpon gyis g.yas bskor gyi shar lho dang /
NK029(ha)001:3292: slob ma nub byang du phyin la gong bzhin zur thig gdab /
NK029(ha)001:3293: de nas slob dpon lho nub dang /
NK029(ha)001:3294: slob ma byang shar du song la gong bzhin gdab /
NK029(ha)001:3295: mdun gyis nam mkha' la ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:3296: de nas dam tshig gi thig skud sngar bzhin thogs la /
NK029(ha)001:3297: phyogs bcu ma lus gyi sogs dang /
NK029(ha)001:3298: sa t+wa sho d+ha ni h+aum phata brjod la /
NK029(ha)001:3299: sngar bzhin tshangs thig la sogs gdab pas /
NK029(ha)001:3300: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs pa dang ldan par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:3301: dkyil 'khor che chung gang yin gyi tshad cig gam /
NK029(ha)001:3304: bcu drug gi cha dgos la zur thig la cha chen bcu gcig yod pa'i mtshan ma byas la /
NK029(ha)001:3305: mtshan ma'i thog du thig ring po phyogs bzhi dkar gdab pas /
NK029(ha)001:3306: cha chen nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa gcig gam /
NK029(ha)001:3310: de la cha bran gdab pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3311: dang po dang drug pa la phyed du gdab cing /
NK029(ha)001:3312: de'i phyi ma la'ang phyed du gdab /
NK029(ha)001:3313: gnyis pa dang bdun pa cha bran bzhi bzhi mnyam por gdab /
NK029(ha)001:3314: gsum pa dang dgu pa phyi dang nang gi cha bran re re gdab /
NK029(ha)001:3315: bzhi pa dang bcu pa phyed phyed du gdab /
NK029(ha)001:3316: lnga pa dang brgyad pa dbus dor la mtha' gnyis su cha bran re re gdab /
NK029(ha)001:3317: cha chen bcu gcig pa ni mi gdag ste /
NK029(ha)001:3319: dkyil 'khor la gdab pa'i thig rab gnas dang ldan pa de la /
NK029(ha)001:3320: 'gong na bde bar gshegs pa la bskur btab par 'gyur bas /
NK029(ha)001:3321: mi 'gong bar bya ba'i don du /
NK029(ha)001:3322: hrih zhes pa'i sgra rings por brjod cing /
NK029(ha)001:3323: dkyil 'khor gyi thig blos nam mkha' la bsteg nas /
NK029(ha)001:3324: ye shes kyi thig dam tshig gi thig skud la /
NK029(ha)001:3325: gnyis med du bsres pa de kun bzang /
NK029(ha)001:3326: zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK029(ha)001:3327: dam tshig gi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK029(ha)001:3328: badz+ra muhzhe thig bskud gnyis kyi byin brlabs rang bzhin gyi gnas su gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:3329: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:3330: lte ba nas tshangs thig gi rgyud la cha bran
NK029(ha)001:3331: drug pa nas bkor ba lte ba'i mu khyud nang
NK029(ha)001:3332: ma bdun pa nas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)001:3333: mu khyud phyi ma cha bran bcu bzhi nas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)001:3334: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud nang la bco lngas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)001:3335: mu khyud phyi gdugs thog gi rtse nas /
NK029(ha)001:3337: cha chen bcu pa'i phyed nas bskor ba rdo rje'i ra ba /
NK029(ha)001:3339: de ni zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i thig go zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor 'bring po ni /
NK029(ha)001:3340: cha bran lnga pa dang drug pa nas lte ba bskor /
NK029(ha)001:3341: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa nas 'khor lo bskor /
NK029(ha)001:3342: cha chen bdun pa'i thog nas glang gur dang rdo rje bskor /
NK029(ha)001:3344: dkyil 'khor brgyan pa la lte ba dang rtsibs bzhi bskor lugs gong ltar la /
NK029(ha)001:3345: lte ba'i dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi bskor shar rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)001:3346: lho'i rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3347: nub rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3348: byang rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhis bskor /
NK029(ha)001:3353: me ri rnams gong dang mtshungs so //
NK029(ha)001:3354: zhi ba'i tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i dkyil 'khor bri na'ang /
NK029(ha)001:3358: dbang phyug rgyas pa'i chas su zhugs ste /
NK029(ha)001:3359: sngar rab gnas byas pa'i tshon rnams ni /
NK029(ha)001:3360: dkyil 'khor gyi steng du nyer sngogs byas la /
NK029(ha)001:3362: 'gying bur ston la phyag g.yas pa'i sor mo lnga la /
NK029(ha)001:3363: nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga bsam nas /
NK029(ha)001:3364: +amo sarba pany+tsa rat+na sa ma ye h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:3366: yig 'bru rnams dang tshon rtsi bsres /
NK029(ha)001:3367: de nas mtheb 'dzub kyi tshon sngon po 'dzin la /
NK029(ha)001:3368: h+aum 'di ni chos dbyings dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:3369: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir /
NK029(ha)001:3370: rim pa dang por yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:3371: dngos grub dam pa rtsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:3373: dbus bskor phur gyi shul du cung zhing blag /
NK029(ha)001:3374: de nas rtsig pa'i bya nga shar gyi 'tshams su
NK029(ha)001:3375: re kha sngon po 'dzub gang pa gcig legs par
NK029(ha)001:3376: bri / de'i lhag ma slar dbus kyi khung bur blug /'og ma kun gyi phyag len des 'dre /
NK029(ha)001:3378: 'di ni me long dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:3379: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)001:3380: rim pa gnyis par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:3381: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:3384: a 'di ni sor rtogs dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:3385: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)001:3386: rim pa gsum par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:3387: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:3390: swa 'di ni mnyam nyid dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:3391: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)001:3392: rim pa bzhi par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:3393: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3396: ha 'di ni bya grub dag ba ste /
NK029(ha)001:3397: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)001:3398: rim pa lnga par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:3399: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3400: brjod pas byang shar mtshams su re kha ljang khu bri /
NK029(ha)001:3401: phud lhag dbus kyi khung bur slug la kham lnga
NK029(ha)001:3402: dag par bya ba'i don du 'byung ba rim brtsegs
NK029(ha)001:3403: bsgom / don la ye shes lnga tshon pa'i rtags
NK029(ha)001:3404: rin po che lnga las grub pa'i ri rab tu
NK029(ha)001:3405: bsgom / bsgom / ri rab de'i steng du gzhal yas khang bzhengs par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:3407: thog ma song par bya ste /
NK029(ha)001:3408: phyis ban rag 'dren pa'i dus su spra brtag cing /
NK029(ha)001:3410: de nas zhal lung thob pa'i slob bu rnams kyi lag sor lnga la /
NK029(ha)001:3411: nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lngas bskor la /
NK029(ha)001:3413: dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi gru chad rtsigs pa mun pa /
NK029(ha)001:3427: chu srin kha nas rdo ra /
NK029(ha)001:3430: me ri rnams legs par bri'o //
NK029(ha)001:3432: gzhan rnams gong dang 'dra ba la /
NK029(ha)001:3435: dkyil 'khor brgyas pa la gzhan rnams dkyil 'khor 'bring po dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:3436: dbus kyi lte ba'i dkyil 'khor lo rtsiiibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3437: shar rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3440: nub rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3443: tshom bu gcig pa dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:3445: gzhan dkyil 'khor 'bring po dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:3446: dbus kyi lte bar 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3447: shar rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3448: nub rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi bri'o //
NK029(ha)001:3449: tshom bu lnga pa la gzhan tshom bu gsum pa dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:3450: lho rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3451: byang rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi bri'o //
NK029(ha)001:3452: bzhi pa tshon ni dbus kyi lte ba ni mthing kha'o //
NK029(ha)001:3453: lte ba'i mu khyud ni 'od zer ro //'khor lo rtsibs bzhi ni /
NK029(ha)001:3457: byang ljang khu ste rigs lnga yab yum gyi gnas so /
NK029(ha)001:3458: gong ras bzhi ni shar lho nas g.yas bskor kyi 'khor lo'i kha dog dang mtshungs pas ste /
NK029(ha)001:3459: kha dog re re la lnga lnga gsungs pas rigs mthun la /
NK029(ha)001:3461: nang sems dpa' yab yum gyis pa'o //'khor lo phyi'i mu khyud ni nag po'o //
NK029(ha)001:3462: gru chad ni phyed ma'i kha dog can ste /
NK029(ha)001:3463: phyi sems dpa' yab yum gyi pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3464: de bzhin du bar 'khyams sgo dang bcas pa ni rigs kyi kha dog ste /
NK029(ha)001:3470: don lhag pa'i ye shes tshon pa'i rtags /
NK029(ha)001:3471: lha med pa'i khang stong bzhi ste rigs kyi kha dog can no //
NK029(ha)001:3472: bar 'khyams ni kun bzang yab yum dang /
NK029(ha)001:3475: tshon spra la bkab pa ka pa la gsal la /
NK029(ha)001:3477: re kha lngas 'tshams sbyar la drangs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3478: mun pa dang glang rgyab nag pa'o //'dod rnams dmar po /
NK029(ha)001:3482: dra gdan nag la dra ba dmar po dang dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:3483: shar bu'i ba dan dmar po la shar bu dngul
NK029(ha)001:3484: dam kha thur du bstan pa lta bu'i dkar po
NK029(ha)001:3485: byeed / mda' yab bzhi nag po /
NK029(ha)001:3486: mda' yab mchod rten dkar po sgrigs /
NK029(ha)001:3487: rta babs snam bu bzhi la gnyis gnyis su byas te brgyad ni /
NK029(ha)001:3490: rin chen sgrom bu rnams 'phyang yees bya ste za ra tsha seng ge rin chen shar bu /
NK029(ha)001:3491: 'phreng ba dang brgyad po mas rim kyi brtsegs la ci ltar mdzes par bri'o //
NK029(ha)001:3495: rtsigs pa dang mtshungs par bris /
NK029(ha)001:3496: chos 'khor dang ri dwags gser po /
NK029(ha)001:3500: chu srin gyi kha nas phyung pa'i rdo rje rtse gsum pa phyogs mdog pad bskor ni sna tshogs /
NK029(ha)001:3501: rdo rje'i ra ba sngon po'i gser po /
NK029(ha)001:3502: me ri sna tshogs su tshon legs par 'gyed /
NK029(ha)001:3508: tshom bu gcig pa yang dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mtshungs so //
NK029(ha)001:3511: tshom bu lnga pa rnams 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3512: lte ba dang lnga sngon po la /
NK029(ha)001:3513: de'i steng gi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:3520: tshon thal shor na dal yams 'byung /
NK029(ha)001:3522: de nas zhal bsros kyi mchod pa bshams la /
NK029(ha)001:3523: dkyil 'khor bris pa la lhag mo sbyangs /
NK029(ha)001:3525: mdun gyi nam mkha' yi lta gon gyi lha tshogs dang /
NK029(ha)001:3526: thig gi lha tshogs rnams brdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor la bstim /
NK029(ha)001:3529: bzhi bsnol gyi sngags kyis mchod do //
NK029(ha)001:3530: dam tshig gi phyag rgyas badz+ra mu /
NK029(ha)001:3531: zhes brjod la tshon gyi rab gnas rang bzhin gyi gnas su gshegs /
NK029(ha)001:3532: rdul tshon lhag ma rnams snod sor sor slug go /
NK029(ha)001:3533: lnga pa rnam par bgod pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3534: thog mar tshul phyag byas la /
NK029(ha)001:3540: spa ra sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)001:3541: rdo rje rtse lnga par gyur /
NK029(ha)001:3543: badz+ra kro ta a mri ta kun+da li h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:3545: bdag bdud rtsid 'khyil pa sku mdog ljang khu /
NK029(ha)001:3546: sna tshogs rdo rje rtse gsum pa gcig bsnams pa gcig tu bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:3547: h+aum yang dag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir /
NK029(ha)001:3548: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas /
NK029(ha)001:3549: 'dul ba'i las ni ma rtogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:3550: thams cad thugs rjes bskang zin gyis /
NK029(ha)001:3551: da lta nyid du so sor dengs /
NK029(ha)001:3552: ci ste bka' las 'da' gyur na /
NK029(ha)001:3553: rdo rje mtshon chen 'bar ba yis /
NK029(ha)001:3554: de ma thag du bkas nas shog /
NK029(ha)001:3555: na ma sa man+ta ka ya wa ga tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra nan /
NK029(ha)001:3556: na mo badz+ra kra d+ha y+aa /
NK029(ha)001:3557: ma h+aa d+ha d+hod i ta ka b+he ra /
NK029(ha)001:3558: a si mu la sa ra shu pa sha ha ta ya /
NK029(ha)001:3559: a mri ta kun ta li /
NK029(ha)001:3561: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi tash+thi tish+tha /
NK029(ha)001:3570: sarba big nan ba na yak+sha /
NK029(ha)001:3572: a d+ha ka ra ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:3573: gnod byed thams cad ma ra ya h+aum phatahcesa brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:3574: rang 'dra ba'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros nas /
NK029(ha)001:3575: bgegs rnams thams cad bskrad par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)001:3576: h+aum zhes pas khro bo'i gur du gyur pa bsam /
NK029(ha)001:3580: bskal pa'i rlung gis kyang mi tshugs par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)001:3581: dbang phyug kun bzangs su gsal ba'i thugs kha nas /
NK029(ha)001:3585: lam gyi yig 'bru mas rim gyis spros pas /
NK029(ha)001:3586: spa ra sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)001:3587: 'byung ba rang kha ma'i rtogs pa sbyangs nas /
NK029(ha)001:3588: kham lnga rnam par dag pa'i 'byung ba rim brtsegs gsal gdab /
NK029(ha)001:3591: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor de nyid /
NK029(ha)001:3592: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi brten gzhal yas khang gsal gdab la /
NK029(ha)001:3593: de las brtan pa lha bgod pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3594: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u dgu pa las /
NK029(ha)001:3595: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang 'god /
NK029(ha)001:3599: gsung yig 'bru yang rung mod kyi /
NK029(ha)001:3600: 'grub na gser dngul zangs lcags la /
NK029(ha)001:3603: ba so la sogs pa bskos pa'am /
NK029(ha)001:3604: rin po che'i che ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:3605: spos dri la sogs pa'i lde gu 'am /
NK029(ha)001:3607: shu gu la bris su bris pa'ang rung ste /
NK029(ha)001:3608: gzungs dang ldan pa'i lhas sku rnams dbang phyug gi phyag tu bsnams la /
NK029(ha)001:3609: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig mum da du shwa ri zhes brjod cing /
NK029(ha)001:3610: mi skyod pa yab yum kyi sku /
NK029(ha)001:3611: dkyil 'khor kyi dbus kyi lte ba la bkod pas /
NK029(ha)001:3612: sku gzi mdangs dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)001:3614: de'i steng du man bya li dbus kyi bum pa'ang 'god do //
NK029(ha)001:3615: de bzhin du dzi na dzig la sogs pas /
NK029(ha)001:3616: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po thams cad rim pa
NK029(ha)001:3617: bzhin rang rang gi gnas su rdzogs par 'god do
NK029(ha)001:3618: // bum pa rnams kyang lha grangs dang mnyam pa yod na /
NK029(ha)001:3619: thad so nas thad sor dgod pa'am /
NK029(ha)001:3621: phyogs bzhi'i lha rnams kyi steng du dgod do //
NK029(ha)001:3622: de yang dbus kyi lha'i zhal dang /
NK029(ha)001:3623: bum pa'i mchu ni shar du bstan no //
NK029(ha)001:3624: gzhan rnams ni gtso bo la /
NK029(ha)001:3626: 'on kyang sgo ba ni zhal phyir bstan par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:3627: las thams cad pa'i bum pa dbang phyug gi g.yas phyogs su dgod do //
NK029(ha)001:3628: rdo rje rnams dkyil 'khor gyi lho phyogs su /
NK029(ha)001:3629: dril bu rnams byang phyogs su dgod do //
NK029(ha)001:3630: yi dam gyi mchod gtor lho nub tu /
NK029(ha)001:3631: ma mgon gyi byang shar dgod /
NK029(ha)001:3632: dge bsnyen gyi shar lho dang /
NK029(ha)001:3634: sman rag gzed zhal dang bcas pa shar du'o //
NK029(ha)001:3635: bzhi ba snol gzed zhal dang bcas pa nub tu'o //
NK029(ha)001:3636: gzhan yang dbu brgyan la sogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:3637: phan dbang gi dbang rdzas dang /
NK029(ha)001:3638: ka pa li la sog pa nub dbang gi dbang rdzas dang /
NK029(ha)001:3640: rtsa rgyud le'u dgu pa las /
NK029(ha)001:3641: bcos bu'i ras ni sna tshogs dang /
NK029(ha)001:3642: brgyan 'phreng gtung dang bro bas bskor /
NK029(ha)001:3646: bar brgyan la sogs pa dang mchod pa'i bye brag ji ltar 'byor pa phun sum tshogs par bya /
NK029(ha)001:3647: mdor na gong sta gon gyi skabs su bkod pa'i mchod gtor /
NK029(ha)001:3651: ral gri la sogs pa legs par bgram mo //
NK029(ha)001:3652: drug pa rab gnas la bcu ste /
NK029(ha)001:3653: sngon du bya ba'i cho ga dang /
NK029(ha)001:3654: ting nge 'dzin gyi lha bskyed pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:3655: ye shes pa spyan drangs shing stim pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:3656: dbang po la sogs kyi skyon sbyangs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:3657: che ba'i yon tan gyi dbang bskur mnga' gsol dang /
NK029(ha)001:3658: chu bdun gyis bkru zhing sku phyi ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:3659: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi puk+tsa 'bul ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:3660: bden pa brjod cing bstan bzhugs bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:3661: yon bdag la sogs kyis phyag bskor ba bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:3662: mi 'bral zhing smon lam gdab pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3669: mdun bskyed kyi bsnyen bsgrub po /
NK029(ha)001:3675: dang po yongs su smin par bya ba'i yan lag ni /
NK029(ha)001:3676: dpon slob rnams bstan la 'khod de /
NK029(ha)001:3677: rol mo'i byin dbab pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK029(ha)001:3679: rtsa ba'i bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam pa
NK029(ha)001:3680: la phyog bcu dus bzhi'i skyabs yul ma tshang ba
NK029(ha)001:3681: med pa / mkha' khyab kyi 'khor lo bzhugs pa thams cad mngon sum du sad pa la /
NK029(ha)001:3682: bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can rnams /
NK029(ha)001:3683: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal /
NK029(ha)001:3684: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:3685: mchog gsum ston pa'i zhing gyur la /
NK029(ha)001:3686: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi /
NK029(ha)001:3687: dngos 'byor yid kyi rnam sprul pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:3688: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3689: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i bgegs //
NK029(ha)001:3690: nyes byas ma lus gshegs par bgyis //
NK029(ha)001:3691: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK029(ha)001:3692: ma chags spyod la rje yi rangs //
NK029(ha)001:3693: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK029(ha)001:3694: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK029(ha)001:3695: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK029(ha)001:3696: dag pa gsum gyis lus 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)001:3697: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK029(ha)001:3698: bsdus ste byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK029(ha)001:3699: zhes lan gsum la sogs par brjod la /
NK029(ha)001:3700: skyabs yul rnams rang la bsdus ste /
NK029(ha)001:3701: ka dag gnyis su med pa'i klong du rang babs su bzhag /
NK029(ha)001:3702: gnyis pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3703: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka /
NK029(ha)001:3704: bdag nyid skad cig gi rdo rje he ru ka
NK029(ha)001:3705: sku mdog mthing nag mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum
NK029(ha)001:3706: phyag drug gis dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse
NK029(ha)001:3708: bar ba gnyis kyis rtse lnga dang b+hany+tsa /
NK029(ha)001:3709: tha ma gnyis kyi zhing dbyug dang 'dzin 'deg pa'i tshul can /
NK029(ha)001:3710: zhabs bzhi g.yon brkyang ba'i gyad kyi dor stabs kyi
NK029(ha)001:3711: ru tra pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba gnan
NK029(ha)001:3712: pa / yum rdo rje khro mo'i dbang phyug ma
NK029(ha)001:3713: sngon mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)001:3714: cing g.yon dung khrag zhal du stob pa zhing gi
NK029(ha)001:3715: pa / g.yang gzhi / glang chen gyi ko rlon /
NK029(ha)001:3718: thod pa sko rlon tshal bu'i con pan /
NK029(ha)001:3719: sa ral dpung brgyan dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:3720: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK029(ha)001:3721: smin dbus su rak+ta'i thig le /
NK029(ha)001:3722: os ko la zhag gi zo ris te /
NK029(ha)001:3723: dur khrod chas brgyan kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:3724: khyad par yum la gzig gi lpags pa'i sham thabs can cher gtum zhing 'khros pa /
NK029(ha)001:3725: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:3726: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shu badz+ra krod+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK029(ha)001:3727: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:3728: zhes brjod pas yab yum gnyis kyi sbyor mtshams nas khro bo 'chol pa /
NK029(ha)001:3729: mtshon cha'i char 'beb pa dpag tu med pa 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:3730: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad gang /
NK029(ha)001:3731: bdud bgegs log par 'dren pa thams cad zil gyis mnan pas /
NK029(ha)001:3734: gsang ba'i dam bcas so so nas /
NK029(ha)001:3735: 'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK029(ha)001:3736: thams cad thugs rjes bkang zin gyis //
NK029(ha)001:3737: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK029(ha)001:3739: rdo rje khro bo'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK029(ha)001:3740: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK029(ha)001:3741: gdon gyur rigs rnams brlag par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:3742: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka mah+aa tsan+da sarba
NK029(ha)001:3743: 'adush+ta ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK029(ha)001:3744: h+aum h+aum phata / zhes brjod cing bskul bas khro bo'i tshogs rnams kyis /
NK029(ha)001:3745: gsang spyod lta bar mi dbang pa'i bgegs thams cad bsdig bskrad rlag par byas /
NK029(ha)001:3746: badz+ra pany+tsa ram yam kham khro bo'i tshogs rnams slar 'dus ste /
NK029(ha)001:3747: khro bo'i rang bzhin gyi rdo rje'i gur khang chen
NK029(ha)001:3748: por bltam pa'i phyi rol kun nas bskal pa'i me
NK029(ha)001:3750: rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs 'khrug pa'i ra ba gsum rims
NK029(ha)001:3751: nam mkha' klas pas gang pas mtshams bcad par gyur
NK029(ha)001:3752: / gsum pa gshegs pa bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:3753: badz+ra sa ma dzahyisa bla ma rigs 'dzin zhi khro
NK029(ha)001:3754: rgyal ba rab 'byam mngon du sad pa'i spyan sngar
NK029(ha)001:3755: / sems can kyi don du mchog gi byang chub
NK029(ha)001:3756: tshe 'di nyid kyis mngon du bya ba mnyam dran
NK029(ha)001:3757: / pas / tshe rab 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas ma 'tshal ste /
NK029(ha)001:3758: sdig pa mi dge ba'i las ci bgyis pa thams cad la gnong zhing 'gyod /
NK029(ha)001:3759: phyin chad srog la bab kyang mi bgyid /
NK029(ha)001:3760: sngar byas kyi gnyen por rnal 'byor gyis rim pa
NK029(ha)001:3761: la 'jug snyam pa'i sems bstan par mngon sum du
NK029(ha)001:3763: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK029(ha)001:3764: zla rgyas bzhin du spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK029(ha)001:3765: thugs rjes nyi gsal 'od bzhin snyoms mdzad pa //'dir gshegs bdag la dgongs shing bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3766: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK029(ha)001:3767: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga gtso //
NK029(ha)001:3768: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya che rol ba'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:3769: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:3770: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyi rnam sprul pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:3771: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK029(ha)001:3772: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya che yongs bkod de //
NK029(ha)001:3773: phyi nang gsang ba mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK029(ha)001:3774: kun tu bzang mo gsang ba'i b+ha ga la //
NK029(ha)001:3775: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rab 'byams ma lus kun //'du 'bral med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pa //
NK029(ha)001:3776: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi mnyes gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:3777: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK029(ha)001:3778: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas 'od gsal zhing //
NK029(ha)001:3779: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:3780: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dud /
NK029(ha)001:3781: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba la //
NK029(ha)001:3782: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK029(ha)001:3783: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //'byung dang 'byung gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK029(ha)001:3784: gsang chen rab dgyes gzugs can bdag nyid ma /
NK029(ha)001:3785: mkha' dbyings klong yangs pad+mo 'khyil ba la //
NK029(ha)001:3786: gnyis med thig le chen por 'od gsal zhing //
NK029(ha)001:3787: ma bcos spros med byang chub snying po'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:3788: cir yang snang ba bde chen g.yung drung lha //'du 'bral med pa gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK029(ha)001:3789: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK029(ha)001:3790: byang chub lcam bral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:3791: rdo rje lha mo tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag /
NK029(ha)001:3792: rigs lnga dpal chen khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK029(ha)001:3793: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:3794: ye shes sprul pa'i lha tshogs mang po dang //
NK029(ha)001:3795: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:3796: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes spyod ma //
NK029(ha)001:3797: phyi nang mkha' 'gro rnam 'byor ma yi tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:3798: dpang gyur rdo rje dam can dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3800: thugs rjes gdung 'tshob rigs 'dzin bdag cag gis //'gro ba'i don du byang chub sems skyed de //
NK029(ha)001:3801: bla med go 'phangs bgrod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:3802: bstan pa rgya mtsho'i so so'i 'dul khrims dang //
NK029(ha)001:3803: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor bsdom pa'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:3804: rdo rje 'da' dka' dam tshig gnyan gyi gter //
NK029(ha)001:3805: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK029(ha)001:3806: snga phyir mnos shing gnyer du smras so 'tshal //
NK029(ha)001:3807: yun du mi gtong 'da' bar mi bgyid cing //
NK029(ha)001:3808: don la gol shing ldog sems ma mchis kyang //
NK029(ha)001:3809: gdod bya long yod mnyam pa'i le lo yis /
NK029(ha)001:3810: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs chung pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:3811: shes bzhin mi ldan bag med dbang gyur ste //
NK029(ha)001:3812: bsgom la mi brtson bsnyen bsgrub g.yel la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:3813: tshor dang ma tshor ma rig dbang gis na //
NK029(ha)001:3814: ston pa'i bka' dang dam las 'das gyur ste //
NK029(ha)001:3815: rnal 'byor gang zhig dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:3816: skad cig tsam yang 'phrad par mi bya zhes //
NK029(ha)001:3817: bka' las byang zhing de ltar ma lcogs te //
NK029(ha)001:3818: gsang sgo 'chol bas dbye gsal dka' ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:3819: mngon shes chung pas skyon can ma rtogs ste //
NK029(ha)001:3820: nyams dang tshogs 'dres nyams pa bkang ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:3821: nyams dang snod min rnams la chos bshad dang //
NK029(ha)001:3822: nyams la mi 'dzem nyams pa'i skyon la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:3823: nyams grib skyon gyi gos par gyur to 'tshal //
NK029(ha)001:3824: tshe 'di'i rkyen dang yun gyis sgribs gyur rnams //
NK029(ha)001:3825: rang mnong 'gyod pa'i sems kyi mthol lo bshags //
NK029(ha)001:3826: byams pa'i thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:3827: gnyis med dbyings las mi 'gyur bdag bkod de //
NK029(ha)001:3828: dmigs med btang snyoms ngang la bzhugs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:3829: gnyis med don gyi tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3830: don dam brjod med spros las 'das pa la //
NK029(ha)001:3831: rnam rtog gang yang dmigs par mi 'gyur zhing //
NK029(ha)001:3832: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam gyi dbang gi na //
NK029(ha)001:3833: nongs pa mchis na rang gnong bzod par gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3834: bzhi pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:3835: lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos //
NK029(ha)001:3836: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa /
NK029(ha)001:3837: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rjes dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK029(ha)001:3838: srid pa gsum gyi gnyer gyur gcig pu pa //
NK029(ha)001:3839: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3840: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK029(ha)001:3841: rnal 'byor dbang phyug grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK029(ha)001:3842: lha dang lha min sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK029(ha)001:3843: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3844: bdag cag rgyal srid mtho rigs longs spyod dang //'dod
NK029(ha)001:3845: pa'i yon tan bdag grub ma lags ste //'gro la
NK029(ha)001:3846: snying brtse kho nas don brtson pa //'di la kun
NK029(ha)001:3847: mkhyen khyed ni dpang du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3848: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK029(ha)001:3849: bdag gis lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyi mkhyen //'phags mchog spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pas //
NK029(ha)001:3850: sun par mi bgyid mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK029(ha)001:3851: snying nas bdag gi khe dang grags la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:3852: g.yo dang zang zing sems kyis bstan spangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:3853: gzhan don sgrub pa gcig pu'i sems bzhag te //
NK029(ha)001:3854: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gis spyad //
NK029(ha)001:3855: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:3856: byang chub mchog tu bdag gi sems bskyed de //
NK029(ha)001:3857: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK029(ha)001:3858: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyis //
NK029(ha)001:3859: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK029(ha)001:3860: dum bu stong du bdag gis lus gtub kyang //
NK029(ha)001:3861: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK029(ha)001:3862: yi dam rgyal ba khyed ni yongs mi spongs //
NK029(ha)001:3863: rdo rje dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni //
NK029(ha)001:3864: rdo rje slob dpon rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK029(ha)001:3865: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la bzhugs pa rnams //
NK029(ha)001:3866: srog gi phyir yang mi btong ci nus bsrungs //'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin las //
NK029(ha)001:3867: bdag ni 'jig pa ci yang ma mchis ste //
NK029(ha)001:3868: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK029(ha)001:3869: phyi ma mthar thug bar du gnas par spro //
NK029(ha)001:3870: gzhan yang 'khor ba rnams su spyod pa na //
NK029(ha)001:3871: byang chub spyod pa brlabs chen bdag gi spyad //'gro drug sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK029(ha)001:3872: rang dbang du ni skye ba blangs par bgyi //
NK029(ha)001:3873: bdag ni yongs su bzung ba'i 'jig rten nam //
NK029(ha)001:3874: mya ngan 'das la sproo ba ma mchis ste //
NK029(ha)001:3875: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK029(ha)001:3876: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK029(ha)001:3877: srid pa yun ring dus su brtson pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:3878: byang chub sems dpa'i yi dam lags pa na //
NK029(ha)001:3879: ji srid ngan song stong bar ma gyur na //
NK029(ha)001:3880: de srid bdag gi skyo ba'i sems mi skye //
NK029(ha)001:3881: shes rab thabs kyi 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:3882: snying rje longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK029(ha)001:3883: sems can dmyal ba yi dwags gshen rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK029(ha)001:3884: lha'i dga' 'tshal lta bur blta bar gyis /
NK029(ha)001:3885: 'gro la thugs brtse dpal gyi mgur nas gsungs //
NK029(ha)001:3886: rnal 'byor dam chos bdud rtsi mchog rnams ni //
NK029(ha)001:3887: bdag gi 'jig rten thugs pa ma mchis bar //
NK029(ha)001:3888: ji ltar mtshams pa bzhin du rgyas par bgyi //
NK029(ha)001:3889: srid pa las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur ste //
NK029(ha)001:3890: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK029(ha)001:3891: me tshogs spu gri'i so la rgal nas ni //
NK029(ha)001:3892: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK029(ha)001:3893: bla med byang chub mchog du sems bskyed de //
NK029(ha)001:3894: sgrub pa mchog la bzhugs pa'i skye bo la //
NK029(ha)001:3895: tshe rabs rnams su mthu rtsal ci mchis kyang //
NK029(ha)001:3896: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu bskangs //
NK029(ha)001:3897: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub pa'i gegs gyur pa //
NK029(ha)001:3898: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK029(ha)001:3899: bdag gi zhi dang khro bo'i 'phrin las kyis //
NK029(ha)001:3900: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par bzhom par bgyi //
NK029(ha)001:3901: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla med dang //
NK029(ha)001:3902: rdo rje rgyal po khyed la brten pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:3903: sangs rgyas zhing sbyangs 'gro la sman slad du //
NK029(ha)001:3904: byang chub snying po bdag gi rtogs par bgyis //
NK029(ha)001:3905: bdag ni 'phags mchog phyag rgyas sngon sprul ste //
NK029(ha)001:3906: gal te skabs med 'chi ba'i dus byung tshe //
NK029(ha)001:3907: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK029(ha)001:3908: khyed kyi zhabs kyi drung du 'chi bar bgyi //
NK029(ha)001:3909: srid gsum sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed kyis mkhyen //
