NK029(ha)001:3910: dmyal sogs me dpung zhi bar bgyid lags so //
NK029(ha)001:3911: sems can don la myur du bdag mchis na //
NK029(ha)001:3912: dam pa rnams kyis nus mthu stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:3913: lnga pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3915: b+ha ga wan sa ma ya ho /
NK029(ha)001:3917: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:3918: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:3919: mthu rtsal 'byung pa'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:3920: byin gyis barlobasa pa'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:3921: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:3923: byin chen byin phobs bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:3924: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:3925: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:3926: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:3927: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum gis byin bsdus pas /
NK029(ha)001:3928: nam mkha' gang ba'i lha tshogs thams cad rang la thim ste /
NK029(ha)001:3929: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo byin gyis brlabs par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)001:3930: drug pa mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:3931: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ris phyi mchod rnams bsang /
NK029(ha)001:3932: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:3933: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK029(ha)001:3934: nga rdor sems su gsal ba'i thugs kha'i h+aum las a d+hu pu a gan rnams 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:3942: bud d+ha nam ga ga kham sa ma ya h+aum swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:3943: sh+ri badz+ra r+aa ga d+ha be d+hu /
NK029(ha)001:3945: a lo ke hrih g+han+he gan /
NK029(ha)001:3946: bsil chab ma la sogs pa'i mchod pa'i lha mo khrus zhong dang /
NK029(ha)001:3947: spos khang la sogs pa thogs pa nam mkha' gang ba rnams su gyur par bsam pas /
NK029(ha)001:3948: phyi mchod rnams byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)001:3950: ram yam kham stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK029(ha)001:3951: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud d+he badz+ra dz+nya na tsakra man+da la b+h+rum /
NK029(ha)001:3952: bdud rtsi'i snod gzhal yas khang du gsal ba'i dbus
NK029(ha)001:3953: su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte bar dri chen
NK029(ha)001:3954: la h+aum mum / shar du byang sems la lam /
NK029(ha)001:3955: lhor sha chen la swa mam /
NK029(ha)001:3956: nub tu rak+ta la am lam /
NK029(ha)001:3957: byang du dri chu la ha tam /
NK029(ha)001:3965: so so'i rigs kyi dril bu rnams su gyur /
NK029(ha)001:3970: dbus su mi skyod pa yab yum mthing kh+aa /
NK029(ha)001:3973: shar du rnam snang yab yum dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:3976: lhor rin 'byung yab yum gser po /
NK029(ha)001:3979: nub du snang mtha' yab yum dmar po /
NK029(ha)001:3982: byang du don yod grub pa yab yum ljang khu /
NK029(ha)001:3985: a nu ra ga ya mi /
NK029(ha)001:3986: a nu ra ga ho ham /
NK029(ha)001:3989: rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyi sbyor bas zhu ba las byung pa'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi /
NK029(ha)001:3990: gyi mtshan pa'i kha spyod rdo rje rgya gram gyi lte bar /
NK029(ha)001:3991: pad+ma ta krid badz+ra mah+aa kro d+ha h+ya g+h+ri wa h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:3992: rta mgrin dmar po pad+ma dang rgya gram 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:3993: lte ba yan chod thon pa /
NK029(ha)001:3994: rwa bzhi la shar du mi pham ma dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:3995: lhor khro gnyer ma ser mo zhags pa /
NK029(ha)001:3996: nub du ro lang ma dmar mo lcags sgrog /
NK029(ha)001:3997: byang shar du ral gcig ma ljang khu dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:3998: gyi 'od zer gyi 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi thams
NK029(ha)001:3999: cad kun dam tshig gi bdud rtsi la ro mnyam
NK029(ha)001:4000: par bsam la / g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gyis rdo rje gzung bas /
NK029(ha)001:4003: sarba pan tsa a mri ta h+aum hrihthah zhes bzlas shing /
NK029(ha)001:4004: mthar g.yon bskor du dkrugs ste /
NK029(ha)001:4006: zhes brjod pas yab yum bzhi bdud rtsi la thim par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:4007: gtor ma ram yam kham stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK029(ha)001:4008: b+h+rum pad+ma b+ha lim ta bi shwa tsakra b+h+rum /
NK029(ha)001:4009: gtor gzhong pad+ma'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du /
NK029(ha)001:4010: gtor rdzas 'dod yon gyi rnam pa /
NK029(ha)001:4011: ma tshang ba med pa la /
NK029(ha)001:4012: s+pha sam b+ha lamngii ta te dzo b+ha lamngi ta
NK029(ha)001:4013: b+ha la b+aa rgya gu h+ya sa ma ye swah+aa
NK029(ha)001:4014: / lan bdun brjod pas 'dod pa drug gi lha
NK029(ha)001:4015: mo nam mkha' gang ba 'dod yon gyi rnam pa
NK029(ha)001:4016: ma tshang ba med par spro ba'i bdag nyid du
NK029(ha)001:4017: / gyur par bsam / rak+ta ram yam kham /
NK029(ha)001:4018: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las b+h+rum /
NK029(ha)001:4020: dmar gyi dung chen yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du /
NK029(ha)001:4024: mah+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum hrihthah rak+ta'i rgya
NK029(ha)001:4025: mtsho rba rlabs 'khrugs pa nam mkha' gang bar bsam
NK029(ha)001:4026: / dngos gzhi la bdun gyi dang po sems bskyed pa la gnyis las /
NK029(ha)001:4027: kun rdzob sems bskyed pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:4028: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK029(ha)001:4029: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang /
NK029(ha)001:4030: rtog pa'i dbang gi 'khor ba las //
NK029(ha)001:4031: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:4032: gnyis pa don dam sems bskyed ni /
NK029(ha)001:4033: e ma ho ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)001:4034: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //
NK029(ha)001:4035: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK029(ha)001:4036: skyes pa nyid ni skye ba med //
NK029(ha)001:4037: e ma ho ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)001:4038: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //'gag pa med
NK029(ha)001:4039: las thams cad 'gag /'gag pa nyid na 'gag pa
NK029(ha)001:4040: med // e ma ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)001:4041: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //
NK029(ha)001:4042: gnas pa med la thams cad gnas //
NK029(ha)001:4043: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK029(ha)001:4044: e ma ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)001:4045: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK029(ha)001:4046: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK029(ha)001:4047: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK029(ha)001:4048: e ma ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)001:4049: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //'gro 'ong med
NK029(ha)001:4051: med // gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gsum ni /
NK029(ha)001:4052: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK029(ha)001:4053: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK029(ha)001:4054: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK029(ha)001:4055: de phyir dngos po dngos med pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4056: zhes pa'i don sgom pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:4057: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:4058: de bzhin nyid ni spros med kyang //
NK029(ha)001:4059: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK029(ha)001:4060: sems can kun la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:4061: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha'i bsgom //
NK029(ha)001:4063: dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK029(ha)001:4065: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK029(ha)001:4066: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK029(ha)001:4067: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK029(ha)001:4068: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK029(ha)001:4069: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya /
NK029(ha)001:4071: sems nyid a dkar po'i rnam par bsgom pa de rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK029(ha)001:4072: gsum pa rten gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:4073: sems nyid a dkar po gsal ba las /
NK029(ha)001:4074: e yam wam sum lam ram rnams chad /
NK029(ha)001:4077: e las nam mkha' chos 'byung 'jam klas pa /
NK029(ha)001:4078: de'i steng du yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sngon po gzhu'i dbyibs can /
NK029(ha)001:4079: de'i steng du bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar po bzlum po /
NK029(ha)001:4080: de'i steng du sum las sa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi gser po /
NK029(ha)001:4081: de'i steng du lam las ri rab rin po che sna bzhi'i rang bzhin zur bzhi pa /
NK029(ha)001:4082: ram las me'i 'khor yug nam mkha'i mtha' klas par 'khor ba /
NK029(ha)001:4083: ri rab kyi steng du b+hum /
NK029(ha)001:4087: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK029(ha)001:4088: yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:4089: lhag pa'i ye shes glo bur gyis mdzes pa /
NK029(ha)001:4090: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad /
NK029(ha)001:4091: so so ma yin zhing ngo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes kun tu 'khyil ba /
NK029(ha)001:4092: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes rin po che'i dbyibs dang /
NK029(ha)001:4093: gzhi dang brgyan dang kha dog dang bkod pa tshad med pas 'phags pa /
NK029(ha)001:4094: zag pa med pa'i 'dod yon gyi rnam pa ma
NK029(ha)001:4095: tshang ba med pa thams cad kyi nam mkha'i mthas
NK029(ha)001:4096: klas pas gang ba'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:4097: seng ge brgyad kyi bteg pa'i rin po che'i khri bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:4098: pam pad+ma man+dala la sur+ya man+da la /
NK029(ha)001:4100: pad nyi zla ba'i gdan cha shas yongs su rdzogs par gyur /
NK029(ha)001:4101: bzhi ba lha bskyed pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:4102: rang gi sems nyid ar gsal ba zla ba'i steng du babs /
NK029(ha)001:4103: yongs su gyur pa las h+aum mthing nag ye shes lnga'i 'od zer 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)001:4106: badz+ra h+aum de rdo rje gyur /
NK029(ha)001:4109: rdo rje yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)001:4110: rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog mthing kha mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal /
NK029(ha)001:4111: zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas dang po rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin zhing /
NK029(ha)001:4112: g.yon dang po dril bu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4113: bar pa gnyis kyis 'khor lo rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4114: tha ma gnyis kyi pad+ma dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4115: mnyam pa'i dkyil mo dkrung gis bzhugs pa //
NK029(ha)001:4116: de'i thugs kha nas g.yon gyi barla steng su mum chad /
NK029(ha)001:4121: mum d+ha t+wi shwa ri yab kyi g.yon phyogs su
NK029(ha)001:4122: nye ba'i spang du yum rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang
NK029(ha)001:4123: phyug ma sngon mo phyag g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas
NK029(ha)001:4125: g.yon rdo rje thugs khar 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4126: brtul zhugs gyi dkyil mo dkrung gis 'khril ba /
NK029(ha)001:4127: gnyis ka'ang dar la'i bstod g.yogs cod pan zi 'dir gar gyi phu rung can /
NK029(ha)001:4128: rin po che'i dbus brgyan snyan cha mgul brgyan sen mo do //
NK029(ha)001:4129: phyag gdub zhabs gdub ska rag do shal rnams kyis mdzes par spras pa /
NK029(ha)001:4130: mnyen cug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK029(ha)001:4131: gsal mtsher lhun sdug gzi sbyin ldan pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:4132: zhi ba'i nyams dgus rgyas pa /
NK029(ha)001:4133: 'od zer kha dog drug re re yang /
NK029(ha)001:4134: bye ba phrag drug du 'phro ba'i klong na /
NK029(ha)001:4135: bde stong gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4136: rang gi lus rdor sems yab yum du gsal ba'i /
NK029(ha)001:4137: yab kyi gtsug gtor gyi rtsal /
NK029(ha)001:4139: rnam snang dkar po g.yas 'khor lo thugs khar 'dzin cing /
NK029(ha)001:4140: g.yon des mtshan pa'i dril bu skur rten pa /
NK029(ha)001:4141: lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4143: kun tu bzang po mthing kha /
NK029(ha)001:4144: mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK029(ha)001:4147: rin 'byung gser po g.yas rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4148: g.yon des mtshan pa'i dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4149: rkang pa gnyis kyi 'doms rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4151: don 'grub ljang khu g.yas ral gri /
NK029(ha)001:4152: g.yon des mtshan pa'i dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4155: snang mtha' dmar po g.yas pad+ma /
NK029(ha)001:4156: g.yon des mtshan pa'i dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4157: kun tu bzang mo rdo rje dkyil mo dkrungs dang /
NK029(ha)001:4158: gzhan rnams mnyam pa'i dkyil dkrung gi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4159: mig gi 'doms rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4161: sa snying dkar po g.yas rin po che'i myu gu 'dzin cing /
NK029(ha)001:4162: g.yon dril bu skur brten pa /
NK029(ha)001:4163: g.yon gyi cha la mee d+ha ra ni swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4164: byams pa dkar ser g.yas klu shing /
NK029(ha)001:4166: rna ba'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4167: badz+ra ku ru pany+tsa hrih phyag rdor mthing kha g.yas rdo rje g.yon dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4169: tha lhim ni swa ram b+aa ya /
NK029(ha)001:4170: sgribs sel dmar ser g.yas chos kyi 'khor lo /
NK029(ha)001:4174: nam snying ser po g.yas ral gri g.yon dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4175: g.yon gyi cha la h+aum pa r+aa dz+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4176: kun bzang dmar ljang g.yas rin po che'i snye ma /
NK029(ha)001:4178: lce'i 'doms rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4180: spyan ras gzigs dmar g.yas pad+ma dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:4183: mum sh+ri a ram g+aa y+aa s+w+aah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4184: 'jam dpal dkar ljang g.yas ud pa la /
NK029(ha)001:4186: brgyad ka'ang zhabs g.yas cung zad brkyang pa'i phyed dkyil kyis bzhugs pa lag mthil g.yas la /
NK029(ha)001:4187: h+aum ya man+ta krid phata gshin rje smug nag mi mgo kha gdang pa 'dzin pa g.yon la /
NK029(ha)001:4189: stobs po che gser nag thod pa rdo rjes mnon thabs su 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4193: rgya gram gnon thabs su 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4196: rta mgrin dmar nag thod pa sprul gyis dkris pa 'dzin ba /
NK029(ha)001:4197: bzhi ka'ang g.yas su phyogs pa'i gyad kyi dor thabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //'tshogs dmar mu ne trim swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4198: lha yi thub pa dkar po pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4201: lha min gyi thub pa mthing kha go cha 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4204: mi'i thub pa gser po gseg shang 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4205: lte bar mu ne pram swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4206: byol song gi thub pa dmar nag /
NK029(ha)001:4208: mgrin par mu ne k+sham swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4209: yi dwags kyi thub pa gser nag /
NK029(ha)001:4210: rin po che'i sgrmo bu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4213: dmyal ba'i thub pa du kha me chu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4214: drug kha'ang 'greng thabs su gshegs pa'i tshul can /
NK029(ha)001:4215: yum rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'i gtsug gtor gyi rtse la /
NK029(ha)001:4217: spyan ma dkar mo g.yas 'khor los mtshan pa'i dril bu bskur brten cing /
NK029(ha)001:4219: lag pa gnyis kyis 'dom rtsi'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4220: a a a badz+ra b+ha tri sa man+ta a /
NK029(ha)001:4222: thal mo thugs khar sbyar ba /
NK029(ha)001:4225: m+aa ma ki ser mo g.yas rin po ches mtshan pa'i dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4227: rkang pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4229: dam tshig sgrol ma ljang khu g.yas ral gris mtshan pa'i dril /
NK029(ha)001:4232: gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas pad+mas mtshan pa'i dril /
NK029(ha)001:4234: kun tu bzang mo pad+ma'i dkyil dkrungs dang /
NK029(ha)001:4235: yum bzhi brtul zhugs kyi dkyil mo dkrungs du bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4236: mig gi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4237: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)001:4238: sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4240: dzahd+hu pe pra be sha gdugs spos ma dkar ser /
NK029(ha)001:4242: rna ba'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4243: tram ma le sa ma ya ho /
NK029(ha)001:4244: 'phreng ba ma gser mo rin po che'i 'phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4250: hrih girti ra ga ho ha /
NK029(ha)001:4251: glu ma dmar mo pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4253: bam d+ai pa pu khi ni /
NK029(ha)001:4254: mar me ma dmar ljang mar me'i sdong bu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4255: lce'i 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)001:4256: a ni r+ya ra ga ya m+ai /
NK029(ha)001:4257: gar ma ljang khu gar gyi phu rung 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4259: ho gan+te tsit+ta dri chab ma dkar ljang dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4260: brgyad ka'ang zhabs g.yon pa bstan gtsugs shing /
NK029(ha)001:4261: g.yas pa dkyil dkrungs phyed pas bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4262: lag thil g.yas mah+aa badz+ra d+ha ra mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ra dz+wi la sh+ai h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4263: lcags kyu ma smug nag lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4264: g.yon la mah+aa rat+na d+ha ra mah+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK029(ha)001:4265: zhags pa ma ser nag zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4267: mah+aa karma d+ha ra mah+aa kro d+hi sh+aa ri dz+aa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4268: dril bu ma ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4269: g.yon la ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro di sh+aahr dz+ai la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4270: lcags sgrogs ma dmar nag lcags sgrogs 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:4271: bzhi ka'ang g.yon du phyogs pa'i gyad kyi dor stabs kyi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4276: kun bzang yab yum rnams zhi ba'i brgyan chas bcu gsum gyis mdzes shing /
NK029(ha)001:4277: tshul dgu'i nyams kyis rgyas pa /
NK029(ha)001:4278: thub pa drug gtsug gtor dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)001:4279: tshangs par spyod pa'i cha lugs can /
NK029(ha)001:4280: khro bo yab yum thod pa dang sbrul gyis brgyan can /
NK029(ha)001:4281: zhing chen gyi stod g.yogs dang /
NK029(ha)001:4282: stag gi lpags pa'i sham thabs gsol ba /
NK029(ha)001:4283: bskal pa'i me'i klong na bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4284: thams cad kyang rdo rje sems dpa' snang stong sgyu
NK029(ha)001:4285: 'phrul d+r+wa pa'i rang bzhin gyi sku gsung thugs mi
NK029(ha)001:4286: zad brgyan gyis 'khor lo'i rnam par dag pa /
NK029(ha)001:4287: rang rang gi srog gi gor rang rang 'dra ba'i
NK029(ha)001:4288: ye shes sems dpa' mtshon gang pa re re dang
NK029(ha)001:4289: bcas pa'o // lnga pa dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:4292: bstan par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:4296: bzlas pa byed pa rnams 'og bum bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)001:4298: thun mongs du shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:4299: gnyis pa bum bskyed la gzhi ste /
NK029(ha)001:4300: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:4301: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:4303: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK029(ha)001:4304: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK029(ha)001:4305: dngos rnams nyid nas dngos med pa /
NK029(ha)001:4306: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das /
NK029(ha)001:4307: shes chos kyi dbyings sems nyid de kho na nyid /
NK029(ha)001:4308: rig pas rtog shing nyams su myong ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:4310: sems can rnams la snying brtse'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:4311: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:4312: zhes de ltar ma rtogs pa'i nam mkhas khyab tshad kyi /
NK029(ha)001:4313: sems can la sgyu ma lta bu'i snying rje phyogs rigs med par nam mkha' lta bur bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:4314: gsum pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK029(ha)001:4315: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya /
NK029(ha)001:4316: rab tu brtan gyur a dkar la /
NK029(ha)001:4318: snying rje dbyer med pa'i ngo bo yi ge a
NK029(ha)001:4319: dkar po gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan par
NK029(ha)001:4320: bsgom / bzhi pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhi ste /
NK029(ha)001:4323: byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)001:4326: brten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:4327: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4328: dang po ni rgyu'i yig a las 'og tu e 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)001:4329: chos 'byung drug gsum mthing nag tshad dpag tu med pa /
NK029(ha)001:4330: de'i steng du yam 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)001:4331: rlung gi dkyil 'khor zla gam sra zhing mkhreg pa du kha /
NK029(ha)001:4333: bam 'phros pa las chu'i dkyil 'khor zlum po dkar po mtha' ma bum pas mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4334: de'i steng du lam 'phros pa las gser gyi sa gzhi zlum po gser po /
NK029(ha)001:4335: tha ma bum pa rdo rjes mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4336: de'i steng du sum 'phros pa las //
NK029(ha)001:4337: rin po che sna bzhi la grub pa'i ri'i rgyal po ri rab gru bzhi pa /
NK029(ha)001:4339: gling bzhi gling phran mtsho lcags ri dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:4340: de'i steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor du gyur ste /
NK029(ha)001:4343: phyed ri rab kyi steng du /
NK029(ha)001:4344: me'i gur khang du gyur de'i nang du h+aum 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)001:4345: rdo rje'i gur khang 'og gzhi sna tshogs rdo rje leb mo lte ba gru bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:4346: ra rtse gsum gsum dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4350: zhes rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i phyi bum pa'i dbyibs /
NK029(ha)001:4351: nang gzhal yas kyi khang pa gru bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:4352: sgo bzhi steng pad rag gi rtsigs pa lnga rims /
NK029(ha)001:4353: de la shar dkar po 'khor los mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4354: lho ser po rin po ches mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4355: nub dmar po pad+mas mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4356: byang ljang khu ral griis mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4358: shar bu la dra ba dang dra phyed pa 'phyang ba /
NK029(ha)001:4359: nang ka ba brgyad kyi btegs pa'i gdung bzhi la sogs pas /
NK029(ha)001:4360: byang chub chen po'i mchod rten gyi dbyibs legs par phub ste /
NK029(ha)001:4361: bang rim bzhi la rdo rje'i gyo lding /
NK029(ha)001:4362: phyi'i rtse la mda' yab dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:4366: sgo khang phyi zur bzhi nas ka ba bzhi bzhis bteg pa'i rta babs rnam bu /
NK029(ha)001:4367: bzhi pa'am brgyad kyi mdzes pa /
NK029(ha)001:4369: pad+ma chos 'khor gdugs ri dwags dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:4370: gzhal yas khang de'i phyi rol du /
NK029(ha)001:4371: ta la'i shing dpag bsam gyi shing la gser gyi nyag thag gis bres shing //
NK029(ha)001:4372: dril bu dang dril bu g.yer kha 'chang ba /
NK029(ha)001:4374: g.yu'i ne'u sing me tog zlum rtsigs dkar po'i tshal /
NK029(ha)001:4375: gzhal yas khang de'i nang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:4380: gru chad phyogs mdog /'khor lo'i dbus su seng ge brgyad la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:4381: rtsibs bzhi la glang po che dang /
NK029(ha)001:4384: shang shang la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:4385: sgo bzhir nyi ma bzhi'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:4387: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i gzhal yas khang bskyed pa la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)001:4389: thugs phyag mtshan gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)001:4391: dang po ni rgyu'i yi ge a dkar po las k+sha sngon po byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:4392: a dang k+sha sbyor ba'i khyad par las /
NK029(ha)001:4393: dbus kyi gdan gyi steng du tha dang /
NK029(ha)001:4395: shar du ta dang ta dkar po gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4396: lhor da dang da ser po gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4397: nub du d+ha dang d+ha dmar po gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4398: byang du na dang na ljang khu gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4399: shar sgor nga dang sha dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:4400: lho sgor nya dang sha ser po /
NK029(ha)001:4401: nub sgor ma dang a dmar po /
NK029(ha)001:4402: byang sgor dang ha ljang khu /
NK029(ha)001:4403: a dang k+sha gnyis dbus kyi tha tha la thim /
NK029(ha)001:4405: sems can ngag gi sgrib pa byang //
NK029(ha)001:4406: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)001:4407: phyag mtshan bcu dang brgyad du gyur //
NK029(ha)001:4408: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)001:4409: shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)001:4410: lhor rin chen dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)001:4411: byang du ral gri dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)001:4412: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu //
NK029(ha)001:4413: lho sgor rdo rje dbyug pa dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)001:4414: nub sgor pad+ma dang dbyug pa lcags sgrog /
NK029(ha)001:4415: byang sgor rgya gram dbyug pa dang dril bu //'od 'phros bde gshegs thugs la mchod //
NK029(ha)001:4416: sems can yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK029(ha)001:4417: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)001:4418: phra mo bcu dang brgyad du gyur //'od 'phros bde gshegs sku la mchod //
NK029(ha)001:4419: sems can lus kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK029(ha)001:4420: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)001:4421: yongs rdzogs bcu dang brgyad du gyur //
NK029(ha)001:4422: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig mum d+ha du shwa ri /
NK029(ha)001:4423: dbus su kun tu bzang po dang /
NK029(ha)001:4424: mi skyod pa dbyer med pa sku mdog mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhal g.yas dkar /
NK029(ha)001:4426: dbus mthing sa la ral pa'i thor gtsugs nag po
NK029(ha)001:4427: 'gying pa phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje
NK029(ha)001:4428: dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4429: g.yas bar pa na 'khor lo 'og ma rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4432: phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyii me 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)001:4433: zhabs snyoms pa'i dkyil dkrungs gis bzhugs pa //
NK029(ha)001:4434: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4435: dpe byad byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4436: yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma sku mdog yab dang
NK029(ha)001:4437: mthun pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)001:4438: cing / g.yon dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4439: dzi na dzig lam ste sha ra te /
NK029(ha)001:4440: shar du rnam par snang mdzad dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)001:4443: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4445: tha ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4448: swa rat+na d+h+rig mam ha ra ti /
NK029(ha)001:4450: rin chen 'byung ldan sku mdog ser po /
NK029(ha)001:4453: phyag dang po gnyis rin po che dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4454: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:4458: am a ro lig pyam r+aa ga ra ti /
NK029(ha)001:4460: snang ba mtha' yas dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug zhal g.yas dkar /
NK029(ha)001:4462: phyag dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4463: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:4465: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4467: ham pra dz+nya d+h+rig tam badz+ra ra ti /
NK029(ha)001:4468: zhes byang du don yod grub pa /
NK029(ha)001:4471: phyag dang po gnyis ral gri dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa //
NK029(ha)001:4472: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:4474: g.yon par ma rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4476: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag kyang ral pa'i mthor btsugs nag po 'gying pa /
NK029(ha)001:4477: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4478: dpe byad bzang po brgyad bcu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4480: brtul zhugs kyi dkyil dkrung gis rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4481: yum thams cad sku mdog yab dang 'dra ba /
NK029(ha)001:4483: phyag g.yas pa yab la 'khyud cing /
NK029(ha)001:4485: yab yum bcu po de rnams ni /
NK029(ha)001:4486: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin te /
NK029(ha)001:4488: spyan gcig gis gcig la gzigs so //
NK029(ha)001:4490: badz+ra d+ha ra mah+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4491: shar sgor khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed dang yum rdo rje lcags kyu ma /
NK029(ha)001:4492: sku mdog mthing nag zhal cig phyag gnyis spyan gsum mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4493: yab kyi phyag g.yas na thod dbyug g.yon thod khrag /
NK029(ha)001:4494: yum gyi phyag na lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4495: dpal chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4496: phung po'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4497: h+aum pra dz+nya ta krid phata /
NK029(ha)001:4498: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4500: lho sgor khro bo chen po stobs po che dang /
NK029(ha)001:4501: yum rdo rje zhags pa ma sku mdog gser nag yab kyi g.yas na rdo rje dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)001:4503: yum gyi phyag na zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4504: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4506: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4508: khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK029(ha)001:4509: yum rdo rje lcags sgrog ma /
NK029(ha)001:4511: yab kyi phyag g.yas na pad+ma'i thod dbyug sbrul gyis dkris pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4512: yum gyi phyag na lcags sgrog bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4513: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4514: h+aum big nan ta krid phata /
NK029(ha)001:4515: karma d+ha ra kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4516: ces byang sgor khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:4517: yum rdo rje dril bu sku mdog ljang nag yab kyi g.yas rdo rje rgya gram gyis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4518: yum gyi phyag na dril bu 'khril ba lha'i bu'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4519: khro bo yab yum de rnams ni rdo rje'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)001:4520: kun kyang spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4521: chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4522: g.yon na thod pa khrag gis bkang ba bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4523: de ni dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i mngon rtogs so //
NK029(ha)001:4524: yang na dkyil 'khor 'bring po ltar na /
NK029(ha)001:4525: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:4528: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis rten gzhal yas khang la /
NK029(ha)001:4530: zhes pa la sogs gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:4531: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus 'khor lo'i lte ba zlum po mthing kha la /
NK029(ha)001:4532: rtsibs bzhi ser po byung pa /
NK029(ha)001:4534: de'i phyi rol mu khyud rdo rje'i ra bas brgyan te /
NK029(ha)001:4535: de'i phyir rol grub chad bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)001:4537: de'i phyi rol lha rnams bsgo bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4538: de nas gdan sting ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:4539: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan /
NK029(ha)001:4540: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK029(ha)001:4541: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK029(ha)001:4542: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK029(ha)001:4544: dbus su mi 'jigs pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i dbus
NK029(ha)001:4545: su seng ge brgyad kyi khri 'byung par 'gyur te
NK029(ha)001:4546: / shar du stobs bcu dang ldan rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4547: glang po che brgyad kyi khri byung pa /
NK029(ha)001:4548: lhor rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4550: nub du dbang bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4551: rma bya brgyad kyi khri byung /
NK029(ha)001:4552: byang du 'phrin las bzhi'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4553: shang shang brgyad kyi khri byung ngo //
NK029(ha)001:4554: de dag gi bar mtshams su rin po che'i ka bas brgyan pa la /
NK029(ha)001:4555: rin po che'i khri'i steng na mu tig gi dra bas g.yogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4556: de'i steng pad+ma dang 'dab ma stong dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4559: rtsibs 'chan bzhi grub chad bzhi dang brgyad la /
NK029(ha)001:4560: rin po che'i khri pad zla nyi ma sum brtsegs dang ldan pa re re /
NK029(ha)001:4562: sgo bzhir bdud bzhi'i steng na nyi ma'o //
NK029(ha)001:4564: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)001:4566: thugs phyag mtshan gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)001:4569: a dkar po las k+sha sngon po byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:4570: a dang k+sha'i khyad par la yi ge bzhi bcu byung ste /
NK029(ha)001:4571: dbus tha dang tha sngon po gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4572: shar du ta dang ta dkar po gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4573: lhor da dang da ser po gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4574: nub tu d+ha dang d+ha dmar po gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4575: byang du na dang na ljang khu gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4577: lho nub du kha dang tsha nub byang du ga dang dza /
NK029(ha)001:4578: byang shar du g+ha dang dz+nya /
NK029(ha)001:4579: yang shar lho'i gru chad la sa dang ya /
NK029(ha)001:4580: lho nub tu pha dang wam /
NK029(ha)001:4581: nub byang du ba dang ra /
NK029(ha)001:4582: byang shar du b+ha dang la /
NK029(ha)001:4594: gnyis pa thugs phyag mtshan ni /
NK029(ha)001:4596: sems can ngag gi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK029(ha)001:4597: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)001:4598: phyag mtshan bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur //
NK029(ha)001:4599: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)001:4600: shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)001:4601: nub du pad+ma dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)001:4602: byang du ral gri dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)001:4604: rin po che'i myu gu dang me long /
NK029(ha)001:4605: lho nub du ral gri dang rin po che'i 'phreng ba /
NK029(ha)001:4606: nub byang pad+ma dkar po dang pi wam /
NK029(ha)001:4607: byang shar du rdo rje dang gar gyi lag pa /
NK029(ha)001:4608: shar lho'i gru chad la klu shing dang gdug spos /
NK029(ha)001:4609: lho nub chos kyi 'khor lo dang me tog /
NK029(ha)001:4610: nub byang du rin po che'i snye ma dang mar me /
NK029(ha)001:4611: byang shar du u pa la dang dri cha /
NK029(ha)001:4612: shar du rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK029(ha)001:4616: lho bsreg shang dang lhung bzed /
NK029(ha)001:4617: nub byang du chos kyi glegs bam /
NK029(ha)001:4618: lho nub du rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4619: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu /
NK029(ha)001:4620: lho sgor rdo rje dbyug pa dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)001:4621: nub sgor pad+ma'i dbyug pa dang lcags sgrog /
NK029(ha)001:4622: byang sgor rgya gram dang dbyug pa dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4623: gsum pa sku phyag rgya'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK029(ha)001:4625: sems can yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK029(ha)001:4626: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)001:4627: phra mo bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur //'od 'phros bde gshegs sku la mchod //
NK029(ha)001:4628: sems can lus kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK029(ha)001:4629: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)001:4630: yongs rdzogs bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur //
NK029(ha)001:4634: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes las byung pa'i rtags su sku mdog mthing nag /
NK029(ha)001:4638: dbu ral pa'i mthor gtsugs nag po 'gyings pa /
NK029(ha)001:4639: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)001:4640: dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4641: g.yas bar ma 'khor lo //'og ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4644: phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)001:4645: zhabs mnyam pa'i dkyil mo dkrung gi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4646: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4647: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4648: yum rdo rje dbyings dbyug ma yab dang mthun pa /
NK029(ha)001:4654: shar du rnam par snang mdzad me long lta bu'i
NK029(ha)001:4655: ye shes las 'byung ba'i rtags su sku mdog dkar
NK029(ha)001:4659: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4660: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:4661: tha ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4664: swa rat+na d+h+rig mam mo ha ra ti /
NK029(ha)001:4665: zhes lho phyogs su rin chen 'byung ldan mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las byung ba'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4666: sku mdog gser po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)001:4669: phyag dang po gnyis rin po che dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4670: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:4673: pyam ra ga ti zhes nub phyogs su snang ba
NK029(ha)001:4674: mtha' yas so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes las byung
NK029(ha)001:4675: ba'i rtags su / sku mdog dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)001:4678: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis pad+ma dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4679: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:4681: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4685: zhes byang du don yon grub pa /
NK029(ha)001:4686: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes las byung ba'i rtags /
NK029(ha)001:4690: phyag dang po gnyis pa ral gri dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4691: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:4693: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4695: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag ral pa'i thor gtsug nag po 'gying pa /
NK029(ha)001:4696: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4697: dpe byad bzang brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4698: zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyi dkyil mo dkrung gis rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4699: yum thams cad sku mdog yab dang 'dra ba /
NK029(ha)001:4700: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4701: g.yon pa dril bu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4702: yab yum bcu po de rnams ni langs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)001:4703: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4704: yab yum zhal sbyor byas shing /
NK029(ha)001:4705: spyan gcig gis gcig la gzigs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4706: sems dpa' yab yum bskyed pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:4708: h+aum la s+ya sa ma ya stam /
NK029(ha)001:4709: zhes shar lho dpal ka la /
NK029(ha)001:4710: sa'i snying po sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4711: yab kyi phyag g.yas ni rin po che'i myu gu /
NK029(ha)001:4712: g.yon na skyabs sbyin yang na dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4713: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyi me long /
NK029(ha)001:4714: zhabs phyed dkrung gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4715: yab yum zhal sbyor du bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4716: yab yum de gnyis ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnam
NK029(ha)001:4717: par snang mdzad kyi thugs dang sku la 'byung pa'o
NK029(ha)001:4719: tram ma le sa ma ya ho //
NK029(ha)001:4720: zhes lho nub kyi rtsibs 'chan la nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK029(ha)001:4721: rin po che'i 'phreng ba ma sku mdog gser mo //
NK029(ha)001:4722: yab kyi g.yas na ral gri /
NK029(ha)001:4723: yum gyi g.yas na rin po che'i 'phreng ba bsnams ste yab kyi dbu la thad bcings pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4724: hri ha ho pad+ma b+ha d+ha ma /
NK029(ha)001:4725: hri g+hirti ra g+ha ya ho //
NK029(ha)001:4726: zhes nub byang gi rtsibs bar ma la //
NK029(ha)001:4727: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
NK029(ha)001:4728: lha mo dbyangs mkhan ma sku mdog dmar po /
NK029(ha)001:4729: yab kyi g.yas na pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4730: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyi chos kyi pi wam brdeb pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4731: dzem gu ru pa na hri /
NK029(ha)001:4732: a nirti ra ga ya mi /
NK029(ha)001:4733: zhes byang shar gyi rtsibs bar ma la phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)001:4734: lha mo gar ma sku mdog ljang khu /
NK029(ha)001:4735: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4736: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis gar gyi lag pa bsgyur
NK029(ha)001:4737: nas zhal zas ro mchog rgya dang ldan pa yab
NK029(ha)001:4738: la stobs pa / don yod grub pa'i thugs dang sku la 'byung ba'o /
NK029(ha)001:4739: me d+ha ra ni swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4740: dza du pe pra be sha zhes shar lho'i gru chad la /
NK029(ha)001:4741: byams pa dang gdug spos ma sku mdog dkar ser /
NK029(ha)001:4742: yab kyi phyag na klu shing dang /
NK029(ha)001:4744: yum gyi phyag na gdug spos bsnams so //
NK029(ha)001:4745: thing lha ni swa da b+ha ya swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4747: zhes lho nub kyi gru chad la sgrib pa rnam par sel ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:4748: lho me tog ma sku mdog ser mo /
NK029(ha)001:4749: yab kyi phyag na chos kyi 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4750: yum gyi phyag na me tog 'phreng ba bsnams so //
NK029(ha)001:4751: h+aum swa ra tsa ya swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4752: bam ti pa pu ke ni /
NK029(ha)001:4753: zhes nub byang gi gru chad la kun tu bzang po dang /
NK029(ha)001:4754: lha mo mar me ma sku mdog dmar mo //
NK029(ha)001:4755: yab kyi phyag na rin po che'i snye ma bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4756: yum gyi phyag na mar me bsnams so //
NK029(ha)001:4757: mum sh+ri am ra ga ye swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:4759: zhes byang shar gyi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)001:4760: 'jam dpal gzhon nu gyur pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:4761: lha mo dri chab ma sku mdog ljang khu //
NK029(ha)001:4762: yab kyi phyag na u pa la bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4763: yum gyi phyag gnyis na dri chab bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4764: sems dpa' yab yum de rnams ni kun kyang ral pa'i thor gtsugs mnga' ba /
NK029(ha)001:4765: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4766: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4767: zhabs phyed dkrung gi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4768: yab yum zhal sbyor du gnas te /
NK029(ha)001:4769: thugs rjes sems can thams cad la bu gcig pa la ma byams pa ltar sems ste /
NK029(ha)001:4770: yab yum de rnams ni mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK029(ha)001:4771: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum zhes pas shar du
NK029(ha)001:4772: bcom ldan 'das byed pa po yid kun tu bzang
NK029(ha)001:4773: po sku mdog sngon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis phyag
NK029(ha)001:4774: mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya'i dkyil na /
NK029(ha)001:4775: rdo rje dkar po brtsegs pa la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)001:4776: zhabs mnyam par bzhag pa'i dkyil mo dkrung gis pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4777: nub tu a a a badz+ra sa man+ta zhes pas
NK029(ha)001:4778: chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas thams cad gnas
NK029(ha)001:4779: su dag pa'i yum kun tu bzang mo //
NK029(ha)001:4780: shes bya'i bag chags dag pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4781: sku mdog dkar mo phyag gnyis chos 'byung gi phyag rgya byas ste /
NK029(ha)001:4782: gdan pad+ma'i steng na zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i dkyil dkrung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4783: yab yum de gnyis ni chos kyi sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)001:4784: dbyings mkhyen pa dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4785: yum gyi zhal shar du gzigs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4786: mkhyen pa'i shes bya dngos po thams cad dbyings su gzigs pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4787: yab kyi zhal nub tu gzigs so //
NK029(ha)001:4789: shar lho lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wammm bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4791: byang du lha ma yin gyi thub pa ljang nag g.yas ral gri /
NK029(ha)001:4794: lhor mi'i thub pa ser po g.yas bsreg shang /
NK029(ha)001:4797: nub byang du byol song gi thub pa ljang ser spyi bo nas chos kyi glegs bam khur ba /
NK029(ha)001:4798: ma rig pa'i mun khang 'byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:4800: lho nub du yi dwags kyi thub pa ljang gser
NK029(ha)001:4801: phyag na rin po che'i za ma tog bsnams pa'i
NK029(ha)001:4802: nang nas yi dwags thams cad la mchod sbyin gtong
NK029(ha)001:4804: byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa nag po g.yas g.yon du me chu bsnams ste /
NK029(ha)001:4805: tsha grang gi sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:4806: thub pa de rnams ni sprul pa'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)001:4807: kun dge slong gi cha byad can /
NK029(ha)001:4808: 'gro ba'i don la bsnyel ba mi mnga' ba'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:4811: badz+ra d+aa ra mah+aa kro d+hi sh+aa ri la ni
NK029(ha)001:4812: h+aum phatahcesa shar sgor khro bo chen po gshen rje
NK029(ha)001:4813: gshed dang / yum rdo rje lcags kyu ma sku
NK029(ha)001:4814: mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ma
NK029(ha)001:4816: yab kyi g.yas na thod dbyug /
NK029(ha)001:4817: g.yon thod khrag yum gyi phyag na lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4818: dpal gyi chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4819: phung po'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs par sgom mo //
NK029(ha)001:4821: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4822: ces pas lho sgor khro bo stobs po che dang /
NK029(ha)001:4823: yum rdo rje zhags pa ma sku mdog ser nag yab kyi g.yas na rdo rje dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)001:4824: g.yon na thod khrag yum gyi phyag na zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4825: 'chi bdag gi bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4827: pad+ma d+ha ra mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4828: ces nub sgor khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK029(ha)001:4829: yum rdo rje lcags sgrog ma sku mdog dmar nag
NK029(ha)001:4830: yab kyi phyag g.yas pad+ma'i dbyug pa sbrul gyis dkris
NK029(ha)001:4831: pa bsnams pa / yum gyis phyag na lcags sgrogs bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:4832: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4833: h+aum big nan ta krid phata /
NK029(ha)001:4834: karma d+ha ra mah+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:4835: ces byang sgor khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:4836: yum rdo rje dril bu ma sku mdog ljang nag
NK029(ha)001:4837: yab kyi g.yas rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbyug pa
NK029(ha)001:4838: / yum gyi phyag na gser gyi dril chen 'khrol ba /
NK029(ha)001:4839: lha'i bu'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4840: khro bo yab yum de rnams ni rdo rje'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)001:4841: kun kyang spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4842: chas chen po bcu drug gi brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4843: g.yon na thod pa khrag gi gang ba bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4844: gzhal yas khang de dag kyang khro bo de dag gi me dpung gis 'khrigs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4845: me ri 'bar ba'i dkyil na bde bar gshegs pa rnams bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4846: de ni dkyil 'khor 'bring po'i bum bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)001:4848: yang na dkyil 'khor rgyas pa ltar na /
NK029(ha)001:4849: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:4850: kun tu snang dang rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:4851: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi gzhal yas khang la ldum rdzings dkar po'i 'tshal /
NK029(ha)001:4852: zhes pa la sogs gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:4853: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus 'khor lo'i lte
NK029(ha)001:4854: ba zlum po mthing kha yi dbus su 'khor lo
NK029(ha)001:4855: gser po rtsibs bzhi lte ba la seng ge la
NK029(ha)001:4859: rgyu'i a la h+aum zung lnga rnams spros /
NK029(ha)001:4860: rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang lngar babs sar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)001:4862: phyag mtshan du gyur pa bsgom ste /
NK029(ha)001:4863: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4864: shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4865: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4866: nub du pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4867: byang du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4868: bar sang gis spro bsdu 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)001:4869: sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:4871: badz+ra d+ha ri shwa ra h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:4872: zhes mi skyod pa dang kun bzang dbyer med pa sku mdog mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)001:4874: dbus mthing pa la ral ba'i thor gtsugs nag po 'gying ba /
NK029(ha)001:4875: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4876: g.yas bar ma 'khor lo //'og ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4879: phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)001:4880: zhabs snyoms pa'i dkyil dkrung gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4881: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4882: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:4883: yum rdo rje dbyings phyag ma sku mdog yab dang mthun pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:4888: sems dpa'i rdo rje sngon po 'khor lo dril bu bsnams pa yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4889: yum rdo rje bstan ma sngon mo /
NK029(ha)001:4890: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4891: yab sems dpa'i dkyil dkrung ste /
NK029(ha)001:4892: zhabs g.yon pa cung zad gdan la 'bebs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4895: zhes rin po chen rdo rje sku mdog sngon po
NK029(ha)001:4896: rin po che dang dril bu bsnams pas yum la
NK029(ha)001:4897: 'khyud pa / 'bar ma rdo rje sngon mo //
NK029(ha)001:4898: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4901: zhes pas rdo rje sku mdog sngon po pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4902: sdud ma sngon mo rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4905: zhes las kyi rdo rje sku mdog sngon po ral
NK029(ha)001:4906: gri dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)001:4907: / bskyod ma rdo rje sku mdog sngon mo yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4910: shar gyi 'khor lo lte ba rtsibs bzhi gser po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:4911: glang po che la sogs pa gdan drug brtsegs brtsegs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4912: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i steng du babs sar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)001:4913: lha rang rang gi phyag mtshan du gyur ste /
NK029(ha)001:4914: dbus su 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4915: shar du rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4916: lhor lcags kyu dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4918: byang du rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:4919: yang sar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)001:4922: 'khor lo'i dbus su rnam par snang mdzad sku mdog dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)001:4924: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4925: g.yas bar pa na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:4926: tha ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:4927: g.yon bar pa na pa pad+ma /
NK029(ha)001:4928: tha ma na ral gri yum bud+d+ha dbyings phyag ma
NK029(ha)001:4929: zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnams
NK029(ha)001:4933: zhes rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:4934: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4935: yum la se ma dkar mo me long dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4938: zhes rdo rje rgyal po sku mdog dkar po lcags
NK029(ha)001:4939: kyu dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)001:4940: / d+hu pe ma sku mdog dkar po spos khang dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4944: zhes rdo rje chags pa sku mdog dkar po mda'
NK029(ha)001:4945: gzhu dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)001:4946: / yum rdo rje lcags kyu ma sku mdog dkar
NK029(ha)001:4947: mo lcags kyu dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la
NK029(ha)001:4948: / 'khyud pa / g.yon du badz+ra sa du //
NK029(ha)001:4950: zhes pas rdo rje legs pa se gol brdab pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4951: yum rdo rje sgrol ma sngo //'phreng ba bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:4952: lho rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:4953: 'khor lo gser po rtsibs bzhi'i lte ba rta mchog brgyad la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:4954: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:4955: rgyu'i yi ge a las tram zung lnga 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:4956: dbus dang rtsibs bzhi la babs /
NK029(ha)001:4958: yig 'bru rnams kyang 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)001:4959: 'khor lo lte ba'i gdan gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)001:4960: rin po che dang dril bur gyur par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:4961: de bzhin du shar gyi rtsibs la /
NK029(ha)001:4963: lho'i rtsibs la nyi ma dang me tog nub kyi rtsibs la rgyan dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)001:4969: dbus su rin chen 'byung ldan sku mdog gser po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)001:4972: phyag dang po gnyis rin po che dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4973: g.yas bar pa na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:4975: g.yon bar pa na pad+ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:4977: yum rin chen dbyings phyug ma sku mdog gser mo
NK029(ha)001:4978: rin po che dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la
NK029(ha)001:4979: 'khyud pa / yab yum gnyis zhabs brtul zhugs kyi dkyil mo dkrung gi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:4980: mdun du rdo rje rin po che sku mdog ser
NK029(ha)001:4981: po rin po che'i myu gu dang dril bu bsnams
NK029(ha)001:4983: yum rdo rje 'phreng ba ma 'phreng ba dang dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4984: g.yas su badz+ra su rgya tram /
NK029(ha)001:4986: zhes rdo rje gzi brjid sku mdog ser po nyi dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4987: yum me tog ma ser mo me tog dang dril bu bsnams nas yab 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4988: rgyab du badz+ra ke tu tram /
NK029(ha)001:4991: rdo rje rgyal mtshan sku mdog ser po rgyal mtshan dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4992: yum rdo rje zhags pa ma ser mo yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:4995: badz+ra ra tri tram zhes rdo rje bzhad pa sku
NK029(ha)001:4996: mdog ser po tshems kyi 'phreng ba dang dril bu
NK029(ha)001:4998: yum rdo rje bsil ma sku mdog ser mo bsil
NK029(ha)001:4999: g.yab dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa'o
NK029(ha)001:5000: // nub rtsibs sngon po'i steng du 'khor lo gser
NK029(ha)001:5001: po rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar rma bya la sogs pa'i
NK029(ha)001:5002: // gdan drug brtsegs / rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5003: rgyu'i yi ge a las hrihzunga lnga 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:5004: dbus dang rtsibs bzhi la babs /
NK029(ha)001:5006: yig 'bru rnams 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)001:5007: 'khor lo'i lte ba'i gdan gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)001:5010: pad+ma myu gu dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5011: g.yas su ral gri dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5014: g.yon du lce dang dril bu sogs /
NK029(ha)001:5016: am a ro lig pyam ra ga ra ti /
NK029(ha)001:5018: snang ba mtha' yas sku mdog dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)001:5021: phyag drug dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5022: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:5024: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:5025: tha ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:5026: yum pad+ma dbyings phyug ma sku mdog dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams pas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5029: badz+ra girti hri zhes rdo rje chos sku mdog dmar
NK029(ha)001:5030: po pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud
NK029(ha)001:5031: pa / yum rdo rje glu chen ma dmar mo
NK029(ha)001:5032: pi wamm dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)001:5037: rdo rje rnon po dmar po ral gri dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5038: yum rdo rje dmar mo mar me dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5040: badz+ra po ta hrih zhes rdo rje sku dmar po
NK029(ha)001:5041: 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud
NK029(ha)001:5042: pa / yum rdo rje lcags sgrogs ma dmar mo
NK029(ha)001:5043: lcags sgrogs dang dril bu bsnams nas nas yab la
NK029(ha)001:5045: badz+ra pa sha hrih badz+ra a lo ke hri /
NK029(ha)001:5046: zhes rdo rje smra ba sku mdog dmar po rdo
NK029(ha)001:5047: rje'i lce dang dril bu bsnams pas yum la 'khyud
NK029(ha)001:5048: pa / yum rdo rje gsal tra ma dmar mo
NK029(ha)001:5049: sgron me dang dril bu bsnams ste yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)001:5050: pa / pa'o // byang rtsibs sngon po'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:5051: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi lte bar shang shang brgyad la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:5052: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5053: rgyu'i yi ge a las ha zung lnga 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:5054: dbus dang rtsibs bzhi la babs /
NK029(ha)001:5055: sar sang gi spro bsdus yig 'bru rnams 'od du
NK029(ha)001:5056: zhu ba'i 'od phung gi 'khor lo'i lte ba'i gdan
NK029(ha)001:5057: gyi steng du / rdo rje rgya gram dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)001:5058: mdun du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5059: g.yas su rdo rje'i go cha dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5060: rgyab tu mche ba dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5061: g.yon du rdo rje dang dril bu la sogs /
NK029(ha)001:5064: tam badz+ra ra ti zhes dbus su don yod grub pa sku mdog ljang khu zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)001:5067: phyag dang po gnyis rgya gram dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5068: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)001:5070: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:5072: yum las kyi dbyings phyug ma sku mdog ljang khu
NK029(ha)001:5073: rgya gram dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)001:5078: rdo rje las sku mdog ljang khu ral gri dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5079: yum gar ma ljang khu rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin zhing /
NK029(ha)001:5080: gar bsgyur ste yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5085: rdo rje bsrungs ba sku mdog ljang khu go cha dang dril bu bsnams ste yum 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5086: yum rdo rje byug pa ma ljang khu dri'i dung
NK029(ha)001:5087: chos dang dril bu bsnams ste yab la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)001:5091: zhes rdo rje gdon sbyin sku mdog ljang khu mche
NK029(ha)001:5092: ba dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)001:5095: zhes khu tshur ljang khu rdo rje khu tshur gyis
NK029(ha)001:5096: rdo rje dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)001:5097: / yum rdo rje 'bebs ma rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas ye shes 'bebs bar mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5098: de ltar gtso 'khor de dag yab yum thams cad kyang zhi ba'i tshul dgu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:5099: brgyad chas bcu gsum gyis brgyan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:5100: dbus kyi gtso bo rnams rdo rje dkyil dkrungs dang /
NK029(ha)001:5101: 'khor rnams sems da pa'i tshul can yab yum rnams 'khril sbyor mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5102: de nas rgyu'i yi ge a las /
NK029(ha)001:5103: yig ge sum cu rtsa gcig 'phros ste /
NK029(ha)001:5104: shar lho'i rtsibs 'chan la ka dang tsa /
NK029(ha)001:5105: lho nub du kha dang tsha /
NK029(ha)001:5106: nub byang du ga dang dza /
NK029(ha)001:5107: byang shar du g+ha dang dz+ha /
NK029(ha)001:5110: lho nub du ya dang wa /
NK029(ha)001:5111: nub byang du ba dang ra /
NK029(ha)001:5112: byang shar du b+ha dang la /
NK029(ha)001:5114: lha rnams kyi byang du i /
NK029(ha)001:5123: lha rnams kyi shar du sha /
NK029(ha)001:5125: lha rnams kyi nub blo 'bur gyi steng du babs /
NK029(ha)001:5127: phyag mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis su gyur /
NK029(ha)001:5128: sar sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)001:5130: h'u la s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)001:5131: zhes shar lho'i dbal ka la /
NK029(ha)001:5132: sa'i snying bo yab yum sku mdog dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:5134: yab kyi phyag na rin po che'i myu gu /
NK029(ha)001:5135: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis me long zhabs phyed dkrung gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:5136: yab yum zhal sbyor du byas pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5138: tram ma le sa ma ya ho //
NK029(ha)001:5140: lho nub kyi rtsibs 'chan la nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK029(ha)001:5141: rin po che'i 'phreng ba ma sku mdog ser mo //
NK029(ha)001:5142: yab kyi g.yas na ral gri /
NK029(ha)001:5143: yum gyi phyag na rin po che'i 'phreng ba bsnams ste /
NK029(ha)001:5144: yab kyi dbu la thod bcings pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5145: hri ha ho pad+ma b+ha tra ma /
NK029(ha)001:5147: zhes nub byang gi rtsibs bar ma /
NK029(ha)001:5148: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
NK029(ha)001:5149: lha mo dbyangs can ma sku mdog dmar mo //
NK029(ha)001:5150: yab kyi g.yas na pad+ma dkar po bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5151: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyi chos kyi pi wam bsdeb pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5152: dzem ku ru pa na hri /
NK029(ha)001:5153: a ni rti ra ga ya mi /
NK029(ha)001:5155: byang shar gyi rtsibs bar la phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)001:5156: lha mo gar mkhan ma sku mdog ljang khu /
NK029(ha)001:5157: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5158: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis gar gyi lag pa bsgyur nas /
NK029(ha)001:5159: zhal zas ro mchog brgyad dang ldan pa yab la stobs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5161: dza du be pra be sha zhes shar lho'i gru chad la /
NK029(ha)001:5162: byams pa dang gdug spos ma sku mdog dkar ser /
NK029(ha)001:5163: yab kyi phyag g.yas na klu shing dang g+hen d+he bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5164: yum gyi phyag na gdug spos bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5168: zhes lho nub kyi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)001:5169: sgrib pa rnam par sel ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:5170: lha mo me tog ma sku mdog gser mo //
NK029(ha)001:5171: yab kyi phyag na chos kyi 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5172: yum gyi phyag na me tog gi 'phreng ba bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5173: h'u swa ra tsa sa swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:5174: bam ta pa bu ke ni /
NK029(ha)001:5175: zhes nub byang gi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)001:5177: lha mo mar me ma sku mdog dmar mo //
NK029(ha)001:5178: yab kyi phyag na rin po che'i snye ma bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5179: yum gyi phyag na mar me bsnams so //
NK029(ha)001:5180: mum sh+ri am ra ga ya swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:5182: byang shar gyi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)001:5183: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5184: lha mo dri chab ma sku mdog ljang khu yab kyi phyag na /
NK029(ha)001:5186: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyi dri chab bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5187: sems dpa' yab yum de rnams ni kun kyang dbu ral pa'i thor gtsugs mnga' ba /
NK029(ha)001:5188: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:5189: dpe byad brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:5190: zhabs phyed dkrung gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:5191: yab yum zhal sbyor du byas te /
NK029(ha)001:5192: thugs rjes sems can thams cad la bu gcig pa la ma byams pa ltar sems te /
NK029(ha)001:5193: yab yum de rnams ni mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK029(ha)001:5194: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:5196: shar du bcom ldan 'das rdo rje byed pa po /
NK029(ha)001:5197: yid kun tu bzang po sku mdog sngon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:5198: mnyam pa'i phyag rgya'i dkyil na /
NK029(ha)001:5199: rdo rje dkar po brtsegs pa la //
NK029(ha)001:5201: zhabs mnyam pa'i dkyil mo dkrung gis pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5202: nub tu a a a badz+ra sa man+ta /
NK029(ha)001:5204: chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas thams cad gnas su dag pa'i yum kun bzang mo //
NK029(ha)001:5205: shes bya'i bag chags dag pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:5206: sku mdog dkar mo phyag gnyis chos 'byung gi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK029(ha)001:5208: zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i dkyil dkrung gi bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5209: yab yum de gnyis ni chos kyi sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)001:5210: dbyings mkhyen dang ldan pa'i rtags su yum gyis zhal shar du gzigs pa /
NK029(ha)001:5211: mkhyen pa'i shes bya dngos po thams cad dbyings su gzigs pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:5212: yab kyi zhal nub tu gzigs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5214: shar lhor lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wam bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5216: byang du lha min gyi thub pa ljang nag g.yas ral gri g.yon khrab /
NK029(ha)001:5218: lhor mi'i thub pa ser po g.yas bsreg shang /
NK029(ha)001:5221: nub byang du byol song gi thub pa ljang ser /
NK029(ha)001:5222: spyi bo nas chos kyi glegs bam khur ba /
NK029(ha)001:5223: ma rig pa'i mun khang 'byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:5225: lho nub du yi dwags kyi thub pa ljang ser
NK029(ha)001:5226: phyag na rin po che'i za ma tog bsnams pa'i
NK029(ha)001:5227: nang nas yi dwags thams cad la mchod sbyin gtong
NK029(ha)001:5229: byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa nag po g.yas su me chu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5230: tsha grang gi sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:5231: thub pa de rnams ni sprul pa'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)001:5232: kun dge slong gi cha byad can /
NK029(ha)001:5233: 'gro ba'i don la bsnyel pa mi mnga' ba'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:5236: badz+ra da ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la na h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5237: ces shar sgor khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed dang /
NK029(ha)001:5238: yum rdo rje lcags kyu ma sku mdog mthing nag
NK029(ha)001:5239: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa
NK029(ha)001:5240: / yab kyi g.yas na thod dbyug /
NK029(ha)001:5242: yum gyi phyag na lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5243: dpal gyi chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:5244: phung po'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs par bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)001:5246: rat+na d+ha ra mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dza la h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5248: lho sgor khro bo chen po stobs po che dang /
NK029(ha)001:5249: yum rdo rje zhags pa ma sku mdog gser nag g.yas na rdo rje dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)001:5251: yum gyi phyag na zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5252: 'chi bdag gi bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5254: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5256: nub sgor khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5257: yum rdo rje lcags sgrogs ma /
NK029(ha)001:5258: sku mdog dmar nag yab kyi phyag g.yas na pad+ma'i dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)001:5259: sprul gyis dkris pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5260: yum gyi phyag na lcags sgrogs bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5261: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o h+aum big nan ta krid phata /
NK029(ha)001:5262: karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwi ra dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5263: ces byang sgor khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:5264: yum rdo rje dril bu ma sku mdog ljang nag yab kyi g.yas rdo rje rgya gram dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)001:5265: yum gyi phyag na gser gyi dril chen 'khrol ba /
NK029(ha)001:5266: lha'i bu'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5267: khro bo yab yum de rnams rdo rje'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)001:5268: kun kyang spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK029(ha)001:5269: chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5270: g.yon na thod pa khrag gi gang ba bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5271: gzhal yas khang de dag kyang khro bo de dag
NK029(ha)001:5272: gi me dpung 'khrigs pa me ri 'bar ba'i dkyil
NK029(ha)001:5273: na bde bar gshegs pa rnams bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5274: de ni dkyil 'khor rgyas pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:5276: mdun bskyed gang la'ang rung ngo //
NK029(ha)001:5277: yang na tshom bu gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor ltar na /
NK029(ha)001:5278: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5279: kun tu snang gi ting 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5281: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis rten gzhal yas khang ldum rdzings dkar po'i tshal /
NK029(ha)001:5282: zhes pa la sogs pa gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:5283: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus su 'khor lo'i
NK029(ha)001:5284: lte ba zlum po mthing ka rtsibs bzhi ser po
NK029(ha)001:5288: seng ge la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:5289: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5290: sgo bzhir nyi ma bdud bzhi'i gdan la /
NK029(ha)001:5291: rgyu'i yi ge a las h+aum zung lnga 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:5292: lte ba dang rtsibs bzhi la babs /
NK029(ha)001:5294: h+aum h+aum h+aum bam h+aum ho //
NK029(ha)001:5296: sar sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las phyag mtshan du gyur par sgom ste /
NK029(ha)001:5297: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5300: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5301: nub du pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5302: byang du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5303: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu /
NK029(ha)001:5304: lho sgor rdo rje rtse lnga dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)001:5305: nub sgor thod sbrul dang lcags sgrogs /
NK029(ha)001:5306: byang sgor sna tshogs rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:5309: sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed de /
NK029(ha)001:5313: zhes pa mi bskyod pa sku mdog sngon po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)001:5317: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5318: g.yas bar ma 'khor lo //'og ma rin po che /
NK029(ha)001:5321: phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba zhabs mnyam pa'i dkyil dkrungs gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:5322: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:5323: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:5324: yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma sku mdog sngon po /
NK029(ha)001:5326: rdo rje dang dril bus yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5330: sems dpa' sngon po 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5331: yum rdo rje bstan ma rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5332: yab sems dpa'i dkyil dkrung ste /
NK029(ha)001:5333: zhabs g.yon pa cung zad gdan la babs pa /
NK029(ha)001:5336: zhes rin po che rdo rje sku mdog sngon po
NK029(ha)001:5337: rin po che dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la
NK029(ha)001:5338: 'khyud pa / bar ma rdo rje sngon mo rdo
NK029(ha)001:5339: rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)001:5343: chos sku rdo rje sku mdog sngon po pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5344: yum sdud ma sngon mo rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams ste yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5347: zhes las kyi rdo rje sku mdog sngon po ral
NK029(ha)001:5348: gri dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)001:5349: / bskyod ma rdo rje sku mdog sngon mo yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:5350: de ltar gtso 'khor yab yum thams cad kyang zhi ba'i tshul dgu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:5351: brgyan chas bcu gsum gyis brgyan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:5352: de yang dbus kyi gtso bo rdo rje dkyil dkrung dang /
NK029(ha)001:5353: 'khor rnams sems dpa'i tshul can yum rnams kyis g.yon zur nas 'khyud pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5357: gshin rje gshed smug nag pe con bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5358: rdo rje lcags kyu ma sngon mo lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5360: badz+ra pa sha h+aum zhes lho sgor stobs po che ser nag rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5361: rdo rje zhags pa ma ser mo zhags pa bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5364: zhes nub sgor rta mgrin dmar nag thod pa sprul gyis dkris pa bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5365: rdo rje lcags sgrogs ma dmar mo lcags sgrogs bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5369: byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag /
NK029(ha)001:5370: sna tshogs rdo rje bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5371: rdo rje dril bu ma ljang khu dril bu 'khrol ba /
NK029(ha)001:5372: sgo ma yab yum brgyad po thams cad kyang /
NK029(ha)001:5373: nyi ma'i gdan la zhal phyogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:5375: yum g.yas brkyang gis gyad kyi dor thabs kyis bsgrad pa /
NK029(ha)001:5376: khro bo'i chas kyi brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:5377: me ri dang me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa bskyed do /
NK029(ha)001:5378: de ni tshom bu gcig pa'i lha ste /
NK029(ha)001:5379: bum bskyed dang mdun bskyed gang yang rung pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5380: tshom bu gsum pa'i dkyil 'khor ltar na /
NK029(ha)001:5381: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5382: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5384: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rten gzhal yas khang gi ldum rdzings dkar po'i tshal /
NK029(ha)001:5385: zhes pa man chad gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:5386: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus 'khor lo'i lte ba zlum po mthing kha rtsibs bzhi sngon po /
NK029(ha)001:5389: sgo dbus lte ba sngon po'i dbus su 'khor lo
NK029(ha)001:5390: ser po rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte bar seng ge la
NK029(ha)001:5392: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5393: shar rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:5394: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar /
NK029(ha)001:5395: glang po che la sogs gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:5396: rtsibs bzhi la pad nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5397: nub rtsibs sngon pa'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:5398: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar rma bya la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:5399: rtsibs bzhi la pad+ma nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5400: gru chad bzhi dang sgo bzhi la nyi ma la
NK029(ha)001:5401: sogs kyi gdan rgyu'i yi ge a las h+aum zung
NK029(ha)001:5402: lnga / dbus su babs zung lnga /
NK029(ha)001:5404: nub kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i steng du babs /
NK029(ha)001:5406: gru chad bzhi dang sgo bzhir babs /
NK029(ha)001:5407: sar sang gi 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)001:5408: phyag mtshan bzhi bcu zhe drug du gyur sar sang 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)001:5409: sku yongs su rdzogs pa zhe drug tu gyur te /
NK029(ha)001:5411: dbus su rdo rje sems dpa' zhal gsum phyag drug yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:5413: rdoo rje rigs kyi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad sgom /
NK029(ha)001:5414: shar rtsibs kyi 'khor lo'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:5415: rnam snang dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:5416: rtsibs bzhi la de bzhin rigs kyi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad sgom /
NK029(ha)001:5417: nub rtsibs kyi 'khor lo'i dbus su snang mtha' yab
NK029(ha)001:5418: yum zhal gsum phyag drug la pad+ma rigs kyi sems
NK029(ha)001:5419: dpa' yab yum brgyad kyis bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)001:5420: ci ltar bsgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK029(ha)001:5421: gong dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i skabs su bshad pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus dang /
NK029(ha)001:5425: badz+ra krod+ha h+aum ka ra h+aum zhes pas /
NK029(ha)001:5426: shar sgor khro bo rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:5427: yum rdo rje snyem ma sku mdog dmar mo zhal
NK029(ha)001:5428: gcig phyag gnyis lcags kyu dang dril bu bsnams pa
NK029(ha)001:5429: / badz+ra kro d+ha ni la rten ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:5430: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5432: khro bo chen po dbyug sngon can sku mdog dkar po dang /
NK029(ha)001:5433: yum rdo rje sder mo yab yum zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:5434: badz+ra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:5435: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5436: lho sgor khro bo chen po gshen rje gshed dang /
NK029(ha)001:5437: yum rdo rje dur khrod bdag mo sku mdog ser mo zhags pa dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:5438: badz+ra kro d+ha ar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5439: ban d+ha ban d+ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5440: lho nub gyi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)001:5441: khro bo chen po mi g.yo sngon po /
NK029(ha)001:5442: yum rdo rje gtun khu ma sku mdog dmar gser zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:5443: badz+ra kro ta ha ya g+h+ri wa hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5444: nub sgor khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5445: yum rdo rje gtum mo sku mdog dmar mo zhal
NK029(ha)001:5446: gcig phyag gnyis lcags sgrogs dang dril bu bsnams pa
NK029(ha)001:5447: / badz+ra kro ta a par tsi ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:5448: ti tha ti tha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5449: nub byang gi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)001:5450: khro bo chen po gzhan gyi mi thub pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5451: yum rdo rje mda' snyem ma sku mdog dmar ljang zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:5452: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:5453: tshin d+hi tshin d+ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5455: khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5456: yum rdo rje rlung 'byin ma sku mdog ljang khu rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:5457: badz+ra kro d+ha kre lo kya b+ai dza ya h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:5458: ban d+ha ban d+ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5460: khro bo chen po khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:5461: yum rdo rje krod ma sku mdog dkar ljang zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:5462: khro bo yab yum de rnams ni nyi ma'i gdan la yab g.yon brkyang dang /
NK029(ha)001:5463: yum g.yas brkyang gi dor thabs kyis bsgrad pa /
NK029(ha)001:5464: khro bo'i chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)001:5465: me ri me dpung gi khung na bzhugs pa bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:5466: de ni tshom bu gsum pa'i mngon rtogs de /
NK029(ha)001:5467: lha bzhi bcu zhe drug yod /
NK029(ha)001:5468: tshom bu lnga pa'i mngon rtogs ltar na /
NK029(ha)001:5469: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5470: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5471: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi brten gzhal
NK029(ha)001:5472: yas khang gi ldum rdzings dkar po'i tshil zhes pa
NK029(ha)001:5473: yan chad gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)001:5474: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:5475: 'khor lo'i lte ba zlum po mthing kha rtsibs bzhi sngon po /
NK029(ha)001:5477: gru chad phyogs mdog la sgo dbus lte ba sngon
NK029(ha)001:5478: po'i dbus su 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi pa'i
NK029(ha)001:5479: lte bar / seng ge la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:5480: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5481: shar rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:5482: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi lte bar /
NK029(ha)001:5483: glang po che la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:5484: rtsibs bzhi pad nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5485: lho rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:5486: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi lte bar rta mchog la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:5487: rtsibs bzhi la pad nyi nyi ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5488: nub rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su 'khor lo ser po
NK029(ha)001:5489: rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar rma bya la sogs pa'i gdan
NK029(ha)001:5490: drug brtsegs / rtsibs bzhi la pad nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5491: byang rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar /
NK029(ha)001:5492: shang shang la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)001:5493: rtsibs bzhi la pad nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)001:5494: gru chad bzhi sgo bzhi steng 'og gnyis dang /
NK029(ha)001:5495: phyogs bcur nyi ma dang phyogs skyong bcu'i gdan sgom /
NK029(ha)001:5496: rgyu'i yi ge a las h+aum zung lnga dbus su bab zung lnga shar du /
NK029(ha)001:5500: h+aum bsgril bcu phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og gnyis dang bcu ru babs /
NK029(ha)001:5501: rgyu'i a dbus kyi h+aum la thim sar sang gis
NK029(ha)001:5502: 'od du zhu ba las phyag mtshan bdun bcur gyur
NK029(ha)001:5503: / sar sang gi 'od du zhu ba las sku yongs rdzogs bdun bcur gyur te /
NK029(ha)001:5504: ci ltar bsgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK029(ha)001:5505: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i skabs ltar pho brang gi lha lnga bcur bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:5506: khro bo yab yum bcu drug kyang /
NK029(ha)001:5507: gong tshom bu gsum pa ltar la /
NK029(ha)001:5508: badz+ra kro ta h+aum ka ra phata /
NK029(ha)001:5509: gar tsha gar tsha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5510: steng du khro bo chen po h+aum mdzad yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:5511: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa pa la h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:5512: s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5513: 'og tu khro bo chen po stobs po che yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:5514: lha bdun bcu po de ni tshom bu lnga pa'i mngon rtogs te /
NK029(ha)001:5515: bum bskyed dang mdun bskyed gang la'ang mthad do //
NK029(ha)001:5516: de yongs su rdzogs pa'i cho 'phrul de song nas /
NK029(ha)001:5518: byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)001:5519: mchod pa 'bul ba'i cho 'phrul dang gsum 'og mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)001:5520: gong bdag bskyed thun mong du bstan no //
NK029(ha)001:5521: gsum pa mdun bskyed la drug ste /
NK029(ha)001:5522: dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)001:5524: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)001:5525: tshom bu gcig pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)001:5526: tshom bu gsum pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)001:5527: tshom bu lnga pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)001:5528: de drug gi de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5529: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)001:5531: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin las bskyed pa'i
NK029(ha)001:5532: cho 'phrul yan chad gong bum bskyed dang mthun la
NK029(ha)001:5533: / gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK029(ha)001:5534: don ye shes lnga'i dbang dang /
NK029(ha)001:5535: rtags rgyal ba rigs lnga'i dbu brgyan gyi dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:5537: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5539: chos thams cad yid dam rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor de
NK029(ha)001:5540: dag don dam par chos kyi dbyings mnyam pa chen
NK029(ha)001:5541: po'i rang bzhin la g.yos pa med par rtog pa
NK029(ha)001:5544: rgyal ba de dag gi spyi gtsug tu mi skyod
NK029(ha)001:5545: pa sku mdog mthing kha res dbu brgyan par bya'o
NK029(ha)001:5546: // ma h+aa a ta ri sha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5547: ces don dam par rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor de dag thams cad kyang /
NK029(ha)001:5548: chos kyi dbyings las 'gag pa med pa'i ye shes rang snang pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5549: rtags rgyal ba de dag gi sprul bar rnam par
NK029(ha)001:5550: snang mdzad sku mdog dkar po re re sgom mo
NK029(ha)001:5551: // ma h+aa sa man+ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5552: zhes don dam par rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor la 'gag pa'i snang ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:5553: ngo bo chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos par ye nas dbyer med par shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:5554: rtags sna ltag g.yas par rin chen 'byung ldan sku mdog ser po re re bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)001:5555: ma h+aa pra d+ha spra b+ae sha dz+nya na badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5556: zhes rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor de dag kyang gdul bya
NK029(ha)001:5557: tha dad pa la mos pa tha dad par shes
NK029(ha)001:5558: par bya'o // rtags ltag pa'i steng du snang ba mtha' yas sku dmar po re bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)001:5559: mah+aa kri te a nu ta dz+nya na badz+ra s+w+aab+ha wa ad+ma ko ham zhes /
NK029(ha)001:5560: don dam par rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du ma 'gag par snang ba ni gzhan don no //
NK029(ha)001:5561: ngo bo ma skyes pa ni bdag don ste /
NK029(ha)001:5563: don dam phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5564: rtags sna ltag g.yon pa'i steng du don yod grub pa re re bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)001:5565: de nas rgyal ba de dag gi dbu la rin po che'i dbu brgyan dang /
NK029(ha)001:5573: sham thabs la sogs pa'i rgyan chen po rnams kyis brgyan par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:5574: de ni dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK029(ha)001:5575: gsum pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul gnyis ni /
NK029(ha)001:5576: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)001:5577: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor phyogs bcu nas spyan drangs nas byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5578: dang po ni sarba ta tha ga ta mah+aa ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5579: zhes bdag gi dbu'i nang du zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)001:5580: sku rdo rje sku mdog dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu can /
NK029(ha)001:5581: de'i thugs khar 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5582: sarba ta tha ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swab+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5583: zhes bdag gi lce thog du pad+ma'i steng du gsung
NK029(ha)001:5584: rdo rje sku mdog dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu
NK029(ha)001:5585: can / de'i thugs khar pad+ma am gyis mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5586: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa tsit+ta badz+ra s+w+aab+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5587: bdag gi thugs khar nyi ma'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:5588: thugs rdo rje sku mdog mthing nag rdo rje dang dril bu can /
NK029(ha)001:5589: de'i thugs khar rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5590: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa a nu ra ga badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5591: lte bar rin po che zur brgyad kyi steng du /
NK029(ha)001:5592: chags pa'i rdo rje sku mdog gser po rin po che dang dril bu can /
NK029(ha)001:5593: de'i thugs khar rin po che zur brgyad pa sogs mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5594: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa pu tsa badz+ra swa b+ha wa a d+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5595: zhes gsang gnas su chos 'byung gru gsum gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)001:5596: mchod pa'i rdo rje sku mdog ljang khu ral gri dang dril bu can /
NK029(ha)001:5597: de'i thugs kar ral gri ham gis mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5598: lha de dag thams cad kyi thugs khar ye shes sems dpa' re re /
