NK029(ha)001:5599: de'i thugs khar phyag mtshan la rang sngags kyi yi ge rnams kyis mtshan pa re re bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:5600: de'i mtha' bskor du rang rang gi sngags kyis bskor ba re re bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)001:5601: gnyis pa spyan drangs nas byin gyis brlabs pa la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)001:5604: bstan par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:5605: dang po ni se go la snol mar rtog cing /
NK029(ha)001:5606: h+aum dmigs med mkha' ltar dag cing khyab pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)001:5607: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang /
NK029(ha)001:5608: thugs rje'i nga nga can chos sku dag pa la /
NK029(ha)001:5609: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:5610: badz+ra sa man ta dza h+aum dza /
NK029(ha)001:5611: gnyis pa spyan drangs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:5612: yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK029(ha)001:5613: nam mkha' bzhin du dam tshig nye bar gshegs //
NK029(ha)001:5614: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par grol ba'i klong //
NK029(ha)001:5615: mi gnas mi dmigs nam mkha'i dbyings gnas shing //
NK029(ha)001:5616: tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs thams cad dbyings kyi lha //
NK029(ha)001:5617: longs spyod rdzogs mdzad rol ba chen po'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:5618: rdo rje sems dpa' bskal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK029(ha)001:5619: thabs kyi ma rmongs bde chen dbyings nas bzhengs /
NK029(ha)001:5620: ye shes sgyu ma rnam par rol ba'i sku //'phags rje sprul pa mang po 'byung pa'i gnas //
NK029(ha)001:5621: thabs dang shes rab che la mnga' mnyes pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:5622: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs pa bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:5623: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan /
NK029(ha)001:5624: mah+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha ho /
NK029(ha)001:5629: a gad dza ya h+aum dza /
NK029(ha)001:5630: gsum pa bstan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:5631: h+aum bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:5632: thugs rje chen po byon pa legs //
NK029(ha)001:5633: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK029(ha)001:5634: dgyes shing bstan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:5639: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi bzhi pa mchod pa 'bul ba'i cho 'phrul la bzhi ste /
NK029(ha)001:5645: phyog bcu dus bzhi sogs pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:5646: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK029(ha)001:5648: snang stong thig le kun rdzob ho //
NK029(ha)001:5649: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK029(ha)001:5650: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK029(ha)001:5651: rdo rje sgra can mtha' yas pa //
NK029(ha)001:5652: rdo rje rgyal po dkyil 'khor che //
NK029(ha)001:5653: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa chee //
NK029(ha)001:5654: yon tan 'phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK029(ha)001:5655: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //'dus pa'i rdzogs chen thig le che //
NK029(ha)001:5656: mi 'khrug mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings /
NK029(ha)001:5657: mtha' yas kun tu sna tshogs 'phros //
NK029(ha)001:5658: mtha' yas kun tu lhun gyis thim //
NK029(ha)001:5659: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen ho //
NK029(ha)001:5660: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten brdul snyed du //
NK029(ha)001:5661: rgyal ba'i don rnams brdul bran rnyed //
NK029(ha)001:5662: sprul pa'i brdul bran bsam yas kyi //
NK029(ha)001:5663: skad cig yud la lhun gyi grub //
NK029(ha)001:5665: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK029(ha)001:5666: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK029(ha)001:5667: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK029(ha)001:5668: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le ho //
NK029(ha)001:5669: gnyis pa mchod pa la dgu ste //
NK029(ha)001:5670: kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:5672: mchod pa gar tshogs kyi mchod pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5675: smad du byung pa bdud rtsi'i mchod pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5678: dang po kun bzang kyi mchod pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:5679: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:5680: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK029(ha)001:5681: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kyis //
NK029(ha)001:5682: spyod pa rgya mtsho smad byung kun //
NK029(ha)001:5683: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK029(ha)001:5684: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu khe b+h+ya sarba tad kham ang+gu te /
NK029(ha)001:5685: s+pha ra na ham mam ga ga na kham s+w+aah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:5687: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK029(ha)001:5688: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK029(ha)001:5689: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK029(ha)001:5690: gnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yi //
NK029(ha)001:5691: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK029(ha)001:5692: mdzes par bris shing spras pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:5694: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog gsil //
NK029(ha)001:5695: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK029(ha)001:5696: brgyan dang dpag bsam 'byon pa'i tshul //
NK029(ha)001:5697: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK029(ha)001:5698: bla res rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK029(ha)001:5699: do shal dpung brgyan sen mo do //
NK029(ha)001:5700: bza' dang btung ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK029(ha)001:5701: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:5702: lha dang lha mo'i brdul brnyed kyis //
NK029(ha)001:5703: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:5704: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK029(ha)001:5705: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK029(ha)001:5707: phyag rgya gar tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:5708: sgyu 'phrul dra ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:5709: dbang po yul du gang bsgyur ba //
NK029(ha)001:5710: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:5711: mnyam pa'i ngang nyid stongs gsal nas //
NK029(ha)001:5712: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK029(ha)001:5713: bskyed can 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK029(ha)001:5714: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)001:5716: bsgul skyod thams cad phyag rgya yin //'di ni spyi rgya chen po ste //
NK029(ha)001:5717: bla med chen pos 'di skad gsungs //
NK029(ha)001:5718: gsang ba de nyid nges pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:5720: mi skyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge /
NK029(ha)001:5721: rin chen zla ba'i dkyil yi ge /
NK029(ha)001:5722: lnga gnyis zung du 'phros pa las //
NK029(ha)001:5723: sbyor bas phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK029(ha)001:5724: dang mum gnyis rtse sbyar te //'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad de //
NK029(ha)001:5725: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:5726: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya //'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs khar bkan //
NK029(ha)001:5727: h'u sgreng rtse mor rdo rje 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:5728: zla btul 'brug sgras dril gsil zhing //'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la rten //
NK029(ha)001:5729: badz+ra d+h+rig /'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs khar bkan //
NK029(ha)001:5730: mum sgrengs rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:5731: nyi ma 'bru lnga las la mkhril //
NK029(ha)001:5732: bsdud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi lta //
NK029(ha)001:5734: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs khar bkan //
NK029(ha)001:5736: zla btul 'brug sgras dril bsil zhing //'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten //
NK029(ha)001:5737: dzi na dzig /'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs khar bkan //
NK029(ha)001:5738: lam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:5740: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi lta /
NK029(ha)001:5741: lam te sha ra te 'bru bzhi sbas //
NK029(ha)001:5742: swo rtse 'bar ba rin po che //
NK029(ha)001:5743: zla btul 'khril ba'i tshul gyi swa rat+na d+h+rika /'bru
NK029(ha)001:5744: bzhi mam sgring nyi ma 'bru lnga btud de mam
NK029(ha)001:5746: 'bru bzhi sgreng rtse mor pad+ma zla btul 'khril ba'i a ro lika /'bru bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:5747: pyam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil nas //
NK029(ha)001:5748: nyi ma 'bru lnga btud de pyam ga ra ti /
NK029(ha)001:5749: 'bru ham sgreng rtse mor ral gri 'bar /
NK029(ha)001:5750: zla btul 'khril ha pradz+nya d+h+rika /'bru bzhi sbas nas
NK029(ha)001:5751: t+r+aam sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //nyi ma 'bru
NK029(ha)001:5752: lnga btud de t+r+aam badz+ra ra ti /
NK029(ha)001:5753: thugs khar rin chen myu gu 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:5754: rin chen dril bsil chos la brten //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi lta ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:5755: sa yi snying po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)001:5757: rdo rje rin chen khur tshur cang //
NK029(ha)001:5758: sku yi thad khar gzung ba ni //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis 'dud pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:5759: sgeg mo'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)001:5760: h+aum la s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)001:5761: rdo rje ral gri thugs kha nas //
NK029(ha)001:5762: rin chen dril bsil chos la brten //'dzum pa'i nam mkha'i snying po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)001:5764: rdo rje rin chen rna ltag bzhag /
NK029(ha)001:5765: rin chen 'phreng ba gzung pa ru //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis 'phreng ba'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)001:5766: tram ma le sa ma ya /
NK029(ha)001:5767: rdo rje pad+ma thugs ka nas //
NK029(ha)001:5768: rin chen dril bsil chos la 'dzum pa'i spyan ras gzigs kyi hrihha h+aum pad+ma /
NK029(ha)001:5769: rin chen pi wam 'dzin par bya //
NK029(ha)001:5770: rdo rje len par byas nas ni //'dzum pa'i dbyangs kyi hrihgi rti ra ga ya ham /
NK029(ha)001:5772: rin chen dril bsil chos 'dzum pa'i phyag na rdo
NK029(ha)001:5773: rje'i phyag rgya dz+him ku ru pa na hrih rin
NK029(ha)001:5774: chen gar thabs bskor na ni //
NK029(ha)001:5775: rdo rje thal mo las la 'khril //'dzum pa'i gar gyi phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)001:5776: a nirti ra ga ya mi //
NK029(ha)001:5777: rdo rje klu shing thugs kha nas //
NK029(ha)001:5778: rin chen dril 'dzum pa'i byams pa mee tri'i phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)001:5780: rin chen gdugs spos thugs kha nas //
NK029(ha)001:5781: rdo rje las la rab tu 'khril //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi gdug spos phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)001:5782: dza d+hup+pe pra be sha ya /
NK029(ha)001:5783: rdo rje po ti thugs ka nas //
NK029(ha)001:5784: rin chen dril gsil 'dzum pa'i sgrib pa rnam sel phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)001:5785: th+l+ham ni pa ram sa ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:5786: rdo rje rin chen rnam ltag du //
NK029(ha)001:5787: me tog snod bcas 'dzin pa la //'dzum pa'i me
NK029(ha)001:5788: tog phyag rgya yin par h+aum push+pe a be sha
NK029(ha)001:5789: ya / rdo rje nyi ma thugs ka nas //
NK029(ha)001:5790: rin chen dril gsil 'dzum pa'i kun tu bzang po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)001:5791: h+aum swa ra ts+aa ya swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:5792: rin chen mar me thugs ka na //
NK029(ha)001:5793: rdo rje sems dpa' las la 'khril //'dzum pa'i mar
NK029(ha)001:5794: me'i phyag rgya yin par pam ti bam su ki
NK029(ha)001:5795: ni swah+aa // rdo rje u pal thugs ka na //
NK029(ha)001:5796: rin chen dril gsil 'dzum pa'i 'jam dpal gyis ni phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)001:5797: mum sh+ri ra ga ya swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:5798: rin chen dbyug pa thugs ka na //
NK029(ha)001:5799: rdo rje dbyug par byed pa ni //'dzum pa'i dri'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)001:5801: rni g+ho gdengs pa gshed po ste //
NK029(ha)001:5803: 'dzub gnyis lkug la lcags kyu'i rgya /
NK029(ha)001:5804: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:5805: rdo rje gnon pa stobs chen rgya /
NK029(ha)001:5807: 'dzub rtse gnyis sprad bzhag pa'i rgya //
NK029(ha)001:5808: rat+na thod sbrul gnon pa rta mgrin rgya //
NK029(ha)001:5811: pad+ma d+ha ra rgya gram gnon pa 'khyil ba'i rgya //
NK029(ha)001:5814: karma d+ha ra pi wam len pa lha'i rgya //
NK029(ha)001:5818: lha min phyag rgya go cha yin //
NK029(ha)001:5820: chos kyi dkyil 'khor byol song rgya //
NK029(ha)001:5822: za ma tog ni yi dwags rgya //
NK029(ha)001:5824: me chu gnyis ni dmyal ba'i rgya //
NK029(ha)001:5826: yab kyi spyi rgya kun bzang gi /
NK029(ha)001:5827: h+aum h+aum h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:5828: yum gyi spyi rgya bzang mor bshad //
NK029(ha)001:5829: a a a badz+ra pa tra sa man ta /
NK029(ha)001:5830: yang na kun bzang yab yum gyi //
NK029(ha)001:5831: rdo rje thal mo nyid du bshad //
NK029(ha)001:5833: rin chen pad+ma dkyil 'jam 'di //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi 'bul lags kyi //
NK029(ha)001:5834: dgyes par rdo rje gsor mdzod nas //
NK029(ha)001:5835: byang chub sems sprin dbab du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:5836: rdo rje gsor ba'i dga' chags 'di //'jam zhing mkhyil ba'i gnas su rol //
NK029(ha)001:5838: rdo rje 'dzin mar gdan la byung //
NK029(ha)001:5839: shes rab dbyings ma yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK029(ha)001:5840: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus chags bkod de //
NK029(ha)001:5841: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i sbyor mchod kyis //
NK029(ha)001:5842: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor tshogs la mchod pa 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:5846: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs bsgom bsgral //
NK029(ha)001:5847: de nas gnyis med blo yi ni //
NK029(ha)001:5848: blo ngan 'jigs rten snying re rje //
NK029(ha)001:5849: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK029(ha)001:5850: zhi gyur chags dang chags bral rnams //
NK029(ha)001:5851: nyi zla'i dkyil du mkhas pas bzhag /
NK029(ha)001:5852: ngar rgyal lag gi 'du byed bsgom //
NK029(ha)001:5853: h+aum du gyur pas rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)001:5854: dbyings su thim nas phyag rgyar 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:5856: gtsug du rnam par rgyal ba bsgom //
NK029(ha)001:5857: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar ba'i thabs //
NK029(ha)001:5858: ye nas bskyed byed de bzhin nyid //
NK029(ha)001:5859: sbyor bsgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:5860: de la byas pa brdul tsam med //
NK029(ha)001:5862: ho rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:5863: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK029(ha)001:5864: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK029(ha)001:5865: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK029(ha)001:5866: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:5867: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK029(ha)001:5868: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK029(ha)001:5869: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs can dang //
NK029(ha)001:5870: khro bo rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK029(ha)001:5871: ma mo mkha' 'gro tshogs chen dang //
NK029(ha)001:5872: lha dang lha min gsang ba'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:5873: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig go /
NK029(ha)001:5874: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK029(ha)001:5875: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK029(ha)001:5876: bdag chags dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK029(ha)001:5877: bzhes de kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK029(ha)001:5878: phul ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:5879: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa argam pra ti tsa ho /
NK029(ha)001:5880: ho rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyi /
NK029(ha)001:5881: srid pa'i sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:5882: bde chen kun bzang yab yum la //
NK029(ha)001:5883: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:5885: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga //
NK029(ha)001:5886: ye shes dbyings su rnam dag pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:5887: rigs lnga bde chen yab yum la //
NK029(ha)001:5888: dam tshig mchog gi mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:5890: rnam shes tshogs dang spyod yul rnams //
NK029(ha)001:5891: byang chub sems su rnam dag pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:5892: sems dpa' lcam bral tshogs rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:5893: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa na ma /
NK029(ha)001:5894: thugs rje chen po 'i byin brlabs kyis //'gro drug dbyings su sbyangs mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:5895: sprul pa thub pa drug rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:5896: dam tshig mchog gi mo na ma /
NK029(ha)001:5897: phyi nang bdud tshogs thams cad 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:5898: gnas yul ro langs rdo rje bcings sdom 'bebs //
NK029(ha)001:5899: sprul pa sgo skyong khro rgyal yab yum la //
NK029(ha)001:5900: dam tshig mchog gi na ma /
NK029(ha)001:5901: tshe rab sngon nas las kyi 'phro mthun pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:5902: mched dang lcam bral karma ging la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:5903: rdo rje lcam dral ma lus tshogs rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:5904: dam tshig mchog gi na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta argam pra ti dza ho //
NK029(ha)001:5905: smad 'byung tshogs kyis gtor mas mchod pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:5906: h+aum gzugs ni lag gnyis me long 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:5907: gzugs mdzes spyod pas phyogs ba cur g.yos //
NK029(ha)001:5908: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:5909: gzugs kyi lha mo spyan la thim //
NK029(ha)001:5911: sgra ni lag gnyis pi wam brdeb //
NK029(ha)001:5912: bde ba'i sgra snyan phyogs bcur bsgrog /
NK029(ha)001:5914: sgra'i lha mo snyan la thim //
NK029(ha)001:5916: dri ni lag gnyis spos bsnams ste //
NK029(ha)001:5917: spos kyi sprin lding gdug pa 'phro //
NK029(ha)001:5918: kun tu tshim byed bro bsrungs thim //
NK029(ha)001:5919: dri yi lha mo shangs la thim //
NK029(ha)001:5921: ro ni lag gnyis snod bsnams ste //
NK029(ha)001:5922: bcud ldan ro mchog lnga brgyar ldan //
NK029(ha)001:5923: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:5924: ro'i lha mo ljags la thim //
NK029(ha)001:5926: reg ni rdo rje yongs 'khyud ma //
NK029(ha)001:5927: gnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yi //
NK029(ha)001:5928: gzugs mdzes spyod pa phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK029(ha)001:5929: reg gi lha mo sku la 'khril //
NK029(ha)001:5931: h+aum chos ni 'dul byas 'dus ma byas //
NK029(ha)001:5932: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:5933: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:5934: chos kyi lha mo thugs khar thim //
NK029(ha)001:5935: d+harma d+hartu badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:5937: h+aum bza' dang bca' dang btung dang sgo //
NK029(ha)001:5938: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK029(ha)001:5940: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i sngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:5942: bro gar phyag rgya 'phro 'du yis //'dzum ma nam mkhar 'gro bar 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:5943: glu tshig sgra'i phyag rgya yis //
NK029(ha)001:5944: chos kyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:5945: brgyan dang bgo ba'i phyag rgya yis //'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:5946: bza' dang btung ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK029(ha)001:5947: yid bzhin sku dang bdud rtsir 'grub //
NK029(ha)001:5948: a li ka li'i phyag rgya yis //
NK029(ha)001:5950: spyi don gsum pa bstod pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:5951: zhi ba'i glu drug nyid dam /
NK029(ha)001:5952: thabs kyi zhags pa nas 'byung ba'i glu brgyad kyis bstod de /
NK029(ha)001:5954: rgyal ba gang bzhugs 'khor dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:5955: bla med lha dang lha mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:5956: grub pa'i byin brlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK029(ha)001:5957: sems dpa' bcu drug rigs kyi gtso //
NK029(ha)001:5958: sems ma bcu drug rigs kyi yum //
NK029(ha)001:5959: mthu chen khro bo khro mo dang //
NK029(ha)001:5960: pho nya 'jig rten skyong bar ldan //
NK029(ha)001:5961: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni //'jig rten thams cad ma lus kun //
NK029(ha)001:5962: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK029(ha)001:5963: phyag rgya chen po bdag sbyor cig /
NK029(ha)001:5964: dpa' bo chen po mthu ldan rnams //
NK029(ha)001:5965: thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK029(ha)001:5966: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnams //'grub par byin gyis brlabs du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:5967: khams gsum zhing du sbyor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:5968: dmigs med chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:5969: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:5970: cir yang sprul pa'i sku la de nas yi dam kun la kha h+ai brjod //
NK029(ha)001:5975: phyag 'tshal mchod bstod la sogs pas gzhung bsrang /
NK029(ha)001:5976: de nas ma tshang ba tshang ba kha bskang la /
NK029(ha)001:5978: yi ge brgya pa rnams brjod /
NK029(ha)001:5979: de nas rgyu 'phrul dbang rgyud kyi gsol 'debs byed pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:5980: de nas bsnyen pa byed pa ni gnyiis te /
NK029(ha)001:5981: lha tog gi bsnyen pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:5986: rtog tshogs gang dang gang yin pa de lha de dang der gyur bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:5987: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid ces sogs dang /
NK029(ha)001:5989: mum da du shwa ri sogs brjod /
NK029(ha)001:5991: mnyam rdzogs dang mnyam rdzogs chen po'o //
NK029(ha)001:5992: dang po ni dkyil 'khor mi bsdu bar rang rdo
NK029(ha)001:5993: rje sems dpa' yab yum du gsal ba'i thugs khar
NK029(ha)001:5994: sngar 'khor bkod / de nas sngar kyi 'phreng ba
NK029(ha)001:5995: rang gi shang gong g.yas su phyung nas yum gyi
NK029(ha)001:5996: g.yon du rgyud bsgril ma g.yon du 'khor /
NK029(ha)001:5997: yang yum gyis g.yas nas rang gi g.yon du zhugs ste snying khar thim /
NK029(ha)001:5998: bsgril mar g.yas su 'khor bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:5999: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika mum da ru shwa ri brjod /
NK029(ha)001:6000: de bzhin du dmigs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:6002: gnyis pa mnyam rdzogs chen po ni /
NK029(ha)001:6003: lha tshogs kun rang yab yum du bsdu la /
NK029(ha)001:6004: lha tshogs spyi'i bsnyen pa rang yab yum gyis byas ste /
NK029(ha)001:6008: nang mchod sman rag gtor gsum /
NK029(ha)001:6012: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag ye shes rgya mtsho sogs kyis bstod /
NK029(ha)001:6013: de nas dam blangs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:6014: rdo rje gcig pa'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK029(ha)001:6015: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK029(ha)001:6016: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6017: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas rnams //'gro la phan phyir don du spyad //
NK029(ha)001:6018: byang chub spyod mchog dam pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:6019: sku gsung thug kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK029(ha)001:6020: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK029(ha)001:6021: rdo rje rgyal pos byin brlabs cig /
NK029(ha)001:6024: bo d+hi tsit+ta sa ma ya h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:6026: zhes gnas gsum du gtug go /
NK029(ha)001:6028: dang po byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:6029: dza gad dang mam sa gtso bor gyur pa'i tshogs
NK029(ha)001:6030: kyi yo byad rnams dkyil 'khor dang nya bar bshams
NK029(ha)001:6031: la / mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri sogs kyis bsangs /
NK029(ha)001:6032: ram yam kham gyi bsreg sogs bya /
NK029(ha)001:6034: zhal zas kyi snod du nyi ma la /
NK029(ha)001:6035: +aah h+aum tram kham 'od du zhu ba las byung
NK029(ha)001:6036: ba'i bza' btung gi dngos po ye shes lnga'i rang
NK029(ha)001:6037: bzhin gyi bdud rtsi ro brgya dang /
NK029(ha)001:6038: 'dod yon gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa /
NK029(ha)001:6039: so so'i lha mo rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang bcas pa'i sprin 'phro bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:6040: yi ge gsum lan gsum du brjod pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)001:6041: gnyis pa tshogs phul spyan drangs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:6042: bsod nams ye shes yongs rdzogs shing //
NK029(ha)001:6043: ma rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK029(ha)001:6044: ye shes zhi khro 'khor lo'i tshul //
NK029(ha)001:6045: tshogs mchog dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6046: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' nyid //
NK029(ha)001:6047: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo dang //'khor gyi khro bo sems dpar bcas //
NK029(ha)001:6048: sgo ba bzhi sogs gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6049: e h+ya hi sogs kyi tshogs zhing dpag tu med
NK029(ha)001:6050: pa zhig tshogs su sad par byas la thugs rje'i
NK029(ha)001:6051: lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK029(ha)001:6059: h+aum he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang /
NK029(ha)001:6060: dur drod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK029(ha)001:6062: dur drod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK029(ha)001:6063: zhing chen gsar rnying gdan du gting //
NK029(ha)001:6064: dmar gyi argam rgya mtshor dkyil //
NK029(ha)001:6065: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6066: ru lu ru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:6067: e h+ya hi a na ya dza h+aum bam hoh
NK029(ha)001:6068: yis khro tshogs dpag tu med pa spyan drangs la
NK029(ha)001:6069: dgu sogs bya / gsum pa mchod pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:6070: h+aum spos kyi sprin lding gdug pa mo sogs dang /
NK029(ha)001:6071: sh+ri badz+ra r+aa ga d+hu pa d+hu sogs bzhi bsnol dang /
NK029(ha)001:6072: h+aum rdo rje sgeg mo rdo rje can //
NK029(ha)001:6073: sems dpa' sngon po'i ye shes 'bebs //
NK029(ha)001:6074: me long lta bu'i ye shes las //
NK029(ha)001:6076: sh+ri badz+ra ra ga la s+ye h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:6077: yid bzhin rin chen 'od 'bar ma //'jam dpal sngon po'i dngos grub 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:6078: mnyam pa nyid kyi badz+ra ma l+ye'i badz+ra ma le'i ma le tram /
NK029(ha)001:6079: pad+ma dbyangs mkhan rma bya'i mgrin //
NK029(ha)001:6080: spyan ras gzigs kyi dngos grub 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:6081: so sor rtog pa'i badz+ra g+hirti'i g+hirti hri /
NK029(ha)001:6082: gar mkhan 'gying bag gzi ldan ma //
NK029(ha)001:6084: bya ba nan tan ye shes badz+ra n+rirti n+rirta a /
NK029(ha)001:6085: bzhi pa tshogs mchod 'bul ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:6090: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:6091: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer rnam par 'phros //'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan ste //
NK029(ha)001:6092: thugs dam bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6093: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos //'dod yon lha mo nam mkha' gang //
NK029(ha)001:6095: spyan sogs bde bas tshim gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6097: u pa b+h+yo ka ma ha hri pra ti ts+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:6100: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK029(ha)001:6101: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa'i dam tshig la //
NK029(ha)001:6102: sems can dbang gi nor 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK029(ha)001:6103: mi 'chab 'gyod pa'i sems kyi mthol lo bshags //
NK029(ha)001:6104: badz+ra sat+wa sogs kyi yi ge brgya pa brjod /
NK029(ha)001:6106: las kyi lam thod pa mtshan ngan du ling ga bcas la /
NK029(ha)001:6107: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:6108: bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa' dang zhi ba la gdug pa can bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:6110: na mo dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:6111: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:6112: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bka' chos can sgyu
NK029(ha)001:6113: 'bras bslu ba med pa' zhi khro sgyu 'phrul rnam
NK029(ha)001:6114: par rol ba'i lha tshogs rnams kyis sprul pa yang
NK029(ha)001:6115: srid bka' nyan dang bcas pa rnams kyis rigs sngags
NK029(ha)001:6116: 'chang rnams kyi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam par dag
NK029(ha)001:6118: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)001:6119: ma rung ba'i sems can bsgral ba'i zhing bcur rtogs pa thams cad /
NK029(ha)001:6120: mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la skad cig tsam gyis mchis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6124: tri badz+ra a ng+gu sha dza /
NK029(ha)001:6125: zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas bskug la /
NK029(ha)001:6126: dza h+aum bam ho yis dgug stim zhing myos par
NK029(ha)001:6127: byas ste gdug pa'i snying khar dwangs ma ye shes
NK029(ha)001:6128: kyi a dkar po dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:6129: bdag dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:6131: bzas pa po'i snying kha'i sgo phye /
NK029(ha)001:6133: ye shes lngar 'bab dug lnga ye shes gnas gyur /
NK029(ha)001:6134: dngas ma lnga sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i 'khor lor spar ste sangs rgyas par gyur /
NK029(ha)001:6136: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma r+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana /
NK029(ha)001:6137: sa ma ya mu tra mat+tam kha kha /
NK029(ha)001:6139: hri da ya pi pa h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:6140: snying ma rang snang sgyu 'phrul gyi 'khor lo khro
NK029(ha)001:6141: tshogs su 'bar bas rdo rje bza' ba'i dam tshig
NK029(ha)001:6143: h+aum nga ni za byed chen po ste /
NK029(ha)001:6144: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:6145: gdul da ka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:6146: sha rus la sogs za bar bya /
NK029(ha)001:6148: sarba dush+tana ma ra ya h+aum phata kyis /
NK029(ha)001:6149: ling ka'i gnas lngar phur bu btab pas bsad /
NK029(ha)001:6151: dum bur gtubs khog pa phral ste /
NK029(ha)001:6154: sh+ri badz+ra he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK029(ha)001:6158: ma h+aa ba su ta ma h+aa pan tsa a
NK029(ha)001:6159: mri ta kha kha kha le le le h+aum b+h+yo
NK029(ha)001:6161: h+aum bgegs dang dpa' ba 'jigs su rung pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:6162: rgod dang bshed dang 'jigs par ston pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:6163: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pas //
NK029(ha)001:6164: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK029(ha)001:6165: gar yang bsgrub po rnam 'byor las //
NK029(ha)001:6166: gar gyis dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK029(ha)001:6167: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK029(ha)001:6168: mam sa la sogs ro mchog bsil //
NK029(ha)001:6169: me tog la sogs tsan dan dri //
NK029(ha)001:6170: bzang dgu dbul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6171: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:6172: byin gyis barlobasa shig rnam 'byor las //
NK029(ha)001:6173: bsgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la /
NK029(ha)001:6174: h+aum dang phata kyi ldan par mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:6175: ces pas bsgral thal sbyor ba'i dam tshig chen por bsgrubs pas lha thams cad tshim par byas la /
NK029(ha)001:6176: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika kyis rdor sems zhi bar nga rgyal 'phos ste /
NK029(ha)001:6178: h+aum rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:6179: ston ka'i zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba //
NK029(ha)001:6180: bcom ldan bde gshegs rdo rje dbyings kyi 'khor //
NK029(ha)001:6181: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK029(ha)001:6182: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
NK029(ha)001:6183: phyag gnyan khro gtum rngam pa'i tshogs la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:6184: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK029(ha)001:6185: dgyes par rol cig mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:6186: zhes ste a la la yis dgyes par mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:6187: badz+ra e sa h+aum se sa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:6189: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:6192: zhes pas 'khor gsum bde ba chen por ro mnyam pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:6193: tshogs phud bzhi pa phud lhag bsre ba'i chas su bzhag /
NK029(ha)001:6194: lnga pa tshogs la rol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6195: dbang gi mthar mdzad pa phyag len yin no //
NK029(ha)001:6196: de nas rjes chog bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6200: dang po lhag ma bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6201: bdag gi thugs kha nas 'dod pa'i rgyal po phyung ste /
NK029(ha)001:6202: mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa drug rang dbang med pa spyan 'dren nas /
NK029(ha)001:6203: bcom ldan 'das rigs lnga'i 'khor brgyad brgyad zur bzhi bzhir bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:6218: sarba nan badz+ra ta ki hri da ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:6220: so so'i snying po phul nas /
NK029(ha)001:6221: zhing tshal pa'i gdan la bzhugs te /
NK029(ha)001:6226: mtshams rnams kyang de ltar bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:6227: kun kyang lag na gri dang thod pa thogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:6228: rus pa'i brgyan gyis lhub pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:6230: bdag gi ljags steng na h+r+aih las bdud rtsi'i chu
NK029(ha)001:6231: rgyun babs pas lha 'gron rnams ljags steng du thim
NK029(ha)001:6233: gtor ma bdud rtsi'i dgongs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:6234: yang gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur par gsal bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:6235: h+aum sarba badz+ra t+aa ka t+aa ki ni /
NK029(ha)001:6236: pra ti dza e mam b+ha ling ta h+aum phata kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:6237: sarba bud+ha t+aa ka ta ki ni pra ti dza e mam b+ha lim ta phata kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:6239: tram sarba rat+na t+aa ka t+aa ki ni pra ti
NK029(ha)001:6240: dza e mam b+ha lim ta tram phata kha hi
NK029(ha)001:6242: hrihsarba pad+ma t+aa ka t+aa ki ni pra ti dza he mam b+ha ling ta hrihphata kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:6244: ha sarba karma t+aa ki t+aa ki ni pra ti
NK029(ha)001:6245: dza e mam b+ha lim ta ha phata kha hi
NK029(ha)001:6246: / byang gi dagu'o //'di rnams rgyas par ni so so'i grangs tshad du bazla'o //
NK029(ha)001:6247: gtor ma dug gsum gyi rgya mtsho sha khrag rus
NK029(ha)001:6248: par bsgom nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams la btab pa
NK029(ha)001:6249: ni / dug gsum gyi dgongs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:6250: de nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams cag ge nyan par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:6251: rdo rje dril bu thogs la 'di skad do //
NK029(ha)001:6252: h+aum bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' la //
NK029(ha)001:6253: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:6254: mngon par dag pa'i 'jig rten na //
NK029(ha)001:6255: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6256: yi dwags stan la yang dag bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:6257: dbang po 'jigs pa'i gzugs bzhin can //
NK029(ha)001:6258: skal ldan rang gi lag char ldan //
NK029(ha)001:6259: gdug pa'i sems kyi ma rig byed //
NK029(ha)001:6260: sha khrag dang ni rgyu ma dang //
NK029(ha)001:6261: rkang dang tshil bu za spyod rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6262: za bar byed cing 'dren par byed //
NK029(ha)001:6263: gsod par byed cing 'phrog par byed //
NK029(ha)001:6264: kun gyi rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK029(ha)001:6265: shar gyi phyogs nas gshegs su gsol //'dir gshegs brgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK029(ha)001:6267: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrubs //
NK029(ha)001:6268: las bcol 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:6269: dpal dang ldan pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK029(ha)001:6270: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6271: gzi brjid che dang 'bar byed ma //'joms byed ma dang bong sna'i mgo /
NK029(ha)001:6272: kun kyang rang gi lho'i phyogs nas gshegs su gsol
NK029(ha)001:6273: //'dur gshegs brgyan gyi gtor ma bka'i pha 'bab 'di
NK029(ha)001:6274: bdag gi bsam pa las bcol bde ba can gyi
NK029(ha)001:6275: 'jig rten nas // rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6276: chags chen ma dang chags bral ma //'khor lo ma dang rgyas 'debs ma //
NK029(ha)001:6277: kun kyang nub kyi phyogs nas gshegs bka'i gtor ma
NK029(ha)001:6278: bdag gi las bcol rnam par dag pa'i 'jig rten
NK029(ha)001:6279: nas // rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6280: sna tshogs lus dang bsrungs ba mo //
NK029(ha)001:6281: gnod sbyin mo dang yang dag 'phrog /
NK029(ha)001:6282: kun kyang byang gi phyogs nas 'dir gshegs bka'i gtor
NK029(ha)001:6283: ma bdag gi las sha chen spungs pa'i 'jig rten
NK029(ha)001:6284: nas // bya rog gdong gi mig 'phrul can //'jigs pa'i mig dang 'jigs pa'i gdong //
NK029(ha)001:6285: shar lho'i nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6286: lag par gri dang khrag zhong thogs //
NK029(ha)001:6287: mchog tu sha dang khrag la dgyes //
NK029(ha)001:6288: kun kyang shar lho'i mtshams nas 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag
NK029(ha)001:6289: gi las bcol keng rus dpungs pa'i 'jig rten nas
NK029(ha)001:6291: khros pas khyi dang phag gi gdong /
NK029(ha)001:6292: lhun grub nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6294: kun kyang lho nub nam mkhar 'dir gshegs bka' yi
NK029(ha)001:6295: bdag gi las bcol rak+ta khrag gi rba klong nas
NK029(ha)001:6296: / rnga mo bung bu'i gdong 'dzin ma //
NK029(ha)001:6297: khros pas ra dang byi la'i gdong //
NK029(ha)001:6298: nub byang nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6299: rgyu ma'i mgo nas za bar byed //
NK029(ha)001:6300: kun kyang nub byang 'tshams nas 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag las bcol thal chen spungs pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK029(ha)001:6301: keng rus dkar po 'dzin pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:6302: khros pas rus pa'i 'phreng ba klubs //
NK029(ha)001:6305: lce spyang gis ni 'khor gyis bskor //'jig rten drag po'i mche ba gtsigs //
NK029(ha)001:6306: kun kyang byang shar 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag gi las bcol dpa' ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yi //
NK029(ha)001:6307: dkyil 'khor de yi grwa bzhi nas //'jigs byed mkha' 'gro bzhi byung ba //
NK029(ha)001:6308: shar gyi phyogs nas byung ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:6309: rdo rje mkha' 'gro chen mo ste //
NK029(ha)001:6310: srin po bong sna gshegs su gsol //'jigs byed 'bum phrag bcu dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:6311: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag gi las bcol lho'i phyogs nas 'byung pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:6312: rin chen mkha' 'gro chen mo ste //
NK029(ha)001:6313: rdo rje dus mtshan gshegs su gsol //'jigs byed 'bum phrag lnga dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:6314: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka'i las bcol nub kyi phyogs nas byung pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:6316: rdo rje dus kyi 'khor lo yang //'jigs byed bye ba 'bum dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:6317: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka'i las bcol byang gi phyogs nas byung ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:6318: las kyi mkha' 'gro chen mo ste //
NK029(ha)001:6319: rdo rje lang ka mgrin bcu yang //
NK029(ha)001:6320: gnod sbyin bye ba gsum dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:6321: byang gi phyogs nas gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6322: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag gi las bcol mkha' 'gro pho mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK029(ha)001:6323: sngon tshe bcom ldan rigs lnga yis //
NK029(ha)001:6324: pho rnams btul ste gdan du byas //
NK029(ha)001:6325: mo rnams btul ste 'dza' mor bya //
NK029(ha)001:6326: sems dpa' dam tshig dgongs pa bzhin //
NK029(ha)001:6327: bdag kyang rgyal ba'i bstan bsrung na //
NK029(ha)001:6328: las bcol 'phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6329: bar du gcod pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6330: myur du bsgral la med par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:6331: bdud 'dul mthu dang skal ldan tshe //
NK029(ha)001:6332: mdzod ldan nor dang 'khor rnams kyis //
NK029(ha)001:6333: dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK029(ha)001:6334: de nas gtor ma nam mkha' mthong par phyir dpags la /
NK029(ha)001:6335: gangs ri'ii rgyud la yod pa'i brtan ma spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:6336: h+aum dkyil 'khor de'i phyi rims nas /
NK029(ha)001:6337: gangs ri'i rgyud la gnas pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:6338: brtan ma'i tshogs kyi bskur ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:6339: lag tu rdo rje byin nas ming gis dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)001:6340: bod khams skyong ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:6341: bstan ma chen mo bcu gnyis kyang //
NK029(ha)001:6342: sngon gyi thugs dam bskong mdzod la //'dir gshegs bcol ba'i b+h+yo gung sngon mthon po'i yar stengs na //
NK029(ha)001:6343: nam mkha'i rgyal po rdo rje ting lo sman //
NK029(ha)001:6344: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum //
NK029(ha)001:6345: mo btsun khu chos rdo rje g.yar mo gsil //
NK029(ha)001:6346: skong btsun de mo rdo rje bod khams skyong //
NK029(ha)001:6347: lho'i skyi mthing rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong //
NK029(ha)001:6348: byang gi rma ting rdo rje ting lo btsun //
NK029(ha)001:6349: btsan la rol pa'i rdo rje sman gcig ma //
NK029(ha)001:6350: gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje g.yu bun ma //
NK029(ha)001:6351: gdal la btsan mo rdo rje ye ge mchog /
NK029(ha)001:6352: skyi mthing gangs kyi rdo rje la rol sman //
NK029(ha)001:6353: yang 'brog gser thang rdo rje 'brog srin mo //
NK029(ha)001:6354: khrag mthung chen mo rdo rje sgyu dril ma //
NK029(ha)001:6355: mi g.yo brtan ma'i rdo rje sa 'dzin mo //
NK029(ha)001:6356: de ltar gangs ri'i rgyud la gnas pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:6357: bstan ma chen mo bcu gnyis rnams //
NK029(ha)001:6358: bdud rtsi sman gyis g.yab dor gnas //
NK029(ha)001:6360: bcol ba'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:6361: bdag cag rnal 'byor 'dir 'dus dang //'khor du gtogs pa'i yon bdag gis //
NK029(ha)001:6362: rkyen la bab na rkyen bzlog cig /
NK029(ha)001:6363: sho la bab na sho gtor cig /
NK029(ha)001:6364: khram la bab na khram chog cig /
NK029(ha)001:6365: rims nad yam nad bcad pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:6366: ci la gyur pa'i nad rnams kun //
NK029(ha)001:6367: yud tsam gyis ni med par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:6368: ma h+aa ma sa la kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:6376: de nas rting shag yig brgya dang bcas pa brjod //
NK029(ha)001:6377: bsngo ba smon lam gyis rgyas gdab //
NK029(ha)001:6378: phun sum pa'i bkra shis brjod //
NK029(ha)001:6379: de nas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bsdu'o //
NK029(ha)001:6380: slar rdo rje sems dpa'i skur skad cig gis bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:6383: spyod lam gyi bya ba rnams bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:6384: zhi ba'i sngon rtogs rdzogs so //
NK029(ha)001:6385: de ltar dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)001:6386: byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)001:6387: mchod pa 'bul ba'i cho 'phrul dang gsum po 'di /
NK029(ha)001:6389: bum bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor drug dang /
NK029(ha)001:6390: mdun bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor drug po re la /
NK029(ha)001:6392: 'on kyang ma lcogs na gcig tu bsdus kyang grub po /
NK029(ha)001:6393: gnyis pa sngon 'gro rab gnas kyi rten rnams la byug pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:6394: sku gzugs pa'i rnam lnga dang /
NK029(ha)001:6395: til mar khu dang shing shun lngas phyis ste /
NK029(ha)001:6396: spos kyi dri zhim par byas la bzhag go /
NK029(ha)001:6397: dang po ba'i rnam lngas byug pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:6398: mkhar ba'i snod du ba'i rnam lnga bsres la dkyil
NK029(ha)001:6399: 'khor gyi lha bstan pa'i me long nang gi gzugs
NK029(ha)001:6400: brnyan la byug / sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ni h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:6404: de nas u dum w+aa ra /
NK029(ha)001:6408: spar pa de lnga'i shun pa phye ma'i lde gus byugs /
NK029(ha)001:6410: de nas ras kyi phyi bzhin rat+na pra ban tsa ra ha s+w+aa h+aa bkru ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:6411: de nas dri lnga'i chus dri bskyed de /
NK029(ha)001:6413: a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ye sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:6415: gu ru'i chas gos lnga ser por byas la /
NK029(ha)001:6416: spyi don gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi lha bskyed pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:6417: thal mo khong stong du sbyar la /
NK029(ha)001:6418: mah+aa shu nya ta d+harma d+hartu swa b+ha wa +aat+ma ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:6420: rab tu gnas par 'os pa'i rten thams cad stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK029(ha)001:6421: de nas bdag gtso bor gsal ba'i thugs kha'i h+aum las /
NK029(ha)001:6422: 'byung pa lnga'i yi ge e yam mam sum lam ram byung nas 'byung rims bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:6423: b+h+rum las gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:6424: de nas bdag yab yum sbyor ba'i byang sems las /
NK029(ha)001:6425: lha so so'i sa bon brgyad dam /
NK029(ha)001:6427: de las lhag pa gang mos ston la /
NK029(ha)001:6428: 'od du zhu ba la phyag mtshan yig 'bru grangs dang mnyam pa /
NK029(ha)001:6430: zhi ba'i lha dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'am /
NK029(ha)001:6432: rgyas pa la sogs mngon rtogs bzhin gsal bar bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:6433: de nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6434: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:6435: chos dbyings ye shes kyi ngo bo mi bskyod pas dbang bskur zhing rdo rje spyi bor btugs /
NK029(ha)001:6436: ma h+aa a ta ri sha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham //
NK029(ha)001:6437: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi ngo bo'i rnam par snang mdzad kyis dbang bskur zhing /
NK029(ha)001:6438: rdo rje dpral par gtug go /
NK029(ha)001:6439: rdo rje sna ltag g.yas su gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:6440: mah+aa sa ma ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:6441: mnyam nyid ye shes kyi ngo bo rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)001:6442: rdo rje rtag par gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:6443: mah+aa pra ta pra be sha na dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa a d+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:6444: sor rtogs ye shes kyi ngo bo snang ba mtha' yas kyi dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)001:6445: rdo rje rna ltag g.yon par gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:6446: ma h+aa kri t+ya nya sh+tha na dz+nya na badz+ra swab+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:6447: bya grub ye shes kyi ngo bo don yod grub pas dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)001:6449: na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang /
NK029(ha)001:6453: 'phrin las dang zhing khams zag pa med pa'i mi
NK029(ha)001:6454: zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang
NK029(ha)001:6455: / bden pa chen po'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)001:6456: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6457: rigs lnga ye shes lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:6458: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar lhun gyis grub pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6459: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6460: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6461: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6462: spyi bor rdo rje gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:6463: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swab+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:6464: lha rnams kyi dbu'i nang du /
NK029(ha)001:6465: sku rdo rje sku mdog dkar po re res byin gyis rlabs /
NK029(ha)001:6466: rdo rje mgrin par gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:6467: sarba ta th+aa ga ta w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:6469: gsung rdo rje sku mdog dmar po re res byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)001:6470: rdo rje thugs khar gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:6471: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:6472: thugs khar thugs rdo rje sku mdog sngon po re res byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)001:6473: rdo rje lte bar gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:6474: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa a nu ra ga badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:6475: lha rnams kyi lte bar yon tan rdo rje sku mdog ser po re res byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)001:6476: rdo rje gsang gnas su gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:6477: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa pu tsa badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:6478: lha rnams kyi gsang gnas su /
NK029(ha)001:6479: mchod pa'i rdo rje sku mdog ljang khu re res byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)001:6481: na mo phyogs bcu dus bcu bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad sku dang /
NK029(ha)001:6485: zhing khams zag pa med pa /
NK029(ha)001:6486: zad mi shes pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:6487: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis brten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6492: 'phrin las mi zad pa brgyan gyis 'khor lo lhun gyi grub pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6493: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6494: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6495: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6496: gsum pa ye shes pa spyan drangs zhing stim pa la snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:6497: h+aum dmigs med mkha' ltar dag cing khyab pa'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:6498: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK029(ha)001:6499: thugs rje'i ngang can chos sku dag pa las //
NK029(ha)001:6500: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6501: badz+ra sa man dza h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:6503: ho yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK029(ha)001:6504: nam mkha' bzhin du dam tshig nye bar gshegs //
NK029(ha)001:6505: yeshesa rgya mtsho rnam par grol ba'i klong //
NK029(ha)001:6506: mi gnas mi dmigs nam mkha'i dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK029(ha)001:6507: tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs thams cad dbyings kyi lha //
NK029(ha)001:6508: longs spyod rdzogs mdzad rol pa chen po'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:6509: rdo rje sems dpa' bskal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK029(ha)001:6510: thabs kyi ma rmongs bde chen dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK029(ha)001:6511: ye shes sgyu ma rnam par rol pa'i sku //'phags rje sprul pa mang po 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK029(ha)001:6512: thabs dang shes rab che la mnga' mnyes pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:6513: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs par bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6514: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha ya ho //
NK029(ha)001:6521: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6522: h+aum bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:6523: thugs rje chen po byon pa legs //
NK029(ha)001:6524: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK029(ha)001:6525: dgyes shing bstan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:6526: badz+ra sa ma ya dza h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:6529: 'gro mgon tshur gshegs gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:6530: khyod kyi bsod nams stobs kyi gdan byung bas //
NK029(ha)001:6531: mi 'jigs stobs kyi glang po dang //
NK029(ha)001:6532: cang shes dang ni dbang gi rma bya dang //
NK029(ha)001:6533: thogs med nam mkha' lding gi khri bshams te //
NK029(ha)001:6534: nyi zla pad+ma rin chen gdan steng su //
NK029(ha)001:6535: stobs bcu rtsal mnga' 'gro ba'i mgon gyur bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:6536: ma rig mun sel rin chen sgron me bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:6537: bdud rigs stong mdzad thar pa'i lam ston bzhugs //'gro ba 'dren mdzad thugs rje'i lcags kyu bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:6538: bcings pa grol mdzad byang chub lcam bral bzhugs //'gro drug sgrol mdzad sprul sku thub drug bzhugs /
NK029(ha)001:6539: bdud bzhi 'joms mdzad ta krid khro rgyal bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:6540: bstan pa bsrungs mdzad chos skyong bsrungs ma bzhugs //
NK029(ha)001:6542: bzhi pa dbang po la sogs kyi skyon gsal ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6543: mig sman dang a mri tas byug pa'i gser gyi thur ma sor brgyad pa thog la /
NK029(ha)001:6544: spyan sngar rab rib rnam rtog skyon bsal ste //
NK029(ha)001:6545: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med mtshan nyid do //
NK029(ha)001:6546: srin zhu'i tshul gyi gser gyi thub ma 'di //
NK029(ha)001:6547: sna tshogs yangs pa'i spyan gyis dbye bgyis pas //
NK029(ha)001:6548: rang dang spyi yi mtshan nyid chos rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:6549: chos sku ji ltar gzigs cing mkhyen pa ltar //
NK029(ha)001:6550: sangs rgyas ye shes spyan gyi dngos grub ste //
NK029(ha)001:6551: bdag blo dmun long lta bu sel bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:6552: tsak+shu tsak+shu sa man ta tsak+shu b+hi shwa d+ha ni swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:6553: ces spyan dbye ba ltar byas ste //
NK029(ha)001:6556: na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang /
NK029(ha)001:6560: 'phrin las zhing khams zag pa med pa zad mi
NK029(ha)001:6561: shes pa'i brgyan gyis 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang
NK029(ha)001:6562: / bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyi /
NK029(ha)001:6563: deng rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la gser gyi
NK029(ha)001:6564: thur mas spyan phyes pas ye shes kyi spyan phun
NK029(ha)001:6566: deng yon gyi bdag po che ge mo dang /
NK029(ha)001:6567: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6568: srid pa gsum gyis sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6569: gser gyi snyan gzhar thogs la /
NK029(ha)001:6570: ma 'gags gsal ba'i skyon rnams rnam dag kyang //
NK029(ha)001:6571: sems can ma lus bag chags bsal slad du //
NK029(ha)001:6572: gser gyi spab gzhar snyan gsal tshul 'di yis //
NK029(ha)001:6573: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can thams cad kyis //
NK029(ha)001:6574: dus gsum rgyal bas legs par gsungs pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:6575: bstan pa'i theg pa phyi nang ma lus kun /
NK029(ha)001:6576: skye ba kun tu thob pa'i dngos grub stsol /
NK029(ha)001:6577: tib bya ka rata na ye yo swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:6578: snyan gsal bar ltar byas la /
NK029(ha)001:6579: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK029(ha)001:6580: de ring rab du gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6581: gser gyi snyan gzhar gyi snyan spab bsal nas /
NK029(ha)001:6582: lha'i snyan rnam par dag pa /
NK029(ha)001:6583: de ring yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6584: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6585: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6586: gser gyi rmang rtse thogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:6587: shangs kyi rlung gis khams su skyod mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:6588: dbang gi mchog gi dri chab yul la rol //
NK029(ha)001:6589: thabs dang shes rab tshul gyi 'gro don mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:6590: nyon mongs skyon bral ye nas rnam dag la //
NK029(ha)001:6591: skur bsti ri mo gser gyi spar tsher gyis //
NK029(ha)001:6592: shangs kyi spu gsal rtogs pa'i dra ba bcom //
NK029(ha)001:6593: ye shes thog med rlung gi bka' bskyed nas //'og min bla med gnas su phyin par shog /
NK029(ha)001:6594: tib bya g+ha d+ha ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:6595: shangs kyi spu 'thog pa ltar byas la /
NK029(ha)001:6597: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6598: gser gyi spar tsher gyi shangs kyi spu rtogs pas /
NK029(ha)001:6599: pha rol sems kyis rnam grangs shes pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6600: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6601: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6602: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6603: gser gyi ljags gzhar thogs la /
NK029(ha)001:6604: ljags kyi dbang po rnam dag nas //
NK029(ha)001:6605: ro rnams thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:6606: sems can rnams gyi don slad du //
NK029(ha)001:6607: ljags kyi dri ma bsal bar bgyi //
NK029(ha)001:6609: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK029(ha)001:6610: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:6611: gser gyi ljags gzhar gyis ljags bzhar bas /
NK029(ha)001:6612: gsung rab mos pa so sor 'chad pa'i 'bras bus /
NK029(ha)001:6613: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6614: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6615: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6616: dngul gyi tshem shing thogs la //
NK029(ha)001:6617: dpal gyi 'gul nas tshangs pa'i ljags phyung bas /
NK029(ha)001:6618: cir yang 'gyur ba'i ljags kyis dbyibs bkram ste //
NK029(ha)001:6619: brgyad khri bzhi stong chos sgo ston mdzad pas //
NK029(ha)001:6620: tshems dkar bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rnam dag la //
NK029(ha)001:6621: rin chen mchog grub dngul gyi tshems shing gis //
NK029(ha)001:6622: bskur sti ri mo tshems kyi sgo gsal nas //
NK029(ha)001:6623: bdag cag gsung gi dngos grub thob gyur nas //'gro drug skad du dam chos ston par shog /
NK029(ha)001:6625: ces tshems kyi dri ma gsal ba ltar byas la /
NK029(ha)001:6627: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6629: tshems kyi dri ma bsal bas /
NK029(ha)001:6631: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6632: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6633: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6634: dung gi so mngas thogs la /
NK029(ha)001:6635: dbu lo rin chen lcang lor 'khyil ba yis //
NK029(ha)001:6636: mthon mthing g.yas su 'khyil ba'i lcang lo 'di //
NK029(ha)001:6637: mdzes pa'i gtsug gtor 'bar bas brgyan pa ltar //
NK029(ha)001:6638: lha mi kun gyi lta bas mi ngom pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:6639: dug gsum dri bral mtshan ma mi mnga' yang //
NK029(ha)001:6640: bskur sti ri mo dung gi so mngas gis //
NK029(ha)001:6641: shad pas dug gsum skyon rnams rang byang nas //
NK029(ha)001:6642: bdag dang 'gro kun rnam grol mchog thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:6644: ces pas longs sku rnams kyi dbu skra shad pa ltar byas la /
NK029(ha)001:6645: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6646: dung gi so mngas kyis dbu skra shad pa thams cad ma 'dres par 'gro ba'i don byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:6647: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6648: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6649: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6650: gser gyi chen po thogs la /
NK029(ha)001:6651: rgyal ba'i dbu gtsug mthon mthing ldan pa la /
NK029(ha)001:6652: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dri mas ma gos ste //
NK029(ha)001:6653: rin chen 'bar bas sdug bsngal kun las 'phags //
NK029(ha)001:6654: bltas pas mi ngom mtshan ma'i skyon bral yang //
NK029(ha)001:6655: bskur sti ri mo gser gyi chen po 'dis //
NK029(ha)001:6656: dbu skra zhabs sen 'brel pa'i tshul bstan nas //
NK029(ha)001:6657: dug gsum zung ngu rtog pa ku bcom nas //
NK029(ha)001:6658: sdug bsngal nyes pa bral nas bde thob ste //
NK029(ha)001:6659: thar pa'i mchog la bdag cag gnas gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6661: sprul sku rnams kyi dbu skra breg pa ltar byas nas //
NK029(ha)001:6663: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:6664: gser gyi chen pas thub pa drug gi dbu skra breg pas /
NK029(ha)001:6665: dug gsum zug ngu thams cad dang bral ba'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6666: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6667: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6668: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6669: de dag kyang lhag pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbang du'o //
NK029(ha)001:6670: thun mongs la sprul sku la so mngas mi dgos /
NK029(ha)001:6671: longs sku la chen pa mi dgos /
NK029(ha)001:6673: de ni tha mal pa'i skyon dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:6674: zag med mngon shes thob pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK029(ha)001:6675: lnga pa zhi ba'i lha rnams la che ba'i yon tan brgyan chas kyi dbang bskur ba gnyis ste /
NK029(ha)001:6676: thun mongs dang khyad par ro //
NK029(ha)001:6677: dang po bum pa'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)001:6678: rnam rgyal bum pa blangs la sngon gleng bzhi brjod /
NK029(ha)001:6680: phun sum tshogs pa'i bkra shis brjod cing /
NK029(ha)001:6681: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni /
NK029(ha)001:6682: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ltar /
NK029(ha)001:6683: lha yi chu ni dag pa yis /
NK029(ha)001:6684: de bzhin bdag gis sku khrus gsol /
NK029(ha)001:6685: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ye sh+ri ye h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:6686: ces dbu la bzhag pa'i tshul bya /
NK029(ha)001:6687: swa b+ha wa ces phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs
NK029(ha)001:6688: kha nas rigs kyi yum bzhi byung nas ye shes
NK029(ha)001:6692: dbu la rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i don dran par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:6694: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la rigs lnga'i dbu brgyan gyis /
NK029(ha)001:6696: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rtogs nas 'khor
NK029(ha)001:6697: ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad
NK029(ha)001:6699: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad ye shes lngar mdzad pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6700: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6701: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6702: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6704: dbu brgyan gyi mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6708: de nas bum chu blug la /
NK029(ha)001:6709: rigs lnga yab yum sbyor ba'i chu rgyun gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:6711: che ge mo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la rigs lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:6712: sems rnam shes tshogs brgyad rnams ye shes lngar gsal bar rtogs nas /
NK029(ha)001:6713: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos /
NK029(ha)001:6714: ye shes lngar mdzad pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6716: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:6717: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6718: cod pan gyi mnga' gsol ni /
NK029(ha)001:6719: h+aum dang hrihls cod pan sngon po dang dmar po bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6721: che ge mo'i dkyil 'khor gyis lha rnams la cod pan gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6722: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa nas /
NK029(ha)001:6723: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po byed pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6725: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6726: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6727: snyan chas mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6729: gser gyi snyan cha khog stong can bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6733: sgra thams cad rang gi rig pa las mi ga zhan pas /
NK029(ha)001:6734: gsan la gang yang ma 'gags par longs spyod pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6736: phyogs cu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6737: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis
NK029(ha)001:6738: thob par gyur cig /'gur chus mnga' gsol ba ni
NK029(ha)001:6742: che ge mo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6744: gsung lnga'i yon tan mthar phyin pas /
NK029(ha)001:6745: chos thams cad kyi don ma 'dres par ston cing /
NK029(ha)001:6746: gdul bya thams cad chud mi za ba'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6748: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6749: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6750: rat+na'i 'phreng bas mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6751: tram las rat+na'i 'phreng ba chu srin kha nas byung pa'i do shal dang /
NK029(ha)001:6756: do shal gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6757: don ma lus pa mi brjed pa'i gzungs dang /
NK029(ha)001:6758: sprul pa mtha' yas nyid las mi zhan pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6760: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6761: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6762: gser gyi dpung brgyan gyi mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6764: gser gyi dpung brgyan mu tig ha ra dang bcas pa bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6767: dpung brgyan gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6769: re dogs kyi mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6771: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6772: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6773: phyag gdub kyi mnga' gsol ni /
NK029(ha)001:6775: rat+na'i phyag gdub dang bcas pa bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6777: che ge mo phyag gdub kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6778: srog chags bsad pa la sogs pas /
NK029(ha)001:6779: yan lag tshul khrims dag pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6781: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6782: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i zhabs gdub kyi mnga' gsol ni /
NK029(ha)001:6783: swa 'phros 'dus pas gser gyi zhabs gdub 'phra mig dang bcas pa bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6784: bden pa'i che ge mo de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu lhun gyis grub pas /
NK029(ha)001:6785: thams cad zil gyis non cing dbang du sdud pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6788: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6791: sham thabs ras kyi gzhi ma ba ti dang /
NK029(ha)001:6792: gdugs sna tshogs kyis brgyan par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6793: bden che ge mo'i shams thabs kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6794: mkhyen pa'i bye brag ma 'dres par gsal /
NK029(ha)001:6795: don thams cad ma 'dres par yongs su rdzogs pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6797: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6798: sems can chen po lnga'i gdan khri'i mnga' gsol ni /
NK029(ha)001:6799: d+h+ai las seng ge la sogs pa'i sems can chen po lnga bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6801: che ge mo'i seng ge la sogs pa'i sems can chen po lnga /
NK029(ha)001:6802: gdan khri la mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6803: che ba'i yon tan lhun gyis grub ste /
NK029(ha)001:6804: mthar phyin pa'i sa non pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6806: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor srid pa gsum rin po che'i khri'i mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6808: rat+na'i khri rkang mdzod mig dang bcas pa lha dang lha mo mang po lang ling can bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6810: che ge mo'i nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK029(ha)001:6813: thabs thugs rje chen pos yongs su khyab pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:6814: shes rab chen pos mtha'i lta ba ngan pa thams cad sel ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:6815: chos thams cad la ma spangs spyod bzhin du ma chags pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6817: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6818: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis
NK029(ha)001:6819: thob par gyur cig /'od zer gyi mnga' gsol ba
NK029(ha)001:6820: ni / +aah h+aum swa h+aa lnga 'phro 'dus pas /
NK029(ha)001:6821: bden pa che 'od zer gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6822: chos thams cad bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes su gsal bas /
NK029(ha)001:6823: mtha' thams cad dang bral ba /
NK029(ha)001:6825: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6826: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6827: phyogs bcu'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor kyi mnga' gsol ni /
NK029(ha)001:6828: a las rgyab rten zla dkyil bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6829: bden che ge rgyab rten zla dkyil gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6830: mdzad pa mtha' dag ma 'gags par spyod kyang mnyam pa nyid las mi g.yo ba'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6832: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can
NK029(ha)001:6833: sku mdog gi mnga' gsol nas che ba'i yon tan
NK029(ha)001:6835: sku mdog mthing kha la sogs pa dkyil 'khor gyi
NK029(ha)001:6836: lha so so rang gi sku mdog gsal bar bsam
NK029(ha)001:6838: che ge mo'i lha rnams kyi sku mdog gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6839: gting dpag dka' ba mi 'gyur ba'i chos nyid do //
NK029(ha)001:6840: skyon gyis ma gos pa'i sems nyid /
NK029(ha)001:6841: yon tan gyi che ba rgyas pa /
NK029(ha)001:6843: sna tshogs rol pa'i 'phrin las la sogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:6845: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6846: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6847: dbu gsum gyi mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6849: dbu gsum gsal bar byas la /
NK029(ha)001:6852: dbu gsum gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6853: rnam thar sgo gsum thob nas /
NK029(ha)001:6854: khams gsum gyi don mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:6855: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis phyag drug gi mnga' gsol ba /
NK029(ha)001:6858: phyag drug gsal bar bya ste /
NK029(ha)001:6860: phyag drug gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6863: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can zhabs bzhis mnga' gsol /
NK029(ha)001:6865: zhabs bzhi gsal bar byas la /
NK029(ha)001:6868: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhis lhun grub kyi sa
NK029(ha)001:6869: la ma bsgrod par phyin cing bdud bzhi zil gyis
NK029(ha)001:6871: yon bdag dang phyogs bcu'i srid pa ljags kyi mnga' gsol /
NK029(ha)001:6873: ljags dmar ser glog ltar 'khyugs par sgom /
NK029(ha)001:6874: bden che ge 'chad byed rdzas kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6875: sgra yi yan lag bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK029(ha)001:6876: 'dul bya thams cad cig tu smin par byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:6877: yon phyogs bcu'i srid par che ba'i mnga' gsol ba /
NK029(ha)001:6878: k+sha'i spro bsdus mche ba dkar la dmar bar bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:6879: bden che ge mche bas mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6880: skye shi'i rtsa ba gcod cing sgrib pa thams cad zad par byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:6881: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can ral pas mnga' gsol pas /
NK029(ha)001:6882: dza'i spro bsdus ral pa mthon mthing lcang lo can bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:6883: bden che ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la ral pas mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6885: mthar mi ltung ba'i lta ba /
NK029(ha)001:6887: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6888: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6890: r+aa las smin ma 'khyug par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:6892: che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la smin mas mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6895: mkhas pas gdul bya thams cad chus mi gson par /
NK029(ha)001:6897: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can phyag mtshan drug gi mnga' gsol ba /
NK029(ha)001:6898: h+aum drug gis spro bsdus phyag mtshan drug bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:6900: che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6901: phyag mtshan gyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6902: ye shes drug gi 'gro don mthar phyin par mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:6904: phyogs bcu'i srid pa de rnams kyi mnga' gsol ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:6905: don drug pa chu dag gis sku khrus gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:6906: gzhung gi phyag 'tshal dkyil 'khor gsum po'i lha'i sku la khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6907: so so'i dri ma dag nas 'bras bu thob par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:6910: ga kun 3 bzang mchod pa dang gsum po las /
NK029(ha)001:6911: gzhung nas so sor blangs la /
NK029(ha)001:6912: de nas bden pa so so'i 'dod gsol bya /
NK029(ha)001:6914: che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6916: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams dang gnyis su med par 'jal ba'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6918: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6919: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6920: phyag brgya'i p+au dza phul ste /
NK029(ha)001:6921: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6922: phyag rgya'i p+au dza phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:6923: phyag rgya dam tshig gi sgo nas /
NK029(ha)001:6924: phyag rgya bzhi yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu /
NK029(ha)001:6925: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum kun tu bzang po'i p+au dza phul te /
NK029(ha)001:6926: bden che ge'i lha rnams la kun tu bzang po'i p+au dza phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:6927: bdag nyid chen po'i p+au dzas longs spyod pa'i skal ba /
NK029(ha)001:6928: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can phyag dang zhabs gsil la /
NK029(ha)001:6929: ye shes sku la dri ma mi mnga' yang /
NK029(ha)001:6930: sems can nyes byas dri ma sbyang slad du /
NK029(ha)001:6931: rgyal ba'i phyag zhabs dag ni bsil bgyis pas /
NK029(ha)001:6932: sems can phyi nang dri ma dag par shog /
NK029(ha)001:6933: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la phyag dang zhabs bsil gsol pas /
NK029(ha)001:6934: phyi nang gi dri ma thams cad yongs su dag pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:6935: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum chu gtsang gis khrus gsol la /
NK029(ha)001:6936: ye shes sku la nyon mongs mi mnga' yang /
NK029(ha)001:6937: sems can nyon mongs bag chags sbyang slad du /
NK029(ha)001:6938: rgyal ba'i sku la chu gtsang khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6939: sems can nyon mongs bag chags dag par shog /

NK029(ha)001:6941: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma thams cad dag /
NK029(ha)001:6942: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyi yung chab gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6943: ye shes sku la rab rib mi mnga' yang //
NK029(ha)001:6944: sems can ma rig mun pa bsal slad du //
NK029(ha)001:6945: rgyal ba'i sku la yung chab khrus gsol bas //
NK029(ha)001:6946: rmongs pa'i rab rib ma lus dag par shog /
NK029(ha)001:6947: bden che ga'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la yung chab kyis sku khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6948: nyon mongs pa shes bya'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:6949: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu /
NK029(ha)001:6951: phyogs bcu'i srid pa 'dag chal gyi khrus gsol la /
NK029(ha)001:6952: rnam dag sku la dri ma mi mnga' yang /
NK029(ha)001:6953: sems can sdug bsngal dri ma gsal slad du /
NK029(ha)001:6954: 'dag chal dag gi sku khrus 'di gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6955: tshul khrims mngon par byang chub sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:6957: bden pa che ge 'dag chal gyi khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6958: nyon mongs pa rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ste /
NK029(ha)001:6959: tshul khrims kyi phung po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6960: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)001:6963: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis thob par gyur cig /'bru chab gsol la /
NK029(ha)001:6964: chos kyi sku la snyel sgrib mi mnga' yang /
NK029(ha)001:6965: sems can mu ge'i sgrib pa sbyang slad du /
NK029(ha)001:6966: rat+na 'bru chab 'di dag gsol ba yis /
NK029(ha)001:6967: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po chos kyi sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:6968: bden che 'bru chab kyi sku khrus gsol bas //
NK029(ha)001:6969: rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag ste /
NK029(ha)001:6970: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6971: chos kyi sku la nyes pa'i bag chags dri ma
NK029(ha)001:6972: thams cad dag yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa spos
NK029(ha)001:6973: chab gsol la / 'phrin las lhun rdzogs bde gshegs sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)001:6974: spos mchog dri yis sku khrus 'di gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6975: dri mchog stong gsum kun tu 'byung ba yis /
NK029(ha)001:6976: shes rab phung po sprul sku thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:6977: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la spos mchog dri yis sku khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6978: 'od gsal shes rab kyi phung po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6981: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum sman chab gsol la /
NK029(ha)001:6982: rdo rje'i sku mchog nam mkha'i rang bzhin la /
NK029(ha)001:6983: dri med chab kyis sku khrus 'di gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6984: nyon mongs duh kha nad 'joms rgyal po 'di /
NK029(ha)001:6985: rnam grol phung po rdo rje'i sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:6987: che ge mo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:6988: sman chab kyi sku khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6989: nyon mongs pa'i nad thams cad dag ste /
NK029(ha)001:6990: rnam par grol ba'i phung po dang /
NK029(ha)001:6993: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:6994: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:6996: chos rnams yongs su rdzogs pa'i sku mchog la /
NK029(ha)001:6997: rat+na lnga chab sku khrus 'di gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:6998: yid bzhin nor ltar re ba bskong pa yi /
NK029(ha)001:6999: ye shes phung po longs spyod rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7000: bden che ge rat+na lnga chab gsol la /
NK029(ha)001:7001: sems can ma lus re ba bskong ste //
NK029(ha)001:7002: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes mthong ba'i phung po dang /
NK029(ha)001:7004: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa ras kyi sku phyis la //
NK029(ha)001:7005: thugs rje lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)001:7006: srid zhu gus phyir ras kyis sku phyis pas /
NK029(ha)001:7007: las dang nyon mongs bag chags kun spangs nas /
NK029(ha)001:7008: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sgo thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:7009: bden che ge ras kyi sku phyis pas /
NK029(ha)001:7010: las dang nyon mongs thams cad dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:7011: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sgo thob /
NK029(ha)001:7012: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum bdun pa phyi nang p+au dza dbul ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:7013: kun tu bzang po gzhung nas len dang /
NK029(ha)001:7014: phyag dang zhabs bsil yang 'dir mdzad /
NK029(ha)001:7015: las gzhung gi me tog dbul ba'i tshig yang 'dir brjod /
NK029(ha)001:7017: yon tan lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)001:7018: rat+na mdzes pa'i me tog 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7019: log lta'i nyon mongs tha ba kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)001:7020: lta bas mi ngoms mdzes pa'i sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:7021: push+pe sngags tshig gis me tog dbul /
NK029(ha)001:7022: bde che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la rat+na'i me tog phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7024: tshogs thams cad yongs su rdzogs nas lta bas mi ngoms pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)001:7026: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7027: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:7029: mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i sku mnga' ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:7030: sangs rgyas sku la bdug spos 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7031: dam tshig sdom pa'i nyes pa kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)001:7032: ye shes thugs rjes ma lus 'dren par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7034: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la gdug spos phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7035: theg pa so so'i sdom pa'i dri ma las grol ste /
NK029(ha)001:7036: dam tshig rnam par dag nas thugs rje chen po dang /
NK029(ha)001:7038: srid pa ma lus pa yongs su 'dzin pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)001:7040: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7041: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:7043: thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)001:7044: mun pa snang byed mar me 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7045: ma rig 'thib po'i mun pa kun gsal nas /
NK029(ha)001:7046: sangs rgyas spyan mnga' yongs su rdzogs par shog /'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7047: a lo ke sngags kyi tshig brjod /
NK029(ha)001:7048: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la mar me phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7049: lhan cig skyes pa'i gti mug las byung pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:7050: rab rib yongs su dag pas /
NK029(ha)001:7053: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7054: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:7056: snyigs ma lnga nyid 'bras bur yongs rdzogs pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:7057: sangs rgyas sku la dri chab 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7058: mya ngan zug ngu'i gdung ba kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)001:7059: 'od zer sna tshogs 'gyed pa'i sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:7061: bden che ge'i lha rnams la dri chab phul pas /
NK029(ha)001:7062: mya ngan gyi gdung ba thams cad dang bral nas 'od zer mtha' yas 'gyed pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)001:7064: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7065: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:7066: sman mchod lugs bzhin gzhung nas slangs bya /
NK029(ha)001:7067: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa yis /
NK029(ha)001:7068: sangs rgyas sku la bdud rtsi 'adiphula bas /
NK029(ha)001:7069: dug lnga gdod nas sems su dag pa yi /
NK029(ha)001:7070: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7071: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la bdud rtsi lnga phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7072: dug lnga ma spangs gnas su dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:7073: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:7075: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7076: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:7077: b+ha ling lugs bazhinah+aum bza' ces gzhang nas blangs /
NK029(ha)001:7079: chos rnams longs spyod rdzogs grub pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:7080: sangs rgyas sku la gtor ma 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7081: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)001:7082: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7083: bden che ge gtor ma phul bas rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba thams cad dang bral nas /
NK029(ha)001:7084: gsang ba'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:7085: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyis p+au dza byas la /
NK029(ha)001:7086: bde gshegs sku la ting 'dzin mchod phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7087: phyi nang gsang don ma lus kun rdzogs te /
NK029(ha)001:7088: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes nas //'bras
NK029(ha)001:7089: bu mtha' yas kun la longs spyod shog bden pa
NK029(ha)001:7090: brjod / che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7091: dngos po ma lus pa'i ngo bo nyid rang bzhin gyi sku dang /
NK029(ha)001:7092: ye shes su lhun gyis grub pa /
NK029(ha)001:7094: spyod yul yongs su dag pa /
NK029(ha)001:7095: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa sgrol mchod sngags gzhung nas slangs tshig brjod la /
NK029(ha)001:7096: ye shes spyod yul yongs dag pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:7097: sangs rgyas sku la ta gan 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7098: khams gsum dug sum rtsad nas dag gyur ste /
NK029(ha)001:7099: sku gsum dngos grub lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7100: bden che ge ta gan 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7101: dug gsum yongs su dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:7102: sku gsum lhun gyis grub ste /
NK029(ha)001:7105: phyogs bcu'i srid pa sbyor mchod tshig sngags bsam rgyud bya /
NK029(ha)001:7107: sangs rgyas sku la g+ha na 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7108: phyi nang byang chub sems su rnam dag ste /
NK029(ha)001:7109: mtha' yas snyoms par 'jug pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7110: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor kyi lha rnams la g+ha na sbyor ba'i p+au dza 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7111: thabs dang shes rab kyi spyod pas snod bcud thig le chen po'i ye shes su dag ste /
NK029(ha)001:7112: mtha' yas lhun gyis grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK029(ha)001:7114: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7115: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad
NK029(ha)001:7116: kyis thob par gyur cig /'dod yon lnga yi p+au
NK029(ha)001:7117: dza phul la / mtha' yas ldan dang bral ba med pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:7118: sangs rgyas sku la 'dod yon lnga phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7119: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung pa kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)001:7120: bde ba chen po'i thabs rnams rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7121: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la 'dod yon lnga phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7122: longs spyod yongs su dag pa sogs pa gcig pa'i thabs yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:7124: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7125: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:7126: lha la glu ye shes kyis p+au dza phul ste /
NK029(ha)001:7127: lang tshor rab rgyas glu dbyangs sgrogs byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:7128: smad byung glu yi mchod pa 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7129: dbang po'i zhen chags gdug pa kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)001:7130: mngon shes legs thob kun gyis bkur bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:7132: na mo phyogs che ge che ba'i ye shes mngon par mthong nas /
NK029(ha)001:7133: so so'i skye bo la sogs pa thams cad kyi bskur gnas su gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:7134: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa lha mo cig tu spros
NK029(ha)001:7135: la rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa phul la
NK029(ha)001:7136: / s+au ra to'i tshig gis dbul /
NK029(ha)001:7137: gdangs snyan sgra yi mchod pa dam pa 'di /
NK029(ha)001:7138: rab 'byams sangs rgyas dgongs pa rdzogs phyir 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7139: zhen 'dzin 'khrul pa ma lus kun bral na /
NK029(ha)001:7140: rna ba'i dga' ston phyogs bcur 'gyed par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7143: che ge mo'i thabs mkhas pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis bya
NK029(ha)001:7144: ba mang pos bdag gzhan gyi don thams cad 'grub
NK029(ha)001:7145: par yon phyogs srid pa lhab lhub bla res la
NK029(ha)001:7146: sogs phul la / gzi byin khyad par shin tu 'phags pa yi /
NK029(ha)001:7147: sangs rgyas sku la lhab lhub bla bre 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7148: log pa'i lta ba mtha' dag kun spangs nas /
NK029(ha)001:7149: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7150: bden na mo phyogs che ge thams cad thugs rje'i dbang gis bla bres brdal ba chen po /
NK029(ha)001:7152: phyogs bcu'i srid pa 'phan phul la /
NK029(ha)001:7153: mdzes pa'i dar lce g.yo ba phyogs bcur bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:7154: sangs rgyas sku la mdzes 'phan 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7155: sems can log pa'i g.yo ba kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)001:7156: mkhyen pa'i ye shes thogs pa med par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7157: bden pa na mo che ge thams cad bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes cir yang mdzes pas /
NK029(ha)001:7158: shes bya thams cad khong du chud cing thams cad 'dir ston pas /
NK029(ha)001:7163: skyabs chen 'khor yug mdzes pa'i brgyan dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:7164: sangs rgyas sku la gdugs mchog 'di phul bas //'khor ba'i tsha gdung sdug bsngal kun bral nas //
NK029(ha)001:7165: thams cad skyobs pa'i mthu dang ldan par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7166: bden na mo phyogs che ge thams cad thugs rje'i
NK029(ha)001:7167: skyabs kyis mtha'i duhkhasa gdungs pa bsil bar byed pa
NK029(ha)001:7168: / yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa rgyal mtshan phul la /
NK029(ha)001:7169: mi mthun phyogs las rgyal ba rgyal mtshan 'dir //
NK029(ha)001:7170: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams la phul ba yis //
NK029(ha)001:7171: mtshan ma yod med kun dang bral gyur nas //
NK029(ha)001:7172: bdud bzhi la sogs kun las rgyal ba shog /
NK029(ha)001:7174: na mo che ge'i bdud bzhin las rgyal ba'i chos kyi tog chen po mngon du byung pa /
NK029(ha)001:7175: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa yol ba phul la /
