NK029(ha)001:7176: mi mthun gnod pa'i g.yo ba kun la skyob //
NK029(ha)001:7177: sangs rgyas sku la yol ba 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7178: nyes tshogs mtha' dag ma lus kun bral nas //
NK029(ha)001:7179: thams cad skyobs pa'i bdag nyid chen por shog /
NK029(ha)001:7180: bden na mo che ge sems nyid rgya dang bral bar rtogs ste //
NK029(ha)001:7181: thams cad bdag nyid che bar skyob pa //
NK029(ha)001:7182: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa na bza' phul la /
NK029(ha)001:7183: byams mgon chen po kun la snyoms pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:7184: sangs rgyas sku la na bza' 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7185: tha bas rgyags pa'i spyod pa kun bral ste //
NK029(ha)001:7186: gzi byin khyad par 'aphata pa'i sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:7187: bden na mo che ge tha bas rgyags pa'i spyod pa dang bral ste /
NK029(ha)001:7188: ngo tsha shes pa thams cad skyob cing gzi byin khyad par du 'phags pa /
NK029(ha)001:7190: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gling bzhi man+dala rat+nasa sprul pa phul la /
NK029(ha)001:7191: 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' mnyes pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:7192: sangs rgyas sku la dkyil 'khor 'di phul bas //'phags pa'i nor gyis dbul ba kun bral ste //
NK029(ha)001:7193: ting 'dzin 'bum phrag yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7194: bden na mo che ge 'phags pa'i nor bdun dang /
NK029(ha)001:7198: yul zhing khang pa dang bcas pa dbul /
NK029(ha)001:7199: h'u 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK029(ha)001:7200: bde gshegs sku la yul mkhar 'di 'bul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7201: yul snang 'dzin pa'i 'ching ba kun bral nas //'phags pa'i zhing khams rnam dag thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7203: che ge mo'i zhing khams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7204: gzhal yas khang yongs su dag pa /
NK029(ha)001:7206: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7207: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i bran pho mo phul ste /
NK029(ha)001:7209: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par 'phags yi //
NK029(ha)001:7210: bde gshegs sku la pho mo'i bran phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7211: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs spong nas //'khor rnams yongs smin tshogs la dbang byed shog /
NK029(ha)001:7213: che ge mo 'khor gsum dag ste dbang bskur ba /
NK029(ha)001:7215: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i bu dang bu mo phul ste /
NK029(ha)001:7217: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par 'phags yi //
NK029(ha)001:7218: bde gshegs sku la lcam sring 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7219: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs su 'dul /
NK029(ha)001:7220: sprul pa'i gdul bya mtha' dag dbang byed shog /
NK029(ha)001:7221: bden che ge mo'i sprul pa bsam yas kyi khams gsum ma lus pa'i don la dbang byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:7222: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa chung ma phul ste /
NK029(ha)001:7224: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par 'phags yi //
NK029(ha)001:7225: bde gshegs sku la gzung ma 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7226: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs su 'dul //
NK029(ha)001:7227: gsang spyod yongs su dag pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7229: che ge mo'i gsang ba'i longs spyod dag pa /
NK029(ha)001:7230: yon bdag phyogs bcu' srid pa gsum gyis rol mo ye shes kyi p+au dza phul te /
NK029(ha)001:7232: rang bzhin rnam dag bde gshegs sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)001:7233: glu dbyangs snyan pa'i mchod pa 'di 'bul bas /
NK029(ha)001:7234: chos rnams skye 'gag med pa'i ngo bo la /
NK029(ha)001:7235: 'gro ba kun gyi spyod yul thob par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7237: rdo rje'i spo la phyin ste /
NK029(ha)001:7238: chos sgra chen po sems can ma lus pa'i rgyud yongs su grol bar byed pa /
NK029(ha)001:7239: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis tshogs gzhung bzhin phul ste /
NK029(ha)001:7240: yongs su smin pa phun sum tshogs pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:7241: bde gshegs sku la tshogs mchod 'di 'bul bas //
NK029(ha)001:7242: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK029(ha)001:7243: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)001:7245: che ge mos bsod nams dang ye shes kyis tshogs su rdzogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:7246: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7247: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:7248: brgyad pa bden pa'i byin brlabs byas te /
NK029(ha)001:7250: slob dpon gyi g.yas pas yung dkar dang rdo rje gsor /
NK029(ha)001:7253: yon bdag gis me tog thogs la /
NK029(ha)001:7254: dam tshig rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7255: rig pa btul shugs kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7256: rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7257: lam yongs su dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7258: dam tshig dang sdom pa rnams kyis bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7259: chos mnyam pa nyid kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7260: ngo bo nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i byin brlabs kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7261: sa rnams yongs su non pa'i yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7262: ta tha rnams kyis mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams ji srid du /
NK029(ha)001:7264: che ge'i don yongs su ma rdzogs kyi bar du
NK029(ha)001:7265: brtan par bzhugs nas sems can kyi don yongs su
NK029(ha)001:7270: ces yungs dkar dang me tog dor /
NK029(ha)001:7271: dgu pa yon bdag gis bskor ba bya /
NK029(ha)001:7272: slob dpon gyis smon lam gdab /
NK029(ha)001:7274: cho ga'i lha rnams la bskor ba byas la /
NK029(ha)001:7275: dus 'di nas ji srid snying po byang chub la thug gi bar du /
NK029(ha)001:7277: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7278: sems can thams cad mos pa yongs su mi nyams shing /
NK029(ha)001:7279: chos thams cad bdag nyid chen por lhun gyis grub pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:7280: ho chos nyid byang chub sems kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7281: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las
NK029(ha)001:7282: mi zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lor sangs rgyas pa'i
NK029(ha)001:7283: bden pa dang / de bzhin gshegs pa 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs dang /
NK029(ha)001:7287: cho ga las kyi rim pa'i gzhung rdzogs par bya ba'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)001:7288: deng 'dir yon bdag che ge mos /
NK029(ha)001:7289: ting 'dzin yon bdag che ge mos /
NK029(ha)001:7290: dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs su gsol ba'i sems bskyed nas /
NK029(ha)001:7291: sku dang brgyan chas bzhengs su gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:7292: yo byad dka' bas bsdus ste /
NK029(ha)001:7293: rab tu gnas pa gzhung bzhin byas nas /
NK029(ha)001:7294: bstan par bzhugs su gsol ba'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)001:7297: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor ma lus pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7298: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad dkyil 'khor 'di dang nam du yang mi 'bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:7299: de dag gi phung po dang /
NK029(ha)001:7301: skye mched thams cad dkyil 'khor 'di yi ngo bor
NK029(ha)001:7302: lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas 'grub par gyur cig
NK029(ha)001:7306: zhi ba'i lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rab gnas cho ga rdzogs so //
NK029(ha)001:7308: bla ma dang yi dam gyi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:7309: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i sbyin bsreg gi rim pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:7310: zhi khro gang byed gzhung bsrang /
NK029(ha)001:7313: rnam rgyal bum pa dang las bum byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)001:7314: zhi khro snying po 'dzab tu bsgrang /
NK029(ha)001:7315: mchod bstod tshar ba dang bdag 'jug blangs /
NK029(ha)001:7316: de nas me thab bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:7318: spangs su chags pa gang ba bya /
NK029(ha)001:7319: de'i dbus su rtse khru gang dbus su zlum por bskor /
NK029(ha)001:7320: sor bzhi nang du bskyal la zlum por bskor /
NK029(ha)001:7321: de'i sor bzhi gyen du rtsigs /
NK029(ha)001:7322: de nas sor bzhi nang du 'jal zlum por bskor /
NK029(ha)001:7323: de'i nang du mtho gang ba gcig yong ste /
NK029(ha)001:7324: de mthur bsag pa brus la nang du sor bzhi tsam 'ong bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:7325: de la me'i sa bon ram bri bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:7326: de'i steng du shug pa la sogs pa'i shing dkar po khru gang pa tsam du btubs ste /
NK029(ha)001:7327: gcig gi steng du gcig bzhag la brtsigs par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:7328: steng du mtha' nas bskor ba'i tshul du brtsigs la khong seng can du cung zad bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:7329: shing med na ba glang gi lci bas kyang gzhung bshad do //
NK029(ha)001:7330: de nas rnal 'byor pa kha shar du bltas la /
NK029(ha)001:7332: khyad par rang gi mchod rdzas bshams /
NK029(ha)001:7333: g.yon phyogs su thun mong gi mchod rdzas bshams /
NK029(ha)001:7334: phyi rim gru chad lha snams sgo la sogs pa grub chad bri bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:7336: mar la sogs bsreg rdzas ni /
NK029(ha)001:7337: thabs kyi yan lag yon bdag rgyas /
NK029(ha)001:7338: ces pas thabs kyang rgyas par bya'o //'byor ba 'phel ba'i phyir mar dang /
NK029(ha)001:7339: gzi brjid 'phel ba'i phyir yam shing dang /
NK029(ha)001:7340: lhag par shes rab 'phel ba'i phyir bud shing dang /
NK029(ha)001:7341: bdag bsrung ba'i phyir ku sha dang /
NK029(ha)001:7342: nad zhi ba'i phyir nyungs dkar dang /
NK029(ha)001:7343: bsod nams rgyas pa'i phyir 'bras dang /
NK029(ha)001:7344: sdig pa dag pa'i phyir til dang /
NK029(ha)001:7345: nor dang 'bru 'phel ba'i phyir so ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:7346: stobs che ba'i phyir sran ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:7347: dbang thang rgyas par bya ba'i phyir nas dang /
NK029(ha)001:7348: tshe 'phel ba'i phyir dur ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:7350: shes rab che ba'i phyir 'o ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:7352: shing gshags pa'i rtser mar byugs la /
NK029(ha)001:7353: brgya rtsa brgyad dam nyi shu rtsa gcig gam /
NK029(ha)001:7354: bdun bdun gyi gang 'grub bsham mo //
NK029(ha)001:7355: zhi rgyas dbang drag kha bsgyur du shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:7356: thab kyi drung du zhi ba la shar /
NK029(ha)001:7359: drag po la las gang byed kyi phyogs su 'dug la /
NK029(ha)001:7360: yang snying po brjod cing nang mchod kyis yo byad bsang /
NK029(ha)001:7362: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum yongs su gyur pa'i thab zhi ba la dkar zlum po /
NK029(ha)001:7363: mu ran la rdo rje'i 'phreng bas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)001:7364: rgyas pa la gru bzhi gser po /
NK029(ha)001:7365: mu ran la rin po che'i 'phreng bas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)001:7366: dbang la zla gam dmar po /
NK029(ha)001:7367: mu ran la pad+ma'i 'phreng bas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)001:7368: drag po la gru gsum nag po /
NK029(ha)001:7369: mu ran la rdo rje gdengs pas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)001:7370: phyogs 'dis phyed la rgya'i phyed kyi dpangs dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:7371: dwangs zhing thogs pa med pa las dang mthun pa'i bud shing rtsigs pas gang par bskyed nas /
NK029(ha)001:7372: slar yang h+aum gis byin gyis brlabs po /
NK029(ha)001:7373: 'jam po gsum la bsreg rdzas g.yas dang /
NK029(ha)001:7375: drag po la bsreg rdzas g.yon dang /
NK029(ha)001:7376: mchod rdzas g.yas su bsham mo //
NK029(ha)001:7377: re re la 'ang +aah h+aum las byung ba'i rdzas dwangs zhing thogs pa med par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:7378: las so so'i sngags kyis byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)001:7379: de nas yi dam kyi snying po'i mthar /
NK029(ha)001:7383: drag po la g.yon bskor ste /
NK029(ha)001:7384: shar lho nas me sbar la bslug cing /
NK029(ha)001:7385: badz+ra dz+wa la'i sngags brjod la /
NK029(ha)001:7387: me de bsang zhing gsos nas teng nge 'dzin gyis dpal chen po'i thugs kha nas /
NK029(ha)001:7388: yi ge ram dmar po 'od dang bcas pas thab khu du byung /
NK029(ha)001:7389: de las me ril po gcig tu gyur /
NK029(ha)001:7390: de las spro bsdus byas pa las /
NK029(ha)001:7391: ag+ne dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:7393: me lha drang srong khros pa'i cha byad can /
NK029(ha)001:7395: phyag g.yas dang po na lcags kyu /
NK029(ha)001:7397: g.yon dang po na lcags kyu /
NK029(ha)001:7399: zangs kyi ra skyes la chibs pa /
NK029(ha)001:7400: dur khrod kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:7401: ye shes kyi me lha mchod cing spyan drangs pa'i rim pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:7403: h'u ye shes sman kyi spyod yul nas /
NK029(ha)001:7404: me lha drang srong 'khor dang bcas /
NK029(ha)001:7405: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis /
NK029(ha)001:7406: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs me'i lha /
NK029(ha)001:7407: sems can don la dam tshig dgongs /
NK029(ha)001:7410: ag ne ye dz+nya na sa ma ye e h+ya hi /
NK029(ha)001:7412: mah+aa ka ru ni ka kri sha ho /
NK029(ha)001:7416: zhes phyag rgya rnam bzhis shar lho nas spyan drangs nas /
NK029(ha)001:7417: h+aum tshangs pa 'jig rten mgon gyi sras //
NK029(ha)001:7418: gzi brjid 'bar ba me'i lha //'dod pa thams cad rab bsgrub phyir //
NK029(ha)001:7419: thugs rjes sems can don mdzad pa //'bar ba'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:7420: ag ne ye sa ma ye tish+tha badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:7421: zhes pas dbyer med par stim zhing bzhugs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:7422: h+aum pad+ma rigs las grub pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:7423: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /'phrin las kun gyis dpang po mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:7425: ag ne ye a la la hoh drang srong chen po sngon chad ma dar ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:7426: ting 'dzin dbang bsgyur zhal zas bdud rtsi rnams //
NK029(ha)001:7427: dag cing gtsang mar spyar ste 'bul lags kyis //
NK029(ha)001:7428: ye shes thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:7429: h+aum lha yi rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK029(ha)001:7430: ra skyes chibs nas glog las mgyogs //
NK029(ha)001:7431: bsreg rdzas kun gyi phyag tshangs mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:7432: tshim byed khyod la mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7433: na ma sa man+ta bud+ha nam /
NK029(ha)001:7434: b+ai ma la ag ne ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7435: tshil chen dang mar me bsgreng ngo //
NK029(ha)001:7436: h+aum tshangs pa 'jig rten mgon gyi sras /
NK029(ha)001:7437: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /'byung po yongs la skyabs pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:7438: thugs dam dbang gi rgyud bskul ba //
NK029(ha)001:7439: rig pa grub pa'i drang srong mchog /
NK029(ha)001:7440: nyon mongs bsreg mdzad shes rab 'od //
NK029(ha)001:7441: bskal pa'i me ltar gzi brjid 'bar //
NK029(ha)001:7442: mngon shes rdzu 'phrul zhabs dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:7443: thabs kyi sprul pas ra la chibs //
NK029(ha)001:7445: bdud rtsi bcud ldan g+han+d+he bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:7446: chos kyi bdud rtsi yongs la bsil //
NK029(ha)001:7447: nyes pa'i skyon bral tshangs par spyod //'jig rten gnas kyang mya ngan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:7448: zhi ba mnyes kyang thugs rje che //
NK029(ha)001:7449: de la bstod de phyag 'tshal kyang //
NK029(ha)001:7450: h+aum me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK029(ha)001:7451: mnyam pa'i ngang la kun snang yang //
NK029(ha)001:7452: chos nyid ngang las ma g.yos pa //
NK029(ha)001:7453: ye shes sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:7455: ye shes klo yangs 'khyiil ba'i ham khung 'dir /
NK029(ha)001:7456: dam rdzas bdud rtsi sbyar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di /
NK029(ha)001:7457: drang srong me lha'i zhal du mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7458: bdag la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol /
NK029(ha)001:7459: na ma sarba pany+tsa a mri ta b+ha lim ta ag+ne swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7462: ho me lha drang srong gi rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa la 'phrin las su gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:7463: me 'bar ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs nas
NK029(ha)001:7464: sbyin bsreg gi rdzas rnams ye shes kyi zhal du
NK029(ha)001:7468: dbang bskur bar gsol ba btab pas /
NK029(ha)001:7469: lha rnams kyis mchod cing dbang bskur bas lus thams cad gang /
NK029(ha)001:7470: dri ma thams cad dag chu lhag ma spyi bor lud pa las /
NK029(ha)001:7471: zhi ba la rnam par snang mdzad kyis dbu brgyan /
NK029(ha)001:7472: rgyas pa la rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK029(ha)001:7474: drag po la don yod grub pas dbu brgyan par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)001:7475: de nas bzang zhing thog pa med pa'i sku sha dag byed du 'bul ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:7476: sku sha 'di ni gtsang zhing dge /
NK029(ha)001:7477: dkon mchog gsum gyi dag byed de //
NK029(ha)001:7478: lha rnams kyi yang dag byed yin //
NK029(ha)001:7479: sa las skyes pa'i snying po mchog /
NK029(ha)001:7480: bdag cag la bgegs med par mdzod cig /
NK029(ha)001:7481: ces brjod la phyogs mtshams brgyad nas 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)001:7482: de nas de'i zhal nas 'od kyi sbu gu byung nas mar khu gsol bar bsam zhing /
NK029(ha)001:7483: ag+ne te wa ri shi ha bya ka bya di bya ma h+aa na ye di bye /
NK029(ha)001:7484: zhes pa'i mthar zhi ba la /
NK029(ha)001:7485: sdig pa dang sgrib pa bar du gcod pa thams cad shin ting ku ru ye swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7486: rgyas pa la tshe dang bsod nams dang 'byor pa thams cad pusha ting ku ru ye //
NK029(ha)001:7487: dbang la che ge mo pa sham ku ru ho /
NK029(ha)001:7488: drag po la che ge mo ma ra ya phata /
NK029(ha)001:7491: de nas ag+ne ye zhes pa'i mthar phyi mchod nang mchod phul nas /
NK029(ha)001:7493: zhu ba'i rdzas rnams zhal dang /
NK029(ha)001:7494: gong bu'i rdzas rnams phyag dang /
NK029(ha)001:7495: yam shing 'bar ba'i dkyil du 'bul bar bya ste /
NK029(ha)001:7500: sarba p+aa pam d+ha ha na badz+ra swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7510: badz+ra mah+aa b+ha la ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7516: badz+ra a mri te ha ta badz+ra ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7517: ku sha rnams byin gyis brlabs la 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)001:7518: ag+ne ye 'ba' zhig gis dbul lo //
NK029(ha)001:7519: mthar rten gyi tshig rnams sngar bshad pa bzhin no //
NK029(ha)001:7524: dbang la me tog 'bras bu dmar po /
NK029(ha)001:7525: drag po la me tog sngon po'i dug sna tshogs /
NK029(ha)001:7528: til la sogs pa la ag+ne ye shin+tam ku ru ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7529: zas mchog la sogs pa la /
NK029(ha)001:7530: ag+ne ye pusha tang ku ru ye /
NK029(ha)001:7531: me tog dmar po la sogs la /
NK029(ha)001:7532: ag+ne ye pa shang ku ru ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7533: khrag la sogs pa la ag+ne y+ae ma ra y+aa phata /
NK029(ha)001:7535: 'jam po gsum la lag pa g.yas dang /
NK029(ha)001:7536: drag po la g.yon pas 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)001:7537: sreg rdzas phul ba'i mthar mchod cing bstod nas /
NK029(ha)001:7539: ag+ne ye dz+wa la ram zhes pas me lha 'bar ba'i rnam par bsam mo /
NK029(ha)001:7541: 'phrin las so so'i dbang gis bsgyur la /
NK029(ha)001:7547: so so'i nyams dang cha lugs dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)001:7548: de'i thugs ka nas 'od 'phros pa'i pho nya rnams kyis las so sor mdzad par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)001:7549: de ni 'jig rten pa'i me lha mchod pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:7550: de nas me lha'i lto bar b+h+rum b+hi sha b+hi
NK029(ha)001:7551: shud+ha sogs gzhal yas khang dang lha rnams sngags kyis
NK029(ha)001:7553: zhi khro gang byed spyan drangs la stim /
NK029(ha)001:7554: de la shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na la sogs pa'i dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)001:7555: sku gsung thugs kyi lho bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:7556: bde bar gshegs so nas mchod pa 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7557: de nas mar la sogs pa bsreg rdzas lag tu thogs ste /
NK029(ha)001:7558: badz+ra d+h+rika mum d+ha du shwa ri kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:7559: zhes pas brgya rtsa brgyad dang lha gzhan yang 'dra'o //
NK029(ha)001:7560: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka kro ti shwa ri kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:7563: rgyas pa la rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka kro ti shwa ri kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:7564: dbang la pad+ma he ru ka kro ti shwa ri kh+aa hi //
NK029(ha)001:7565: drag po la karma he ru ka kro ti shwa ri kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:7568: bsreg rdzas bstun ste dbul ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:7569: h+aum rdo rje rigs mchog 'khor ba stong mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:7570: dus gsum 'gyur ba med cing sra brtan sku /
NK029(ha)001:7571: rdo rje sems dpa' che la sbyin bsren bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7572: h+aum de bzhin rigs mchog long spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)001:7573: nam mkha' dang 'dra cis kyang ma slad pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:7574: rnam par snang mdzad che la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7575: h+aum rin chen rigs mchog mi zad gter ldan pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:7576: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyis brgyan pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)001:7577: rin chen 'byung ldan che la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7578: h+aum pad+ma'i rigs mchog ma chags cis ma gos /
NK029(ha)001:7579: tshe dang ye shes nam mkha'i mthar mnyam pa /
NK029(ha)001:7580: snang ba mtha' yas che la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7581: h+aum las kyi rigs mchog rgyud drug stong mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:7582: 'gro ba'i don la skyo ngal mi mnga' ba'i /
NK029(ha)001:7583: don yod grub pa che la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7584: h+aum ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i ho ma khung du /
NK029(ha)001:7585: chags pa'i rgyud lnga'i bag chags ma lus bsreg sbyangs nas /
NK029(ha)001:7586: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7587: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7588: skye med rnam dag hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7589: chos can skye ba'i yam shing las //
NK029(ha)001:7590: spros med byang chub ye shes mes //
NK029(ha)001:7591: mtshan ma'i bag chags bsreg sbyang 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7592: rnam dag b+ha ga'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7593: chags pa'i bag chags yam shing la //
NK029(ha)001:7594: bde chen byang chub sems spar ste /
NK029(ha)001:7596: dpal chen zhal gyi hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7597: nyon mongs lnga'i yam shing la //
NK029(ha)001:7598: ye shes lnga'i me spar ste /
NK029(ha)001:7600: snang srid nam mkha'i hom khung du //'byung ba bzhi'i yam shing la //
NK029(ha)001:7601: phyag rgya tshogs kyi me sbar ste //
NK029(ha)001:7602: snang srid dngos po bsreg sbyangs 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7603: thab chen lnga'i hom khung du //'khor ba'i sdug bsngal yam shing la //
NK029(ha)001:7604: ye shes chen po'i me klong du //
NK029(ha)001:7606: klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7607: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i yams shing la //
NK029(ha)001:7608: bsreg rdzas skye ba'i chos yin ste //
NK029(ha)001:7609: rang bzhin nyid la thim par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:7610: nyon mongs lnga'i dam rdzas dag /
NK029(ha)001:7612: phung po lnga'i dam rdzas dag /
NK029(ha)001:7613: thabs mchog yab lnga'i sku la 'bul //'byung lnga 'dus pa'i bsreg rdzas rnams //
NK029(ha)001:7614: shes rab yum bzhi'i klong du 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7615: h+aum dam nyams dam bskongs dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7616: h+aum nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma ni ye nas rnam rtog bral //
NK029(ha)001:7617: thugs kyi longs spyod sna tshogs rdzogs mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:7618: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyis yum //
NK029(ha)001:7619: yum chen dbyings phyug ma la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:7620: rdo rje dbyings phyug ma ni ye nas rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)001:7621: longs spyod rdzogs mdzad de bzhin gshegs pa'i yum //
NK029(ha)001:7622: sangs rgyas kun gyis sku yi mchod mnga' ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:7623: yum chen sangs rgyas spyan la sbyin bsreg mchod pa 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7624: h+aum rin chen dbyings phyug ma ni ye nas gter dang ldan //
NK029(ha)001:7625: yon tan rin chen mang po'i'abyunga gnas yum //
NK029(ha)001:7626: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum mchog ma ma ki /
NK029(ha)001:7627: yon tan gter 'dzin khyed la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7628: h+aum pad+ma dbyings phyug ma ni 'dod chags skyon dang bral //
NK029(ha)001:7629: gsungs rabs sgra yi mchod pa mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:7630: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi gsung mnga' ba //
NK029(ha)001:7631: yum chen na bza' dkar la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7632: h+aum las kyi dbyings phyug ma ni dug gsum rol
NK029(ha)001:7633: bar mdzad //'phrin las sna tshogs ma lus grub pa
NK029(ha)001:7634: mo //'phags pa'i sa bcur sgrol ba sgrol mdzad ma
NK029(ha)001:7635: // yum chen dam tshig sgrol la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7636: h+aum ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //'byung ba lnga yi bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7637: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7638: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7639: skye med rnam dag hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7640: zhes pa rnams bar bar du 'adre'o //
NK029(ha)001:7641: h+aum bskal bzang sems dpa' brgyad rnams ni //
NK029(ha)001:7642: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyis sras mchog ste //
NK029(ha)001:7643: yon tan mi zad sprul pa bsam yas pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:7644: byang chub sems dpa' brgyad la sbyin bsreg mchod pa 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7645: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7646: rnam shes brgyad gyi bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7647: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7648: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7649: h+aum sgeg mo 'phreng thog rin chen glu gar can //
NK029(ha)001:7650: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i mchod pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK029(ha)001:7651: bde gshegs rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:7652: byang chub lha mo brgyad la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7653: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7654: yul brgyad bag chags ma lus bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7655: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi mcho da par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7656: dam nyams dam bskongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7657: h+aum ye shes thugs rje nam mkha'i mtha' khyab pa //
NK029(ha)001:7658: byed pa thams cad rdo rje kun tu bzang //
NK029(ha)001:7659: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kun gyi 'byung gnas gtso //
NK029(ha)001:7660: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7661: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7662: yid chos bag chags ma lus bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7663: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsis dam nyams dam bskongs ye shes rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po nas //
NK029(ha)001:7664: gnyen po'i stobs kyis so sor 'dul mdzad pa //'phrin las rgya mtsho'i yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK029(ha)001:7665: thub pa chen po drug la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7666: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7667: rgyud drug bag chags ma lus bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7668: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas dam nyams dam bskongs rta mgrin la sogs khro rgyal chen po bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:7669: gdug pa 'dul zhing 'phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:7670: gshin rje stobs chen rta mgrin bdud rtsi 'khyil /
NK029(ha)001:7671: khro rgyal bzhi la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7672: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7673: bdag rtogs rnam bzhi'i bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7674: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas dam nyams dam bskongs
NK029(ha)001:7675: mthu dang rdo rje gdong mo mgyogs ma pho nya
NK029(ha)001:7676: bzhi // tshad med bzhi rdzogs gsang ba yum gyi ngang //
NK029(ha)001:7677: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrogs dril bu ma //
NK029(ha)001:7678: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7679: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7680: rtag chad bzhi yi bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7681: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams kyis bzhes nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:7682: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7683: bsgrub mchog rnams pa stsol zhing bstan par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:7684: h+aum ye shes rdo rje nyon mongs 'khor ba 'joms //
NK029(ha)001:7685: thabs ldan mtshon cha'i bskal pa dngos po 'jig /
NK029(ha)001:7686: zhe sdang tshul gyis zhe sdang 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:7687: badz+ra he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7688: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7689: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //'gro rnams 'dul zhing gshegs mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:7690: shes rab nam mkha'i bskal pas 'joms //
NK029(ha)001:7691: gti mug tshul gyis gti mug 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:7692: bud+ha he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7693: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7694: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7695: rin chen dbyings ltar re ba kun bskong zhing //
NK029(ha)001:7696: bdag med zhi gnas chu'i bskal pas 'a khru //
NK029(ha)001:7697: nga rgyal tshul gyis nga rgyal 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:7698: rat+na he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7699: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi 'khor ba'i 'dam du pad ltar sku 'khrungs shing //
NK029(ha)001:7700: lhag mthong me chen bskal pa'i me chen bsreg /'dod chags tshul gyis 'dod chags 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:7701: pad+ma he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7702: ye shes klog yangs 'khyil ba'i ho khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7703: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas bla med sku gsung
NK029(ha)001:7704: thugs kyi 'phrin las rgya mtsho 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK029(ha)001:7705: pa // shes rab thog med bskal pa'i rlung gi bskyod //
NK029(ha)001:7706: phrag dog tshul gyis phrag dog 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:7707: karma he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7708: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7709: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas bla med sku gsung
NK029(ha)001:7710: thugs kyi ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba sman bla
NK029(ha)001:7711: med thugs kyi longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing
NK029(ha)001:7712: // brtson 'grus mthar phyin zhe sdang rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)001:7713: rtag pa reg bya' mchod pas mnyes mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:7714: sra bstan rdo rje dbang bskur khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:7715: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)001:7716: badz+ra kro ti'i sku la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7717: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi h+aum sku'i longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing //
NK029(ha)001:7718: shes rab mthar phyin gti mug rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)001:7719: phyag rgya gzugs kyis mchod pas mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:7720: chos dbyings nam mkha'i dbang phyug khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:7721: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7722: sman dang dam rdzas 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)001:7723: bud+ha kro ti ma la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7724: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi h+aum yon tan longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing //
NK029(ha)001:7725: sbyin pa mthar phyin nga rgyal rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)001:7726: ting 'dzin ro yi mchod pas mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:7727: bdag med zhi gnas dbang bskur khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:7728: ye shes klong yangs dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)001:7729: rat+na kro ti shwa ri ma la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7731: h+aum gsung gi longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing //
NK029(ha)001:7732: tshul khrims mthar phyin 'dod chags rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)001:7733: gsung rab sgra yi mchod pas mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:7734: lhag mthong ye shes dbang phyug khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:7735: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7736: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)001:7737: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri ma la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7738: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //'phrin las longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing //
NK029(ha)001:7739: bzod pa mthar phyin phrag dog rnam pa dag /
NK029(ha)001:7740: tshul khrims dri yi mchod pas mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:7741: thog med las la dbang bskur khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:7742: yeshesa klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7743: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)001:7744: karma kro ti shwa ri ma la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7745: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi h'u /
NK029(ha)001:7746: koo ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni //'jigs byed yab yum rol ba'i sras mchog ma //
NK029(ha)001:7747: lus tshul sku mdog phyag mtshan ma nges gsal //
NK029(ha)001:7748: thugs rje so so'i 'phrin las mdzad pa la //
NK029(ha)001:7749: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7750: rnam shes brgyad kyi bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7751: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchog par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7752: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7753: h+aum seng ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams kyang //
NK029(ha)001:7754: dpa' chen dbang phyug rol pa'i sras mchog ma //
NK029(ha)001:7755: smon lam dbang gi 'khor ba'i cha 'dzin ma //
NK029(ha)001:7756: thugs rjes so so'i 'phrin las grub mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:7757: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7758: yan lag bzhi'i bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7759: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7760: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub rtsol /
NK029(ha)001:7761: h+aum rdo rje sring 'gro la sogs sga ma bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:7762: dgyes pa'i byang chub sems las sku bskyed ma //
NK029(ha)001:7763: thugs rje dbang gi so so'i 'phrin las mdzad //
NK029(ha)001:7764: dkyil 'khor sgo bzhir rngam gzugs gnas pa la //
NK029(ha)001:7765: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7766: dam nyams dam bskongs yan lag bzhi'i bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7767: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7768: dam nyams dam bskong mthu dang h+aum mdzad la sogs khro bo chen po bcu //
NK029(ha)001:7769: khros pa'i byang chub sems las sku bskyed pa //
NK029(ha)001:7770: steng 'og phyogs bcu kun gyi bdud 'dul zhing //
NK029(ha)001:7771: rngam pa'i stobs kyi rab brjid mtshon cha rnams //
NK029(ha)001:7772: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7773: mi dge bcu'i bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7774: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7775: dam nyams dam bskongs dbang dang dbang grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7776: h+aum ma sring la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //'jig rten lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK029(ha)001:7777: las kyi dbang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres so sor gsal /
NK029(ha)001:7778: dpal chen slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:7779: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)001:7780: sgal tshig nyi shu brgyad kyis bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:7781: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:7782: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:7784: gzhan yang phyi yi mchod pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:7785: nang bdud rtsi'i mchod pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:7786: yid las byung ba'i mchod pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:7788: gang 'byor gyis mchod nas gtor ma phul la bsreg rdzas rnams sngar ltar byin gyis brlabs ste /
NK029(ha)001:7789: bsreg rdzas de dag gang la bsnyen pa song pa'i sngags kyis 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)001:7790: grangs ni zhi ba la brgyad //
NK029(ha)001:7791: rgyas pa la brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK029(ha)001:7792: dbang la nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK029(ha)001:7793: drag po la drug cu tham pa rnams phul ba'i
NK029(ha)001:7794: thog ma dang tha ma'i spel tshig dang sbyar ro
NK029(ha)001:7796: shin tu mang du phul ba'i mthar //
NK029(ha)001:7797: g+hu ya dz+nya na la sogs pa'i rjes su so
NK029(ha)001:7798: so'i spel tshig dang bcas pa ci rigs par dbul
NK029(ha)001:7801: mar ni me'i tshang du phul la //
NK029(ha)001:7802: mthar lha'i sngags spel tshig dang bcas pas mar dgang bslugs gsum 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)001:7803: slar yang 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab /
NK029(ha)001:7804: ma 'byor pa dang nyams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7805: gang yang bdag rmongs blo yis ni //
NK029(ha)001:7806: bgyis pa dang ni bgyid brtsal ba //
NK029(ha)001:7807: de kun mgon pos bzod par mdzo //
NK029(ha)001:7808: ces lan gsum gyis bzod par gsol nas //
NK029(ha)001:7809: khyed kyi sems can don kun mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:7810: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:7811: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang /
NK029(ha)001:7812: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:7813: yi ge brgya pa'i sngags brjod la gshegs par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:7815: dam tshig pa bdag nyid la bsdu'o /
NK029(ha)001:7816: thabs kyi dbus nas thal ba cung zad blangs pa
NK029(ha)001:7817: dpral bar skus pa ni dam tshig pa bdag la
NK029(ha)001:7818: bsdu ba'o //'jin rten las 'das pa'i me lha mchod
NK029(ha)001:7819: pa ste de ni dngos gazhi'o //
NK029(ha)001:7820: de nas mar blug gzar gang thabs kyi dbus su blugs nas /
NK029(ha)001:7821: dz+wa la ram zhes brjod pas 'jig rten pa'i me
NK029(ha)001:7822: lha gsal bar dmigs nas snga ma bzhin mchod cing
NK029(ha)001:7823: bstod nas / bsreg rdzas rnams rdzogs par phul ba'i mthar mar dgang blugs gsum dbul lo //
NK029(ha)001:7826: ag+he ye na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo /
NK029(ha)001:7827: la sogs pa lan gsum gyis phul nas /
NK029(ha)001:7828: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba btab la /
NK029(ha)001:7830: bdag chags las dang po pa'i gang zag du gyur pas /
NK029(ha)001:7833: cho ga 'khrul pa la sogs pa'i nyes pa thams cad bzod par gsol /
NK029(ha)001:7835: dbyu gu gsum pa'i phyag rgya las 'gyed pa'i tshul du bya zhing /
NK029(ha)001:7837: sid d+hi tam g+ha ts+tsha ha bya 'bu ka /
NK029(ha)001:7840: sarba sid+hi ku ru sha me /
NK029(ha)001:7842: me lha'i ye shes pa gshegs su gsol la //
NK029(ha)001:7843: snga ma bzhin dam tshig pa rang la stim //
NK029(ha)001:7845: tsa ru bza' ba la longs spyod //
NK029(ha)001:7849: de ltar bu'i cho ga phun sum tshogs pa'i sbyin bsreg byas pas /
NK029(ha)001:7850: bzlas pa'i lhag chad kyi nyes pa dag par 'gyur zhing /
NK029(ha)001:7851: gsang sbyang gi nyes pa 'dzin pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7852: rang gi lhag pa'i lha gnyes nas mchog dang thun
NK029(ha)001:7853: mongs gi dngos grub bstsol bar 'gyur ba nyid do
NK029(ha)001:7854: // gnyis pa 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la /
NK029(ha)001:7858: yon tan rnam bcus rgyas shes bya /
NK029(ha)001:7860: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang /
NK029(ha)001:7861: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang /
NK029(ha)001:7862: bgegs bskrad lhar brlab dam tshig sbyin /
NK029(ha)001:7863: de nyid dbog dang chu nan dang /
NK029(ha)001:7864: sgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:7865: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang /
NK029(ha)001:7866: mig dbye dkyir 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7867: tshogs mchod yon rnams bco brgyad do //'di yis yan lag rdzogs par 'gyur /
NK029(ha)001:7870: dad brtson gsum dang btul zhugs gsum /
NK029(ha)001:7871: gang la snang ba de'i snod /
NK029(ha)001:7874: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7875: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:7883: dbang phyug gis snyim par me tog gi 'phreng ba thogs ste /
NK029(ha)001:7884: dkyil 'khor kyi shar sgor gus pas 'dug ste /
NK029(ha)001:7885: dkyil 'khor de nyid 'og min gyi gnas rten dang brten par dmigs la /
NK029(ha)001:7888: h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:7889: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7890: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:7891: zhes rig pa'i me tog dor bas /
NK029(ha)001:7892: sngags brjod pa'i go rim bzhin /
NK029(ha)001:7893: bdag dkyil 'khor kyi lha rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:7894: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las dbyer med par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:7895: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK029(ha)001:7896: yon tan 'phrin las smad po che //
NK029(ha)001:7897: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK029(ha)001:7898: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK029(ha)001:7900: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams 'od du zhu nas /
NK029(ha)001:7901: bdag dbang phyug la phog pas /
NK029(ha)001:7902: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang dgongs pa tha mi dad par mos la /
NK029(ha)001:7906: zhes brjod pas go rim bzhin /
NK029(ha)001:7907: ye shes rdo rje'i dam tshig dus la bab po /
NK029(ha)001:7911: de ltar gnas nas bskul ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:7913: de dag ni bsdus pa'i rim pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:7915: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ltar /
NK029(ha)001:7917: zhugs pa'i yon tan dang bcas pas /
NK029(ha)001:7918: phyi nang gi dbang rgyas par blangs zhing 'jug go /
NK029(ha)001:7919: gnyis pa slob dpon gyis 'jug par gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:7920: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:7921: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK029(ha)001:7923: bdag gi slob ma gzhugs par bya //
NK029(ha)001:7925: snyim pa'i me tog dkyil 'khor gyi lha la dor ba'i blos /
NK029(ha)001:7926: dor ba'i tshul byas pas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams
NK029(ha)001:7927: zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis slob bu dkyil 'khor du
NK029(ha)001:7928: chug cing / dbang bco brgyad snod dang 'tsham par bskur bar rigs so //
NK029(ha)001:7929: zhes gnang ba thob par mos la //
NK029(ha)001:7930: me tog 'phreng ba spyi bor bcing ngo //
NK029(ha)001:7931: gnyis pa dbang len pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:7938: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum /
NK029(ha)001:7939: slob ma la ji ltar bskur ba ltar /
NK029(ha)001:7940: slob dpon rang gis kyang dbang legs par len no //
NK029(ha)001:7941: gnyis pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba la gnyis ste /
NK029(ha)001:7942: slob ma dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:7960: lha bsgom par nan tan bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:7965: slob bu rnams phyir phyung nas /
NK029(ha)001:7966: dri bzang po'i chus khrus byas la /
NK029(ha)001:7967: gos gsar pa dang ldan par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:7969: ma rig pa dang 'dod chags kyi dri mas gnyis med kyi ye shes sgribs so //
NK029(ha)001:7971: ras sam dar dmar po mig dgab cing /
NK029(ha)001:7972: dar la sogs pa las byas pa'i me tog rin po che'am /
NK029(ha)001:7974: dbyar gyi dus su me tog dngos kyang rung ste /
NK029(ha)001:7976: gnas khang gi nang du gus pa dang bcas pa'i tshul gyis 'dug la /
NK029(ha)001:7977: rdor sems gtso bo khyod la 'dud //
NK029(ha)001:7978: thar pa chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK029(ha)001:7979: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK029(ha)001:7980: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song ste //
NK029(ha)001:7981: theg chen khang par gzhugs pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:7982: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la rtsol //
NK029(ha)001:7985: dkyil 'khor du chug cig par gsol ba 'debs par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:7988: bu khyod ci la dga' zhes dris pa'i lan du /
NK029(ha)001:7990: skal ba bzang la bdag daga'o //
NK029(ha)001:7992: dbang phyug gi las mkhan gyis rdo rje phyed /
NK029(ha)001:7993: slob bu rnams kyi lag du sbyin la //
NK029(ha)001:7994: bu khyod tshur shog ci bde ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:7995: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:7996: sku gsung thugs kyis rdo rje gzung //
NK029(ha)001:7997: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen dang //
NK029(ha)001:7998: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK029(ha)001:7999: ser sna spangs pa'i dwangs yid kyis //
NK029(ha)001:8000: stong zhing rang sems brtan par gzung //
NK029(ha)001:8001: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK029(ha)001:8002: zhes dbang phyug gi mdun du slob bu rnams drangs so //
NK029(ha)001:8003: bzhi pa lus dbul ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:8005: spyi bor thal mo sbyar bas /
NK029(ha)001:8006: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis sku gsung thugs dang /
NK029(ha)001:8007: yon tan 'phrin las kyis ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:8008: sangs rgyas rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa rnams la lus phul bar dmigs la /
NK029(ha)001:8009: sarba bud d+ha pu tsa sas+tha na ya ad ma nam nyir+ya ta ya mi /
NK029(ha)001:8010: zhes lan gsum kyang phyag btsal bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:8011: yang thal mo smin mtshams su sbyar la /
NK029(ha)001:8012: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ye shes thob pa'i snod du rung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:8013: da ltar gyis sangs rgyas bla ma rnams la lus 'bum bar dmigs la /
NK029(ha)001:8014: +aa tsar+ya p+au tsa sas+tha ya ad ma nam nir+ya ta ya mi /
NK029(ha)001:8016: yang thal mo snying khar sbyar nas /
NK029(ha)001:8017: sems can thams cad kyi don mi dor zhing mthar phyin par bya ba'i don du /
NK029(ha)001:8018: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad la lus phul bar dmigs la /
NK029(ha)001:8019: pa ka la pa ta p+au tsa sas+tha ya ad ma nam /
NK029(ha)001:8021: zhes phyag sngar bzhin btsal lo //
NK029(ha)001:8022: lnga pa tshe mi yal ba bya ba'i phyir bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:8023: dbang phyug gi thugs kha'i sa bon las /
NK029(ha)001:8024: yi ge b+h+rum re slob ma rnams kyi dpral bar 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:8025: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud d+he zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:8026: zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas khang /
NK029(ha)001:8027: gnam sgo gcig pa khyud can gcig bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:8028: de'i nang du h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:8029: slob ma'i tshe'i dngos po thams cad h+aum la bsdu /
NK029(ha)001:8030: badz+ra h+aum ka ra h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:8032: h+aum ka ra sngon po tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa cig du bsam /
NK029(ha)001:8033: zla gam gyi gnam sgo la /
NK029(ha)001:8034: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:8036: khro bo mi g.yo ba ljang nag ral gri dang /
NK029(ha)001:8037: bsdig 'dzub can bskyed nas sgo bsrungs bar bsam nas /
NK029(ha)001:8038: yi dam lha'i nga rgyal gyis bi sh+aa badz+ra'i sngags kyis sprul pas spro /
NK029(ha)001:8039: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK029(ha)001:8040: 'dir 'dus pa'i slob bu rnams la gnod cing 'tshe
NK029(ha)001:8041: ba'i 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par dengs
NK029(ha)001:8042: byer cig / sum b+ha ni sum+b+ha ni h+aum zhes lan gsum gyis bskrad de /
NK029(ha)001:8043: drug pa lhar brlabs pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:8044: rdo rje slob dpon gyis lag pa g.yas kyi sor
NK029(ha)001:8045: mo'i bre kha lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la
NK029(ha)001:8046: gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga dang /
NK029(ha)001:8047: g.yon gyis sor mo'i bre kha lnga la gnas pa'i dpa' mo 'bru lnga bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8049: zhes dpa' bo dpa' mo sbyar /
NK029(ha)001:8051: badz+ra b+han d+ha zhes phyag rgya bsdam /
NK029(ha)001:8052: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK029(ha)001:8053: slob bu 'di rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:8054: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:8055: lta ba dman pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:8056: chos kyis 'phongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:8057: bag chags ngan pa'i sgrib pa la sogs te /
NK029(ha)001:8058: sgrib pa'i phung po ji rnyed pa thams cad phyag rgya'i 'od zer 'dis bral ba gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:8060: zhes pa'i sngags mang du brjod cing /
NK029(ha)001:8061: phyag rgya spros pas 'bru bcu rigs lnga yab yum du gyur pa sbyor ba mdzad pas /
NK029(ha)001:8062: byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba'i 'od zer gyis /
NK029(ha)001:8063: slob bu rnams kyi sgrib pa mtha' dag bsreg shing /
NK029(ha)001:8064: h+aum ka ra dang mi g.yo ba gnyis yang 'od du zhu nas /
NK029(ha)001:8065: slob bu rnams kyi rnam shes dang ga cig tu gyur ste /
NK029(ha)001:8066: dngul chu zhun ma lta bur gnas de /
NK029(ha)001:8067: cho ga gsum gyis rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog
NK029(ha)001:8068: dkar po brgyan cha lugs dang ldan par bskyed la
NK029(ha)001:8069: / shu nya ta la sogs pa'i sngags kyis dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)001:8070: gnas gsum du rdo rje gtug cing /
NK029(ha)001:8072: byin gyis brlabs par bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)001:8073: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra la sogs pa brjod /
NK029(ha)001:8074: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:8075: dpral bar sku yis lha snang mdzad dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:8076: 'khor lo dkar po gyis mtshan pa 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:8077: de bzhin du mgrin pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:8078: snying khar gsung thugs kyi lha 'dra'o //
NK029(ha)001:8079: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgyas /
NK029(ha)001:8080: badz+ra ka wa tsi rak+sha rak+sha zhes rdo rje'i go khrab dkon /
NK029(ha)001:8081: rdo rje bsrungs pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK029(ha)001:8082: trum gi rdo rje gnod sbyin dang /
NK029(ha)001:8083: khro bo mi 'chi thal sbyor gnyis kyis lus gyi gnas drug bsrungs par bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)001:8084: bdun pa dam tshig sbyin pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:8086: a la la ste mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:8087: a la la ste mnyes par mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:8088: a la la ste dam tshig bskongs /
NK029(ha)001:8089: a la la ste dngos grub stsol /
NK029(ha)001:8090: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba /
NK029(ha)001:8091: mi phyed rdo rje sku rang bzhin /
NK029(ha)001:8092: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni /
NK029(ha)001:8093: rdo rje'i sku ru mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:8095: dbang phyug gis b+han+d+ha bdud rtsi cung zad blug la /
NK029(ha)001:8096: +aah h+aum zhes brjod cing sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin yig 'bru gsum gsal bar bsgom la /
NK029(ha)001:8097: badz+ra a mri ta h'u hrihth+aah zhes pa'i sngags lan gsum gyi bdud rtsi chur byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK029(ha)001:8098: dbang phyug gi phyag g.yas pa rdo rje dang bcas pa'i srin lag gi bdud rtsi blangs la /
NK029(ha)001:8099: slob bu rnams kyi dpral bar zhes brjod cing thig le byas la dkar po bsam /
NK029(ha)001:8100: de las 'od zer dkar po 'phros pas /
NK029(ha)001:8101: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis sku yi byin brlabs bsdus nas /
NK029(ha)001:8102: dpral bar la thim par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8103: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:8104: zhes brjod cing byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK029(ha)001:8105: slob bu dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:8107: dpal ldan rdo rje gsung 'chang ba /
NK029(ha)001:8108: mi phyed rdo rje gsung rang bzhin /
NK029(ha)001:8109: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni /
NK029(ha)001:8110: rdo rje gsung du mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:8112: slob bu'i mgrin par thig le byas pa'i +aah yis 'phro 'dus /
NK029(ha)001:8113: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+ha
NK029(ha)001:8114: wa ata ma ko&a hamh sngags kyis gsung gi dam
NK029(ha)001:8117: dpal ldan rdo rje thugs 'chang ba /
NK029(ha)001:8118: mi phyed rdo rje'i thugs rang bzhin //
NK029(ha)001:8119: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni /
NK029(ha)001:8120: rdo rje'i thugs su mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:8122: slob bu'i snying khar thig le byas pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:8124: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa
NK029(ha)001:8125: ata ma ko&a hamh kyis thugs kyi dam tshig thob
NK029(ha)001:8126: par bsam mo // brgyad pa dam tshig 'bog pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:8127: dbang phyug gi slob bu'i snying khar rdo rje bzhag la /
NK029(ha)001:8128: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:8129: dam nyams ma 'dres med pa la //
NK029(ha)001:8130: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK029(ha)001:8131: theg pa chen po ston byed pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:8132: nga la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK029(ha)001:8133: sku gsung thugs la rtags gnas shing //
NK029(ha)001:8134: ma lus sems can don gyis shig ces bago'o //
NK029(ha)001:8135: dgu pa chu nan bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:8136: tsan dan dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu la /
NK029(ha)001:8137: cho ga gsum gyis rdo rje sems par bskyed cing /
NK029(ha)001:8139: bdud rtsir zhu bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8140: thog mar skyon gyi sgo nas /
NK029(ha)001:8142: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK029(ha)001:8143: dam tshig nyams na bsreg par byed //
NK029(ha)001:8144: rdo rje'i ni gtung bar gyis /
NK029(ha)001:8148: slob bu'i lce la lan gsum bzhag go /
NK029(ha)001:8149: yon tan gyi sgo nas chu nan bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:8150: de bas na bu khyod kyis /
NK029(ha)001:8151: dam tshig 'di dag srungs bar gyis //
NK029(ha)001:8152: dam tshig bsrungs na dngos grub thob //
NK029(ha)001:8153: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'thungs shig /
NK029(ha)001:8157: lan gsum slob bu'i lce la bzhag go /
NK029(ha)001:8158: slob bu kun la chu nan zin rjes thog tu //'di skad do //
NK029(ha)001:8159: de ltar bdud rtsi'i chu de /
NK029(ha)001:8160: bzhag pa lce la bzhag kyang /
NK029(ha)001:8161: bab pa snying gi dkyil du babs nas /
NK029(ha)001:8162: gal ste dam tshig ma bsrungs na /
NK029(ha)001:8163: chu de rdo rje gnod sbyin zhes bya ba /
NK029(ha)001:8164: lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu par gyur nas /
NK029(ha)001:8166: tshe thung zhing nad mang ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:8167: tshe phyi mar dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gyis nyams thag par 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)001:8168: dam tshig bsrungs na chu de rdo rje sems dpar gyur nas /
NK029(ha)001:8169: des rtag tu byin gyis brlab cing /
NK029(ha)001:8172: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)001:8173: gdon stong phrag brgyad bcus mi tshugs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:8174: phyi mar bla na med pa'i byang chub thob nas /
NK029(ha)001:8175: sems can thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las
NK029(ha)001:8176: 'das pa'i gnas su 'dren pa'i ded dpon byed par
NK029(ha)001:8178: bcu pa dam bsgrags pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:8179: dbang phyug gi phyag g.yas pa rdo rje dang bcas pa gcig /
NK029(ha)001:8180: slob bu rnams kyi spyi bor bzhag la /
NK029(ha)001:8181: thabs dang shes rab sems nyid kyis //
NK029(ha)001:8182: rtag tu dgos pa med bgyis la //'dod pa lnga'i yon tan spyod //
NK029(ha)001:8183: gzhan yang stong khams thams cad na //
NK029(ha)001:8184: shes rab dbyings dang 'dod don gzhan //
NK029(ha)001:8185: rab 'bring tha mas thams cad spyod //
NK029(ha)001:8186: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:8187: skye bo gang zhig dam la gnod //
NK029(ha)001:8188: brtul zhugs can gyis de drongs la //
NK029(ha)001:8189: khrag chen snying la btung bar bgyis //'di la mi bya cung zad med //
NK029(ha)001:8190: sems nyid theg par rab nges nas //
NK029(ha)001:8191: nyon mongs 'dod lnga kun spyod kyang //
NK029(ha)001:8193: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:8194: bya dang mi bya cung zad med //
NK029(ha)001:8196: bcu gcig rin chen dor ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:8197: rang rang gi yi dam dang 'brel ba rtag pa'i don du /
NK029(ha)001:8199: dbang phyug rigs thams cad kyis bdag por mos pas /
NK029(ha)001:8200: dbang phyug mngon par phyogs te //
NK029(ha)001:8201: me tog la sogs rin chen 'phreng //
NK029(ha)001:8202: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK029(ha)001:8203: thugs rje bzung bar dgongs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:8204: gang yin de la 'bab gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:8207: dbang phyug gi phyag gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu ldan pas /
NK029(ha)001:8208: thugs khar dril bu dkrol zhing //
NK029(ha)001:8209: slob bu rnams kyang dril bu'i sgra la gtad la /
NK029(ha)001:8211: yi dam gyi rigs ngos bzung ste /
NK029(ha)001:8212: dbus dang mtshams rnams de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs /
NK029(ha)001:8213: lag pa g.yas kyi cha rdo rje'i rigs /
NK029(ha)001:8214: g.yon gyi cha rin po che'i rigs /
NK029(ha)001:8215: rkang pa g.yas kyi cha las kyi rigs /
NK029(ha)001:8216: g.yon gyi cha pad+ma'i rigs yin pas /
NK029(ha)001:8217: rang rang gi rigs yid la ma brjed par zungs shig /
NK029(ha)001:8218: ces brjod cing me tog 'phreng ba spyi bor bcing ngo //
NK029(ha)001:8219: bcu gnyis pa lha dbab pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:8220: slob bu rnams lus bde lugs su bsrang ste /
NK029(ha)001:8221: snying gi nang du chu nan gyis dus kyi rdo rje sems dpa' gsal bar bsam zhing /
NK029(ha)001:8222: shes pas skad cig kyang ma yengs par gyis shig /
NK029(ha)001:8224: dbang phyug gis rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgyas /
NK029(ha)001:8225: h'um badz+ra d+h+rika sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)001:8227: rdo rje sems dpa' chos sku las /
NK029(ha)001:8228: gzugs skur bzhengs par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8229: las slob rnams kyis spos dang rol mo'i sgra sbyar zhing /
NK029(ha)001:8230: dbang phyug gi lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas /
NK029(ha)001:8232: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan mah+aa k+aa ru ni ka tri sha ho //
NK029(ha)001:8235: zhes pas 'og min gyi gnas nas /
NK029(ha)001:8236: ye shes sems dpa' rang bzhin gyis rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK029(ha)001:8237: slob bu rnams kyi snying nang du spyan drangs la /
NK029(ha)001:8238: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes su yang /
NK029(ha)001:8239: dbang phyug gi phyag g.yas pa rdo rje dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:8240: slob bu 'di'i tsit+ta'i dkyil du ye shes sems dpa'i rang bzhin du zhugs nas /
NK029(ha)001:8243: phyi ma bla na med pa'i byang chub tu gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:8244: gal te dam tshig nyams na rdo rje gnod sbyin du gyur ste /
NK029(ha)001:8245: srog rtsa'i khrag 'jib par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:8247: pra be sha phata kyis slob bu'i lus dbye /
NK029(ha)001:8248: a be sha ya as snying gi dkyil du chu
NK029(ha)001:8249: nan gyi chu dang gnyis su med par bstim par
NK029(ha)001:8250: bya'o // bcu gsum pa lha bsgom par nan tan bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:8251: thams cad legs par nyon la yid la zungs shig /
NK029(ha)001:8252: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir bzhugs nas /
NK029(ha)001:8253: lha bsgom pa dang ma bral ba'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)001:8254: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs dang /
NK029(ha)001:8255: skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes thob ste /
NK029(ha)001:8256: 'dod pa'i don ci bsgrub kyang nye bar 'grub cing /
NK029(ha)001:8257: tshe gcig lus gcig la dngos grub ya mtshan chen
NK029(ha)001:8258: po sangs rgyas kyi go 'phangs thob par 'gyur ste
NK029(ha)001:8259: / rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK029(ha)001:8260: skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes te //
NK029(ha)001:8261: gnyer na nya bar 'byung ba yi //
NK029(ha)001:8262: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges //
NK029(ha)001:8264: sgyu 'phrul man ngag lam gyi rim pa nas /
NK029(ha)001:8265: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK029(ha)001:8268: zhes brjod do //'o na lha bsgom pa la phan yon chen po 'dug mod /
NK029(ha)001:8269: ma bsgom na skyon ci yod snyam na /
NK029(ha)001:8270: yi dam gyi lha spangs na /
NK029(ha)001:8271: dge ba gzhan spyad kyang don med par 'gyur zhing /
NK029(ha)001:8272: dad pa med pa'i stobs kyis dam tshig nyams na
NK029(ha)001:8273: kun du nyon mongs pa ngan song gsum gyi sdug
NK029(ha)001:8275: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob pa'i lam las gol nas /
NK029(ha)001:8276: rigs chad pa'i gnas su 'gyur te /
NK029(ha)001:8277: gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud las /
NK029(ha)001:8278: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:8280: sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las rim las /
NK029(ha)001:8281: lha spangs dge spyad don med de //
NK029(ha)001:8282: gang zhig phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK029(ha)001:8283: nyon mongs nga rgyal gnas su skye //
NK029(ha)001:8285: bla med 'gro ba'i rgyun yang bcad //
NK029(ha)001:8286: rigs chad nyid du gnas par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:8287: zhes gsungs pa'i don go bar gyis shig /
NK029(ha)001:8289: bcu bzhi pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:8290: dbang phyug gi thugs kha nas 'od zer thur ma dang 'dra ba byung nas /
NK029(ha)001:8291: slob bu 'am ma rig pa'i ling thog bsal bas
NK029(ha)001:8292: rang la gnas pa'i don dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK029(ha)001:8293: tshogs rnams kyi zhal mthong bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8294: de ring dad pa'i shugs kyis ni /
NK029(ha)001:8295: dkyil 'khor dam pa bstan par bya /
NK029(ha)001:8296: sangs rgyas gsung gi rigs su 'khrungs //
NK029(ha)001:8297: dngos grub mchog tu 'gyur par bya //
NK029(ha)001:8298: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK029(ha)001:8299: ces pas mig dar bshus la /
NK029(ha)001:8302: bco lnga pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:8303: dbang phyug gis chags shing thogs ste /
NK029(ha)001:8304: thog mar gzhal yas khang gi don rtogs bshad par bya ste /
NK029(ha)001:8305: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa la spros pa'i mtha' gang yang
NK029(ha)001:8306: med pa'i rtags su lte ba zlum por byung ba'o
NK029(ha)001:8307: // de bzhin du rang byung gi ye shes bzhi
NK029(ha)001:8308: shar nas gdul bya la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK029(ha)001:8309: ba'i rtags su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang
NK029(ha)001:8310: // bcas pa byung / don ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:8311: rin po che'i rtsigs pa lnga sbrag tu byung /
NK029(ha)001:8312: chos nyid ye shes bzhir rgyas ba'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:8314: ting nge 'dzin bzhi'am rnam par thar pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:8315: gzhal yas khang gi sgo bzhir byung /
NK029(ha)001:8316: theg pa brgyad nas zhugs nas /
NK029(ha)001:8317: mthar a tir 'jug pa'i rtags su rta babs brgyad du byung /
NK029(ha)001:8318: gdan ni thabs ma 'gags pa'i rtags su zla ba shes rab 'dzin pa'i rtags su nyi ma /
NK029(ha)001:8319: chos thams cad rnam par dag pa la nyes pa mi gos pa'i pad+ma /
NK029(ha)001:8320: yon tan zad pa med cing bskor bdun lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:8321: rin po che'i khri rkang dang gdugs /
NK029(ha)001:8322: mi 'jigs bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su seng ge'i khri /
NK029(ha)001:8323: stobs bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags glang po /
NK029(ha)001:8324: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su rta /
NK029(ha)001:8325: dbang bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags su rma bya /
NK029(ha)001:8326: 'phrin las thogs pa med pa'i rtags su nam mkha' lding gi khri'o //
NK029(ha)001:8327: de ltar brten gzhal yas khang gi don rtags bshad nas /
NK029(ha)001:8328: rten pa lha'i don rtags ni /
NK029(ha)001:8329: nyon mongs drug gnas su dag pa'i rtags su thub pa drug /
NK029(ha)001:8330: yid chos gnas su dag pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)001:8332: lus kyi chos bzhi dang rtag chad kyi phyin ci log bzhi dag pa sgo ba yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:8334: dus bzhi dag pa phyi sems dpa' yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:8335: rnam shes bzhi dang yul bzhi dag pa nang gi sems dpa' yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:8336: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba rigs lnga yab yum yin la /
NK029(ha)001:8337: de'i nang nas kyang khyod kyi yi dam gyi lha 'di yin no //
NK029(ha)001:8338: zhes me tog g.yas pa stod la phog pa rdo rje rigs kyi slob bu rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:8339: mi skyod pa yab yum bsgom pa'i mngon par rtogs pa 'bog /
NK029(ha)001:8340: da phyin chad yi dam gyi lha 'di dang mi 'bral bar bsgom shig /
NK029(ha)001:8341: snying po h+aum badz+ra ka mum d+ha du shwa ri /
NK029(ha)001:8344: ces lan gsum rjes bzlos byed du bzhug /
NK029(ha)001:8345: gsang mtshan pho rnams kyi rdo rje snying po rtsal /
NK029(ha)001:8350: zhes pa la sogs pa thugs kyi rigs kyi gsang mtshan gang rung dang /
NK029(ha)001:8351: mo rnams kyi rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsal bya ba yin pas /
NK029(ha)001:8354: rdo rje'i rigs su mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i tshe /
NK029(ha)001:8357: sa steng gsum du grags par 'gyur zhing /
NK029(ha)001:8358: sems can gyi don byed pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:8359: khyad par du zhe sdang can gyi gdul bya 'dul bar 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)001:8361: de bzhin du dbus la phog na /
NK029(ha)001:8362: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis yi dam ni /
NK029(ha)001:8363: rnam snang yab yum kyi snying po ni /
NK029(ha)001:8364: dza ni dzika lam ste shwa ra ti /
NK029(ha)001:8369: rdo rje b+aee ro tsa na rtsal /
NK029(ha)001:8371: de bzhin dbyings phyug rtsal bya ba yin no //
NK029(ha)001:8372: bya ba la sogs pa'i 'gres kyis rigs lnga ka la shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:8373: me tog yon bstod la phog pa /
NK029(ha)001:8374: rin po che'i rigs rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:8375: rdo rje yon tan gter 'byung rtsal /
NK029(ha)001:8377: rdo rje rin chen snying po rtsal /
NK029(ha)001:8378: mo rnams la rin chen dbyings phyug rtsal /
NK029(ha)001:8379: g.yas pad+ma la phog pa las kyi rigs rnams las /
NK029(ha)001:8386: g.yon pad+ma la phog pas pad+ma'i rigs rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:8390: rdo rje ma chags pad+ma rtsal /
NK029(ha)001:8394: de bzhin du thams cad shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:8395: de ltar lha ngo bstan nas /
NK029(ha)001:8396: da lha bsgom pa dang 'bral du mi rung bar nan tan bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:8397: thams cad legs par nyon la yid la zungs shig /
NK029(ha)001:8398: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir zhugs nas /
NK029(ha)001:8399: lha bsgom pa ma bral ba'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)001:8400: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs dang skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes thob ste /
NK029(ha)001:8401: 'dod pa'i don ci bsgrub kyang nye bar 'gyur cing /
NK029(ha)001:8402: tshe gcig lus gcig la dngos grub ya mtshan chen
NK029(ha)001:8403: po sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par 'gyur te
NK029(ha)001:8404: / rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK029(ha)001:8405: skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes ste //
NK029(ha)001:8406: gang gi gnyer na nye bar 'byung ba yi //
NK029(ha)001:8407: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges //
NK029(ha)001:8409: sgyu 'phrul man ngag lam gyi rim pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8410: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK029(ha)001:8413: zhes brjod do //'o na lha bsgom pa la phan yon chen po 'dug mod /
NK029(ha)001:8414: ma bsgom na skyon ci yod snyam na /
NK029(ha)001:8415: yi dam gyi lha spangs na /
NK029(ha)001:8416: dge ba gzhan spyad kyang don med par 'gyur cing /
NK029(ha)001:8417: dad pa med pa'i stobs kyi dam tshig nyams na /
NK029(ha)001:8418: kun tu nyon mongs pa ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal myong ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:8419: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob pa'i lam las gol nas /
NK029(ha)001:8420: rigs chad pa'i gnas su gyur ste /
NK029(ha)001:8421: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud las /
NK029(ha)001:8422: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)001:8424: sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las kyi rim pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8425: lha spangs dge spyad don med de //
NK029(ha)001:8426: gang zhig phyag rgya 'di spangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:8427: nyon mongs ngan song gsum du skye /
NK029(ha)001:8429: bla med 'gro ba'i rgyun yang bcad //
NK029(ha)001:8430: rigs chad nyid du gnas par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:8431: zhes gsungs pa'i don go bar gyis shig /
NK029(ha)001:8433: bcu drug pa tshogs mchod dang yon 'bul ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:8434: tshogs mchod rgya chen po bshams la /
NK029(ha)001:8435: tshogs kyi cho ga rgyas par byed /
NK029(ha)001:8436: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud las /
NK029(ha)001:8437: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK029(ha)001:8438: rgyal srid dag ni rang gi lus //
NK029(ha)001:8439: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK029(ha)001:8441: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK029(ha)001:8442: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin //
NK029(ha)001:8443: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor smos ci dgos //
NK029(ha)001:8444: nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:8445: zhes pa'i don khong du chud par bya'o //'on kyang phyag len du skabs 'dir /
NK029(ha)001:8447: yon dngos dbang rdzogs pa'i rjes su ci 'byor pa 'bul mod kyi /
NK029(ha)001:8448: skabs 'dir me tog 'grem bsdud byas nas dngos su man+dala dbul zhing /
NK029(ha)001:8449: yid kyi lus longs spyod thams cad ltos pa med par phul kyang chog par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)001:8450: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)001:8451: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud las /
NK029(ha)001:8452: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK029(ha)001:8453: sdang 'jal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK029(ha)001:8454: byas ste dad ldan rab zhugs nas //'dod pa yid 'ong mnyam par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:8456: zhugs pa'i yon tan bzhi ste /
NK029(ha)001:8458: dkyil 'khor thams cad du zhugs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK029(ha)001:8459: las dang po la lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa yin kyang /
NK029(ha)001:8460: sngon 'og min du thar lam pa zhugs pa dang skal pa mnyam pa'i yon tan dang /
NK029(ha)001:8461: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK029(ha)001:8462: 'dir mos pa tsam yang skye ba sngon rol nas
NK029(ha)001:8463: / yi dam gyi lha bsnyen pa'i stobs kyis sangs
NK029(ha)001:8464: rgyas thams cad kyis nye ba'i sras su dgongs par
NK029(ha)001:8466: dkyil 'khor 'dir zhugs nas dam tshig ma nyams na /
NK029(ha)001:8467: thun mongs dang mchog gi dngos grub thams cad thob par 'gyur ba'i yon tan no //
NK029(ha)001:8468: dang po ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las rim las /
NK029(ha)001:8469: sgyu 'phrul dra bar legs zhugs pas /
NK029(ha)001:8470: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi /
NK029(ha)001:8471: dkyil 'khor kun du zhugs pa yin /
NK029(ha)001:8475: sdang 'byal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK029(ha)001:8476: byas ste dad ldan rab zhugs na //'dod pa yid 'ong mchog la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:8477: sngon byas pa dang mnyam par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:8478: gsum pa ni rtsa rgyud le'u bcu gsum pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8480: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK029(ha)001:8481: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK029(ha)001:8482: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:8483: nye ba'i sras su dgongs 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)001:8485: bzhi pa rdo rje las rim las /
NK029(ha)001:8486: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rigs nges shing //
NK029(ha)001:8487: gdon rnams bzlog cing ngan song sbyong //
NK029(ha)001:8488: long spyod 'du ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK029(ha)001:8489: ye shes spyan gyis bzhin bsdu nges //
NK029(ha)001:8490: de la sogs pa bsam yas mchog /
NK029(ha)001:8492: gong gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i skabs su /
NK029(ha)001:8495: tshom bu cig gsum lnga pa la'ang lha ngo ci rigs par bstan par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:8496: spyi don gnyis pa dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)001:8501: slob bu rnams kyis dbang phyug dang /
NK029(ha)001:8502: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la phyag byas nas /
NK029(ha)001:8504: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK029(ha)001:8505: rtse ba dgongs ste bdag la yang //
NK029(ha)001:8506: dbang bskur bdud rtsi chen po nyid //
NK029(ha)001:8507: de ring rab tu gsal bar mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:8508: ces gsol ba btab par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:8510: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyis //
NK029(ha)001:8511: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK029(ha)001:8512: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pas //
NK029(ha)001:8513: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK029(ha)001:8515: spos dang rol mo dang bcas pas kun gyis dkyil 'khor la bskor zhing /
NK029(ha)001:8517: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bstod nas /
NK029(ha)001:8518: be k+aa kra ma yam gyis sngags dang /
NK029(ha)001:8520: gzhal yas khang lha dang bcas pa mdun gyi nam mkhar btegs la /
NK029(ha)001:8522: me tog dang bcas pa'i thal mo sbyar nas gsol ba gdab par byas ste /
NK029(ha)001:8523: sa man dza'i sngags dang phyag rgyas de bzhin gshegs
NK029(ha)001:8524: pa thams cad kyi mdun gyi nam mkha' la sbyan
NK029(ha)001:8525: drangs la / hoh phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:8526: bdag rdo rje che slob dpon che ge mo 'di
NK029(ha)001:8527: zhes bya bas sogs pa'i slob bu 'di rnams la
NK029(ha)001:8528: / sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:8529: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:8532: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK029(ha)001:8534: rdo rje shugs kyis bsgral nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:8535: byin brlabs dam pa nod par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:8536: zhes brjod cing dbang phyug dbu brgyan gon la /
NK029(ha)001:8537: dkyil 'khor gyi drung ngam steng du dbang khrir 'dug par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:8539: rtsa rgyud le'u dgu pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8540: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs nas /
NK029(ha)001:8541: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:8542: rim pa bzhin du bskur ba bya /
NK029(ha)001:8544: dad pa can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bskur ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:8545: brtson 'grus can nang nus pa'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:8546: brtul zhugs can la gsang ba zab mo'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:8548: bum pa'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:8549: snying po lnga'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:8550: dbu brgyan gyi cod pan gyi 'phreng ba'i go cha'i
NK029(ha)001:8551: rgyal mtshan gyi gdugs kyis bza' btung gi phyag rgya'i
NK029(ha)001:8552: dbang bskur ba'o // dang po bum pa'i dbang la /
NK029(ha)001:8554: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu dang //
NK029(ha)001:8555: rim las skyon yon brgyad ces bya /
NK029(ha)001:8563: bum dbang ma thob pa'i skyon dang /
NK029(ha)001:8565: dang po la mtshungs rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:8566: rtsa gnas rnams thigs les gang ba /
NK029(ha)001:8567: bum pa'i dbang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8568: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:8569: rigs rang rang gi lhas rab gnas byas pa'i dbang rdzas bum pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8570: gnyis pa rkyen la rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8571: dbang bskur du rung pa'i skyes bu ste /
NK029(ha)001:8572: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:8573: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8575: rdzas la chags pa che ba ni yi dwags kyi rgyu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8576: gnyid che ba ni gti mug ste byol song gi rgyu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8577: rang phyogs che ba ni rtsod pa'i rgyu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8578: chang dad che ba ni nyes pa du ma'i rgyu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8579: nga rgyal dang dregs pa che ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:8581: gzhan la bskur pa 'debs pa ni sgrib pa'i rgyu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8582: phrag dog che ba ni dngos grub mi 'byung ba'i rgyu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8583: le lo che ba ni 'bras bu yal ba'i rgyu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8584: dam tshig la nan tan mi byed pa ni thar
NK029(ha)001:8585: pa'i lam la rings ba'i rgyu yin pas dbang bskur
NK029(ha)001:8587: gnyis pa mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa ni gong gi skyon rnams las log pa /
NK029(ha)001:8588: dbang la nan tan che ba /
NK029(ha)001:8592: yon tan de rnams dang ldan na rigs ngan dang /
NK029(ha)001:8594: zha sgur la sogs pa la dbang bskur du rung ba ste /
NK029(ha)001:8596: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8597: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa te /
NK029(ha)001:8598: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu rnams kyang /
NK029(ha)001:8599: skabs kyi stobs kyis rkyen du 'gyur bas /
NK029(ha)001:8602: yo byad tshogs pa'i nus mthu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8603: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8604: bum dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma ste /
NK029(ha)001:8605: yon tan bcu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8610: log pa'i dug lnga spangs pa /
NK029(ha)001:8611: yang dag pa'i dug lnga ye shes lnga dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:8612: bla ma'i man ngag yod pa /
NK029(ha)001:8614: las kyi bya ba la mkhas pa /
NK029(ha)001:8615: bla ma rgyud pa'i man ngag rgyun ma chad pa /
NK029(ha)001:8617: las sbyor mang po mthong bas /
NK029(ha)001:8619: dbang gi dngos gzhi la lnga rdzogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:8620: rang la nyams myong yod pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8621: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8622: dbang snga ma snga mas go phye nas /
NK029(ha)001:8623: phyi ma phyi ma 'byung ba'i rkyen byed pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:8624: 'jug chog thob pas go phyed ste /
NK029(ha)001:8625: bum dbang thob pa'i rkyen byed do //
NK029(ha)001:8626: gsum pa dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK029(ha)001:8629: nus pa dngos su bskyed pa de /
NK029(ha)001:8630: rno la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8632: zag pa med pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NK029(ha)001:8634: dang po la sogs sems rigs lnga //
NK029(ha)001:8635: de la sogs kyi mngon no //
NK029(ha)001:8637: thog mar bum dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:8638: drug pa las rim pa lnga ste /
NK029(ha)001:8643: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang bskyed dang lnga'o //
NK029(ha)001:8645: bum pa lnga'i chu ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin gyi chu rgyun du bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8647: bum pa zlum po'i pho brang du //
NK029(ha)001:8648: snod bcud ma lus kun bsdus nas //
NK029(ha)001:8649: thig le chen por rgyas gdab pas //
NK029(ha)001:8650: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas yin //
NK029(ha)001:8651: h'u badz+ra k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:8652: b+hud+ha k+aa la tram rat+na k+aa la sha hrihpad+ma k+aa la +aahkarma k+aa gsum pa bskur gnas ni /
NK029(ha)001:8653: mgo'i gnas lngar gtso bo'i bum pa la sogs go
NK029(ha)001:8654: rims ma nor bar bum pa bzhag cing bum chu
NK029(ha)001:8655: blug / bzhi pa bstim gnas ni /
NK029(ha)001:8656: rtsa gnas kyi thig le la stim mo //
NK029(ha)001:8657: lnga pa sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang bskyed ni /
NK029(ha)001:8658: sngar phan chad phung po lnga dang /
NK029(ha)001:8660: nyon mongs pa rang kha ma'i sgrib pa ma spangs gnas su dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:8661: da phyin chad ye shes rnam pa lnga'i chu rgyun
NK029(ha)001:8662: la longs spyod pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par
NK029(ha)001:8663: sgom / drug pa bden pa brjod pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:8664: na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gsheg pa
NK029(ha)001:8665: thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon
NK029(ha)001:8666: tan dang / 'phrin las zhing khams zag pa med
NK029(ha)001:8667: pa zad mi shes pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka'
NK029(ha)001:8668: tan dang / bden pa dang / bden pa chen
NK029(ha)001:8669: po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis rigs kyi bu 'di rnams
NK029(ha)001:8670: tan dang / bden pa dang / la / bum pa byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:8671: phyi nang gi dri ma yongs su dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:8672: byang chub kyis sems ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:8673: bdun pa bum dbang ma thob pa'i skyon dang /
NK029(ha)001:8674: brgyad pa thob pa'i yon tan ni 'og nas byung ba bzhin /
NK029(ha)001:8675: gnyis pa snying po lnga yi dbang la brgyad kyi /
NK029(ha)001:8676: dang po rgyu la mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:8677: khams lnga'i bcud dam rdzas lnga'o //
NK029(ha)001:8678: lhan cig skyes pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:8679: rigs lngas rab gnas byas pa'i snying po lnga'o //
NK029(ha)001:8680: rkyen bzhi la rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8681: dbang bskur du rung pa'i slob ma /
NK029(ha)001:8682: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing mthun gyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8683: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8684: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:8687: rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa rin po che la s+w+aas mtshan pa //
NK029(ha)001:8689: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8690: snying po lnga'i dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8691: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8692: bum dbang gis go phye nas snying po lnga'i dbang thob pa'i rkyen byed do //
NK029(ha)001:8693: gsum pa ngo bo ni snying po lnga'i dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:8695: nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste sno la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8697: bum pa'i dbang gi rjes su snying po lnga'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:8698: drug pa las rim las sku'i bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:8699: dbang phyug gi thugs kha'i h+aum las 'od 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:8700: slob bu'i spyi bor zla gdan la dkar po bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8701: spa ra sam gyi spro bsdu byas pas /
NK029(ha)001:8702: 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8703: rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo bsnams pa bskyed pa sku'i dbang thob pa bsam /
NK029(ha)001:8705: bde gshegs sku yi ngo bo las /
NK029(ha)001:8706: mi shig rdo rje rgyal ba'i gtso /
NK029(ha)001:8707: sngags dang phyag rgyas ldan pa yis /
NK029(ha)001:8708: rdo rje sku yi gtso bor shog /
NK029(ha)001:8709: sarba ta tha ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:8710: zhes brjod cing bskur gnas ni /
NK029(ha)001:8711: dpral bar dbang rdzas 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:8712: stim gnas ni ma tshungs ldan gyi rgyu ste /
NK029(ha)001:8713: bdud rtsi dri chen gyi khams la stim mo //
NK029(ha)001:8714: gsung gi bsam rgyud ni dbang phyug gi thugs kha'i h+aum las 'od 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:8715: slob bu'i mgrin par pad+ma'i gdan la +aa dmar po bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8716: spar sam gi spro bsdu byas pas /
NK029(ha)001:8717: pad+ma +aah gyis mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8718: snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma bsnams pa bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:8719: gsung gi dbang phyug thob par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:8721: bde gshegs gsung gi ngo bo las /
NK029(ha)001:8722: mi shigs rdo rje chos kyi dbyings //
NK029(ha)001:8723: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:8724: rdo rje gsung gi gtso bor shog /
NK029(ha)001:8725: sarba ta th+aa ga ta swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:8727: bskur gnas ni lce la pad+ma gyis mtshan pa gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:8728: stim gnas khrag gi khams la stim mo //
NK029(ha)001:8729: thugs kyi dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:8730: dbang phyug gi thugs kha'i h+aum las 'od 'phros /
NK029(ha)001:8731: slob bu'i snying khar rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:8732: spa ra sam gis spro bsdu byas pas /
NK029(ha)001:8733: rdo rje h+aum gis mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8734: mi skyod pa mthing kha rdo rje bsam pa bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:8735: thugs kyi dbang thob par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)001:8737: h+aum bde gshegs thugs kyi ngo bo las /
NK029(ha)001:8738: mi shig rdo rje chos kyi dbyings //
NK029(ha)001:8739: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa yis //
NK029(ha)001:8740: rdo rje thugs kyi gtso bor shog /
NK029(ha)001:8741: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:8744: snying khar rdo rje h+aum gi mtshan pa gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:8745: bstim gnas byang sems kyi khams la bstim mo //
NK029(ha)001:8746: yon tan gyi dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:8747: dbang phyug gi thugs kha'i h+aum las 'od 'phros slob
NK029(ha)001:8748: bu'i lte ba'i g.yas su rin po che swos mtshan
NK029(ha)001:8749: par bsam la / spar sam gi spro bsdu byas la /
NK029(ha)001:8750: rin po che la swos mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8751: rin chen 'byung ldan ser po rin po che bsnams pa bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:8752: yon tan gyi dbang thob par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:8754: s+w+aah mi 'gyur ba yi zhing khams la //
NK029(ha)001:8755: ma skyes pa yi 'bras bu las //
NK029(ha)001:8757: cir yang 'gyur ba ye shes kyi //
NK029(ha)001:8758: rang dbang thabs kyis bsgyur bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:8759: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+auny+tsa badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:8760: bskur gnas lte ba'i g.yas su rin po che swahmatshana pa la gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:8761: bstim gnas sha chen gyi khams la stim mo //'phrin las kyi dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:8762: dbang phyug gi thugs kha'i h+aum las slob bu'i lte ba'i g.yon du /
NK029(ha)001:8763: ral gri has mtshan pa bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8764: spa ra sam gi spro bsdu byas la /
NK029(ha)001:8765: ral gri has mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8766: don grub ljang khu ral gri bsnams pa bskyed la /
