NK029(ha)001:8767: 'phrin las kyi dbang thob par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:8769: h+aah thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:8771: las dang dngos grub kun snang pa /
NK029(ha)001:8772: ma lus mnyam par sbyor bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:8773: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa a nu ra ga badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:8774: bskur gnas lte ba'i g.yon phyogs su ral gri has mtshan pa gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:8775: bstim gnas dri chu'i khams la stim mo //
NK029(ha)001:8776: de ltar snying po lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:8777: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang bskyed na /
NK029(ha)001:8778: sngar phan chad khams lnga las byung pa'i bdud rtsi lnga /
NK029(ha)001:8779: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lngas ma dag pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:8780: de dag gi ngo bor dag pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)001:8782: na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK029(ha)001:8783: thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon
NK029(ha)001:8784: tan dang 'phrin las dang zhing khams zad mi shes
NK029(ha)001:8785: pa mi zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden
NK029(ha)001:8786: pa dang / bden po chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)001:8788: snying po lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:8789: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung
NK029(ha)001:8790: dang thugs dang yon tan dang 'phrin las lnga'i dbang
NK029(ha)001:8793: bdun pa snying po lnga'i dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)001:8794: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u bcu pa las /
NK029(ha)001:8795: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK029(ha)001:8796: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na //
NK029(ha)001:8797: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa rnams //'bras bu med cing brlag par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:8799: brgyad pa dbang thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)001:8801: dus 'di tshun chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK029(ha)001:8802: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:8803: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:8804: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por gyur //
NK029(ha)001:8806: gsum pa dbu brgyan gyi dbang la brgyad kyi dang po rgyu la mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:8808: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:8809: dbu brgyan rin chen 'byung ldan gyis rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)001:8810: rkyen bzhi las dang po ni /
NK029(ha)001:8812: dbang bskur du rung pa'i slob ma mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:8813: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8814: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8815: dbu brgyan rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)001:8816: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8817: dbu brgyan gyi dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8818: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8819: snying po lnga'i dbang gi go phyes nas dbu brgyan gyi dbang thob pa'i rkyen byed do //
NK029(ha)001:8823: nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste rno la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8825: snying po lnga'i dbang gi rjes su dbu brgyan gyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:8827: dbu brgyan gyi dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:8828: rin 'byung gyis rab gnas byas pa'i dbu brgyan dbang phyug gis thogs la /
NK029(ha)001:8829: rat+na mu gu tram a b+hi shiny+tsa tram tram tram tram tram /
NK029(ha)001:8830: zhes slob bu'i mgo la bskon pas /
NK029(ha)001:8831: rin po che'i khang bu lnga gdan dang bcas pa bsam /
NK029(ha)001:8832: dbang phyug gi lag pa g.yas pa'i sor mo'i bre
NK029(ha)001:8833: kha lnga la nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo
NK029(ha)001:8834: 'bru lnga dang / sor mo g.yon pa'i bre kha
NK029(ha)001:8835: lnga la zla ba la gnas po'i dpa' mo 'bru
NK029(ha)001:8836: 'bru lnga dang / lnga bskyed / rdo rje gdams
NK029(ha)001:8837: pa'i gung mo gnyis sbyar zhing mi skyod pa yab
NK029(ha)001:8838: yum sbyor ba mdzad par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8840: mum d+ha tu shwa ri a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:8842: sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun mthing kha slob bu'i spyi bor thim pas /
NK029(ha)001:8843: gzhi don gyi kun gzhi stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su dag par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8845: h+aum chos dbyings mnyam pa chen po las /
NK029(ha)001:8846: ye shes gsal ba rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)001:8847: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
NK029(ha)001:8848: skyon med chos la dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:8849: mah+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:8850: de bzhin du 'dzub gnyis sbyar ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:8851: dzi na dzika gi sngags kyis /
NK029(ha)001:8852: snang mdzad yab yum gyi sbyor 'tshams nas /
NK029(ha)001:8853: byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun dkar po dpral bar thim /
NK029(ha)001:8854: sbyor ba don gyi kun bzhi me long lta bu'i ye shes su dag par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8855: dag cing gsal ba'i rang bzhin ste //
NK029(ha)001:8856: skyon med sems nyid rin po chen //
NK029(ha)001:8857: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK029(ha)001:8858: srid pa gsum la dbang bskur shog /
NK029(ha)001:8859: ma h+aa a ti sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:8860: srin lag gnyis sbyar ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:8861: swa rat+na d+h+rika gi sngags kyis /
NK029(ha)001:8862: rin 'byung yab yum gyi byang chub kyi sems gser gyis mdog can rna ltag g.yas su thim pas /
NK029(ha)001:8863: nyon yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su dag par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8865: khams gsum re bskongs rgyal po de /
NK029(ha)001:8866: yid bzhin rin chen gter gyi mchog //
NK029(ha)001:8867: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis /
NK029(ha)001:8868: 'gro ba re bskong rgyal por shog /
NK029(ha)001:8869: ma h+aa sa man ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:8870: mtheb chen gnyis sbyar ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:8872: mtha' yas yab yum gyis byang chub sems byi ru'i mdog can ltag par thim pas /
NK029(ha)001:8873: yid so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes su dag par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:8874: nyes pa'i skyon bral dri ma med //
NK029(ha)001:8875: skye 'gags med pa'i dngos grub gter //
NK029(ha)001:8876: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi //
NK029(ha)001:8877: srid gsum nyes dmigs sel bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:8878: mah+aa pra te be k+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:8879: mathe'u chung gnyis sbyar ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:8880: ha pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rika tam badz+ra ra ti a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:8881: zhes pa'i sngags kyis don grub yab yum gyi byang sems ljang khu rna ltag g.yon du thim pas /
NK029(ha)001:8882: sgo lnga bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su dag par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8883: h+aah dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor mthar phyin cing //
NK029(ha)001:8884: grub pa las kyi bye brag las //
NK029(ha)001:8885: bya ba nan tan ye shes kyis //
NK029(ha)001:8886: skye 'gro dbyings su sgrol bar shog /
NK029(ha)001:8887: ma h+aa kro ta a nu ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:8888: bskur gnas mgo bo'i gnas lngar /
NK029(ha)001:8889: rigs lnga rang rang gi dam tshig gi phyag rgya gtugs la /
NK029(ha)001:8890: bstim gnas rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad la rigs lnga yab yum bstim mo //
NK029(ha)001:8891: de ltar dbu brgyan gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:8892: sngar phan chad rnam shes tshogs brgyad du 'khrul pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:8893: da de nyid ma spangs ye shes lngar gsal ba'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)001:8894: bden pa dbu brgyan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:8895: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ma spangs gnas
NK029(ha)001:8896: su dag nas ye shes lnga'i dbang dam pa thob
NK029(ha)001:8897: par gyur cig / bdun pa skyon ni //
NK029(ha)001:8898: dbang ma thob na nyan pa dang rtsom pa la
NK029(ha)001:8899: sogs la 'bras bu med cing brlag par 'gyur ro
NK029(ha)001:8901: tshe ring bde skyed phun sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)001:8902: bzhi pa cod pan gyi dbang la brgyad kyi dang po rgyu la /
NK029(ha)001:8903: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni rtsa ro rkyang gnyis so //
NK029(ha)001:8904: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni dar mthing dmar gyi
NK029(ha)001:8905: cod pan rdor sems dang mtha' yas kyi rab gnas
NK029(ha)001:8906: can no // rkyen bzhi la rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8907: dbang bskur du rung pa'i slob ma mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:8908: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8909: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8910: cod pan rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)001:8912: cod pan gyi dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8913: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:8914: dbu brgyan gyi dbang thob par go phye nas /
NK029(ha)001:8915: cod pan gyi dbang thob ma rags pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:8918: bzhi pa 'bras bu ni nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:8919: rno la ngar ba tags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:8921: dbu brgyan gyi dbang gi rjes su /
NK029(ha)001:8922: cod pan gyi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:8923: drug pa las rim la bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:8924: cod pan gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:8925: gdugs pa can zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:8926: chos kyi rgyal srid la mnga' mnyes par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:8928: h+aum cod pan mi 'gyur dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)001:8929: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po'i dbang /
NK029(ha)001:8930: khams gsum kun gyis dbang phyug che //
NK029(ha)001:8931: chos kyi rgyal por dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:8932: badz+ra ar+ya lam po ta ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih h+r+aih bskur gnas mgo la cod pan ba cings /
NK029(ha)001:8934: rtsa ro rkyang gnyis la stim /
NK029(ha)001:8935: sngar phan chad gdugs pa can zil gyis mi non
NK029(ha)001:8936: zhing chos kyi rgyal srid la midabanga ba'i sgrib pa
NK029(ha)001:8937: dag nas // gdugs pa can zil gyis non cing
NK029(ha)001:8938: chos kyi rgyal srid la mnga' brnyees pa'i nus pa
NK029(ha)001:8939: dngos su bskyed par bsgom la /
NK029(ha)001:8940: bden pa cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:8941: dmar po g.yon nas gyen du 'phur bas srid gsum
NK029(ha)001:8942: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po la dbang byed pa
NK029(ha)001:8943: dang / mthing kha g.yas nas thur du 'chang bas
NK029(ha)001:8944: khams gsum gyi gdug pa thams cad zil gyi gnon

NK029(ha)001:8975: 'bras bu'i chos la dbang bskur ro //

NK029(ha)001:8980: sngon chad 'bras bu'i chos la mnga' ma brnyees pa'i sgrid pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:8981: da gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin gyi stobs kyi 'bras
NK029(ha)001:8982: bu'i chos la mnga' brnyees pa'i nus pa dngos su

NK029(ha)001:8986: 'bras bu'i chos thams cad la dbang bskur ba'i dbang

NK029(ha)001:9059: log par lta ba zil gnon mtshan //
NK029(ha)001:9060: thams cad tshar gcod ye shes gsung //
NK029(ha)001:9061: yon tan mngon 'byung dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:9062: badz+ra ke ru a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /

NK029(ha)001:10027: yab yum slob bu dang bcas pa rjes chags kyi
NK029(ha)001:10029: 'od phung seng po las rin chen 'byung ldan du bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:10030: dbang phyug gi rgyud kyi po ti'am ka p+aa la
NK029(ha)001:10031: rin chen 'byung ldan gyi rab gnas dang ldan pa
NK029(ha)001:10032: bsnams la / gnyis pa bsgrag tshig ni /
NK029(ha)001:10033: tram gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gi /
NK029(ha)001:10034: gsang ba kun la nyan pa pya /
NK029(ha)001:10035: gsang ba'i don nyid rtag pa la /
NK029(ha)001:10036: gzhan la smra bar bya ba min /
NK029(ha)001:10038: gsum pa bskur gnas slob bu'i lag par dbang rdzas gtad /
NK029(ha)001:10040: sgra reg byed nyan shes kyi thig le la ba stim /
NK029(ha)001:10041: lnga pa sngon chad bka' phyi nang gi don la
NK029(ha)001:10042: thog pa med par mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag
NK029(ha)001:10043: nas / da phyin chad nyan nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skye bar bsgom la /
NK029(ha)001:10045: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams la nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:10046: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' phyi nang thams cad la
NK029(ha)001:10047: thogs pa med par nyan nus pa'i dbang dam pa
NK029(ha)001:10049: bdun pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)001:10050: nyan dbang ma thob na nyan pa rtsom pa la sogs 'bras bu med cing brlag pa'i skyon no //
NK029(ha)001:10052: nyan pa la dbang 'byor pa'i yon tan yod do //
NK029(ha)001:10053: gnyis pa bsgom dbang la brgyad de /
NK029(ha)001:10054: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu go rim las rim skyon yon tan no //
NK029(ha)001:10055: dang po la mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10056: snying gi 'dom rtsa dran byed reg shes kyi thig le'o //
NK029(ha)001:10057: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10059: yi dam gang yin gyi rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)001:10062: dbang bskur du rung ba'i skyes bu de /
NK029(ha)001:10063: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:10064: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10065: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10066: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10067: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10068: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma ste /
NK029(ha)001:10069: yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10070: bzhi pa de ma thag rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10071: nyan dbang gi go phyes nas bsgom dbang thob ma rag pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10075: nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:10076: rno la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:10078: nyan dbang gi rjes su bsgom dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:10079: drug pa las rim la lnga las /
NK029(ha)001:10081: dbang phyug kun bzang yab yum du bsgom pa'i sbyor 'tshams nas /
NK029(ha)001:10082: yi dam gang yin gyi kha dog can gyi b+h+rum chad de /
NK029(ha)001:10083: slob bu rnams kyi snying gi 'doms rtsar 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)001:10084: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa sngar bzhin bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:10085: cho ga gsum gyis lha bac+wa brgyad bskyed de /
NK029(ha)001:10086: slob bus me tog dor ba'i dus su rin po che'i rigs la me tog phog na /
NK029(ha)001:10087: rin chen 'byung ldan gyis gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa brgyad po /
NK029(ha)001:10088: bshad ma thag pa'i nyan dbang gi skabs ltar bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10089: gal te pad+ma'i rigs la phog nas /
NK029(ha)001:10090: snang ba mtha' yas kyi gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa brgyad po /
NK029(ha)001:10091: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i 'chad dbang gi skabs ltar bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10092: de bzhin du las kyi rigs la me tog phog na /
NK029(ha)001:10093: don yod grub pas gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa brgyad 'phrin las kyi skabs ltar bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10094: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la me tog phog na
NK029(ha)001:10095: rnam par snang mdzad kyis gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa
NK029(ha)001:10096: brgyad bskyed do // dbang phyug gi thugs kha nas
NK029(ha)001:10097: dbus kyi 'khor lo la dkar po zung lnga dang
NK029(ha)001:10098: brgyad bskyed do // / sgo khyud bzhi la /
NK029(ha)001:10099: h+aum dzahh+aum h+aum h+aum bamhh+aum hoh rnams spros la s+pha
NK029(ha)001:10100: ra sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba las
NK029(ha)001:10101: / dbus kyi lte ba nas go rim bzhin 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:10107: rdo rje rtse lnga dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)001:10109: sna tshogs rdo rje dang dril bu rnams su gyur par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:10120: slar spar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)001:10121: phyag mtshan rnams go rim ltar /
NK029(ha)001:10125: rnam par snang mdzad 'khor lo bsnams pa la /
NK029(ha)001:10126: sangs rgyas spyan ma dril bu bsnams pas 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:10129: rdo rje sems dpa' dang sgeg mo ma me long bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10132: rdo rje rgyal po lcags kyu dang /
NK029(ha)001:10133: spos me ma spos khang bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10136: rdo rje chags pa 'da' gzhu dang /
NK029(ha)001:10137: rdo rje skyo kha ma lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10140: rdo rje legs pa se gol brdebs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10141: rdo rje gsal bkra ma sgron le bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10142: yab yum bcu po thams cad kyang sku mdog dkar po rgyan tshul dang ldan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10143: ya man ta kri ta h'u /
NK029(ha)001:10151: zhes sgo ba yab yum brgyad po bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:10152: sku mdog phyag mtshan rigs gang yin kyang kun mthun ste sngar nyan dbang du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK029(ha)001:10153: de bzhin du mgo ma la /
NK029(ha)001:10154: yang me tog rdo rje'i rigs la phog pa'i slob
NK029(ha)001:10155: ma rnams la mi skyod pas gtso byas pa'i lha
NK029(ha)001:10157: 'khor lo'i lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa las /
NK029(ha)001:10159: sgo bzhi la h+aum dzahh+aum h+aum h+aum bam h+aum ho
NK029(ha)001:10160: rnams 'phros pa s+phar sang gi spro bsdus 'od du
NK029(ha)001:10161: zhu ba las / phyag mtshan du gyur par bsgom ste /
NK029(ha)001:10165: rin po che dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:10169: rdo rje rtse lnga dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)001:10171: sna tshogs rdo rje dang dril bu rnams bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:10172: s+phar sang gi 'phro 'dus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)001:10174: badz+ra d+ha ri shwa ra h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:10175: mi skyod pa rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10176: chos kyi dbyings phyug mas dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:10179: sems dpa' rdo rje 'khor lo bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10180: brtan ma rdo rje dril bu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10184: rin chen rdo rje rin po che bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10185: 'bar ma rdo rje dril bu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10188: chos rdo rje pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10189: sdud ma rdo rje dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:10192: las kyi rdo rje ral gri bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10193: bskyod ma rdo rje dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:10194: de ltar yum lnga char dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:10195: yab yum bcu kha sku mdog mthing kha /
NK029(ha)001:10196: brgyan tshul dang ldan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10197: de ltar mi bskyod pas gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa brgyad po dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:10200: ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab drangs bstim brtan /
NK029(ha)001:10201: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK029(ha)001:10202: sbyor ba'i brdas bskul ba la sogs pa sngar bzhin bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:10203: mdor na rang gi yi dam gang yin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:10205: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po /
NK029(ha)001:10206: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung /
NK029(ha)001:10207: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mchod la /
NK029(ha)001:10208: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor /
NK029(ha)001:10213: snying gi 'dom rtsar dran byed rtog shes kyi thig le la stim /
NK029(ha)001:10214: lnga pa sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK029(ha)001:10215: sngar phan chad lha rtog dbyer med bsgom mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:10216: da bsgom nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skye bar bsgom la /
NK029(ha)001:10219: lha dang mi rtog pa thams cad la thogs pa
NK029(ha)001:10220: med pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa'i dbang dam pa
NK029(ha)001:10221: thob par gyur cig bdun pa ma thob pa'i skyon
NK029(ha)001:10222: ni / bskyed rdzogs sgom mi nus pa la sogs pa'i skyon yod do //
NK029(ha)001:10224: nyan bsgom mthar phyin mngon du gyur pa'i yon tan yod do //
NK029(ha)001:10225: gsum pa 'phrin las kyi dbang la brgyad kyi dang po la rgyu la mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10226: lag pa gnyis gyi 'dom rtsa'i bskyod byed reg shes kyi thig le'o //
NK029(ha)001:10227: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10228: rgya gram don grub gyi rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)001:10229: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi'i dang po rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10230: dbang bskur du rung pa'i slob bu ste /
NK029(ha)001:10231: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:10232: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10233: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10234: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10235: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10236: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:10237: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10238: sgom dbang thob pas go phyes nas /
NK029(ha)001:10239: 'phrin las kyi dbang thob la ma rag pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10243: nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste rno la ngar rtags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:10245: bsgom dbang gi rjes su 'phrin las kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:10246: drug pa las rim pa lnga'i bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:10247: dbang phyug yab yum kun bzang yab yum du bskyed
NK029(ha)001:10248: pa'i sbyor 'tshams nas b+h+rum ljang khu slob bu'i lag
NK029(ha)001:10249: pa gnyis kyis 'doms rtsar 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)001:10250: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa sngar bzhin bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:10254: h+aum dzahh+aum h+aum h+aum bamhh+aum ho /
NK029(ha)001:10256: s+pha ra sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)001:10263: badz+ra p+aa sha ka p+aa la /
NK029(ha)001:10267: rdo rje rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:10268: ral gri dang gar gyi phu dung /
NK029(ha)001:10269: rdo rje'i go cha dang dung chos /
NK029(ha)001:10270: phag rgod kyi mche ba dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)001:10271: khu tshur dang lha'i nam bzar gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:10272: s+phar sang gi spro bsdus sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:10273: badz+ra a mo ka sid+hi a /
NK029(ha)001:10274: badz+ra ta re ye ha zhes pas /
NK029(ha)001:10275: don yod grub pa rgya gram bsnams pa la /
NK029(ha)001:10276: sgrol ma dril bu bsnams pas 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)001:10279: rdo rje las ral gri ba snams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10280: rdo rje gar ma gar bsgyur ba /
NK029(ha)001:10283: rdo rje bsrung ba go cha bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10284: rdo rje dbyug pa ma dri'i dung chos bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10287: rdo rje gnod sbyin phag rgod kyi mche ba bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10288: rdo rje dril bu ma dril bu bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10291: rdo rje khur tshul khu tshur bcangs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10292: rdo rje gnod sbyin rma bya'i sgro rgya gram bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10293: yab yum bcu kha yang sku ma dog ljang khu rgyan tshul dang ldan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10302: zhes sgo khyud bzhi la sgo ba yab yum sku mdog phyag mtshan sngar bzhin bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10303: de ltar bskyed pa'i dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la /
NK029(ha)001:10311: bzhi bsnol gyis mchod sbyor ba'i brdas bskul bas snyoms par zhugs pa'i bde bas /
NK029(ha)001:10312: lha bac+wa brgyad slob bu dang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba las don yod grub par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:10314: khyod ni rdo rje las yin gyis /
NK029(ha)001:10315: las rnams ma lus khyod kyis byos /
NK029(ha)001:10317: khyod kyi dgongs pa byed pa yin /
NK029(ha)001:10319: bskur gnas ni lag par dbang rdzas rgya gram gtad /
NK029(ha)001:10321: lag pa gnyis 'dom rtsa'i skyod byed kyi thig le la stim /
NK029(ha)001:10322: lnga pa ni sngon chad 'phrin las bzhis 'dul ma
NK029(ha)001:10323: nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skye bar bsam zhing
NK029(ha)001:10326: 'phrin las rnam bzhis srid pa gsum sems can ma
NK029(ha)001:10327: lus pa'i don ji lta ba 'dul ba bzhin byed
NK029(ha)001:10328: pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:10332: bzhi pa 'chad dbang la brgyad kyi dang po rgyu
NK029(ha)001:10333: la gnyis kyi dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni
NK029(ha)001:10334: / lce'i 'dom rtsa myong byed reg shes kyi thig le'o //
NK029(ha)001:10335: gnyis pa lhan cig pa byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10336: dung chag shing 'khor lo gsum mtha' yas kyi rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)001:10337: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi'i dang po rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10338: dbang bskur du rung pa'i skyes bu ste /
NK029(ha)001:10339: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:10340: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10341: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10342: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10343: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10344: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10345: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10346: 'phrin las kyi dbang thob pas go phyes nas /
NK029(ha)001:10351: nus pa dngos su ba skyed pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:10352: rno mtshon la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:10354: 'phrin las kyi dbang gi rjes su 'chad dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:10356: drug gi dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:10357: dbang phyug kun bzang yab yum du gsal ba'i sbyor
NK029(ha)001:10358: 'tshams nas b+h+rum slob bu'i lce'i steng du 'phros pas
NK029(ha)001:10359: / gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa sngar bzhin gsal la /
NK029(ha)001:10360: 'khor lo la gdan gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)001:10362: sgo khyud la h+aum dzahhum h+aum h+aum bo h+aum ho /
NK029(ha)001:10363: s+pha ra sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)001:10367: tsakra po ta bak+sha ko ke pa /
NK029(ha)001:10369: badz+ra pa sha ka pa la sh+ri kha la /
NK029(ha)001:10375: 'khor lo dang lcags sgrog rnams bskyed la s+phar sang
NK029(ha)001:10376: gi spro bsdus 'khor lo'i lte ba la snang ba
NK029(ha)001:10377: mtha' yas yab yum pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams pa
NK029(ha)001:10378: bskyed / de bzhin du rtsibs bzhi la /
NK029(ha)001:10379: rdo rje chos pad+ma kha 'byed pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10380: rdo rje glu len pa pi wang bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10386: rdo rje gsal ka ma sgron me bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10387: sgo ba yab yum rang rang gis sngags kyis bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10392: sbyor ba'i brdas bskul snyom par zhugs pa rjes chags kyi mes /
NK029(ha)001:10393: lha bac+wa brgyad slob bu dang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung dmar po las /
NK029(ha)001:10394: snang ba mtha' yas su gyur par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:10396: gyis bdud rtsi bla med kyis /
NK029(ha)001:10397: dad ldan skyes bu ngom par byos /
NK029(ha)001:10398: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la /
NK029(ha)001:10399: mthun par gsang bsgrag gzhan du min /
NK029(ha)001:10404: 'khor lo dung chags shing gsum las /
NK029(ha)001:10406: lag pa g.yas su dung dang /
NK029(ha)001:10407: g.yon du chags shing gtad la /
NK029(ha)001:10410: lce la gnas pa'i smra byed reg shes kyi thig
NK029(ha)001:10411: le la stim zhing sngon chad sems can gyi shes
NK029(ha)001:10412: rgyud la / chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:10413: da chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun mi 'chad par bskor
NK029(ha)001:10414: nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgom zhing
NK029(ha)001:10416: 'chad pa'i dbang bskur bas sems can thams cad kyi shes pa'i rgyud la /
NK029(ha)001:10417: theg pa mtha' dag gi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:10418: bdun pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)001:10419: dbang ma thob par 'chad pa la sogs byas na /
NK029(ha)001:10420: 'bras bu med cing brlag par 'gyur ba'i skyon yod do //
NK029(ha)001:10421: brgyad pa dbang thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)001:10423: tshe ring bde skyid phun sum 'tshogs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10424: phyi mar mtho ris dang thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)001:10425: lnga pa rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams gyi dbang la /
NK029(ha)001:10426: brgyad kyi dang po rgyu la gnyis kyi dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10427: yan lag lnga'i 'dam rtsa na bskyod byed reg shes kyi thig le lnga gnas pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10428: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10429: rdo rje dril bu kun bzang yab yum kyi rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)001:10430: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi'i dang po'i slob ma ste /
NK029(ha)001:10431: mi mthun phyogs gyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:10432: mthun phyogs gyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:10433: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10434: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10435: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10436: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10437: bzhi pa de ma theg pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10438: 'chad dbang thob pas rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams gyi dbang thob pa'i sgo phye ste /
NK029(ha)001:10441: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyii dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:10442: bzhi pa 'bras bu ni nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:10443: rno mtshon la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:10446: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:10447: drug pa las rim la lnga'i dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:10448: dbang phyug yab yum kun bzang yab yum du gsal ba'i sbyor 'tsham gyi /
NK029(ha)001:10451: lag 'thil g.yas g.yon rnams su 'phros pas /
NK029(ha)001:10452: b+h+rum bi shwa b+ai shud d+he'i sngags lan lnga brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:10453: mgo la sogs pa'i gnas lngar gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa cha lnga bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:10454: mgo'i gzhal yas khang gi dbus kyi 'khor lo la /
NK029(ha)001:10456: de bzhin du lag pa g.yas pa h+aum zung lnga lag pa g.yon pa la swa zung lnga /
NK029(ha)001:10457: rkang pa g.yon pa la am zung lnga /
NK029(ha)001:10458: g.yas pa la h+aa zung lnga /
NK029(ha)001:10467: bshang lam rnams su h+aum zung re re bkod la /
NK029(ha)001:10469: lha bdun bcu rang rang gi phyag mtshan du gyur te /
NK029(ha)001:10470: de yang s+phar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)001:10471: lha bdun bcu rang rang gi bskyed sngags kyis sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:10472: thog mar slob bu'i mgo la bskyed pa'i gzhal yas
NK029(ha)001:10473: khang gi 'khor la gnas pa'i nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan
NK029(ha)001:10474: la / dbus kyi lte ba la /
NK029(ha)001:10477: tsakra g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10481: zhes rnams snang yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10490: zhes rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)001:10491: la s+ye ma me long bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10497: sam ha ra na h'u badz+ra ra dza /
NK029(ha)001:10499: zhes rdo rje rgyal po lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10500: d+hu pe ma spos khang bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10509: zhes rdo rje chags pa 'da' gzhu 'gengs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10510: rdo rje lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10519: zhes rdo rje legs pa se gol brdeb pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10520: rdo rje sgrol ma sngo po 'phreng ba bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10521: lag pa g.yas kyi gzhal yas khang gi gdan gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)001:10524: cho ga gsum gyis lha bskyed de /
NK029(ha)001:10525: h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10531: mum da du shwa ri h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:10532: zhes mi skyod pa yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10534: h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10538: zhes sems dpa' rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)001:10539: brtan ma rdo rje skur brten ma /
NK029(ha)001:10540: g.yas su h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10542: rat+na dz+wa la s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10543: sam ha ra na h'u rat+na badz+ra h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:10545: zhes rin chen rdo rje rin chen 'bar ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:10546: 'bar ma rdo rje me 'od bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10547: rgyab du h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10553: zhes chos kyi rdo rje pad+ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:10554: bsdud ma rdo rje spo ti bsnams pa g.yon du h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10561: zhes rdo rje 'phrin las shang lang dang /
NK029(ha)001:10562: bskyod ma rdo rje ba dan bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10563: lag pa g.yon gyi gzhal yas khang gi 'khor lo'i lte ba la /
NK029(ha)001:10564: swa swa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10566: rat+na g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10568: swa rat+na d+h+rika mam mo ha ra ti swah+aa zhes rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10577: zhes rdo rje rin chen rin po che'i myu gu dang phreng ba bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10578: g.yas su s+w+aa s+w+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10580: sur+ya push+pe s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10584: rdo rje gzi brjid nyi ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:10585: me tog ma me tog bsnam pa /
NK029(ha)001:10586: rgyab du s+w+aa s+w+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10588: ke du pa sha s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10592: zhes rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang /
NK029(ha)001:10593: rdo rje zhags pa ma zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10594: g.yon du s+w+aa s+w+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10596: ha s+ye ra ti s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10598: badz+ra ha s+ye s+w+aa badz+ra rat+na s+w+aa zhes /
NK029(ha)001:10599: rdo rje gzhad pa tshems kyi 'phreng ba ston pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10600: rdo rje bsil yab rin po che'i bsil yab bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10601: rkang pa g.yon gyi gzhal yas khang gi 'khor lo'i lte ba la /
NK029(ha)001:10602: am am s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10604: pad+ma g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10606: a ro lika am pyam ra ga ra ti am /
NK029(ha)001:10607: zhes snang ba mtha' yas yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10609: am am s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10611: d+harma git+ti s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10616: rdo rje glu len ma pi wam bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10624: badz+ra a lo ke am zhes /
NK029(ha)001:10625: rdo rje rnon po ral gri dang /
NK029(ha)001:10626: rdo rje mar me ma mar me bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10627: rgyab du am am s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10629: tsakra spo ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10633: zhes rdo rje rgyu 'khor lo dang /
NK029(ha)001:10634: rdo rje lcags sgrog ma lcags sgrog bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10639: pak+sha ke pa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10644: rdo rje smra ba rdo rje'i lce dang rdo rje gsal kra ma rdo rje bsnams par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10645: rkang pa g.yas pa'i gzhal yas khang gi 'khor lo'i lte ba la /
NK029(ha)001:10646: khang+gu ga n+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10650: don yod grub pa yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10652: ha ha s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10654: bi shwa badz+ra nirti s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10656: badz+ra karma h+aa badz+ra nirti h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:10658: rdo rje las sna tshogs rdo rje pad+ma /
NK029(ha)001:10659: rdo rje gar ma gar bsgyur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:10663: rak+sha g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10667: rdo rje bsrung ba go cha dang /
NK029(ha)001:10668: rdo rje tri ma dbyug pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:10669: rgyab tu h+aa h+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10671: tram tram g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10675: zhes rdo rje gnod sbyin phag rgod kyi mche ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:10676: rdo rje dril bu ma dril bu bsnams pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:10677: g.yon du h+aa h+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10679: san ti par she s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10683: rdo rje khu tshur skur brten pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10684: rdo rje reg ma lha'i nam bza' pan tsa li ka bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10689: gis spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)001:10690: badz+ra b+han+ha s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:10692: bcus khro bo bcu'i thugs phyag mtshan rdo rje dung dmar bcur gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)001:10693: sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10694: spyi gtsug tu badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum ka ra h+aum h+aum las /
NK029(ha)001:10695: h+aum ka ra sngo skya g.yas dkar /
NK029(ha)001:10697: phyag dang por rdo rje dang dung dmar /
NK029(ha)001:10699: tha ma gnyis phur pa 'dril ba /
NK029(ha)001:10700: dur drod kyi chas brgyad dang /
NK029(ha)001:10701: gar dgu'i brgyan pa dang 'od kyis yum sgra 'byin ma dang bcas par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10702: de bzhin du 'chad par 'gyur ba'i khro bo thams cad kyang /
NK029(ha)001:10703: dbus zhal sku mdog dang mtshungs pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10704: phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dung dmar /
NK029(ha)001:10705: bar ma gnyis rang btags kyi phyag mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)001:10706: tha ma gnyis ri rab kyi phur pa 'dril ba /
NK029(ha)001:10707: dur khro kyi chas brgyad kyi brgyan zhing /
NK029(ha)001:10708: rang 'od kyi yum rdo rje snyem ma la sogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:10709: g.yas gtso bo la 'khyud nas g.yon pas dung dmar
NK029(ha)001:10710: gtso la stobs pa dang bcas me dpung gi klong
NK029(ha)001:10714: snying khar rnam rgyal dkar po zhal g.yas sngo skya /
NK029(ha)001:10715: g.yon sngon po kha tram tri shul bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10717: zhes nu kha g.yas la dbyug pa sngon po g.yas dkar /
NK029(ha)001:10719: dbyug pa dang me dpung bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10720: ya man ta ka h+aum h+aum zhes /
NK029(ha)001:10724: g.yon ljang ben con dang dgra s+t+wa bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10725: sog steng g.yas par ar+ya a tsa la h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:10727: mi g.yo mgon po sku mdog ljang dmar /
NK029(ha)001:10730: spu gri dang zhags pa bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10731: sog phrag tu h+ya g+h+ri ba h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:10736: ral gri dang sbrul zhags 'dzin pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:10737: sog steng g.yon du a pa ra dzi ta h+aum h+aum zhes /
NK029(ha)001:10738: gzhan gyis mi thub pa sngon po /
NK029(ha)001:10740: b+han rgya dang rnga yab bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)001:10742: a mri ta kun+da li h+aum h+aum zhes /
NK029(ha)001:10746: rgya gram dang dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10747: nu kha g.yon par tre lo kya bi dza ya h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:10749: khams gsum rnam rgyal ser po /
NK029(ha)001:10750: g.yas ljang g.yon du kha 'khor lo dang mche ba 'dzin pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10751: bshang khar ma h+aa ba la h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:10752: zhes stobs po che dung kha g.yas ser /
NK029(ha)001:10756: de ltar lha tshogs bdun bcu po la /
NK029(ha)001:10757: shu nya tas ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur la /
NK029(ha)001:10758: rang rang gi rigs kyi bdag po /
NK029(ha)001:10759: dbus na gnas pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan par bsgom la /
NK029(ha)001:10760: k+aa ya badz+ra la sogs sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlabs /
NK029(ha)001:10761: rang bzhin gyis gnas nas rang 'dra ba'i ye shes pa /
NK029(ha)001:10766: ka ya waka tsit+tasa brtan par byas /
NK029(ha)001:10767: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod pas /
NK029(ha)001:10768: lha yab yum thams cad phan tshun mkha' gsang brlabs /
NK029(ha)001:10770: snyom par zhugs pa'i bde ba chen pos /
NK029(ha)001:10771: slob bu dang bcas pa zhu bar gyur pa'i 'od phung sngon po las /
NK029(ha)001:10772: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po kun tu bzang po bsam /
NK029(ha)001:10774: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i thams cad kyi //
NK029(ha)001:10775: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK029(ha)001:10776: dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po //
NK029(ha)001:10777: dkyil 'khor kun gyis sbyin pa mos //
NK029(ha)001:10780: dbang phyug gi rdo rje dang dril bu bsnol ma gtad de /
NK029(ha)001:10781: snying khar bsnol du bcug la /
NK029(ha)001:10783: yan lag lnga'i reg shes kyi thig le la /
NK029(ha)001:10785: sngon chad slob ma dkyil 'khor du zhugs cing dbang
NK029(ha)001:10786: bskur ba la sogs pa gzhan don bya bar mi
NK029(ha)001:10787: nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:10788: da dbang phyug chen por gyur ste /
NK029(ha)001:10789: bdag dang gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs par spyod
NK029(ha)001:10790: cing sgrub nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par
NK029(ha)001:10793: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:10794: slob ma dkyil 'khor du zhugs cing dbang bskur pa
NK029(ha)001:10795: la sogs pa'i las thams cad byed pa'i rdo rje
NK029(ha)001:10796: rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang dam pa thob
NK029(ha)001:10797: par gyur cig / bdun pa bka' rab 'byams kyis dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)001:10798: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u bcu pa las /
NK029(ha)001:10799: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK029(ha)001:10800: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na /
NK029(ha)001:10801: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams //'bras bu med cing brlag par 'gyur /
NK029(ha)001:10803: brgyad pa dbang thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)001:10805: dus 'di tshun chad rgyal ba'i sras /
NK029(ha)001:10806: ngan song thams cad med pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10807: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:10808: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur /
NK029(ha)001:10810: de dag ni nang nus pa'i dbang gi las kyi rim pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:10811: nang nus kyi dkyil 'khor du bskur pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10813: bsgom dbang thob pas bdag don nus /
NK029(ha)001:10814: 'phrin las kyi dbang 'chad dbang thob pas gzhan don nus /
NK029(ha)001:10815: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang thob pas /
NK029(ha)001:10816: bdag gzhan thams cad kyi don phun sum tshogs pa nus pa'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:10817: nus pa'i dbang zhes tha snyad du bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:10818: spyi don gsum pa zab mo'i dbang la /
NK029(ha)001:10819: gsang rgyud le'u bcu pa las /
NK029(ha)001:10820: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya mas /
NK029(ha)001:10821: bde ba'i 'bru tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun /
NK029(ha)001:10822: rdo rje lam nas pad mor dkyil /
NK029(ha)001:10823: rtse nas stim zhing dkyil 'khor bsgyur /
NK029(ha)001:10826: gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:10827: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:10828: bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:10829: dang po la brgyad kyi dang po rgyud la gnyis kyi /
NK029(ha)001:10830: dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10831: kun rdzob tsam du skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong gi sems rang chas su gnas pa de'o //
NK029(ha)001:10832: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10835: chos gsum bshad pa'i bu mo mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lo nyi shu lon pa de'o //
NK029(ha)001:10838: gsang dbang bskur du rung pa'i skyes bu ste /
NK029(ha)001:10839: mi mthun phyogs gyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:10840: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10841: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10842: bu mo lo nyi shu ma yum lnga la sogs pas byin gyis ba rlabs pa de'o //
NK029(ha)001:10843: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10844: gsang dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma ste /
NK029(ha)001:10845: yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:10847: de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10848: dbang snga ma nang nus dbang lnga thob pas go phye nas /
NK029(ha)001:10849: gsang dbang 'byung ba'i rkyen byed pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:10850: gsang dbang thob la ma rag pa de'o //
NK029(ha)001:10851: gsum pa dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK029(ha)001:10854: nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:10855: rno mtshon la ngar brtag pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:10857: nus dbang gi rjes su gsang dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:10858: drug pa las rim lnga'i dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:10859: thog mar phyag rgya ma mtshan nyid brtag pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:10860: dam tshig rdo rje gsal bkra las /
NK029(ha)001:10861: pad can dung can ri mo can /
NK029(ha)001:10862: ba glang can dang lcugs phran can /
NK029(ha)001:10863: sdong gcig me rig chal ba brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:10864: bsnyen grangs snyed ring stod smad phyed /
NK029(ha)001:10865: yan lag phra 'jam tshig mig zlum /
NK029(ha)001:10866: dpral ba'i dbyes che mig kyus ring /
NK029(ha)001:10867: mig dpral dkyil na ud dpal mdog /
NK029(ha)001:10868: mchur zhing gnyis ka 'bring du bshad /
NK029(ha)001:10869: lus la chu rlung ga bur dri /
NK029(ha)001:10870: gsang thub shes rab spyod pa dal /
NK029(ha)001:10871: dad ldan 'grogs shing dad che ba /
NK029(ha)001:10873: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa bkug cing /
NK029(ha)001:10875: bza' btung longs spyod man+dala dang bcas pas bla ma la phul /
NK029(ha)001:10876: de nas bla mas yum la ji ltar 'os pa'i dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)001:10877: de nas yab yum gnyis bdag bskyed bsgoms ste /
NK029(ha)001:10878: yab kun du bzang por sgom pa'i gnas lnga rigs lnga yan lag bzhi la sgo ba bzhi bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10879: rgyas pa ltar na bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi lus dkyil bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:10881: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gos shugs la shes /
NK029(ha)001:10882: yum kun du bzang mor sgom /
NK029(ha)001:10884: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10887: de la ye shes pa spyan drangs nas ba stim mchod bstod /
NK029(ha)001:10888: de nas yab kyi gsang ba'i h+aum las /
NK029(ha)001:10889: rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga pa rwa lnga la yab kyi 'bru lnga /
NK029(ha)001:10892: yum gyi mkha' la pad+ma 'dab brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:10893: ze 'bru la e mthing ka med 'od dang ldan pa bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:10895: zhi ba'i bsnyen pa ci rigs par byed do //
NK029(ha)001:10897: dkyil 'khor sor bzhi'i tshad du bya gsungs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:10899: ka p+aa la'i steng gi me long la pad+ma 'dab
NK029(ha)001:10900: bzhi gru chad sgo 'dogs can la sogs bri zhing
NK029(ha)001:10901: / yum lnga sgo ma dang bcas pa la sogs bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:10903: gsungs pa dang mtshungs par me long gi steng gi
NK029(ha)001:10904: rdo rje la rigs lnga sgo ba bzhi dang bcas
NK029(ha)001:10908: bsnyen pa dang bcas pa byed do //
NK029(ha)001:10909: de nas mdun bskyed kyi lha tshogs la gsang dbang
NK029(ha)001:10910: gi bdag 'jug bla ma yab yum gnyis kas len
NK029(ha)001:10911: no // de nas bus man+dala phul la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:10912: rdo rje slob dpon yab yum dgongs //'dod pa 'byung pa rin chen gter //
NK029(ha)001:10913: dgyes pa chen po thabs lam gyis /
NK029(ha)001:10914: chu bo bzhi las bdag sgrol mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:10917: bu khyod bsgrol dang thabs lam 'di //
NK029(ha)001:10918: rgyal ba yongs kyis sbas pa yin //
NK029(ha)001:10919: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:10920: gtsang smes 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:10921: dri sha chu rnams bza' btung dang //
NK029(ha)001:10922: b+ha ga'i ye shes dkyil 'khor la //'o dang 'jib dang bsgreng ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:10923: sems chu gdung bar khyod nus sam /
NK029(ha)001:10925: e ma ho thabs lam ye shes phyir //
NK029(ha)001:10926: bdag ni ci yang mi nus med //
NK029(ha)001:10927: de dag bdag gis spyad par bgyi //
NK029(ha)001:10928: ji ltar spyad phyir bdag la bstsol /
NK029(ha)001:10930: de nas bla mas yab yum bde ba'i bstan chos bshad /
NK029(ha)001:10931: 'o dang 'khyud pa la sogs pas bde ba rgyas par byed /
NK029(ha)001:10932: de nas phyag rgya bzhis rol /
NK029(ha)001:10933: yum gyis mkha' la rgyal ba'i dal bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:10934: thig le dbab la mchod pa 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:10935: de nas yum gyis byang sems dkar dmar du 'dres pa des /
NK029(ha)001:10936: slob bu la dbang bskur te /
NK029(ha)001:10937: bya dang bye'u'i tshul du bskur ba'i /
NK029(ha)001:10938: ba dang be'u'i tshul du bskur ba'am /
NK029(ha)001:10939: bung ba dang me tog gi tshul du bskur ba'am /
NK029(ha)001:10941: me long yu ba can gyi blang la bu ram
NK029(ha)001:10942: sogs pa'i mngar bsreg la lce thog du bzhug pas
NK029(ha)001:10943: / don dam rtog med kyi ye shes rgyud la skye /
NK029(ha)001:10944: tsit+ta'i snying gi nang du rigs drug gi sa bon yi ge drug sbyangs /
NK029(ha)001:10945: lus kyi rtsa gnas thig le dang bde bas gang par bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)001:10947: dri med skyon bral shel sgong mu tig 'dra //
NK029(ha)001:10948: pad+ma r+aa ga chags pa chen po'i gnas //
NK029(ha)001:10949: chos nyid dag pa'i 'gro don mthar phyin zhing /
NK029(ha)001:10950: byang chub sems kyi dbang mchog thob bya'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:10951: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta yab kyi byang chub sems /
NK029(ha)001:10952: don dam dbyer med byang chub chen po'i ngang /
NK029(ha)001:10953: sin d+hur dmar po yum gyi byang chub sems /
NK029(ha)001:10954: thar pa'i lam mchog bde ba'i lam 'dren zhing /
NK029(ha)001:10955: 'khor ba'i lam las kun rgyal dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:10956: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:10957: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ka ma la sid+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:10960: lce thog tu bdud rtsi bzhag /
NK029(ha)001:10962: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la stim mo //
NK029(ha)001:10963: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang dag skye ni /
NK029(ha)001:10964: sngar phan chad gsang dbang ma thob pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:10965: longs spyod rdzogs pa yi sku thob pa'i nus pa skye bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:10967: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:10968: thabs shes gnyis su med par dbang 'byor nas /
NK029(ha)001:10969: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med cing 'du 'bral
NK029(ha)001:10970: med pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig bdun
NK029(ha)001:10971: pa skyon dang / brgyad par yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)001:10973: gnyis pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang la brgyad
NK029(ha)001:10974: kyi dang po rgyu la gnyis kyi dang po mtshungs
NK029(ha)001:10976: don dam du skye ba med /
NK029(ha)001:10979: 'gro 'ong med pa'i byang chub kyi sems rang chas su gnas pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10980: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:10984: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi'i dang po rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10985: dbang bskur du rung pa'i skyes bu ste mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:10986: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10987: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10988: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10989: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10990: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:10991: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:10992: gsang dbang thob par go phyes nas /
NK029(ha)001:10993: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob pa la ma rag pa'o /
NK029(ha)001:10995: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:10997: nus pa dngos su skyes pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:10998: rno la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:11000: gsang dbang gi rjes su shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:11001: drug pa rim pa lnga'i dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:11002: gzungs ma lo bcu drug mtshan dang ldan pa bkug cing khrus byas /
NK029(ha)001:11005: longs spyod man+dala dang bcas pa bla ma la 'bul lo /
NK029(ha)001:11006: bla mas phyag rgya ma la dge bcu bshad /
NK029(ha)001:11011: bdag bskyed lus dkyil ltar rgyas par bsgom la /
NK029(ha)001:11012: spyan 'dren la sogs mchod bstod dang /
NK029(ha)001:11013: bsnyen pa 'bum tshar nas mdun bskyed me long dang /
NK029(ha)001:11014: rdo rje la dmigs pa'i mdun bskyed spyan 'dren mchod bstod bsnyen pa yan chad tshar ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11015: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur ste /
NK029(ha)001:11016: de nas slob bus thal mo sbyar la //
NK029(ha)001:11017: rdo rje dga' ma bdag la dgongs //'dod pa 'byung ba rin chen gter //
NK029(ha)001:11018: dgyes pa chen pos thabs lam gyis //
NK029(ha)001:11019: chu bo bzhi las bdag sgrol cig /
NK029(ha)001:11021: bu khyod smros dang thabs lam 'di /
NK029(ha)001:11022: rgyal ba yongs kyis sbas pa yin /
NK029(ha)001:11023: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa ru /
NK029(ha)001:11024: gtsang sbras 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:11025: dri sha chu dang bza' btung dang /
NK029(ha)001:11026: nga'i b+ha ga'i ye shes bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:11027: 'o dang gzhib dang drangs ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11028: sems chu btung bar spyod nus sam /
NK029(ha)001:11031: thabs lam ye shes chen po'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:11032: bdag ni ci yang mi nus med /
NK029(ha)001:11033: de dag bdag gis spyad par bgyi /
NK029(ha)001:11034: ci ltar spyad phyir bdag la bstsol /
NK029(ha)001:11036: de nas gnyis pa bsgrag tshig ni /
NK029(ha)001:11037: bla mas rig ma mtshan ldan gyi lag nas gzung ste /
NK029(ha)001:11038: slob ma la gtad pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:11039: skye med chos dbyings rig pa 'byung ba'i yum /
NK029(ha)001:11040: mtshan ldan rig ma mchog gis brgyan /
NK029(ha)001:11041: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med rol pa las /
NK029(ha)001:11042: lhag pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor spro /
NK029(ha)001:11043: 'phags mchog bde bsgrub 'bras bu kun mnyes pa /
NK029(ha)001:11044: gnyis med don spyod chos nyid dag pa'i brgyan /
NK029(ha)001:11045: dgyes pa'i ro mchog bde chen dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:11046: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa gu h+ye pradz+ny+aa shwa ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:11048: de nas 'dod pa'i bstan chos kyi bde ba rgyas pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11049: bde ba dbab pa'i thob gtum mo sbar ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11050: rtsa rlung thig le bsgom pa'i thabs rnams slob la /
NK029(ha)001:11051: sha chen gyi tshod ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:11052: dri chen gyi bza' ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11054: nye'u shing khu ba btung ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11056: lus snum dang dri zhim pos byug la /
NK029(ha)001:11058: lus sems stong pa nyid las kun tu bzang mor bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:11060: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi 'god /
NK029(ha)001:11061: mkha' ga sang las pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad e mthing khas mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)001:11062: e mthing ka me 'od dang ldan pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:11063: bu rdo rje sems dpa' bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)001:11065: yan lag bzhi la sgo ba bzhi bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:11066: gsang ba h+aum las rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga pa bsgom pa'i r+aa la /
NK029(ha)001:11068: dbus kyi rtsa gsum la 'bru gsum sum mdor phata bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:11069: dri zhim po sbrang gi sbyar ba'i ril bu mur
NK029(ha)001:11070: zhing pad+ma la bltas ste yongs su rgyas nas phyag
NK029(ha)001:11073: spyi bo nas 'khor lo bzhi la rim pa bzhin dbab cing /
NK029(ha)001:11074: dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:11075: rang rig ye shes kyi ngo bo lhag pa byang
NK029(ha)001:11076: chub kyi sems ngo bo rdo rje nor bu'i rtser
NK029(ha)001:11077: phebs pa'i dus na gzung zhing bskyil ste /
NK029(ha)001:11078: de yang rlung bum pa can gzung pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11079: yig 'bru'i sbyor bas gzung ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11080: lus kyi 'khrul 'khor gyi gzung ba la sogs pas thig les bzung pa'i dus na /
NK029(ha)001:11081: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK029(ha)001:11082: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes bde stong dbyer med
NK029(ha)001:11083: kyi chos nyid / 'od gsal dri ma med pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:11084: ci bzhin ye mnyam chen po'i dgongs pa gnyis med
NK029(ha)001:11085: thig le nyag gcig gi rtogs pa ci lta ba
NK029(ha)001:11086: bzhin nyams su myong zhing ngo shes par gyur to
NK029(ha)001:11087: // de nas gnyis ka'i lag pa nas bzung nas /
NK029(ha)001:11088: bu khyod 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las //
NK029(ha)001:11089: grol zhing thar nas skad cig gis //
NK029(ha)001:11090: rdo rje nam mkha'i ye shes che //
NK029(ha)001:11091: bla ma chen po'i sar gnas su //
NK029(ha)001:11092: thams cad rigs kyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:11093: gcig pu sa bzung mnga' brnyes nas //
NK029(ha)001:11094: bde khyab chen po'i 'phrin las kyis //
NK029(ha)001:11095: khams gsum sras su gzung bar byos //
NK029(ha)001:11100: bstim gnas bde ba la bde ba stim mo //
NK029(ha)001:11101: bdun pa dbang ma bskur ba'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)001:11102: de kho na nyid kyi dbang bskur du mi rung pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11103: phyag rgya mo la brten pa'i bde ba lam du mi rung ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11104: sbyor ba lam du mi slong ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11105: lhan gcig skyes pa'i bde chen dang /
NK029(ha)001:11106: rang ngo mi 'phrod pa'i skyon yod do //
NK029(ha)001:11108: lam gyi dus na sa bcu gcig pa thob pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11109: 'bras bu'i dus na bde ba chen po'i sku thob pa'i yon tan yod do //
NK029(ha)001:11110: gsum pa bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba la brgyad kyi dang po /
NK029(ha)001:11111: rgyu la gnyis kyi dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)001:11112: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med /
NK029(ha)001:11114: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med /
NK029(ha)001:11115: dmigs pa nyid nas dmigs pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:11116: bden gnyis ye nas dbyer med par rang chas su gnas pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11117: gnyis pa mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni phyag rgya mo lo bcu gnyis ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11118: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi la dang po rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:11119: dbang bskur du rung pa'i slob ma ste /
NK029(ha)001:11120: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)001:11121: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11122: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:11123: bu mo lo bcu gnyis mar rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11124: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:11125: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma ste /
NK029(ha)001:11126: yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11127: bzhi pa de ma theg pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)001:11128: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob pas /
NK029(ha)001:11129: bde ba chen po'i dbang thob pa'i sgo phye ste /
NK029(ha)001:11130: dbang thob la ma rag pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11131: gsum pa dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK029(ha)001:11132: bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:11134: nus pa dngos su skyes pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:11135: rno mtshon la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)001:11137: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi rjes su bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:11138: drug pa las rim la lnga'i dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)001:11139: phyag rgya ma lo bcu gnyis ma bkug cing /
NK029(ha)001:11142: bza' btung longs spyod man+dala dang bcas pa bla mar 'bul /
NK029(ha)001:11143: de nas bla mas ji ltar 'os pa'i yum la dbang bskur la sbyor ba byas ste /
NK029(ha)001:11144: gzugs ma'i don dam pa'i lte ba nas /
NK029(ha)001:11145: zla ba tshes pa lta bu'i nang na byang chub
NK029(ha)001:11146: sems kyi thig le nyung dkar tsam zhig rang bzhin
NK029(ha)001:11147: gyis gnas pa la ting nge 'dzin gyis dmigs te
NK029(ha)001:11148: / gsang ba'i rdo rje ye shes kyi ro can dang /
NK029(ha)001:11151: yab kyi lhag pa'i b+ho d+hi thig le dang mkha' la gnas pa de basre'o //
NK029(ha)001:11152: de nas ru bab la pad+ma'i 'khyams na b+ho d+hi yod pa theb srin gyis blangs la /
NK029(ha)001:11153: gzungs ma'i lce thog tu bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:11154: de nas ya ba yum gnyis kas bdag bskyed zhi
NK029(ha)001:11155: ba'i lha zhe gnyis snying po brjod pas rdzogs pa'i
NK029(ha)001:11157: sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK029(ha)001:11159: dzahh+aum bam hohsaganyisa su med par stim la /
NK029(ha)001:11160: mchod bstod bsnyen pa ci rigs pa bya /
NK029(ha)001:11161: mdun bskyed kyang gong ltar du bsnyen pa yan chad byas la /
NK029(ha)001:11163: de nas slob bu'i gung mo g.yas pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11164: gzungs ma'i gung mo g.yon pa rat+na'i 'phreng bas bcings ste /
NK029(ha)001:11165: de'i mdo' nas slob dpon gyis gzung ste /
NK029(ha)001:11167: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK029(ha)001:11168: shes rab thabs kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //'di dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK029(ha)001:11169: dngos grub ster bas 'di mi spongs //
NK029(ha)001:11170: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK029(ha)001:11171: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas khyod las byung //
NK029(ha)001:11172: spangs na rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsa //
NK029(ha)001:11173: dgug dang bsgom pa ma shes na //
NK029(ha)001:11174: rdo rje skal pa mtha' slas pa //
NK029(ha)001:11175: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)001:11176: de'i don rgyas par bshad do //
NK029(ha)001:11183: thog ma gzung ma mthong pas bde ba g.yos pa dga' ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:11184: de dus gzungs ma byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11185: srin lag sprel ba la sogs pa byas pas bde
NK029(ha)001:11186: ba skye ba mchog daga'o //'dod pa'i chos kyi cha
NK029(ha)001:11187: byed pa ni / dga' bral lo //
NK029(ha)001:11188: gzugs ma dang rang lus rdul zhing bem gyis song ba ni lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK029(ha)001:11190: rang dang gzungs ma gnyis ka la /
NK029(ha)001:11192: bde ba chen po'i tsakra ni dga' ba /
NK029(ha)001:11193: longs spyod de tsakra ni mchog daga'o //
NK029(ha)001:11194: dar ma tsakra ni dga' bral /
NK029(ha)001:11195: sprul pa'i tsakra ni lhan skyes so /
NK029(ha)001:11197: gu h+ya badz+ra tsa ba ni dga' ba /
NK029(ha)001:11198: rdo rje sked pa ni mchog dga' /
NK029(ha)001:11199: rdo rje'i bum pa ni dga' 'bral /
NK029(ha)001:11200: rdo rje'i rtse mo ni lhan cig skyes daga'o //
NK029(ha)001:11201: de rnams re re la yang thig le bzhi bzhi rtsis pas bcu drug ste /
NK029(ha)001:11204: bcu gsang ba'i sa bcu shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:11205: de ltar gdam ngag phog nas /
NK029(ha)001:11206: bus sbyor ba la snyom par 'jug ste /
NK029(ha)001:11207: rdo rje la h+aum gcig bkod de spro bsdu la /
NK029(ha)001:11208: rdo rje rtse lnga pa gcig tu gyur /
NK029(ha)001:11210: rtse mo yi bu gar phata nag po /
NK029(ha)001:11211: b+ha ga la phata nag po gcig bsam /
NK029(ha)001:11214: de'i dbus su e mthing kha gru gsum pa /
NK029(ha)001:11215: de'i steng du h+aum dmar po gcig bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:11216: de nas gzungs ma la 'dod pa'i bstan chos kyi cha rnams bya /
NK029(ha)001:11218: rdo rje phyed tsam pad+mara bsdams ste /
NK029(ha)001:11220: sra bar myong pas 'byung pa sa'i rdul cung zad gsher ba chu cung zad dro ba me /
NK029(ha)001:11221: de nas shes pa zhib tu brtags pas bde ba g.yo ba rlung ngo //
NK029(ha)001:11222: de nas bde ba bzlog ste thabs kyi bzlog pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11224: phyag rgyas bzlog pa gsum las /
NK029(ha)001:11225: dang po ni bde ba g.yo ba tsam na /
NK029(ha)001:11226: rdo rje e tsam gcig pha tshad la phyung la /
NK029(ha)001:11227: lto ba rgal tshig la sbyar /
NK029(ha)001:11229: b+ho d+hi de slar ldog pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11230: ting nge 'dzin gyi bzlog pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:11233: ro rkyang gnyis kyi rtsa sna dbus kyi kun d+har 'brel nas yod pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11234: ro rkyang nas dbugs zhugs pa las /
NK029(ha)001:11235: kun d+har gyi lhag pa'i b+ho d+hi gyen la sna
NK029(ha)001:11236: 'khyil gyis ldog nas dkar chil gyis ldog par bsam
NK029(ha)001:11238: rdo rje'i rtsa ba nas phar /
NK029(ha)001:11239: sor mo gnyis kyi thub tshad mnan la ldog sprul pa'i 'khor lo nas gyen la de ltar ldog /
NK029(ha)001:11240: rdo rje'i rtsa ba nas dang /
NK029(ha)001:11242: rtse mo nas rim par ldog /
NK029(ha)001:11244: rdo rje rtsa ba'i dga' ba'i thig le bzhi'i theg
NK029(ha)001:11245: le gsum pa nas rdo rje sked pa'i mchog dag'i
NK029(ha)001:11246: / thig le gnyis pa ma chad ni gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa 'gag pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11247: mchod dag'i thig le gnyis pa yan chad ni /
NK029(ha)001:11249: de nas rdo rje rtse mo /
NK029(ha)001:11250: lhan gcig skyes pa'i gnas su zla ba dang nyi ma'i thig le /
NK029(ha)001:11252: rang rang gi kha nas ma shor bar zin tsam nas /
NK029(ha)001:11253: rang rig pa'i don nyams su myong ba de kun tu 'od kyi sa'o /
NK029(ha)001:11254: de'i dus su rgyu'i zung 'jug nyi zla 'dres pas /
NK029(ha)001:11255: 'bras bu'i zung 'jug ye shes rang snang gi lha
NK029(ha)001:11256: dang lha mor snang bzhin du rang bzhin med pa'o
NK029(ha)001:11257: // de tsam na zhen pa med pa'i pad+ma can gyi sa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11258: de la smon lam gyi dbang gis gzugs sku gnyis 'byung ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:11259: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis sa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11260: de ni theg pa 'og ma dang sgo bstun pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11261: de nas rgyu 'bras bzlog pa'i theg pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:11262: nyi zla thig le rang gi gnas su rtse mo nas tshur bzlog pas rims gyis bsgrod de /
NK029(ha)001:11263: rdo rje'i rtsa bar byin pa ni kun du 'od kyi sa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11264: de nas sprul pa'i tsakrara phyin pa pad+ma can no //
NK029(ha)001:11265: thig le rang gnas su phyin pa las /
NK029(ha)001:11266: rang bzhin lhun grub gyi dkyil 'khor mthong ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:11267: tshogs chen gyis mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK029(ha)001:11268: gal te b+ho d+hi shor na /
NK029(ha)001:11269: byang sems h+aum dmar sha ltag bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:11270: 'theb srin gyis blangs la khong du mid do //
NK029(ha)001:11271: gzungs ma la yang sbyin no //
NK029(ha)001:11272: sbyor la mi rtog pa'i bde ba skyes pa'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:11274: gzung ma mi dgos par mi rtog pa la blo gnas so /
NK029(ha)001:11276: yang dbang don de la blo gtad pas /
NK029(ha)001:11278: de ltar bsgom pa'i don la gnas par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:11279: bskur gnas lus kyi dbang po la bskur /
NK029(ha)001:11280: bstim gnas thig le la bstim /
NK029(ha)001:11281: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK029(ha)001:11282: bde ba chen po'i dbang thob pas shes bya'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)001:11283: bde ba chen po'i dbang thob pa'i nus pa skye bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:11285: bdun pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)001:11286: sems nyid rdzogs pa chen po yang dag don gyi lta ba mi rtogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:11287: gnas lugs chos nyid kyi don nyams su blang mi rung pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11288: dngos grub gnyis 'dzin gyi mtshan ma sna tshogs kyis 'chings pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11289: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa phyin ci ma log pa ngo ma 'phrod pa'i skyon yod do //
NK029(ha)001:11290: brgyad pa thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)001:11291: kun tu bzang po dbyer ba med pa'i sa thob pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11292: 'bras bu'i dus na chos kyi sku dang ngo bo nyid kyi sku thob po /
NK029(ha)001:11293: de dag rgyas par ni sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad
NK029(ha)001:11294: pa'i dbang gi skabs nas dbang gi gal po la
NK029(ha)001:11295: sogs pa rnams su blta bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:11296: de dag ni gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gi las kyi rim pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:11298: shes rab ye shes ni b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor dang
NK029(ha)001:11299: dbyer med bde ba chen po ni sems kyi dkyil
NK029(ha)001:11301: de yang gsang dbang thob nas /
NK029(ha)001:11302: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11303: steng sgo 'khor lo'i man ngag sgom pa /
NK029(ha)001:11304: gsang ba shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob nas /
NK029(ha)001:11305: las kyi phyag rgya bsten pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11306: 'og sgo khams gsum bsrub sbyor gyi man ngag sgom pa la dbang /
NK029(ha)001:11307: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang thob nas /
NK029(ha)001:11308: kun rdzob snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)001:11309: don dam bskor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi skur lhun gyis grub pa las ma g.yos par rtogs shing /
NK029(ha)001:11310: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen po mngon du 'gyur pa'i don gsang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:11311: de yang thog ma gnyis ni dkyil 'khor b+ha ga dang /
NK029(ha)001:11312: dbang rdzas nyi zla byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK029(ha)001:11316: bung ba dang me tog gi tshul dang /
NK029(ha)001:11317: nyams len ka ra na'i bstan bcos brgyad dam drug bcu rtsa bzhi la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK029(ha)001:11318: 'jig rten pa rnams kyi gzhad gad kyi gnas su 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK029(ha)001:11319: phyi ma blo chung ba rnams la rang gsang thabs kyi chod nas /
NK029(ha)001:11320: rang la gnas pa'i don de /
NK029(ha)001:11321: bstan kyang mi go mtshon kyang mi rtogs /
NK029(ha)001:11322: yon tan brjod kyang brod pa'i blo mi skye ba'i
NK029(ha)001:11323: phyir gsang ba zab mo'i dbang zhes tha snyad du
NK029(ha)001:11324: byas pa'o // don gsum pa rjes kyi bya ba la bdun ste /
NK029(ha)001:11325: dbang rtag sbyin zhing bka' sgo ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11326: bum chu blud zhing smon lam 'debs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11327: dbang phyug gi dbang dbab cing slob bu'i lus 'bul ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11328: btang rag gi mchod cing yon dbul ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11329: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal gdab cing lhag bstan skyong ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11330: dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing spyod lam rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11331: lam rjes shis par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:11334: dbang bac+wa brgyad rdzogs pa'i slob bu rnams gral la 'khod la /
NK029(ha)001:11335: dbang phyug gi rdo rje dril bu bsnams la //
NK029(ha)001:11336: sangs rgyas kun gyis rdo rje'i dbang //
NK029(ha)001:11337: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK029(ha)001:11338: sangs rgyas kun dang rab bsgrubs phyir //
NK029(ha)001:11339: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyi long /
NK029(ha)001:11340: zhes brjod cing rdo rje gsor /
NK029(ha)001:11341: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:11342: thabs dang shes rab dbang chen des //
NK029(ha)001:11344: chos la 'dod sbyin dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)001:11345: zhes brjod cing dril bu dkrol /
NK029(ha)001:11346: badz+ra g+han+de a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11348: rdo rje dril bu bsnol nas slob bu rnams kyi
NK029(ha)001:11349: lag pa g.yas g.yon du sbyin la rdo rje gsor
NK029(ha)001:11350: zhing dril bu dkrol du bzhug go /
NK029(ha)001:11351: kun rdzogs pa'i rjes thob su bden pa /
NK029(ha)001:11352: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams la dbang rtags rdo rje dril bu gtad de dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:11353: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pas 'gro ba
NK029(ha)001:11354: sens can gyi don rgyun mi 'chad pa byed pa'i
NK029(ha)001:11355: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:11356: ces brjod nas dbang phyug dbang khri la 'dug /
NK029(ha)001:11357: zhabs g.yas pas slob bu'i mgo la bzhag cing /
NK029(ha)001:11358: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyis /
NK029(ha)001:11359: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin pas /
NK029(ha)001:11360: nga yi ji skad sgo ba bzhin /
NK029(ha)001:11361: bu khyod kyis ni bya dgos so //
NK029(ha)001:11363: gnyis pa ni dbang phyug bzhengs ste /
NK029(ha)001:11364: dbus kyi bum pa phyag du bzhes la /
NK029(ha)001:11365: dbu brgyan cod pan 'phreng ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:11366: go cha rgya mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK029(ha)001:11367: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK029(ha)001:11368: snying po lnga yi dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)001:11369: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK029(ha)001:11370: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:11371: tshe rings bde ba phun sums tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:11372: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:11375: slob bu rnams la slud cing /
NK029(ha)001:11376: tish+tha badz+ra zhes pas dbang brtan par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:11377: bden pa bdag rdo rje che ge mos /
NK029(ha)001:11378: rdo rje che ge mo la sogs pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:11379: slob bu rnams sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)001:11381: ngan song gsum la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal thams cad bral nas /
NK029(ha)001:11382: mtho ris bde ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan ste /
NK029(ha)001:11383: de las kyang rgyal ba'i sras /
NK029(ha)001:11384: rigs phun sum tshogs pa'i sras su nges par dbang gi 'bras bu ma lus pa thob nas /
NK029(ha)001:11385: srid pa'i sem can mtha' dag gi don yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:11387: rgyal khams thams cad du dus kyi 'khrug pa zhi bar gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:11388: mtshon gyi skal pa nyams par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:11389: mi nad phyug nad thams cad rgyun chad par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:11390: char chu dus su phebs par lo chu rtag tu legs ste /
NK029(ha)001:11391: sems can thams cad bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa'i bskal pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:11394: dbang bac+wa brgyad kyi dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa rnams bsogs la /
NK029(ha)001:11395: dbang phyug kun tu bzang por gsal ba'i thugs kha'i h+aum las 'od 'phros pas /
NK029(ha)001:11396: dbang rdzas rnams rim pas sngar rab tu gnas pa'i lha gsal btab /
NK029(ha)001:11398: dbang phyug gi bskur gnas rnams su /
NK029(ha)001:11399: rang rang gi dbang rdzas gtugs pas /
NK029(ha)001:11400: 'od du zhu nas rang rang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la bstim pas /
NK029(ha)001:11401: sngar bas kyang nus pa cher skyes par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:11402: dbang rdzas thams cad kyi rab gnas bsdu ba zin pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11403: slar yang thugs kha'i h+aum las 'od 'phros ste /
NK029(ha)001:11404: sngar dpang po'i tshul du bzhugs pa'i mdun gyi nam
NK029(ha)001:11405: mkha'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'od du zhu
NK029(ha)001:11406: nas dbang phyug la thim pas /
NK029(ha)001:11407: 'od dang gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)001:11408: de nas slob bu rnams kyis phyag byas nas /
NK029(ha)001:11409: gus pa'i tshul gyis gnyis med rgyal ba'i mchog la rab gnas shing /
NK029(ha)001:11410: sku gsung thugs kyi rol pa cir ston pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:11411: bla med sman pa'i rgyal po dgongs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:11412: zang zing rdzas kyi dgos pas ma 'brel kyang /
NK029(ha)001:11413: bdag 'dzin sdug bsngal rtogs pas bcings pa yi /
NK029(ha)001:11414: 'khor ba'i 'dam rdzab klong nas drangs pa'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:11415: sbyor bas dmigs pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:11417: sngar lus phul 'dod pa'i slob bu rnams kyis /
NK029(ha)001:11418: ci 'byor pa'i yon gyis lus bslu bar bya'o /
NK029(ha)001:11419: bzhi pa slob bu'i gtso bos /
NK029(ha)001:11420: ka pa la mtshan dang ldan pa bdud rtsis bkang ba mar chol dang bcas pa btegs la /
NK029(ha)001:11421: khyod ni ye nas sku gsung thugs kyi dpal //
NK029(ha)001:11422: dpal gyi phyag rgya mang po thob pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:11423: dus gsum kun tu sangs rgyas yin pa'i rtags //
NK029(ha)001:11424: rdo rje che mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)001:11426: dbang phyug zhal du grangs la /
NK029(ha)001:11428: de yang dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i dus su /
NK029(ha)001:11431: rtsa rgyud kyi lung dang mi 'gal bar phul la /
NK029(ha)001:11433: smin lam rgya chen bro gdab po /
NK029(ha)001:11437: lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa nas /
NK029(ha)001:11438: lhag phud bsre ba'i bar byas la /
NK029(ha)001:11440: lhag chog btang zhing bstan ma bskyang nas /
NK029(ha)001:11441: gtor ma rin chen mchod bstod gyis /
NK029(ha)001:11442: sems can thams cad yid la gang 'dod pa tshim par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:11443: drug pa thog mar dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kun bzang zhabs bsil /
NK029(ha)001:11444: bzhi bsnol gyis btang rag gi tshul du mchod nas /
NK029(ha)001:11445: yi ge brgya bas lhag chad bskang zhing /
NK029(ha)001:11448: dbang phyug gi ngo bo bsdams te /
NK029(ha)001:11449: shar sgo'i tshangs thig gi lam nas h+aum zhes brjod cing /
NK029(ha)001:11450: dbus kyi gtso bo'i gnas kyi bar du bsdu /
NK029(ha)001:11454: byang nas kyang de gzhal yas khang lha la bsdu /
NK029(ha)001:11456: gtso bo thugs ka'i sa bon la bsdu /
NK029(ha)001:11457: sa bon yang na dkyil 'khor la bsdu ste /
NK029(ha)001:11458: yang na me long la has btab pa bzhin du yal nas /
NK029(ha)001:11459: stong pa nyid kyi ngang la cung zhig bzhag /
NK029(ha)001:11462: ri mthon po'i rtse la skyal /
NK029(ha)001:11464: bum chu don du gnyer pa yod na sbyin /
NK029(ha)001:11465: med na mis ma 'gong pa'i sar spo /
NK029(ha)001:11466: rdzas dang yo byad rnams dben par 'tshags bya'o /
NK029(ha)001:11467: de ltar rtag pa'i mtha' bsal nas /
NK029(ha)001:11468: slar yang chad pa'i mtha' bsal ba'i don du /
NK029(ha)001:11469: skadaciga dran rdzogs su yi dam gang yin du rang nyid gsal btab la go bsgo /
NK029(ha)001:11471: dbang nod spyod lam ba zhir /
NK029(ha)001:11472: yi dam lha'i nga rgyal dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)001:11474: 'og phyogs kyi phur pa nas rtsams /
NK029(ha)001:11475: mtshams phur bcu po lugs bzlog tu bsdus la /
NK029(ha)001:11476: phur pa'i lha ye shes pa gshegs /
NK029(ha)001:11477: dam tshig pa bdag yi dam lha'i thugs khar bsdu'o //
NK029(ha)001:11478: de nas sgo byang bsdus te /
NK029(ha)001:11479: lha'i sgo byang ye shes pa gshegs /
NK029(ha)001:11480: dam tshig pa bdag la bsdu /
NK029(ha)001:11483: de nas phyi'i rgyal chen gyi tho rnams lugs bzlog tu bsdus ste /
NK029(ha)001:11484: sngar tho 'dzugs pa'i dus kyi mchod pa bzhin btang rag gi mchod la /
NK029(ha)001:11485: rgyal chen gshegs su gsol lo //
NK029(ha)001:11489: khud dkar po gtsang ma'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:11490: ci 'byor pa'i bkra shis kyi rdzas /
NK029(ha)001:11491: bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs la /
NK029(ha)001:11493: bkra shis rab mchog dang bkra shis brgyad pa la sogs pa brjod cing /
NK029(ha)001:11494: bkra shis kyi rdzas dkyil 'khor rol par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:11496: chos skyong gzhi bdag la btang rag btang ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11497: skye bo la sbyin pa gtong ba la sogs pa bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:11498: de dag ni dbang bskur ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11499: gnas bsrungs ba'i las kyi rim pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:11500: nub bzhi pa ste tha ma'i cho ga'o //
NK029(ha)001:11504: gnyis pa khro bo'i dbang la gnyis te /
NK029(ha)001:11505: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11510: tshon dang bri ba'i rnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11511: rab gnas sbyin bsreg ces gsungs pas /
NK029(ha)001:11517: sku gsung thugs kyi rten rnam pa 'god pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11520: dang po ni lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor tshad dang /
NK029(ha)001:11522: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi tshad dang /
NK029(ha)001:11523: bum dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad dang /
NK029(ha)001:11524: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad dang gsum /
NK029(ha)001:11525: gong zhi ba'i skabs dang mthun no //
NK029(ha)001:11526: gnyis pa thig la bdun las /
NK029(ha)001:11533: rgyu ni mi yi rgyus pa la byed gsungs /
NK029(ha)001:11535: gzhan zhi ba'i skabs dang 'dra ba las /
NK029(ha)001:11536: de nas bye brag tu mu khyud bskor ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:11537: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11539: rgyas pa dang gsum zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor 'bring po dang bskor lugs mthun /
NK029(ha)001:11542: lnga pa yang mthun par snang /
NK029(ha)001:11545: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa gnyis kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11546: lnga la 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa re re bskor /
NK029(ha)001:11549: shar nub kyi rtsibs gnyis la rtsibs bzhi pa re res bskor /
NK029(ha)001:11550: tshom bu gcig pa la 'khor lo'i lte bar 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa gcig bskor ro //
NK029(ha)001:11551: gsum pa dkyil 'khor bri ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:11552: gzhan rnams zhi ba'i skabs dang mthun pa la /
NK029(ha)001:11553: cha chen bzhi pa lha snams la phyed du bgos pa yi nang ma la /
NK029(ha)001:11558: sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'i gnas /
NK029(ha)001:11559: lha rnams kyi phyi ma la phyogs mdog la dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi bzhugs gnas /
NK029(ha)001:11560: lha rnams phyi ma'i gru bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)001:11561: sgo bzhi steng 'og gnyis dang bcur khro bo yab yum bcu'i gnas /
NK029(ha)001:11563: phal cher zhi skabs dang mthun /
NK029(ha)001:11564: lnga pa rnam pa dgod pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:11565: zhi ba'i skabs dang mthun la /
NK029(ha)001:11566: bye brag du khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa /
NK029(ha)001:11570: tshom bu lnga pa'i tsa ka li rnams lha rang rang gi byin brlabs dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)001:11571: rang rang gi gnas su dgod /
NK029(ha)001:11573: thugs rten yang ci rig par dgod /
NK029(ha)001:11574: gzhan yang ka p+aa la la sogs pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:11577: mchod gtor la sogs rnams sta gon gyi skabs ltar legs par dgod par bya'o /
NK029(ha)001:11578: drug pa rab gnas la dgu ste /
NK029(ha)001:11579: sngon du bya ba'i cho ga dang /
NK029(ha)001:11580: ting nge 'dzin gyi sku bskyed cing dbang bskur byin brlabs bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11581: ye shes drangs zhing bstim pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11582: dbang po sogs skyon bsal ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11583: chu bdun khrus dang sku phyi ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11584: mnga' gsol rgyas par bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11585: pu tsa gsum dbul pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11586: bden brjod bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:11587: phyag bskor bya zhing smon lam btab pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:11589: bdag mdun bum pa bskyed pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:11596: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo /
NK029(ha)001:11600: badz+ra kro ta sh+ri he ru ka h+aum a a h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11602: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11604: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11605: badz+ra kro d+ha ni la d+han+da h+aum da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11606: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h'u pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK029(ha)001:11607: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11609: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+h+ri wa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11610: hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11611: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa ra dzi ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11613: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+ta li tshin+d+ha tshin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11614: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza y+aa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11616: badz+ra kro d+ha mah+aa ba la h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11617: s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11618: na ma sa man+ta bud+d+ha nan /
NK029(ha)001:11619: k+aa ya w+aak+ka tsit+ta badz+ra ni ma h+aa dam sho
NK029(ha)001:11620: ta ka tra b+hee ra na ya a si mu
NK029(ha)001:11621: si la sata sha s+aa h+aa sbra ya a mri
NK029(ha)001:11622: ta kun+ta li h+aum h+aum kha kha kha h+ai kh+aa
NK029(ha)001:11633: ma h+aa ga na pa ti /
NK029(ha)001:11634: dzi bi tan+ta k+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11635: h+aum ram badz+ra sa ma ya dza h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11637: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK029(ha)001:11638: zla rgyas bzhin du spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK029(ha)001:11639: thugs rje nyi gsal 'od bzhin snyoms mdzad lha //'di gshegs bzhugs shing bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:11640: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK029(ha)001:11641: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga gtso //
NK029(ha)001:11642: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya cher rol pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:11643: zhi khro sprul pa'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:11644: dngos su 'byor dang yid gyi rnam sprul pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:11645: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK029(ha)001:11646: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya chen yongs bkod de //
NK029(ha)001:11647: phyi nang gsang ba mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK029(ha)001:11648: kun tu bzang mo yum gyi b+ha ga la //
NK029(ha)001:11649: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus kun bkod pa //'du bral med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pas //
NK029(ha)001:11650: gnyis med byang chub sems kyis mnyes gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:11651: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK029(ha)001:11652: chos rnams rnag dag ye nas 'od gsal zhing //
NK029(ha)001:11653: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:11654: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dud //
NK029(ha)001:11655: kun bzang rdzogs ye nas gsal ba la //
NK029(ha)001:11656: phyi nang gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor bkod pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:11657: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //'byung dang 'byung 'gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK029(ha)001:11658: gsang chen rab dgyes gzungs chen bdag nyid ma //
