NK029(ha)001:11659: mkha' dbyings klong yangs pad+mo 'khyil ba la //
NK029(ha)001:11660: gnyis med thig le chen por 'od gsal zhing //
NK029(ha)001:11661: ma bcos spros med byang chub snying po'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:11662: cir yang snang ba bde chen g.yung drung lha //'du 'bral med pa gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK029(ha)001:11663: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK029(ha)001:11664: byang chub lcam bral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:11665: rdo rje lha mo tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag /
NK029(ha)001:11666: rigs lnga dbal chen khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK029(ha)001:11667: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi //
NK029(ha)001:11668: ye shes sprul pa'i lha tshogs mang po rnams //
NK029(ha)001:11669: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:11670: legs nyes btang 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod ma //
NK029(ha)001:11671: phyi nang mkha' 'gro rnal 'byor ma yi tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:11672: dpang gyur rdo rje dam can dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:11673: h+aum thugs rje'i gdung 'tshob rdo rje che ge mos //'gro ba'i don phyir byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:11674: bla med go 'phang bsgrod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:11675: bstan pa rgya mtsho'i so so'i 'dul khrims dang //
NK029(ha)001:11676: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor sdom pa'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:11677: rdo rje mda' ka dam tshig bstan gyi gnyer //
NK029(ha)001:11678: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK029(ha)001:11679: snga phyir mnos shing gnyer du smra 'o 'tshal //
NK029(ha)001:11680: yun du mi gtong mda' bar mi bgyid la //
NK029(ha)001:11681: don las 'gal zhing ldog sems ma mchis kyang //
NK029(ha)001:11682: bzod bya long yod mnyam pa'i le lo yi //
NK029(ha)001:11683: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs chung ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:11684: shes bzhin mi ldan bag med dbang gyur te //
NK029(ha)001:11685: bsgom la mi brtson bsnyen bsgrub g.yel la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:11686: tshor dang ma tshong ma rig dbang gis na //
NK029(ha)001:11687: ston pa'i bka' dang dam las 'gal gyur ste //
NK029(ha)001:11688: rnal 'byor gang zhig dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:11689: skad cig tsam yang 'phrad par mi bya zhes //
NK029(ha)001:11690: bka' las byung zhing de ltar ma lcogs te //
NK029(ha)001:11691: gsang sgo 'chol bas dbye gsal dka' ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:11692: mngon shes chung bas skyon can ma rtogs ste //
NK029(ha)001:11693: nyams dang tshogs 'dres nyams pa bkang ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:11694: nyams dang snod min rnams la chos bshad dang //
NK029(ha)001:11695: nyams la mi 'dzem nyams pa'i skyon la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:11696: nyams dang 'grogs shing nyams pa de dag gi /
NK029(ha)001:11697: nyams grib skyon gyis gos par gyur to 'tshal //
NK029(ha)001:11698: tshe 'di'i rkyen dang yun gyi sgrib gyur rnams //
NK029(ha)001:11699: rab gnong 'gyod pa'i sems kyi mthol lo bshags //
NK029(ha)001:11700: byams pa'i thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:11701: gnyis med dbyings las mi 'gyur bdag bkod de //
NK029(ha)001:11702: mi dmigs btang snyoms ngang du bzhugs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:11703: gnyis med don gyi tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:11704: don dam brjod med spros las 'das pa la //
NK029(ha)001:11705: rnam rtog gang yang dmigs par ma gyur ste //
NK029(ha)001:11706: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam gyi dbang gi na //
NK029(ha)001:11707: nongs pa mchis na rab gnong bzod par gsol //
NK029(ha)001:11708: rnal 'byor dbang phyug ye shes mthar phyin pa //'gro la phan mdzad thugs rje'i dbang gyur cing //
NK029(ha)001:11709: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gyur gcig pu pa //
NK029(ha)001:11710: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:11712: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK029(ha)001:11713: rnal 'byor mchog gi grub pa'i tshogs chen dang /
NK029(ha)001:11714: lha dang lha mi sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK029(ha)001:11715: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:11717: bdag ni rgyal srid mtho ris longs spyod dang //'dod
NK029(ha)001:11718: pa'i yon tan bdag bsgrub ma lags ste //'gro la
NK029(ha)001:11719: snying rtse kho na don brtson pa //'di la kun
NK029(ha)001:11720: mkhyen khyed nyid dpang du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:11722: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' ba //
NK029(ha)001:11723: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyis mkhyen //'phags pa'i spyan sngar bdag gi dam bcas pa //
NK029(ha)001:11724: sun par mi bgyid mgon po bslu ma lags //
NK029(ha)001:11726: deng nas bdag gi khe dang grags la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:11727: g.yo dang zang zing sems ni gtan spangs nas //
NK029(ha)001:11728: gzhan don bsgrub pa gcig pu'i sems bzhag ste //
NK029(ha)001:11729: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gi rtsom //
NK029(ha)001:11731: kun du bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:11732: byang chub mchog tu bdag gi sems bskyed de //
NK029(ha)001:11733: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK029(ha)001:11734: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su gzung bar bgyid //
NK029(ha)001:11736: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK029(ha)001:11737: dum bu stong du bdag gi lus gtubs kyang //
NK029(ha)001:11738: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK029(ha)001:11739: yi dam rgyal khyod ni yongs mi spong //
NK029(ha)001:11745: 'phags mchog thugs rje dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:11746: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:11747: mthu rtsal 'byung pa'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:11748: dgra bgegs dbyung ba'i dus la babs //
NK029(ha)001:11749: dam tshig bskang pa'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:11750: dngos grub rtsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:11752: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:11753: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:11754: dngos grub mchog rtsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)001:11755: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:11757: badz+ra mah+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11760: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shu d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra /
NK029(ha)001:11764: e man+da la h+aum s+w+aa am h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:11765: mum lam mam p+aam tam s+phar na phata /
NK029(ha)001:11769: sam ha ra ra na h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11771: m+aum d+h+aa t+ai shwa ri dzi na dzika /
NK029(ha)001:11780: badz+ra a tsan+da man+da la phata /
NK029(ha)001:11781: pam pad+ma man+da la e am /
NK029(ha)001:11784: a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK029(ha)001:11785: a nu r+aa ga y+aa ham /
NK029(ha)001:11786: dzah h+aum bam hoh h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11794: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum hri tha /
NK029(ha)001:11795: bi shwa bi shud+d+he a mri ta h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11796: d+ha rma a mri ta h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11797: h+aum badz+ra yak+sha kro ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11798: phata pad+ma b+aa lim ta bi shwa tsakra b+h+rum /
NK029(ha)001:11813: gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:11817: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+tala la h+aum kham /
NK029(ha)001:11822: a ha ra a ha ra sarba bid+ya d+ha ra p+au dzi to /
NK029(ha)001:11823: na mahs man ta bud+d+ha nan /
NK029(ha)001:11824: ga ga na sa ma ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:11839: h+aum 'dzin pa'i dbang gi sdug bsngal zhing //
NK029(ha)001:11840: gdug pa srid gsum 'dul ba yi //
NK029(ha)001:11841: nga rgyal chen po brtan pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:11843: e ma ho ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)001:11844: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //
NK029(ha)001:11845: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK029(ha)001:11846: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK029(ha)001:11849: bde chen spros med thig le las //
NK029(ha)001:11850: stong pa nyid du rab gsal ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:11851: snying rje'i yul ni bsgom par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:11858: nges pa las ni rdo rje che //
NK029(ha)001:11859: de las dpal chen he ru ka /'bar ba chen
NK029(ha)001:11860: po'i gar dgu yis //'jigs pa 'di ni dus ltar
NK029(ha)001:11861: drag / e ham ra kem ram /
NK029(ha)001:11868: de dkyil gzhal yas steng gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:11869: rlung nag dkyil 'khor rdo rje che /
NK029(ha)001:11870: rgya gram dbang chen gtams pas kyang /
NK029(ha)001:11871: thams cad 'degs pa'i shugs dang ldan /
NK029(ha)001:11874: ra rak+sha sa mu tra man+da la /
NK029(ha)001:11877: kem ni ri ti man+da la /
NK029(ha)001:11881: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:11882: khrag gi rgya mtsho 'khrugs pa'i dkyil //
NK029(ha)001:11883: keng rus chen po ri rab kyi //
NK029(ha)001:11884: steng gi 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK029(ha)001:11887: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud d+he badz+ra ban+d+h+aa dz+nya na tsakra da na di ma sur+ya man+dala /
NK029(ha)001:11893: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK029(ha)001:11894: phyogs bcu rgya yongs ma chad pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:11895: phyi dang nang med kun du nang //'bar ba'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa //
NK029(ha)001:11896: gru chad bzhi yis rnam par brgyan //
NK029(ha)001:11897: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //'bar ba'i bar 'khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK029(ha)001:11898: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi zlas brjid //'bar ba'i khroo ba mang po 'khrug /
NK029(ha)001:11899: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK029(ha)001:11900: gtum po dom gyi spar bas ni //
NK029(ha)001:11901: dbang phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK029(ha)001:11902: h+aum badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11903: badz+ra mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11904: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK029(ha)001:11905: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK029(ha)001:11906: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:11907: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas ni //
NK029(ha)001:11908: khro mo dbang phyug mngon phyung ste //
NK029(ha)001:11909: hi hi dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyi //
NK029(ha)001:11910: rin chen pad+ma rgyas mdzad des //
NK029(ha)001:11911: gnyis med 'khril bas dgyes par thim //
NK029(ha)001:11912: ma s+aur+ya man+da la h+aum badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:11913: a tsan+da la man+da la phata /
NK029(ha)001:11914: sam pad+ma man+da la e am /
NK029(ha)001:11917: a nu r+aa ga y+aa mi /
NK029(ha)001:11918: a nu r+aa ga y+aa ho /
NK029(ha)001:11919: dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11921: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la h+aum phata phata /
NK029(ha)001:11922: ha le ha le h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11923: dz+wa la ram dz+wa la ram dz+wa la ram /
NK029(ha)001:11925: badz+ra mah+aa kro d+ha shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11927: bud+d+ha mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11929: rat+na mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11931: pad+ma mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11933: karma mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11939: h+aum sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni /
NK029(ha)001:11940: 'jig rten ma lus thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)001:11941: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK029(ha)001:11942: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK029(ha)001:11943: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:11944: ye shes zer gyis lus rtogs sbyangs //
NK029(ha)001:11945: gser zhun lta bu'i sems dag la //
NK029(ha)001:11949: yam s+pha ra na phata h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11952: badz+ra g+han+da s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:11955: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11958: bsnyen pa dang ni nye ba bsnyen po /
NK029(ha)001:11959: sgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NK029(ha)001:11961: bde ba dang ni dkyil 'khor spro //
NK029(ha)001:11962: sangs rgyas sprin tshogs ma lus kun //
NK029(ha)001:11963: dgyes mnyam mchog gi sbyin bas ba stim //
NK029(ha)001:11964: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba du sh+tan /
NK029(ha)001:11965: ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11966: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata dzah +aa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11969: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK029(ha)001:11970: ma h+aa tsa n+ta sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11971: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri sarba du sh+tan h+aum phata dza /
NK029(ha)001:11972: rat+na mah+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka mah+aa tsan+ta sarba dush+tana /
NK029(ha)001:11973: ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:11974: ma h+aa s+aur+ya rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai bi da ma h+aum phata dza /
NK029(ha)001:11975: pad+ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai ri he ru ka ma h+aa
NK029(ha)001:11976: tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK029(ha)001:11978: hrihsh+ru ta sa ma te pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+hi
NK029(ha)001:11979: shwa ri kh+aa hi h+aum phata dzah karma ma h+aa
NK029(ha)001:11980: sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta
NK029(ha)001:11981: ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum
NK029(ha)001:11982: phata / sarba a mo g+ha karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri bi shwa h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:11985: badz+ra tsoo r+ai hah badz+ra pra mo he ha /
NK029(ha)001:11989: badz+ra sma sh+aa n+ai h+aah badz+ra tsana ta l+ai ha /
NK029(ha)001:11992: badz+ra bya g+h+ri mu kh+ai hi /
NK029(ha)001:11993: badz+ra sh+r+ai ga la mu kh+ai he /
NK029(ha)001:11994: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK029(ha)001:11996: badz+ra kang ka mu kh+ai he /
NK029(ha)001:11997: badz+ra kh+aa kha mu kh+ai hi /
NK029(ha)001:11998: badz+ra u lu k+aa mu kh+ai he /
NK029(ha)001:11999: phata dzah badz+ra +aad+ya te dza te nga dzah badz+ra a mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12001: badz+ra b+ha smi pa ya la ba tu ho //
NK029(ha)001:12003: +aa h+aumh b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK029(ha)001:12004: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK029(ha)001:12005: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK029(ha)001:12006: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK029(ha)001:12037: sa la sogs ste phyag rgyar byas //
NK029(ha)001:12038: rnam grol rim pa thob par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:12039: dag pa'i ye shes kyi sbyangs pas //
NK029(ha)001:12040: smos ci dgos ste de nyid yin //
NK029(ha)001:12041: sngo nag smug nag ser nag dang //
NK029(ha)001:12042: dmar nag ljang nag 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK029(ha)001:12043: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir bsgrad //
NK029(ha)001:12044: ko rlon gos ni sna tshogs gyon //
NK029(ha)001:12045: rngam pa'i sgra chen 'jigs par sgrogs //
NK029(ha)001:12046: sprul dang thod rlon nyi zla'i chas //
NK029(ha)001:12048: rdo rje dung chen gang pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:12049: ral gri sgra sta bshol la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:12050: rang rang lag cha tshogs 'dzin pa //
NK029(ha)001:12052: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dang //
NK029(ha)001:12053: sgo bzhi'i phyag rgya rab mdzes shing //
NK029(ha)001:12054: slas dang byi mo bran mo tshogs kyi gtso //
NK029(ha)001:12055: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad kyis mdzes //
NK029(ha)001:12056: rang gi bstan dang lag char bcas //
NK029(ha)001:12057: ci bgyi zhes ni chas te gnas //
NK029(ha)001:12058: de ltar dkyil 'khor gsal bkod nas //
NK029(ha)001:12059: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yis //'jig rten drug
NK029(ha)001:12060: gi phyogs bcu na //'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar
NK029(ha)001:12061: gnang // h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:12063: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:12064: ma h+aa +aa dar sha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:12065: ma h+aa sa man+ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:12066: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:12067: ma h+aa krir+ya a nush+tha na dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:12073: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:12074: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:12075: h+aum phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK029(ha)001:12076: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK029(ha)001:12077: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK029(ha)001:12078: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK029(ha)001:12079: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:12080: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK029(ha)001:12081: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK029(ha)001:12082: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12083: e h+ya hi +aa na ya ho /
NK029(ha)001:12086: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12087: khro la khro bas zhi mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:12088: thugs rje khros dpal rngam pa'i tshogs //'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK029(ha)001:12089: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK029(ha)001:12090: badz+ra kro d+ha sa m+aa ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)001:12091: badz+ra kro d+ha sa m+aa ya phata /
NK029(ha)001:12092: kro d+ha sa m+aa ya ho /
NK029(ha)001:12094: ta li ta p+aa li dam sh+ta go na roo tri /
NK029(ha)001:12095: kha ram yo gi n+ai kh+aa hi ho /
NK029(ha)001:12096: kha ram yo gi n+ai kh+aa hi ho /
NK029(ha)001:12097: h+aum h+aa he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK029(ha)001:12098: sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:12099: sarba dush+tana sa ma ya mu tra m+aa ram pra b+hany+dza h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12100: ka ya wa k+ka tsit+ta dish+tha badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:12101: sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa sarba d+hush+tana /
NK029(ha)001:12103: a pra stam+b+ha ya ka h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12104: badz+ra guh+ya t+yi sh+ya ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)001:12105: badz+ra gu h+ya trish+ya sa ma ya phata /
NK029(ha)001:12107: sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba d+hu sh+ta /
NK029(ha)001:12109: mu tra m+aa ram pra b+hany+dza /
NK029(ha)001:12114: bud+d+ha k+she tri pra ti stam+b+ha ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12115: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing /
NK029(ha)001:12116: byams dang snying rjes dgra zun mi mnga' yang //
NK029(ha)001:12117: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //'jigs byed he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12118: srid gsum 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12119: mnyam nyid ngang gi khro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12120: khros pas longs spyod mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12121: rdo rje 'du 'phro mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12122: mi gnas mi dmigs chos skur dag pa la //
NK029(ha)001:12123: bdud 'dul khro ba'i mchog gi skur ston pa //
NK029(ha)001:12124: thugs rje gzi ldan gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul //
NK029(ha)001:12125: bcom ldan khro rgyal gtso la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12126: khro mo dbang phyug sku la gnyer gnas shing //
NK029(ha)001:12127: thabs dang shes rab 'brel pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK029(ha)001:12128: mkha' 'gro mi zad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro ma //
NK029(ha)001:12129: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12130: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK029(ha)001:12131: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:12132: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12135: bde bar gshegs pa khyod ci 'dra //
NK029(ha)001:12136: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:12137: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //'gro la phan phyir bdag gi spyod //
NK029(ha)001:12138: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:12139: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK029(ha)001:12140: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ngo //
NK029(ha)001:12141: rdo rje rgyal pos byin brlabs mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12143: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrubs //
NK029(ha)001:12144: byang chub spyad dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK029(ha)001:12146: bdag cag bsam pa grub gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:12148: he ru ka yi kalpo dang /
NK029(ha)001:12149: gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud dag las /
NK029(ha)001:12150: rnam par grol ba mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:12151: dbus kyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK029(ha)001:12152: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK029(ha)001:12153: rtse dgu rtse lnga ti ra g.yas //
NK029(ha)001:12154: dril bu dung dmar 'jig rten g.yon //
NK029(ha)001:12155: dpal chen rdo rje thabs kyi rgya //
NK029(ha)001:12156: shes rab yum gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK029(ha)001:12157: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog mthing //
NK029(ha)001:12158: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la rten //
NK029(ha)001:12159: g.yon pas dung dmar gtso la stobs //
NK029(ha)001:12160: kro d+hi shwa ri dbyings kyi rgya //'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12161: mchod bzhes dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:12162: shar gyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni /
NK029(ha)001:12163: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus smug zhal //'khor lo rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK029(ha)001:12164: dril bu dung dmar tri shul g.yon //
NK029(ha)001:12165: dpal chen bud+d+ha thabs kyi rgya //
NK029(ha)001:12166: shes rab yum gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK029(ha)001:12167: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog smug /
NK029(ha)001:12168: g.yas pas shes rab thabs la rten //
NK029(ha)001:12169: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stobs //
NK029(ha)001:12170: kro d+d+hi shwa ri dbyings kyi rgya //'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12171: mchod bzhes dam bskong mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:12172: lho yi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK029(ha)001:12173: g.yas sngo g.yon dkar dbus ser zhal //
NK029(ha)001:12174: rin chen rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK029(ha)001:12175: dril bu dung dmar dgra sta g.yon //
NK029(ha)001:12176: dpal chen rat+na thabs kyi rgya //
NK029(ha)001:12177: shes rab yum gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK029(ha)001:12178: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog ser //
NK029(ha)001:12179: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la rten //
NK029(ha)001:12180: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stobs //
NK029(ha)001:12181: kro sti shwa ri dbyings kyi rgya //'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12182: mchod bzhes dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:12183: nub kyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni /
NK029(ha)001:12184: g.yas dkar g.yon ser dbus dmar zhal //
NK029(ha)001:12185: pad+ma rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK029(ha)001:12186: dril bu dung dmar rnga chung g.yon //
NK029(ha)001:12187: dpal chen pad+ma thabs kyi rgya //
NK029(ha)001:12188: shes rab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK029(ha)001:12189: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog dmar //
NK029(ha)001:12190: g.yas pas shes rab thabs la rten //
NK029(ha)001:12191: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stobs //
NK029(ha)001:12192: kro ti shwa ri dbyings kyi rgya //'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang /
NK029(ha)001:12193: mchod bzhes dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsool /
NK029(ha)001:12194: byang gi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni /
NK029(ha)001:12195: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dkyil ljang zhal //
NK029(ha)001:12196: rgya gram rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK029(ha)001:12197: dril bu dung dmar mthong bshol g.yon //
NK029(ha)001:12198: dpal chen karma thabs kyi rgya //
NK029(ha)001:12199: shes rab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK029(ha)001:12200: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog ljang //
NK029(ha)001:12201: g.yas pas shes rab thabs la rten //
NK029(ha)001:12202: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stobs //
NK029(ha)001:12203: kro d+hi shwa ri dbyings kyi rgya //'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12204: mchod bzhengs dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12205: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK029(ha)001:12206: koo ri b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK029(ha)001:12208: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan dmar /
NK029(ha)001:12212: sme sha mthing nag byis snying za /
NK029(ha)001:12214: 'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang /
NK029(ha)001:12215: mchod bzhengs dam bskong mthu dang dngos grub stsol /
NK029(ha)001:12216: sid+ha kha ro snol ser seng /
NK029(ha)001:12217: bya g+h+ri gnas ltag snol mar stag /
NK029(ha)001:12218: sri la nag po byis ldag wa /
NK029(ha)001:12219: shwa na 'dral lta mthing kha sbyang //
NK029(ha)001:12221: kang ka zhing phrag snar mgo ring //
NK029(ha)001:12222: kha kha kha ro ban gri nag /
NK029(ha)001:12223: hu lu lcags kyu mthing tshogs 'ug /'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12224: mchod bzhes dam bskong dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12225: rta gdong sngon po lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:12226: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK029(ha)001:12227: seng gdong lcags sgrog me 'bar ma //
NK029(ha)001:12228: spyang gdong dril bu sna tshogs mdog /'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12229: mchod bzhes dam bskongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //'jig rten 'das dang 'jig rten pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:12230: ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:12231: ma mo rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK029(ha)001:12232: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK029(ha)001:12233: tshangs pa dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:12234: lha chen dkar ljang tri shul 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:12236: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK029(ha)001:12237: brgya byin dkar mo in+da gdengs //
NK029(ha)001:12238: rdo rje ser mo tsan dan 'thung //
NK029(ha)001:12239: bdud rtsi dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK029(ha)001:12240: zla ba dkar mo pun+da ri //
NK029(ha)001:12241: be con ljang nag dbyug to 'phyar //
NK029(ha)001:12242: srin mo dmar mo dung khrag mthung //
NK029(ha)001:12243: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK029(ha)001:12244: dga' ba dmar mo ka tar 'phyar //
NK029(ha)001:12245: stobs chen dkar mo bshol 'dzin ma //
NK029(ha)001:12246: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod //'dod pa dmar mo'i mda' gzhu 'gengs //
NK029(ha)001:12247: nor bsrungs dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:12248: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan 'phyar //
NK029(ha)001:12249: gsod byed dmar mo ral gri 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:12250: me mo dmar mo gsal shing 'chang //
NK029(ha)001:12251: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK029(ha)001:12252: rgan byed dmar mo zhing chung za //
NK029(ha)001:12253: sna chen dkar mo thod khrag 'thung //
NK029(ha)001:12254: chu lha sngon mo sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:12255: rdo rje nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK029(ha)001:12256: rdo rje ser mo ra mgo zhags //
NK029(ha)001:12257: rdo rje dmar mo lcags sgrogs sdom //
NK029(ha)001:12258: rdo rje ljang nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK029(ha)001:12260: 'bar ba'i gdan las bzhes nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12261: mchod bzhes dam bskongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:12262: bde bar gshegs so khro rgyal gtso //
NK029(ha)001:12263: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyi /
NK029(ha)001:12264: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK029(ha)001:12265: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol /
NK029(ha)001:12266: sh+r+ai sa man+ta b+ha tra sarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo /
NK029(ha)001:12268: sarba tat+kham ud ga te s+pha ra na i mam ga ga na kham swah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:12269: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //'gro ba rnams kyi don slad du //
NK029(ha)001:12270: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12271: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12273: +aa ha ra sarba bid+ya d+ha ra p+au dzi te /
NK029(ha)001:12274: na ma sa man+ta bud+d+ha n+aam ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK029(ha)001:12275: pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK029(ha)001:12276: ti pu pa ra mu sarba ta tha ga ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12278: sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12279: sh+ri badz+ra r+aa ga d+hu pe d+hu /
NK029(ha)001:12280: pa na pem pe nu su ra to //
NK029(ha)001:12282: sarba ta th+aa ga ta si d+d+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12284: sarba mah+aa su kha sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12285: sh+r+aii badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK029(ha)001:12286: pa na pem pe nu su ra to //
NK029(ha)001:12287: ti pu pa ra mu sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12288: sa ma yo ta mu sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12289: sh+ri badz+ra ra ga +aa lo ke hrih pa na
NK029(ha)001:12290: pem pe nu su ra to ti pu pa ra
NK029(ha)001:12291: mu / sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12292: sa ma yo ta mu sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12293: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ga gan+d+he gan /
NK029(ha)001:12295: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12296: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa 'grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12298: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12299: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa 'grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12301: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12302: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po dag par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12304: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12305: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po dag par mdzad du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12306: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)001:12307: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK029(ha)001:12308: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK029(ha)001:12309: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK029(ha)001:12310: rgyud drug sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:12311: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK029(ha)001:12312: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK029(ha)001:12313: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen gyi //
NK029(ha)001:12314: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig go /
NK029(ha)001:12315: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK029(ha)001:12316: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskangs ba'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:12317: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK029(ha)001:12318: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyi //
NK029(ha)001:12319: thugs rje dgongs nas bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12320: bzhes nas kun tu dgyes mdzod la //'phrul gyi dngos grub bstsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12321: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa argam pra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:12322: sh+ri b+aa na kha ram kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:12323: h+aum tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /'bar ba'i rgyal po khro rgyal yab lnga la //
NK029(ha)001:12324: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12325: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub bstsol //
NK029(ha)001:12326: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa argam
NK029(ha)001:12327: pra tits+tsha ho sh+ri b+aa na kha ram kh+aa hi
NK029(ha)001:12328: / dpal chen sku la gnyis med lhun sbyor ba'i /
NK029(ha)001:12329: kro d+hi shwa ri yum chen lnga rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:12330: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12331: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:12332: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa argam
NK029(ha)001:12333: pra tits+tsha ho sh+ri b+aa na kha ram kh+aa hi
NK029(ha)001:12334: / mthing kha mchog rnams rdo rje gsang ba'i yum //
NK029(ha)001:12335: koo ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:12336: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12337: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:12338: na mas sarba ta th+aa ga ta argampra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:12339: sh+ri b+aa na kha ram kh+aa h+ai /
NK029(ha)001:12340: rdo rje mgo brnyan za byed mche gshog can //
NK029(ha)001:12341: seng ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:12342: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12343: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12344: na mas sarba ta th+aa ga ta argampra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:12345: sh+r+ai b+aa na kha ram kh+aa h+ai /
NK029(ha)001:12346: sgo bzhi rab rngam rdo rje gdong mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:12347: rta gdong la sogs sgo ma bzhi rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:12348: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12349: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12350: na mas sarba ta th+aa ga ta argam pra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:12351: sh+ri b+aa na kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12352: dpal chen 'khor tshogs badz+ra a ra li //
NK029(ha)001:12353: mkha' la shugs 'gro ma sring rgya mtsho la //
NK029(ha)001:12354: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12355: thugs rje brtse dgongs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12356: na mas sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa argam pra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:12357: sh+ri b+aa na kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12358: bskal ba me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK029(ha)001:12359: bdud 'dul khro bo chen po bcu rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:12360: rnams dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12361: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12362: na mas sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa argam pra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:12363: sh+ri b+aa na kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12364: ci bgyi bka' nyan ging dang pho nya'i tshogs //'bar ma la sogs pho nya'i tshogs rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:12365: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12366: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12367: sdom la gnas shing rig 'dzin grub pa'i sa //
NK029(ha)001:12368: lha dang lha min phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor la //
NK029(ha)001:12369: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12370: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12371: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12372: dam tshig dbang dang shes rgyud gab sbas pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:12373: nges pa'i lung ston rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK029(ha)001:12374: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12375: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12376: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12377: shes pa'i khyad par rim par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:12378: rgyal theb can dang karma ging rnams la //
NK029(ha)001:12379: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12380: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)001:12381: mah+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12382: tshe rabs sngon nas smon lam 'phro 'thud pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:12383: rgyal ba'i gdung 'a tshob mched dang lcam dral la //
NK029(ha)001:12384: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12385: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12386: mah+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12387: yun rings dus nas bsnyen zhing bsgrubs pa'i lha //
NK029(ha)001:12388: dam can rgya mtsho chos skyong bsrungs ma la //
NK029(ha)001:12389: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12390: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12391: mah+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:12392: 'jig rten 'di dang snga phyi gnyis ka ru //
NK029(ha)001:12393: lus srog bskyed pa'i dus gsum pha ma la //
NK029(ha)001:12394: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12395: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12396: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:12398: lce'i rdo rje dam tshig la //
NK029(ha)001:12399: rdo rje can gyi h'u bsgoms nas //
NK029(ha)001:12400: bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba'i sman //
NK029(ha)001:12401: zos nas dngos grub gsum thob 'gyur //
NK029(ha)001:12405: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)001:12409: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa wa ka badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko hmo /
NK029(ha)001:12413: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swab+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:12414: ka ya wa ga tsit+ta sid+hi tish+tha badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:12416: sh+r+ai he ru ka mah+aa badz+ra i dam d+hu pe /
NK029(ha)001:12420: b+ha lim ta pra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:12421: sh+r+ai b+aa na kha kha kh+aa hi kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:12422: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam par sbyar ba 'di //
NK029(ha)001:12423: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer rnam par 'phro //'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yi rab brgyan ste //
NK029(ha)001:12424: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12425: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12426: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK029(ha)001:12427: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK029(ha)001:12428: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK029(ha)001:12429: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:12431: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:12432: pad+ma la ni rdo rje zhugs //'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK029(ha)001:12433: bdag nyid mnyes sam mnyes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:12436: a nu ra ga ya mi /
NK029(ha)001:12437: a nu ra ga y+aa ham /
NK029(ha)001:12440: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:12442: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)001:12443: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /
NK029(ha)001:12444: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12445: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo /
NK029(ha)001:12446: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK029(ha)001:12448: chos nyid la yang chos nyid rol //
NK029(ha)001:12450: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:12454: sh+ri b+aa na kha kh+aa kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12455: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK029(ha)001:12456: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK029(ha)001:12457: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs pas //
NK029(ha)001:12458: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK029(ha)001:12459: zhing chen gsar snying ti rar bcas //
NK029(ha)001:12462: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12464: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa sarba dush+tana sa ma
NK029(ha)001:12465: ya mu tra m+aa ram kha kh+aa kha hi kh+aa
NK029(ha)001:12466: hi / hri da ya b+ai sa h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12467: nga ni za byed chen po te //
NK029(ha)001:12468: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //'dul dka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:12469: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:12471: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK029(ha)001:12476: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK029(ha)001:12477: ma h+aa argam pra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:12483: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:12484: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par byed pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:12485: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pas //
NK029(ha)001:12486: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yis //
NK029(ha)001:12487: gar byas grub po rnal 'byor pa //
NK029(ha)001:12488: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK029(ha)001:12489: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK029(ha)001:12490: mam sa la sogs bro mchog gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12491: me tog la sogs tsan dan dri //
NK029(ha)001:12492: bzang dgu 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12493: mi mo rnams ni reg bya'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:12494: byin gyis barlobasa shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK029(ha)001:12495: grub pa'i rdzas 'di ni thams cad la //
NK029(ha)001:12496: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12497: gzigs pa rnam pa sna tshogs 'gyur pa med pa'i rgyas thob la //
NK029(ha)001:12498: rnam pa sna tshogs 'o byed 'khyud pas rmongs mdzad de //
NK029(ha)001:12499: rnam pa sna tshogs bde mchog ston kun gson mdzad la //
NK029(ha)001:12500: rnam pa sna tshogs bde mchog ngo mtshar bstan du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12501: rgyas btab rmongs byed bsnams su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12502: bde mchog ngo mtshar bde la bzhugs /
NK029(ha)001:12503: h+aum a la la ho gnang bar mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12504: rnal 'byor bde mchog sgyu mas sprul //
NK029(ha)001:12505: dam tshig bdag la 'jug tu gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12506: nyon mongs kun las rgyal bar mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12507: ma lus pa dag bsnams su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12508: nyon mongs thams cad bsal bar mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12509: hi hi dbang phyug sku gsung thugs kyi rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams //
NK029(ha)001:12510: e ha hi e ha hi tshur byon 'khor dang bcas /
NK029(ha)001:12512: spyan 'dren ma lus gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:12513: ka la ki la ha ha dga' ba'i gzhad mos khong /
NK029(ha)001:12514: bde drongs bde spyod a ho su kha sham+ba ya /
NK029(ha)001:12516: slob ma chug gcig gnang bar mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:12517: rol shig dgongs shig 'dod pa'i bdag nyid tish+tha kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12519: ha ra har ra zo cig ngo mtshar mchog tu stobs po kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:12520: bdud rtsi la sogs dmar chen snying po lnga /
NK029(ha)001:12521: mam sa la sogs tshe 'phel dpa' bo mchog /
NK029(ha)001:12522: madz+dza me dza rak+ta ru k+ti ti ma tam /
NK029(ha)001:12523: nye bar sgrub pa'i snying po ma lus grub pa rnams //
NK029(ha)001:12524: dri med gzi ldan mchog gi mchod pa dam par sbyar ba 'di //
NK029(ha)001:12525: ye shes rgya mtsho thams cad dgyes shing rol du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12526: myos byed stong pas lhag par bde bar 'dod pa'i
NK029(ha)001:12527: gzugs ston pa //'dul ba'i dbang gis gshin rje stong
NK029(ha)001:12529: zhi ba'i sku yang tshangs pa stong pas shin tu lhag par ston //
NK029(ha)001:12530: dkyil 'khor kun gyi mchog tu de bzhin gshegs kun grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12531: thams cad dag par mos pas ngo mthon stobs kyis rnam par gnon /
NK029(ha)001:12532: dgra bgegs thams cad hi hi he he dbang phyug thams cad shig shig rab tu shig /
NK029(ha)001:12533: rab gyi rtsal gyis gnon pa'i stobs kyi ngo mthon dbang phyug gnon //
NK029(ha)001:12534: sbyor chen hu lu hu lu dmig gsum po las gsum du drongs //
NK029(ha)001:12535: rab kyi rtsal gyis gnon pa'i stobs kyi ngo mthon mthu chen gnon //
NK029(ha)001:12536: mnyam sbyor ru tra'i snying nas dpal mos drongs cig rab drongs cig //
NK029(ha)001:12537: rab kyi rtsal gyis gnon pa'i stobs kyi ngo mthon 'chang sa gnon //
NK029(ha)001:12538: sbyor chen tshangs las sgrol mas drongs shig sma ra tha //
NK029(ha)001:12539: rab kyi rtsal gyi gnon pa'i stobs kyi ngo mthon dga' dbang gnon //
NK029(ha)001:12540: rnal 'byor kun gyi bdag la dga' drongs gcig //
NK029(ha)001:12542: gdug cing khro la gtum pa'i sems can bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:12543: sgrub bzhugs a la la ho /
NK029(ha)001:12544: sum+b+ha ni sum+b+ha h+aum h+aum phata phata /
NK029(ha)001:12545: 'dza' bo mi la bya'am mi bya ba //
NK029(ha)001:12546: yongs su rtogs pa de dag med kyang sla //
NK029(ha)001:12547: de 'dra'i 'dza' bo sgyu ma yin pas na //
NK029(ha)001:12548: de la 'dza' zhes su zhig zer //
NK029(ha)001:12549: sgo ba gang la bya 'am mi bya ba //
NK029(ha)001:12550: yongs su rtogs pa de dag med kyang sla //
NK029(ha)001:12551: de 'dra'i sgo ba sgyu ma yin pas na //
NK029(ha)001:12552: de la dpa' zhes su zhig zer //
NK029(ha)001:12556: ku ti ra kah ko l+aa khya /
NK029(ha)001:12560: rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK029(ha)001:12561: ston ka'i zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba'i //
NK029(ha)001:12562: bcom ldan bde gshegs rdo rje dkyil 'khor dbyings //
NK029(ha)001:12563: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK029(ha)001:12564: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
NK029(ha)001:12565: phyag brnyan gtum chen rngam pa'i tshogs la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:12566: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi rab rdzogs te //
NK029(ha)001:12567: dgyes par rol ba'i dus kyi mchod pa dam par sbyar ba 'di //
NK029(ha)001:12568: bzhes ste a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12572: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12575: ho spros pa med pa'i dbyings /
NK029(ha)001:12576: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa na /
NK029(ha)001:12577: dus gsum du gshegs zhing bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom
NK029(ha)001:12578: ldan 'das rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK029(ha)001:12579: kyi bye brag dang ldan pa bcom ldan 'das rdo
NK029(ha)001:12580: rje ye shes pa la sogs te /
NK029(ha)001:12581: rigs lnga'i bde bar gshegs pa rigs mchog bzungs kyi dbyings na rnam par bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:12582: 'khor phun sum 'tshogs pa dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:12584: thun mong ma yin pa'i spyod pas rnam par 'phro shing ye shes chen po'i rol ba /
NK029(ha)001:12585: rmad du byung ba'i drag shul /
NK029(ha)001:12586: bla na med pa'i thabs rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang ldan pa'i rgyal po /
NK029(ha)001:12587: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK029(ha)001:12589: yum kro d+hi shwa ri dang gnyis su med pa rol pa'i byin brlabs las byung ba /
NK029(ha)001:12591: dpal chen po yab yum dang /
NK029(ha)001:12593: sing ha'i 'khor nang gi rnal 'byor ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:12594: phyi'i grub pa mo ye shes dang las la skyes pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:12595: 'khor bsam gyi mi khyab pa thams cad mkhyen pa
NK029(ha)001:12596: dang byin gyis brlab pa dam pa mdzad du gsol
NK029(ha)001:12597: / gzhan yang rnal 'byor pho dang rnal 'byor mo /
NK029(ha)001:12598: pho nya pho dang pho nya mo /
NK029(ha)001:12599: ci bgyi bka' nyan thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)001:12600: phyogs bcu dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK029(ha)001:12601: mched lcam bral dgongs pa rnal 'byor gyi don gcig rtse gcig tu dgongs shing /
NK029(ha)001:12602: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i don la bka' gzhung
NK029(ha)001:12603: bzhin du mdzad pas thams cad mkhyen pa dang byin
NK029(ha)001:12604: gyis brlabs pa dam pa mdzad du gsol lo //
NK029(ha)001:12605: gzhan yang rnal 'byor gyi mchod yon dam pa phud kyi khyad par gyi mchog 'di las /
NK029(ha)001:12607: 'byung ba chen po kun rdzo ba sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid tsam bsdus nas /
NK029(ha)001:12608: deng sprul pa las sprul pa rol cing /
NK029(ha)001:12609: rnal 'byor gsang ba mchog gi mchod pa dam pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i tshul du sbyar ba 'di /
NK029(ha)001:12610: bdag nyid chen po 'khor dang bcas pa khyed rnams la /
NK029(ha)001:12611: dbang mi 'tshal ba'i slad du phud dang gtsang mar sbag te /
NK029(ha)001:12612: dga' 'gu gus pa'i sems kyis mchod pa'i lha mo ltar /
NK029(ha)001:12614: ye shes kyi spyi gtsug la blangs ste /
NK029(ha)001:12615: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rin po che'i gzhal yas khang /
NK029(ha)001:12616: chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' klas pa /
NK029(ha)001:12617: phyur bur bskang nas 'bul zhing mchis na /
NK029(ha)001:12618: thugs rje chen po'i dbang gi gnyis su med pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:12619: bde ba chen pos dgyes pa dang lhun grub tu dgongs ste /
NK029(ha)001:12620: ye shes chu zla lta bur sgyu ma la sgyu mar rol cing /
NK029(ha)001:12621: sku gsung thugs kyi longs spyod mi zad pa'i gter chen po bzhes su gsol lo //
NK029(ha)001:12622: mthol gshags bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:12623: deng bdag cag rnams kyi dang po gsang ba'i rdo rje theg pa'i sgor khas 'che ste /
NK029(ha)001:12624: dam tshig gnyan po mngon par nos pa las rtsa
NK029(ha)001:12625: ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig las nyams chags
NK029(ha)001:12627: lha nye bar ma bsgoms pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:12628: snying po dag par ma bsgrangs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:12629: sbyor sgrol mang po'i bar bkum pa /
NK029(ha)001:12630: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcags pa /
NK029(ha)001:12631: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:12633: dam rdzas dang du len rngo ma thogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:12636: ting nge 'dzin thang lhod du gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:12637: le lo dang snyom las kyi dbang du gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:12638: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod klong du ma gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:12639: sems can gyi shes pa rang thad du gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:12640: snga slad du dam tshig nyams chags su gyur pa
NK029(ha)001:12641: ci mchis pa thams cad dus 'dir shin du gnong
NK029(ha)001:12642: zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis bsam pa thag pas mthol
NK029(ha)001:12644: dbyings nyid mkha' dang 'dra ba'i ngang gi sku /
NK029(ha)001:12645: bzod pa chen po dang du bzhes nas tshangs pa dam pa'i mchog yid bzhin du stsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:12647: shes bya thabs cad la thog pa med pa'i shes rab mi brjed pa'i gzungs /
NK029(ha)001:12652: dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub gyi
NK029(ha)001:12653: bla ma man chad nas dngos kyi skal ba dang
NK029(ha)001:12654: / rgyu gang lags pa dus phyi ma la bsdad
NK029(ha)001:12655: mi 'tshal bar dus 'di nyid du thob par mdzad
NK029(ha)001:12656: du gsol lo //'phrin las dang snyan du gsol ba
NK029(ha)001:12657: / ni / bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa la sdang bar sems pa'i dgra /
NK029(ha)001:12660: rno ba'i mtshon sbyar ba'i dug /
NK029(ha)001:12664: so so'i rmi lam ngan pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:12666: mi shis pa'i rkyen de dag thams cad phyir bzlog cing ming yang mi grags cing /
NK029(ha)001:12667: zhi ba chen po mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:12668: gal te zhi bas mi 'dul zhing mchis na'ang /
NK029(ha)001:12669: drag po'i 'phrin las kyis dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:12671: gzir cing mnan pa la sogs te /
NK029(ha)001:12672: 'phrin las drag thal rnam pa bzhis /
NK029(ha)001:12673: ji ltar 'dul zhing 'tshams pa bzhin du mdzad nas
NK029(ha)001:12674: ming yang mi grags zhing zhi ba chen por mdzad
NK029(ha)001:12675: du gsol lo // bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du bzhugs pa rnams /
NK029(ha)001:12676: bcad gtu bas sdug bsngal lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur zhing /
NK029(ha)001:12677: grib mas phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod pas /
NK029(ha)001:12678: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong ba'i mod la 'tsho ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:12679: gzi byin lus la 'jug pa'i nyi ma stong phrag
NK029(ha)001:12680: gi /'od bzhin 'jigs rten khams 'dir rtag tu 'char
NK029(ha)001:12681: ba dang / lus ngag sems dang tshe ni rdo rje rab snang ste /
NK029(ha)001:12682: re smon thams cad dus 'dir thob par stsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:12683: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud d+he phata dzah zhes rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gong ltar gsal gdab /
NK029(ha)001:12687: h+aum yun ring dus nas bsnyen cing bsgrub pa'i lha //
NK029(ha)001:12688: bcom ldan dpal chen badz+ra he ru ka /'khor gyi gsang bdag yum chen mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)001:12689: dam tshig dngos grub gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK029(ha)001:12690: da lta nyid du mngon gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:12691: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12693: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar /
NK029(ha)001:12695: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin /
NK029(ha)001:12696: mche ba zangs yag za byed che ho /
NK029(ha)001:12697: h+aum h+aum rngam pa'i nga ros 'brug stong ldir /
NK029(ha)001:12698: gtum chen ri rab 'bum snyil skad /
NK029(ha)001:12699: a la la'i gad brgyang che //
NK029(ha)001:12700: skyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yengs pa che hoh h+aum khro bo shes rab 'od po che /
NK029(ha)001:12701: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal /
NK029(ha)001:12703: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che hoh h'u khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po /
NK029(ha)001:12706: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che ho /
NK029(ha)001:12708: bdud kun gyis ni bdud chen po /
NK029(ha)001:12709: bdud kyi bdud de bdud rnams 'joms /
NK029(ha)001:12711: 'jigs byed chen po'i thig le che /
NK029(ha)001:12712: hoh h+aum rdo rje brag chen sra ba po /
NK029(ha)001:12713: rdo rje chu ste sdud chen po /
NK029(ha)001:12714: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che /
NK029(ha)001:12715: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che hoh h+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he a mri te h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12716: d+harma a mri te h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12717: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12719: ram yam kham pad+ma b+aa ling ta b+ai shwa tsakra h+aum b+h+rum /
NK029(ha)001:12720: ma sur+y+aa man+ta la h+aum sma ra na phata /
NK029(ha)001:12725: b+ha lim ta te dz+wa ba lim ta ba la ba ti gu h+ya sa ma ye swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)001:12726: h+aum dbang phyug chen po yab yum dang /
NK029(ha)001:12727: byang chub rdo rje lcam dral dang /
NK029(ha)001:12728: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang /
NK029(ha)001:12729: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:12730: lha dang lha min rnal 'byor pa /
NK029(ha)001:12732: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol /
NK029(ha)001:12733: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:12735: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK029(ha)001:12749: ma h+aa badz+ra sarba du sh+tan /
NK029(ha)001:12750: sa ma ya mu tra pra b+hany+tsa h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12751: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam par sbyar pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:12752: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phros //'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan ste //
NK029(ha)001:12753: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12754: tshogs mchod dam pa rgya cher 'degs pa 'di //
NK029(ha)001:12755: mchod sprin sna tshogs nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //'dod yon lha mo sgeg mo bsam yas pa //
NK029(ha)001:12756: zhing khams khyab pa'i mchod pa sprin phung 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12758: su ra ta u pa b+h+yahka ma l+aa badz+ra a
NK029(ha)001:12759: mri ta ha ra na pra ti tits+tsha b+ha ga
NK029(ha)001:12762: pa na pem pe nu su ra to /
NK029(ha)001:12764: sarba ta tha ga ta si d+d+hi sa ma yo ta mu sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:12765: de nas tshogs gsum du spros la /
NK029(ha)001:12766: h+aum sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:12767: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par byed pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:12768: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pa //
NK029(ha)001:12769: sku yis dngos po shin+tu bsgyur ba yi //
NK029(ha)001:12770: gar byas grub pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK029(ha)001:12771: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK029(ha)001:12772: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK029(ha)001:12773: mam sa la sogs bro mchog gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12774: me tog la sogs tsan dan dri //
NK029(ha)001:12775: dri bzang 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:12776: mi mo la sogs reg bya'i mchog /
NK029(ha)001:12777: byin gyis brlabs shig rnal 'byor pa //
NK029(ha)001:12778: grub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
NK029(ha)001:12779: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12780: dzahh+aum bam hohsh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra i dam /
NK029(ha)001:12785: ba lim ta pra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:12786: sh+r+ai b+aa na kha kha kh+aa hi kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:12788: h+aum tshe rabs thog ma med pa tshun chad nas /
NK029(ha)001:12789: skye ba 'di la thug pa yan chod du /
NK029(ha)001:12790: lus kyi sdig pa sdig byas ngan du spyad /
NK029(ha)001:12791: ngag gi tshig 'khyal smra ba ngan du brjod /
NK029(ha)001:12792: sems kyi blo nor log pa bsam la sogs /
NK029(ha)001:12793: 'dod khro gti mug dbang gis nongs bgyis rnams /
NK029(ha)001:12794: bkram pa'i lha tshogs khyed la gzod par gsol /
NK029(ha)001:12795: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang /
NK029(ha)001:12796: de'i 'khor du rtog pa'i lha srin rnams /
NK029(ha)001:12797: mi yi skyon mthong tsam la chad pas gcod /
NK029(ha)001:12798: nongs bgyis 'gal 'khrul mchis na mthol zhing gshags /
NK029(ha)001:12799: mthol gshags bzhes nas tshangs pa stsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:12802: ro d+ha ram ni dzi mu ta ni ba no /
NK029(ha)001:12803: kha tam ga gar b+h+yo dza la da na /
NK029(ha)001:12804: la na s+aut+ti ba sti ka /
NK029(ha)001:12806: a pa na pad+ma tsan dan /
NK029(ha)001:12808: da re dza pa sa stam /
NK029(ha)001:12812: tig nan damsh+ta ka ra la /
NK029(ha)001:12813: tha ma thod par bsdus ste /
NK029(ha)001:12817: sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12818: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK029(ha)001:12819: phata ba h+aum bi d+ha ro hu ti /
NK029(ha)001:12829: badz+ra sam ba le tsa le tsa le h+aum b+h+yo /
NK029(ha)001:12830: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo /
NK029(ha)001:12832: na mo dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12833: dkon mchog gsum gyis bka' bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:12834: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK029(ha)001:12835: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po 'khor dang bcas pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:12836: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)001:12837: bdag cag kyi dgra bgegs che ge mo 'di /
NK029(ha)001:12838: thang cig yud tsam la dbang du khugs par gyur
NK029(ha)001:12839: cig /'di'i rgyab rten dang dpung gnyen du byed pa'i
NK029(ha)001:12840: pho lha dang yul lha dang /
NK029(ha)001:12842: ban bon gyi bsrungs ma byed pa'i lha rnams nyon cig /
NK029(ha)001:12843: che ge mo 'di las ngan pa byed pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:12844: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' la bsdo ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:12847: dam las log pa zhes pa de lta bu byas pas /
NK029(ha)001:12848: 'di yi rgyab rten dang dpung gnyen ma byed par yal bar thongs shig /
NK029(ha)001:12849: gal te rgyab brten dang dpung gnyen byed pa na /
NK029(ha)001:12850: khyod nyid kyang gnas dang bcas ste bkug ta re /
NK029(ha)001:12851: khyed nyid kyang las ngan pa 'di'i sdong grogs byed na /
NK029(ha)001:12852: mnar med pa'i sems can dmyal bar lhung ba ste /
NK029(ha)001:12853: de lta bu'i don chung ngu la nyen chen po la ma bsdo bar thongs shig /
NK029(ha)001:12854: gzhan yang yul phyogs 'di'i sa bdag lha klu nyon cig /
NK029(ha)001:12855: khyed la phur ba'i rtse mo mi bton /
NK029(ha)001:12856: nyug dkar gyi rbab mi sgril /
NK029(ha)001:12857: drag po las kyi pho nya mi 'gyed /
NK029(ha)001:12858: gnod pa'i sbyor ba gang yang mi byed pas /
NK029(ha)001:12859: ma 'jigs ma skrag par rang rang gi gnas su 'dug la /
NK029(ha)001:12860: nged kyi rgyab dang dpung gnyen gyis la /
NK029(ha)001:12861: dgra bgegs 'di dbang du bsdus shig h+aum bzlas /
NK029(ha)001:12862: e yig tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /'bar ba gtum chen rngam pa la //
NK029(ha)001:12863: khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK029(ha)001:12864: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK029(ha)001:12865: bdud rtsi lnga 'am zas lnga la //
NK029(ha)001:12866: mtshan ma ming du bcas par bya //
NK029(ha)001:12867: bkug nas rdo rje phur bus gdab //
NK029(ha)001:12868: rdul du byas nas tshogs la 'bul //
NK029(ha)001:12869: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //'jig rten khams ni rab 'byams kun //
NK029(ha)001:12870: thal ba bzhin du brlag nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12871: drag po'i las rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:12872: lha mo blo ldan tshogs kyi bdag /
NK029(ha)001:12873: he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:12874: slob dpon la ni brnyas byed dang //
NK029(ha)001:12875: rnal 'byor bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK029(ha)001:12876: dam tshig gnyan po 'dral ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:12877: rdo rje spun la 'khu byed rnams //
NK029(ha)001:12878: khyed kyis rdul du brlag nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:12879: gnod sems ma lus gtan nas phyung //
NK029(ha)001:12880: gang la bya ba khyed shes kyi //
NK029(ha)001:12881: dmigs pa'i gnas nas khug la shog /
NK029(ha)001:12883: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la /
NK029(ha)001:12885: ha la ha la h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12886: tri yam dza dza tri yam dza /
NK029(ha)001:12889: badz+ra am gu sha dza pra be sha phata /
NK029(ha)001:12896: dzah dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab /
NK029(ha)001:12897: zhe sdang tshul gyis zhe sdang 'joms mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:12898: zhe sdang 'joms mdzad badz+ra he ru ka /
NK029(ha)001:12899: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab /
NK029(ha)001:12900: gti mug tshul gyis gti mug 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:12901: gti mug 'joms mdzad bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK029(ha)001:12902: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12903: nga rgyal tshul gyis ngar rgyal 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:12904: nga rgyal 'joms mdzad rat+na he ru ka /
NK029(ha)001:12905: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //'dod chags tshul
NK029(ha)001:12906: gyis 'dod chags 'joms mdzad pa //'dod chags 'joms mdzad
NK029(ha)001:12908: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12909: phrag dog tshul gyi phrag dog 'joms mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)001:12910: phrag dog 'joms mdzad karma he ru ka /
NK029(ha)001:12911: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab /
NK029(ha)001:12913: phog par rgyob cig kee ri ma //
NK029(ha)001:12914: snying la gzer cig tsoo ri ma //
NK029(ha)001:12915: dbang du bsdus shig pra mo ha //
NK029(ha)001:12916: brdul du barloga cig be rta li //
NK029(ha)001:12917: rgyu zhags drongs shig push+ka si //
NK029(ha)001:12919: tsit+ta phung zhig sme sha ni //
NK029(ha)001:12920: mgo lus phrol shig tsan+da li /
NK029(ha)001:12921: dzah sha la rol cig seng ha ma //
NK029(ha)001:12922: rus pa 'chos shig bya gri ma /
NK029(ha)001:12923: khrag la 'thung zhig sri ga ma //
NK029(ha)001:12924: lpags chen phrol shig shwa na ma //
NK029(ha)001:12925: nang grol drongs cig gri d+ha ma /
NK029(ha)001:12926: zhing chen khur cig kam ka ma //
NK029(ha)001:12927: hril mid mdzod cig kha ga ma //
NK029(ha)001:12928: thod khrag 'thung shig a lu ma /
NK029(ha)001:12929: dzah snying nas drongs shig lcags kyu ma //
NK029(ha)001:12930: mgul nas chings shig zhags pa ma //
NK029(ha)001:12931: yan lag sdom zhig lcags sgrog ma //
NK029(ha)001:12932: myos par gyis shig dril bu ma /
NK029(ha)001:12933: dzah shar nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun /
NK029(ha)001:12934: khyed kyi zhi ba'i las mdzod cig /
NK029(ha)001:12935: lho nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK029(ha)001:12936: khyed kyis rgyas pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK029(ha)001:12937: nub nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun /
NK029(ha)001:12938: khyed kyis dbang gis las mdzod cig /
NK029(ha)001:12939: byang nas gshegs pa'i rnal 'byor bdun //
NK029(ha)001:12940: khyed kyis drag po'i las madzodaciga /
NK029(ha)001:12941: gang la bya ba khyed kyis shes //
NK029(ha)001:12942: dmigs pa'i gnas nas khug la shog /
NK029(ha)001:12946: dzahsprula pa chen po dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12947: steng gi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs 'gugs pa //
NK029(ha)001:12948: h+aum chen dgra 'byin phag dang rmigs bu'i mgo /
NK029(ha)001:12949: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12950: shar gyi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs 'gugs pa //
NK029(ha)001:12951: rnam rgyal snyems ma stag dang bya rgod mgo /
NK029(ha)001:12952: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12953: shar lho mtshams nas dgra dang bgegs 'gugs pa //
NK029(ha)001:12954: dbyug sngon sder mo g.yag dang bya rog mgo /
NK029(ha)001:12955: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12956: lho yi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs 'gugs ma //
NK029(ha)001:12957: gshin rje dur khrod sha ba 'ug pa'i mgo /
NK029(ha)001:12958: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12959: lho nub 'tshams nas dgra dang bgegs 'gugs ma //
NK029(ha)001:12960: mi g.yo gtun khung gzig dang kh+aa ta'i mgo //
NK029(ha)001:12961: khyed kyi dam tshig dus ma bab //
NK029(ha)001:12962: nub kyi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs 'gugs pa //
NK029(ha)001:12963: rta mgrin gtum mo byi la pu shud mgo /
NK029(ha)001:12964: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12965: nub byang 'tshams nas dgra dang bgegs 'gugs pa //
NK029(ha)001:12966: dpal ldan 'da' bsnyems spyang ki khra'i mgo /
NK029(ha)001:12967: khyed kyis dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12968: byang gi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs 'gug pa //
NK029(ha)001:12969: bdud rtsi rlung 'byin seng ge pha wang mgo /
NK029(ha)001:12970: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12971: byang shar mtshams nas dgra dang bgegs 'gugs pa /
NK029(ha)001:12972: khams gsum gsod byed dred dang sre mong mgo /
NK029(ha)001:12973: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //'og gi phyogs nas dgra dang bgegs 'gugs pa //
NK029(ha)001:12974: stobs chen skyod ma dom dang byi ba'i mgo /
NK029(ha)001:12975: khyed kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:12976: gang la bya ba khyed kyi shes //
NK029(ha)001:12977: dmigs pa'i gnas nas khug la shog /
NK029(ha)001:12985: g+ha ta ya'i sngags kyi phur bskor bya /
NK029(ha)001:12986: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya phata dzah ma sur+y+aa man+da la /
NK029(ha)001:12994: badz+ra ki li ki li ya h+aum phata dza /
NK029(ha)001:12995: badz+ra kro d+ha ha na ha na dib+ta tsakra h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12997: badz+ra sa tra r+aa dza ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:12998: k+aa ya wa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra nan /
NK029(ha)001:13002: sarba dush+tana ma h+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13005: h+aum h+aum badz+ra ki li ki la ya /
NK029(ha)001:13006: badz+ra d+ha ro a dz+nya pa ya ho /
NK029(ha)001:13007: k+aa ya wa k+ka tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai la y+aa h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13008: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai li ya h+aum a a yam s+pha ra na h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13010: bo d+hi tsit+ta dz+nya na sid+hi ku ru h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13011: badz+ra tish+ta na hrihsh+ti bi kri t+aa /
NK029(ha)001:13012: dgra bgegs dam sri sarba sha trum /
NK029(ha)001:13023: bee d+aur sngon po'i rin chen ri rab la /
NK029(ha)001:13024: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer gdal ba ltar //
NK029(ha)001:13025: sems dpa' sngon po 'od kyi dkyil 'khor can /
NK029(ha)001:13026: dpal ldan gzi brjid 'bar la phyag 'tshal lo /
NK029(ha)001:13027: 'od phung stug po sprin ltar 'khrigs pa yi /
NK029(ha)001:13028: 'jigs byed rngam stabs brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs /
NK029(ha)001:13029: za byed bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar ba ste /
NK029(ha)001:13030: gdug pa thams cad rdo rje'i zhal du 'dren /
NK029(ha)001:13031: mi zad mche bas brgyan pa'i zhal gdangs shing /
NK029(ha)001:13032: khams gsum za bar byed pa'i skan sgra can /
NK029(ha)001:13033: nyi zla 'bar ba'i can gyi sdang mig gis /
NK029(ha)001:13034: bgegs dpung bsreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo /
NK029(ha)001:13035: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa ri kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13036: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13037: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa ri kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13039: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa ri kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13041: karma kro d+hi shwa ri kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13042: koo ri khro mo brgyad kyi zhal du kh+aa h+ai /
NK029(ha)001:13043: sid+ha phra men brgyad kyi zhal du kh+aa h+ai /
NK029(ha)001:13044: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi'i zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13045: dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13046: ye shes khro bo bcu'i zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13047: dam can chos skyong bsrungs ma'i zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13048: dgra bgegs 'byung po sha khrag kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13050: sh+ri he ru ka mah+aa badz+ra a be sha ya a be sha ya /
NK029(ha)001:13053: sh+r+ai b+aa na kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13054: 'chi med bdud rtsi a mri ta //
NK029(ha)001:13055: dug gi phung po 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:13056: ro yi khams rnams blong bar byed //
NK029(ha)001:13057: rtsi mchog sman gyi mchod bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13058: mah+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13060: bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK029(ha)001:13061: mched dang lcam bral rnams kyis ma h+aa mam sa gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:13062: rdo rje sems dpa'i sku tshe dang longs spyod la mnga' mnyes par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:13063: dza gad dpal bo gsol pas /
NK029(ha)001:13064: 'gro ba mang po dbang du 'dus par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:13065: zhal zas kyi bye brag mang po gsol bas /
NK029(ha)001:13066: zhi khro'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa la mnga' mnyes par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:13068: mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas pa /
NK029(ha)001:13069: ngan rtog mtshan pa'i spyod yul ngang gis zhi /
NK029(ha)001:13070: gzung 'dzin mtshan ma kun las 'das pa'i don /
NK029(ha)001:13071: mnyam rdzogs chen pa'i mchod pa rnam par grol /
NK029(ha)001:13074: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud d+he badz+ra ban+ha dz+nya na da ni s+aur+ya tsan+da rat+na pad+ma man+dala /
NK029(ha)001:13080: badz+ra he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13086: h+aum las kyi rdo rje byed par dbang bskur ba'i mkha' 'gro kim dang dbang phyug ma mo'i tshogs /
NK029(ha)001:13087: lhag ma kha chu'i dam la gtogs pa rnams /
NK029(ha)001:13088: dam tshig tshul bzhin mchod kyi gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13089: hohlhaga ma dang kha chu'i dam tshig la gtogs pa'i mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:13090: sgrol chen gyi ging pho dgu mo dgu bac+wa brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:13091: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:13092: dpal ldan gnyan gyi re ma ti /
NK029(ha)001:13094: sring mo chen mo bzhi 'khor dang bcas pa rnams
NK029(ha)001:13095: sngon gyis thugs dam las ma 'da' bar sgrub pa
NK029(ha)001:13096: po'i sdong grogs la gshegs shig /
NK029(ha)001:13097: e a ra li hohhrim hrim dzahh+aum bam ho /
NK029(ha)001:13098: ta ki ni +aa ka ra sha ya /
NK029(ha)001:13108: sarba badz+ra ta ki n+ai n+aam /
NK029(ha)001:13111: ta ki ni h+aum dzah hoh bdag dang chos skyong
NK029(ha)001:13112: ba'i rgyal po dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK029(ha)001:13114: rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku dgrar gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:13115: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu'i rigs la gtogs pa thams cad sgrol cig /
NK029(ha)001:13116: bzhes shig sangs rgyas kyi zhing bde ba can du gnas spor cig /
NK029(ha)001:13118: sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba tush+tana sa ma ya mu tra /
NK029(ha)001:13125: bud+d+ha k+she tre pra ti stam+b+ha ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13138: sarba badz+ra ta ki ni n+aam hrihd ya /
NK029(ha)001:13140: badz+ra ta ki ni pra tits+tsha ma h+aa ba lim ta h+aum phata kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13141: bud+d+ha t+aak+ki ni prat+tshi ma h+aa b+ha lim ta phata kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13142: rat+na ta ki ni pra t+tshi ma h+aa b+ha lim ta tram phata kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13143: pad+ma ta ki ni pra tits+tsha ma h+aa ba lim ta h+r+aih phata kh+aa h+ai /
NK029(ha)001:13144: karma ta ki ni pra tits+tsha ma h+aa ba lim ta h+aa phata kha hi /
NK029(ha)001:13145: gu ru kro d+ha rat+na sa ma ya pri sha
NK029(ha)001:13146: sarba bud+d+ha k+shi ta k+sho b+ha ka ra h+aum phata
NK029(ha)001:13148: rnam dag chos dbyings zhi ba las /
NK029(ha)001:13149: thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa 'byung //
NK029(ha)001:13150: thabs chen zla gsang thig le las //
NK029(ha)001:13151: yal gam can rnams 'du bar mdzod //'du mdzad rnam dag 'di bzhes la //
NK029(ha)001:13152: grub pa'i tshogs kyi bdag mo rnams //
NK029(ha)001:13153: re ba bskangs phyir gnas pa rnams //
NK029(ha)001:13154: mngon sum snang ba shar bar mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13155: h+aum rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)001:13156: yi dwags stan la yang dag zhon //
NK029(ha)001:13157: gdug pa'i sems kyis sdig byed cing //
NK029(ha)001:13158: dpa' bo brjid pa'i ga zugs 'dzin ma //
NK029(ha)001:13159: skal ldan rang gi lag char ldan //
NK029(ha)001:13160: sha khrag dang ni sgyu ma rnams //
NK029(ha)001:13161: rkang dang tshil bu za zhing spyod //
NK029(ha)001:13162: dga' bar byed dang 'dren byed ma //
NK029(ha)001:13163: spro bar byed dang bsod byed ma //'bar bar byed
NK029(ha)001:13164: dang gzi brjid ma //'joms byed ma dang bong bu'i
NK029(ha)001:13165: mgo / chags byed ma dang chags bral ma //'khor lo ma dang rgyas 'debs ma //
NK029(ha)001:13166: sna tshogs lus dang bsrung pa mo //
NK029(ha)001:13167: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsrungs bar byed //
NK029(ha)001:13168: gnod sbyin mo dang yang dag 'phrog /
NK029(ha)001:13169: bya rog gdong ste mig grung zhing //'jigs pa'i mig la 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK029(ha)001:13170: lag par gri dang mkhar zhong thog /
NK029(ha)001:13171: bzhad dang 'ug pa'i gdong rings ma //
NK029(ha)001:13172: khros pa khyi dang phag gi gdong //
NK029(ha)001:13173: gsus po che la stobs chen po //
NK029(ha)001:13175: khros pas ra dang byi ba'i gdong /
NK029(ha)001:13176: sgyu ma'i mgo nas za byed cing /
NK029(ha)001:13177: keng rus dkar po 'dzin pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:13178: khros pas rus pa 'phreng ba klub /
NK029(ha)001:13179: gsus po che la bum pa 'dzin /
NK029(ha)001:13180: phan tshun 'thab pa rtsom pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:13181: lce spyang gi ni 'khor gyi rnams /
NK029(ha)001:13183: rnam par bsgyur ba'i gzugs 'dzin ma /
NK029(ha)001:13184: 'khor bcas ma lus gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13185: shar nyid du ni bum sna ste /
NK029(ha)001:13186: nub tu da sha gri ba'o /
NK029(ha)001:13187: lho ru rnam par 'joms pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:13188: byang nyid du ni 'bod sgrogs so /
NK029(ha)001:13189: mdor na ye shes las grub pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:13190: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams /
NK029(ha)001:13191: don gyis sangs rgyas yin mod kyang /
NK029(ha)001:13192: sgrub pa po la phan 'dogs phyir /
NK029(ha)001:13193: bran gyis tshul du khas blangs ste /
NK029(ha)001:13194: gnas 'dir rtse cig gshegs nas kyang /
NK029(ha)001:13195: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la /
NK029(ha)001:13196: bcol pa'i las rnams 'grub par mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:13197: mkha' la 'gro ba sum bcu rtsa gnyis kyi zhal du /
NK029(ha)001:13198: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa h+ai /
NK029(ha)001:13199: ma h+aa b+aa lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13200: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13201: ma h+aa mam sa kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13204: ma h+aa ba su ta kh+aa h+ai /
NK029(ha)001:13205: ma h+aa go ro tsa na kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13206: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13207: mkha' 'gro bsang ba rgyud kyi dam tshig la gtogs pa'i mkha' 'gro ma sum bcu rtsa gnyis la /
NK029(ha)001:13209: rnal 'byor pa bdag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi sdang bar byed pa'i dgra thul /
NK029(ha)001:13210: gnod pang byed pa'i bgegs chom /
NK029(ha)001:13211: bsam pa la bar chad ma btang cig /
NK029(ha)001:13212: sa ma ya dam tshig dus la bab po /
NK029(ha)001:13213: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru ka /
NK029(ha)001:13214: ging chen ka ra'i tshogs kyi bskor ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:13215: dpa' bo tshogs kyi las rnams kun byed pa //
NK029(ha)001:13216: khro bo chen po badz+ra ging ka ra //
NK029(ha)001:13217: khro bo chen mo khams gsum dbugs bsdud bcas //
NK029(ha)001:13218: ta na ga na'i 'phrin las dus la bab //
NK029(ha)001:13219: rdo rje gnod sbyin rdo rje srin po dang //
NK029(ha)001:13220: rdo rje 'byung po rdo rje shwa na dang //
NK029(ha)001:13221: rdo rje gshin rje rdo rje ro langs dang /
NK029(ha)001:13222: rdo rje 'chi bdag rdo rje dus 'tshams dang //
NK029(ha)001:13223: dbang bsdud lcags kyus 'dren ma chen mo dang /
NK029(ha)001:13224: khams gsum g.yab mos bsdud ma chen mo dang //
NK029(ha)001:13225: gzugs med rlung ltar rgyu ba chen mo dang //
NK029(ha)001:13226: gar gyi klog bzhin 'gyu ba chen mo dang //
NK029(ha)001:13227: rbod stong len par byed pa chen mo dang //
NK029(ha)001:13228: sna snyan phra ma zer ba chen mo dang //
NK029(ha)001:13229: khams gsum snying rjes gsod ma chen mo dang //
NK029(ha)001:13230: tshogs kyi phyag tshang byed pa ma sogs ste /
NK029(ha)001:13231: rdo rje byi nu pho mo 'khor dang bcas /
NK029(ha)001:13232: khams gsum bsgrol ba'i ging chen bac+wa brgyad rnams /
NK029(ha)001:13233: lta na ga na'i tshogs kyi gnas chen 'dir /
NK029(ha)001:13234: sngon gyi thugs dam bzhin du 'dir gshegs la /
NK029(ha)001:13235: bdud rtsi dmar gyi longs spyod 'di bzhes la /
NK029(ha)001:13236: dgyes pa'i gar gyis rol ba'i 'phrin las mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:13237: kim ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13238: gim chen bac+wa brgyad kyi zhal du ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13239: ma h+aa pa lim ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13240: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13241: dpal 'bar mkha' 'gro mo rgyud kyi dam tshig la
NK029(ha)001:13242: gtogs pa'i ging chen bac+wa brgyad la 'phrin las su
NK029(ha)001:13243: bcol ba ni / rnal 'byor pa bdag la sdang pa'i dgra thul /
NK029(ha)001:13245: bsam pa la bar chad ma btang zhig /
NK029(ha)001:13246: sa ma ya dam tshig gi dus la bab po /
NK029(ha)001:13247: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru la /
NK029(ha)001:13248: dbang phyug tshogs kyi sa bskor ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:13249: grub pa'i ma tshogs rnal 'byor ma //
NK029(ha)001:13250: snying rje byams pa'i spyod yul can //
NK029(ha)001:13251: tshangs ma la sogs nyi shu brgyad //'jigs rten rnams kyi sring mo ste //
NK029(ha)001:13252: lag na blo snying nang khrol thogs //
NK029(ha)001:13253: kha la khrag dang snying la 'jib //
NK029(ha)001:13254: spu gri so la skra yegs ma //
NK029(ha)001:13255: mche ba rtse gsum 'bri tshugs lta //
NK029(ha)001:13257: gsod pa'i las rnams kun la rtsom //
NK029(ha)001:13258: rgyal mo dang ni blon mo dang //
NK029(ha)001:13259: bran mo dang ni yang bran mo //
NK029(ha)001:13260: g.yog dang yang g.yog 'khor dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:13261: ma mo chen mo khyed rnams kyang //'das pa'i dus la sngon byung ba //
NK029(ha)001:13262: de tshe dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NK029(ha)001:13263: spyan sngar khas slangs dam bcas pa //'jigs rten 'das dang 'jig brten pa'i //
NK029(ha)001:13264: ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)001:13265: sgrub pa rnams kyi las bya zhes //
NK029(ha)001:13266: rdo rje byin nas ming rtag tshe //
NK029(ha)001:13267: dam bcas bzhin du he ru ka'i //
NK029(ha)001:13269: da ltar khyed kyi gzugs mchog rnams //
NK029(ha)001:13270: mngon par ston la grub par phul //
NK029(ha)001:13271: ji srid grub mchog ma phul zhing //
NK029(ha)001:13272: khyed rnams mngon du ma gyur na //
NK029(ha)001:13273: bar du sta na'i gnas 'dir ru //'dug pa'i las rnams kun gyis shig /
NK029(ha)001:13274: rnal 'byor bcol pa'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13275: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi zhal du //
NK029(ha)001:13276: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13277: ma h+aa p+aa ling ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13278: mah+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13279: gsang ba'i snying po khro bo rang bzhin gyi le'u
NK029(ha)001:13280: bac+wa lnga pa la gtogs pa'i dbang phyug ma nyi
NK029(ha)001:13281: shu rtsa brgyad la 'phrin las su bcol ba ni
NK029(ha)001:13282: / rnal 'byor pa bdag cag la sdang par byed pa'i dgra thul /
NK029(ha)001:13283: gnod par byed pa'i bgegs chom /
NK029(ha)001:13284: bsam pa la bar chad ma btang cig /
NK029(ha)001:13285: sa ma ya dam tshig dus la bab bo //
NK029(ha)001:13286: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru ka /
NK029(ha)001:13287: ma mo'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:13288: dpal ldan nag mo re ma ti //
NK029(ha)001:13289: lcags kyi drel rta rkang gsum chibs //
NK029(ha)001:13290: d+r+aa ba dgu'i steng leb na //
NK029(ha)001:13291: byi ru dmar po'i brgyan leb can //
NK029(ha)001:13292: nyid kyi sku mdog mthing nag la //
NK029(ha)001:13293: ral pa'i zar bu g.yas nas g.yon du 'khyil //
NK029(ha)001:13294: zhal nas mi sha rta sha 'dzag /
NK029(ha)001:13295: mig nas khrag 'dzag zu lu lu //
NK029(ha)001:13296: dril rta rkang gsum rab skyod de //
NK029(ha)001:13297: dpag tshad brgyad khri bzhi stong yang //
NK029(ha)001:13298: mtshan mo gcig la khyab par nyul /
NK029(ha)001:13299: rnal 'byor chen mo a la la //
NK029(ha)001:13300: g.yas na gshin rje'i khram bam bsnams /
NK029(ha)001:13301: dgra bo khram la gdab tu gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13302: g.yon na btsan gyi sho rde'u 'grem /
NK029(ha)001:13303: dgra bo sho d+he'u nag pa khrmo /
NK029(ha)001:13304: mchan khug g.yas na byad dmar sped /
NK029(ha)001:13305: dgra bgegs byad dmar kus la thob /
NK029(ha)001:13306: g.yon na nad kyi rkyal pa sped /
NK029(ha)001:13307: dgra la yams nad rims nad thong /
NK029(ha)001:13308: 'phongs nas mtshon gyi gru gu thogs /
NK029(ha)001:13309: mtshon nad khrag du skyug tu chug /
NK029(ha)001:13310: rnam lnga dmar gyis mchod pa 'di bzhes la /
NK029(ha)001:13311: bdag gi bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:13312: h+aum rgya mtsho chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas /
NK029(ha)001:13313: dpal ldan shugs sgrol gtso mo ste //
NK029(ha)001:13314: ri rab snyil ba'i rngam stabs can //
NK029(ha)001:13315: kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho skem //
NK029(ha)001:13316: rdo rje kun grags gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13318: mdzes pa'i tshul gyi 'od 'phro zhing //'jig rten 'chi bdag gzi 'phrog ma //
NK029(ha)001:13319: kun tu bzang mo gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13321: nam mkha' stong la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK029(ha)001:13322: bdud dpung drag snyem kun 'dul ma //
NK029(ha)001:13323: rdo rje drag snyem gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13324: dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK029(ha)001:13325: khro mo gtum chen za byed ma //
NK029(ha)001:13326: pho nya mo ste drug bcu'i gtso //
NK029(ha)001:13327: sha chen khrag la longs spyod cing //
NK029(ha)001:13328: gdug pa ma lus kun 'dul ma //
NK029(ha)001:13329: rdo rje chen mo ye shes mchog /
NK029(ha)001:13330: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13331: khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK029(ha)001:13332: rdo rje dra ba'i phreng thogs shing //
NK029(ha)001:13334: rdo rje 'od chags gshegs su gsol //'od phung 'khrigs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK029(ha)001:13335: zhags pa stong gi gdeng ldan zhing //'phrin las 'byung po kun 'dul ma //
NK029(ha)001:13336: rdo rje gsal 'phro gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13337: dbang phyug chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK029(ha)001:13338: lcags kyu d+r+wa ba'i phreng thogs shing //
NK029(ha)001:13340: dam tshig nyams pa sgrol byed ma //
NK029(ha)001:13341: rdo rje g.yu sgron gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13342: ma mo chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK029(ha)001:13343: kun kyang nag mo ral pa can //
NK029(ha)001:13344: kun kyang kha nas khrag 'dzag ma //
NK029(ha)001:13345: kun kyang mig nas me 'bar ma //
NK029(ha)001:13346: ri rab snyil ba'i rngam stabs can //'khor bcas ma
NK029(ha)001:13347: lus gshegs su gsol //'khor bcas ma lus gshegs nas
NK029(ha)001:13348: kyang // rnam lnga dmar gyi mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK029(ha)001:13349: bdag gi bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13350: gling bzhi 'gyogs ma lha yi sring //
NK029(ha)001:13351: shar gyi 'gyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13352: mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK029(ha)001:13353: lho yi 'gyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13354: dmar mo g.yag thod klu yi sring //
NK029(ha)001:13355: nub kyi 'gyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13356: nag mo sder chen gnod sbyin sring //
NK029(ha)001:13357: byang gi 'gyogs ma gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13358: sring mo chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK029(ha)001:13359: shin tu gdung ba'i dam tshig can //
NK029(ha)001:13360: khro dang zhi ba'i las mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)001:13361: sring bzhi sprul pa mang po'i 'phro 'du can //
NK029(ha)001:13362: dam tshig yal gam can la brtse dgongs la //'khor bcas ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13363: rnam lnga dmar gyis mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK029(ha)001:13364: bdag gi bcol pa'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
