NK029(ha)001:13365: dpal ldan gnyen gyi re ma ti //
NK029(ha)001:13366: ma mo chen mo bdun sring ma chen mo bzhi'i zhal du mah+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13367: mah+aa b+aa lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13369: ma mo srid pa rgyud lung gi dam tshig la gtogs pa'i dpal ldan gnyan gyi re ma ti /
NK029(ha)001:13371: sring mo chen mo bzhi la 'phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:13372: rnal 'byor pa bdag la sdang ba'i dgra thul /
NK029(ha)001:13373: gnod par byed pa'i bgegs chom /
NK029(ha)001:13374: bsam pa la bar chad ma btang cig /
NK029(ha)001:13375: sa ma ya dam tshig dus la babs so /
NK029(ha)001:13378: sa ma ya b+ha k+sha h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13379: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13380: dzahh+aum bam ho pra tits+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)001:13381: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka'i 'khor /
NK029(ha)001:13384: ye shes las la grub pa'i ma sring thams cad mkhyen pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:13385: byin gyis brlabs pa dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13386: ho rnal 'byor gyi mchod yon dam pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i tshul du sbyar ba 'di /
NK029(ha)001:13387: rdul dang phyag dar dang dri ma dang /
NK029(ha)001:13388: kha chu la sogs ste so sor rang rang gi
NK029(ha)001:13389: dam tshig gi brtul bzhugs kyi so so nas ji
NK029(ha)001:13390: ltar dgyes pa bzhin du byin gyis brlabs te phul
NK029(ha)001:13391: bas / phud la dgyes pa rnams ni phud la bsnam du gsol lo //
NK029(ha)001:13392: lhag ma dang kha chu la dgyes pa rnams ni
NK029(ha)001:13393: so so'i dam tshig bzhin gsol nas mnyes shing tshim
NK029(ha)001:13394: par gyur cig / mthol gshags bzod pa gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:13395: bdag gi sngar slad du gsang ba mchog gi bka' nos pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:13396: dam tshig rtsa ba dang yan lag las tshor ba
NK029(ha)001:13397: dang ma tshor ba'am nyams pa ci mchis pa rnams
NK029(ha)001:13398: shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol bshags
NK029(ha)001:13399: mchis na / dbyings nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra bas bzod pa dang du bzhes ste /
NK029(ha)001:13400: tshangs pa dam pa yid bzhin du thob par stsal du gsol lo //
NK029(ha)001:13401: dngos grub du gsol na ni /
NK029(ha)001:13404: khyad par du yang las rnam bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:13405: bsam pa tsam gyis grub pa'i dngos grub kyi skal ba dang rgyu gang lags pa /
NK029(ha)001:13406: dus da lta nyid du thob par bstsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13407: 'phrin las snyan snyung du gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:13409: gnod par byed pa'i bgegs gdug pa'i dbal gyur pa /
NK029(ha)001:13413: so so'i rmi lam ngan pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:13415: mi shis pa'i rkyen de dag thams cad phyir bzlog
NK029(ha)001:13416: cing ming yang mi grags par zhi ba chen por
NK029(ha)001:13418: gal te zhi bas mi 'dul pa zhig mchis nas
NK029(ha)001:13419: drag po'i 'phrin las kyi dbang du bsdu ba dang
NK029(ha)001:13421: gzir cing mnan pa la sogs te /
NK029(ha)001:13422: 'phrin las bzhis ji ltar 'dul zhing 'tshams par mdzad nas /
NK029(ha)001:13423: thams cad zhi ba chen por mdzad du gsol lo //
NK029(ha)001:13424: ces 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab po /
NK029(ha)001:13425: rdo rje dpal chen khro rgyal phyag gnyan ni /
NK029(ha)001:13426: thugs rje thabs mkhas ye shes sprul pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:13427: rang rgyud dag pas rnal 'byor grub pa can //
NK029(ha)001:13428: rdo rje lcam dral ma lus dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13429: kun tu bzang po rdo rje 'dzin pa yi //
NK029(ha)001:13430: snying la gnas pa'i dam tshig byin brlabs pa /
NK029(ha)001:13431: theg chen khyed kyis dang du blangs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:13432: zhal mchis gang lags rjes su dgongs par mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:13433: bdag gi mig la sogs te dbang po rnams /
NK029(ha)001:13434: so so'i rang bzhin rnam shes ma sbyangs pas /
NK029(ha)001:13435: khyed kyi sku gsung mi thos mi mthong ste /
NK029(ha)001:13436: mun pa'i tshogs dang 'dra ba mchis mod kyang /
NK029(ha)001:13437: 'on kyang yid ches sems kyi rtse gcig tu /
NK029(ha)001:13438: mngon sum bzhin du rtag tu rjes dran na /
NK029(ha)001:13439: dus gsum ma sgrib kun du khyed mkhyen pas /
NK029(ha)001:13440: rnal 'byor lcam bral rtag tu bdag la gzigs /
NK029(ha)001:13441: bdag gi rdo rje dam tshig mchog gsum po /
NK029(ha)001:13442: khyed kyi thugs dam mchog kyang de lags na /
NK029(ha)001:13443: rigs mi mthun kyang dam tshig gcig gi bsdus /
NK029(ha)001:13444: lcam dral tshul du nye zhing gdung bar mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:13445: ye shes mngon shes ldan zhing thugs brtse ba'i /
NK029(ha)001:13446: rdzu 'phrul rmad byung phan pa'i dgongs pa can /
NK029(ha)001:13447: gzhan gyis ma bcol nyid kyis zhal 'a ches pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:13448: bden pa gsung la rtag tu grogs mdzod cig /
NK029(ha)001:13449: gang dag byang chub sems dang ldan pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:13450: sku gsum rnam 'byor brtson pa rnams la ni //
NK029(ha)001:13451: kun nas bsrung zhing re ba bkang ngo zhes //
NK029(ha)001:13452: khyed kyi thugs dam mchog kyang de lags na /
NK029(ha)001:13453: bdag la bla med byang chub sems mchis shing //
NK029(ha)001:13454: sku gsum rnal 'byor brtson par bgyid lags kyis //
NK029(ha)001:13455: rdo rje dam can ma lus rgya mtsho yi //
NK029(ha)001:13456: kun nas bsrung zhing re ba bkang du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13457: sngon 'das dus na dam chos 'jig pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:13458: zhe sdang gdug pa'i dgra bgegs gang byung bar //
NK029(ha)001:13459: lhag par khyed kyi thugs dam der byung zhes //
NK029(ha)001:13460: drag shul thabs kyi spyod pa ji lta bar //
NK029(ha)001:13461: da lta dus ngan dam chos 'jig la sogs //
NK029(ha)001:13462: sdig pa'i 'bras bu smin par khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK029(ha)001:13463: sngon gyi thugs dam snyan po rjes dgongs ste //
NK029(ha)001:13464: ji ltar 'tshams pa bzhin du 'phrin las mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13465: mi lus mthu dang mngon shes ma mchis kyang //
NK029(ha)001:13466: dam tshig phyir lus srog 'phang pa med //
NK029(ha)001:13467: skyes chen khyed kyi mthu dang ldan 'gyur yang //'gro ba'i mgon skyabs ci phyir bskul la bzhes //
NK029(ha)001:13468: mda' dka' rdo rje dam tshig mchog bsrungs par //
NK029(ha)001:13469: grub pa khyed dang bdag tu 'dra bas na //
NK029(ha)001:13470: chos bsrungs 'gro don bdag gis mi lcogs na //
NK029(ha)001:13471: byin brlabs mchog dang ldan pa grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13472: theg chen rnal 'byor bskyang par zhal ma ches pas //
NK029(ha)001:13473: dus dang tshad mkhyen mthu dang ldan bzhin du //
NK029(ha)001:13474: skyes chen khyed kyang btang snyoms mdzad na ni //
NK029(ha)001:13475: dang po'i dam bcas 'gal bar mi 'gyur ram //
NK029(ha)001:13476: gang gis gang nyid de yis dam bcas pa //
NK029(ha)001:13477: de yi de nyid don du gnyer 'os ste //
NK029(ha)001:13478: gzhan gyis bskul zhing gsol gdab mi 'tshal bas //
NK029(ha)001:13479: khyed kyi thugs dam 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13480: srid pa las kyi dus la ma bab zhes //'gro ba 'dul ba'i 'phrin las mi mdzad cing //
NK029(ha)001:13481: thams cad kun tu las kyi mthu btsan na //
NK029(ha)001:13482: thugs rje byin brlabs yong ye su la bgyi //
NK029(ha)001:13483: dbang phyug la sogs bgyi pa khas 'ches kyang //
NK029(ha)001:13484: dngos por lta ba rnams kyis bgyid mi nus //
NK029(ha)001:13485: khyod ni sgyu ma'i chos la mnga' mnyes pas //
NK029(ha)001:13486: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin cir yang grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13487: gang zhig chos dang mi 'gal brtson pa la //'bad pa'i 'bras bu med par mi 'gyur na //
NK029(ha)001:13488: snying rje thabs dang shes rab ldan pa la //
NK029(ha)001:13489: re ba bskong bar lta ni smos ci 'tshal //
NK029(ha)001:13490: dam tshig 'da' la sogs ste nyes pa gang //'tshe ba 'di la bdag gi myong gyur na //
NK029(ha)001:13491: chos bsrungs 'gro don kun gyi rtogs par nus //
NK029(ha)001:13492: chos la dbang bsgyur khyed kyis bzlog du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13493: theg chen spyod pa'i rnal 'byor lcam dral la //
NK029(ha)001:13494: nyon mongs dman pa'i sems kyis mi gsol ste //'gro don byang chub sems kyi smre gsol na //
NK029(ha)001:13495: thugs dang 'gal bar gyur pa mthol lo bshags //
NK029(ha)001:13497: badz+ra mah+aa kro d+ha sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13499: ho bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+ri he ru
NK029(ha)001:13500: ka'i 'khor nag mo bzhin mi sdug gi bu mo
NK029(ha)001:13502: dmar mo khro gnyer can gyi bu mo gnod sbyin mo chen mo bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:13503: dkar sham bzhin bzang ma'i bu mo sman btsun ma chen mo bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:13504: bod khams skyong pa'i bstan ma bcu gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:13505: 'khor zhing gi brdul brnyed dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)001:13506: sngon gyi thugs dam las ma 'da' bar /
NK029(ha)001:13507: dpal chen po bka' yi pha 'bab blangs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:13508: sgrub pa po'i sdong grogs la gshegs shing /
NK029(ha)001:13510: e +aa ra li hrim hrim h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13511: bka' yi tshogs dang bcas nyid du //
NK029(ha)001:13512: khrag 'thung de bzhin nam mkha'i sku //
NK029(ha)001:13513: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs skyong ma rnams //'dir spyon dam bskong mchod par bzhes //
NK029(ha)001:13514: bdag nyid chen mo rdo rje kun grags ma //
NK029(ha)001:13515: dpal ldan ha ri rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong //
NK029(ha)001:13516: gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje kun du bzang //'brog chen 'khor 'dul rdo rje bgegs kyi gtso //
NK029(ha)001:13517: bdud mo chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK029(ha)001:13518: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs ste //
NK029(ha)001:13519: lhab lhub mang po'i brgyan dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:13520: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //'dir byon dam bskongs mchod pa bzhes //
NK029(ha)001:13521: bcol pa'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13522: gangs dkar sha med rdo rje'i g.yu bun ma //
NK029(ha)001:13523: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum //
NK029(ha)001:13524: gzer chen mkha' la rgyu ba'i rdo rje rlung mo dang //
NK029(ha)001:13525: sma ri rab 'byam rdo rje grag mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)001:13526: gnod sbyin chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK029(ha)001:13527: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs ste //
NK029(ha)001:13528: lhab lhub mang po'i brgyan dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:13529: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang bcas //'di byon dam bskongs mchod par bzhes //
NK029(ha)001:13530: bcol ba'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13531: kong btsun de mo rdo rje bod khams skyong //
NK029(ha)001:13532: btsan la rol ba rdo rje sman cig ma //
NK029(ha)001:13533: ma btsun u ga chos rdo rje g.yar mo gsil /
NK029(ha)001:13534: g.yu yi dril snyan rdo rje gzugs legs ma //
NK029(ha)001:13535: sman btsun chen mo khyed bzhi yang //
NK029(ha)001:13536: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs ste //
NK029(ha)001:13537: lhab lhub mang po'i brgyan dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:13538: bran g.yog mang po'i 'khor dang byon //
NK029(ha)001:13539: bcol ba'i 'phrin las grub bar mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:13540: che zhes chen mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK029(ha)001:13542: a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK029(ha)001:13543: rnam lnga zhing gi mchod bkram nas //
NK029(ha)001:13544: lag tu rdo rje byin nas ni //
NK029(ha)001:13545: zhing chen 'gyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK029(ha)001:13546: rdo rje 'chang gi gral du bzhag /
NK029(ha)001:13547: bsgrub pa po la grogs bya'o zhes //
NK029(ha)001:13548: thar pa thob phyir ming btags te //
NK029(ha)001:13549: nad rnams thams cad bzlog pa dang //
NK029(ha)001:13550: dgra bgegs thams cad 'dul ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:13551: bsam pa thams cad sgrub po zhes //
NK029(ha)001:13552: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa //
NK029(ha)001:13553: dam tshig de las khyed 'das na //
NK029(ha)001:13555: snying gi dkyil nas khrag drangs nas //'o dod 'bod par gdon mi za //
NK029(ha)001:13556: de bas sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs ste //
NK029(ha)001:13557: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes nas //
NK029(ha)001:13558: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod /
NK029(ha)001:13562: ma ma sring 'gro ma h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13563: bstan ma chen mo bcu gnyis kyi zhal du mah+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13564: ma h+aa b+aa lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)001:13566: bstan ma las rgya mtsho'i rgyud kyi dam tshig la
NK029(ha)001:13567: gtogs pa'i bstan ma bcu gnyis la 'phrin las su
NK029(ha)001:13568: bcol ba ni / rnal 'byor pa bdag cag gi sdang bar sems pa'i dgra thul /
NK029(ha)001:13569: gnod par sems pa'i bgegs chom /
NK029(ha)001:13571: sa ma ya dam tshig dus la dbab po //
NK029(ha)001:13575: tram rat+na tree lok+sha s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13578: rgyal ba mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:13579: dam can thugs dam bskong gyur cig /
NK029(ha)001:13580: pha ma la sogs 'gro drug la //
NK029(ha)001:13581: tshad med gtor ma 'di bsngosa pas //
NK029(ha)001:13582: longs spyod ldan zhing tshogs rdzogs nas //
NK029(ha)001:13583: thams cad sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK029(ha)001:13587: de nas rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal btab la /
NK029(ha)001:13589: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13593: badz+ra ka ba tsi rak+sha rak+sha /
NK029(ha)001:13603: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13604: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra mah+aa kro d+ha shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13605: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13606: karma he ru ka badz+ra mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13608: badz+ra sarba sa t+wa sa ma ya /
NK029(ha)001:13610: bsngo ba smon lam la sogs bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:13614: // // gsum pa sgrub dbang gi chu bo las /
NK029(ha)001:13616: gsum pa bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo la /
NK029(ha)001:13617: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bya /
NK029(ha)001:13620: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:13622: dang po la tshad thig dang /
NK029(ha)001:13623: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:13635: dkyil 'khor chung tshad la khru gang dang /
NK029(ha)001:13636: khru bzhi'o //'bring tshad la khru bcu gnyis dang bcu drug go //
NK029(ha)001:13637: dkyil 'khor che tshad la khru nyi shu /
NK029(ha)001:13639: dbang gsum pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la /
NK029(ha)001:13642: de dag ni lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad do //
NK029(ha)001:13644: sbyin bdag 'byor ba che chung dang /
NK029(ha)001:13645: phyag len mkhas mi mkhas gyis ji ltar rigs par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:13646: lhag par ting 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK029(ha)001:13649: rab tshad nam mkha'i dbyings bsam yas pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:13650: de dag kyang slob dpon dgongs pa zab mi zab dang /
NK029(ha)001:13651: slob bu las dag tshabs che chu nga gi dbang gis 'chad par gyur pa'i rten dang /
NK029(ha)001:13652: brten pa yi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i dus so /
NK029(ha)001:13653: gnyis pa thig la bdun la /
NK029(ha)001:13655: rab gnas dang lnga ni gong sta gon gyi skabs su bshad zin la /
NK029(ha)001:13659: nang bar snga bar langs ste /
NK029(ha)001:13660: b+he ga ra sa ma yi /
NK029(ha)001:13662: 'degs pa'i phyag rgyas sta gon gyi la rten dang /
NK029(ha)001:13663: brten par bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor nam mkhar bteg la bzhugs pa bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:13664: 'bras bu'i tshom bu la sogs rnams bsdus la 'gol par bzhags /
NK029(ha)001:13666: ba byung la sogs pa'i dri bzang rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:13667: mgo ma yid sum bcus legs par chags chags gdab /
NK029(ha)001:13670: dbang phyug kun bzang gis ting 'dzin gyi ye shes kyi thig skud /
NK029(ha)001:13673: slob bu kun tu bzang mor bskyed la thig skud kyi sne mo gtad /
NK029(ha)001:13676: thig skud sems kyi rang bzhin kha dog lngar brengs kyis bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:13678: bdag rdo rje slob dpon che ges /
NK029(ha)001:13679: slob ma che ge mo la sogs pa dbang bskur ba'i phyed du /
NK029(ha)001:13680: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs gsang ba las /
NK029(ha)001:13681: ches gsang ba yang gsang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor 'dus pa mdo'i dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)001:13682: lhag par gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs pa'i thig 'debs pas /
NK029(ha)001:13683: bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13686: rdo rje ye shes kyi thig gdab du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13687: phyogs bcu ma lus dus gsum gyi /
NK029(ha)001:13688: rgyal ba sras bcas thams cad kun /
NK029(ha)001:13689: thig gi sgra 'dis rab bskul nas /
NK029(ha)001:13690: byin gyis brlabs par mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13691: badz+ra su tra sa ma ya ma tikra ma h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13693: gsang ba'i thad kar shar nub kyi tshangs thig gdab /
NK029(ha)001:13694: de nas thig 'gros dang bcas pas /
NK029(ha)001:13696: slob ma byang du phyin la /
NK029(ha)001:13698: sngags gong ltar gyis tshang thig gnyis pa gdab /
NK029(ha)001:13699: de nas slob dpon g.yas bskor gyis shar lho dang /
NK029(ha)001:13700: slob ma nub byang du byin la gong bzhin zur thig gdab /
NK029(ha)001:13701: de nas slob dpon lho nub dang /
NK029(ha)001:13702: slob ma byang shar du song la gong bzhin gdab /
NK029(ha)001:13703: mdun gyi nam mkha' la ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:13704: de nas dam tshig gi thig skud sngar bzhin thog la /
NK029(ha)001:13705: ho dgongs su gsol zhes sogs dang /
NK029(ha)001:13706: sarba shwa d+ha ni h+aum phata brjod la /
NK029(ha)001:13707: sngar bzhin tshangs thig la sogs pa gdab pas /
NK029(ha)001:13708: sku gsung thugs kyis byin brlabs dang ldan par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:13709: de yang dkyil 'khor gyi lte ba nas zur thig
NK029(ha)001:13710: bzhi rgyud la sor gnyis kyi tshad yod pa'i shing
NK029(ha)001:13711: bus cha chen bac+wa lnga bac+wa lnga'i mtshan ma rim
NK029(ha)001:13712: bzhin da bye / de nas sor gsum gyi tshad
NK029(ha)001:13713: yod pa'i shing bus cha chen nyi shu rtsa bdun
NK029(ha)001:13714: rtsa bdun yod pa'i mtshan ma rim bzhin bya /
NK029(ha)001:13715: de nas sor drug yod pa'i shing bus cha chen bdun bdun yod pa'i mtshan ma bya /
NK029(ha)001:13716: de'i steng du thig ma nor bar gdab bo //
NK029(ha)001:13717: de nas tshangs thig g.yas g.yon du /
NK029(ha)001:13718: phyi nang rang rang gi cha chen gyi tshad gyi cha chen gnyis gnyis gdab /
NK029(ha)001:13719: de nas dkyil 'khor nang gi cha bran gdab pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:13720: shar nub kyi tshangs thig gi rgyud las /
NK029(ha)001:13721: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13722: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13723: lho byang du'ang de bzhin du gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13724: de nas 'phreng du gdab pa ni //
NK029(ha)001:13725: gsum pa phyi'i cha phran gcig gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13726: bzhi pa lha snam phyed du gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13727: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13728: drug pa phyed gdab phyed ma gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13729: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13730: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK029(ha)001:13731: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:13732: cha bran lnga dang drug pa nas 'khor lo'i lte ba bskor /
NK029(ha)001:13733: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa nas rtsi bas rtse'i mu khyud bskor /
NK029(ha)001:13734: cha chen bdun pa'i thog tu glang gur dang rdo rje rwa bzhi bskor /
NK029(ha)001:13735: cha chen dgu pa dang bcu pa la pad rwa dang rdo rje rwa ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:13736: me ri gsum ci rigs 'tshams par bskor ro //
NK029(ha)001:13737: cha chen bcu gcig gi nang cha dang /
NK029(ha)001:13738: bco lnga phyi ma la 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad kyi mu khyud bskor /
NK029(ha)001:13739: dkyil 'khor bar ma la shar nub kyi tshangs thig gi g.yas g.yon du cha bran gong bzhin gdab /
NK029(ha)001:13740: de nas 'phred du sgo 'khyams dgu po la 'khyams dgu pa dor zhing /
NK029(ha)001:13743: phyed gdab phyi ma gdab pa kho na'o //
NK029(ha)001:13745: shar nub kyi tshangs thig g.yas g.yon du cha bran gong bzhin gdab /
NK029(ha)001:13746: 'phred du cha chen dang po lha rnam dor /
NK029(ha)001:13747: gnyis pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab pa /
NK029(ha)001:13753: phyi ma gdab pa d+r+wa ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:13756: bzhi pa dang lnga pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:13757: drug pa gsum cha bzhi mnyam du gdab pa /
NK029(ha)001:13758: rta babs snam bu brgyad dang /
NK029(ha)001:13759: ka ba chen mo'i ka gzhu dang /
NK029(ha)001:13760: rta babs kyi ka ba gsum ste /
NK029(ha)001:13762: bdun pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab /
NK029(ha)001:13764: chos 'khor dang gdugs kyi thig go /
NK029(ha)001:13765: de nas rta babs kyi dkyil du glang gur dang /
NK029(ha)001:13767: gdugs tog gi phyi nas dur khrod dang /
NK029(ha)001:13769: me ri rnams ji ltar 'os pas bskor ro //
NK029(ha)001:13770: de nas ye shes kyi thig dam tshig gi thig dang /
NK029(ha)001:13771: gnyis su med par ba stim /
NK029(ha)001:13773: thig skud kyi lha la kun bzang /
NK029(ha)001:13774: zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod la /
NK029(ha)001:13775: thig gi lha rnams h+r+aih zhes sgra ring por brjod
NK029(ha)001:13776: cing nam mkhar bteg thig skud kyi lha badz+ra mu
NK029(ha)001:13777: / zhes rang bzhin gyi gnas su gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13778: gsum pa dkyil 'khor bri ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:13779: dbang phyug rgyas pa'i chas su zhugs ste /
NK029(ha)001:13780: sngar rab tu gnas pa'i tshon rnams ni dkyil 'khor gyi steng du nyer ldog byas la /
NK029(ha)001:13783: phyag g.yas pa'i sor mo lnga la nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga bsam nas /
NK029(ha)001:13784: sarba pany+tsa rat+na sa ma ye h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13786: yig 'bru rnams dang tshon rtsi bsre /
NK029(ha)001:13787: med na 'theb 'dzub kyis tshon sngon po 'dzin la /
NK029(ha)001:13788: h+aum 'di ni chos dbyings dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:13789: sems can khams rnams rab sgrol phyir //
NK029(ha)001:13790: rim pa dang por yang dag ldan /
NK029(ha)001:13791: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)001:13794: phur gyi shul du cung zhig blug /
NK029(ha)001:13795: de nas rtsig pa'i sa byang shar gyi mtsham su
NK029(ha)001:13796: re kha sngon po 'dzub gang ba gcig legs par
NK029(ha)001:13797: bri / de'i lhag ma slar dbus kyi khung blug /'og ma kun gyi phyag len des 'gre /
NK029(ha)001:13799: 'di ni me long dag pa te /
NK029(ha)001:13800: sems can khams rnam rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)001:13801: rim pa gnyis par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:13802: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13804: tshon dmar po 'dzin la //+aah'adi ni sor rtog dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:13805: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)001:13806: rim pa gsum par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:13807: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13810: s+w+aa 'di ni mnyam nyid dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:13811: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)001:13812: rim pa bzhi par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:13813: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13816: h+aa 'di ni bya grub dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)001:13817: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)001:13818: rim pa lnga par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)001:13819: dngos grub dam pa bstsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)001:13820: brjod la byang shar gyi 'tsham su re kha ljang khu bri /
NK029(ha)001:13821: phud lhag dbus kyi khung bur blug la /
NK029(ha)001:13822: khams lnga dag par bya ba'i don du 'byung ba
NK029(ha)001:13823: rim brtsegs sgom pas don ye shes lnga tshon pa'i
NK029(ha)001:13824: rtags rin po che las grub pa'i ri rab tu
NK029(ha)001:13825: bsgom / ri rab de'i steng du gzhal yas khang bzhengs par bsam la /
NK029(ha)001:13826: ka pa las bkab zangs gzhongs zer ba snang /
NK029(ha)001:13827: thor ma song bar bya ste /
NK029(ha)001:13828: phyis snang re kha 'dren pa'i dus su 'dren brtag cing /
NK029(ha)001:13830: de nas zhal lung thob pa'i slob bu rnams kyis
NK029(ha)001:13831: lags sor lnga la nyi ma las gnas pa'i dpa'
NK029(ha)001:13832: bo 'bru lnga bkod la re kha bri ste /
NK029(ha)001:13833: dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi gru chad /
NK029(ha)001:13835: rtsigs pa lnga la nang nas sngon po dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:13838: ljang khu lngar gyi tshon bkra dang sbrel /
NK029(ha)001:13848: rta babs kyi sa la cha bran bcu gnyis yod pa la /
NK029(ha)001:13850: de'i steng du gnyis la rta rkang dang chu skyes /
NK029(ha)001:13851: bzhi pa la ka ba lnga pa dang drug pa la rin chen sgrom dang za ra tshags /
NK029(ha)001:13852: bdun pa ka ba brgyad pa dang dgu pa la rnam 'phyang dang chun 'phyang /
NK029(ha)001:13853: bcu pa la ka ba bcu gcig pa dang bcu
NK029(ha)001:13854: gnyis pa la shar gnyis bu dang sna tshogs khyung
NK029(ha)001:13855: mgo / rta babs bang rim bzhi byas kyang rung /
NK029(ha)001:13856: de'i steng du chos 'khor gyi gdan pad+ma /
NK029(ha)001:13858: g.yas g.yon du ri dwags pho mo /
NK029(ha)001:13860: rta babs kyi g.yas g.yon du chu srin gyi kha nas phyung pa'i rdo rje'i ra gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:13861: gdugs kyi phyi rol du pad+ma'i ra ba /
NK029(ha)001:13862: rdo rje dang me ris bskor ba /
NK029(ha)001:13864: 'khor lo rwa'i lte ba yi mu khyud 'khor lo'i rtsibs brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:13871: lha rnam rtsig pa la sogs dkyil 'khor nang ma dang mthun la /
NK029(ha)001:13873: pad+ma'i rwa ba'i tshab ma la dur khrod bri /
NK029(ha)001:13874: phyi rol du ma tram 'am tu tra bri'o //
NK029(ha)001:13876: dbus kyi lta ba mthing kha /
NK029(ha)001:13877: mu khyud gdan nag po la mi thig dkar po /
NK029(ha)001:13880: mu khyud gdan dmar po la mu thig ser po /
NK029(ha)001:13885: lha rnams dang sgo phyogs mdog /
NK029(ha)001:13886: mun pa dang glang gur gyi nang nag po /
NK029(ha)001:13888: ka brgyan de las pogs pa /
NK029(ha)001:13891: d+r+wa ba bzhi nag po la /
NK029(ha)001:13892: dra ba dmar po dang dkar po'i mu thig /
NK029(ha)001:13893: shar bu gzhi dmar po la shar bu dkar po dngul dam kha thur du bstan pa lta bu /
NK029(ha)001:13894: mda' yab gzhi nag po la /
NK029(ha)001:13895: mda' yab dkar po mchod rten nam rtse phran gyi gzugs /
NK029(ha)001:13899: chos 'khor dang ri dwags ser po /
NK029(ha)001:13905: rdo rje'i rwa ba gzhi nag po la rdo rje ser po /
NK029(ha)001:13907: dkyil 'khor bar ma'i lte ba'i mu khyud /
NK029(ha)001:13912: phyi'i mu khyud gzhi nag po la rdo rje phreng ba ser po /
NK029(ha)001:13913: gru chad dang blo 'bur phyogs mdog /
NK029(ha)001:13921: mun pa rnams spyi dang mthun /
NK029(ha)001:13934: dkyil 'khor phyi ma'i rtsig pa la sogs nang dang 'dra ba la rta babs snam bu brgyad pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:13939: sna 'phyang 'phreng ba dkar chun 'phyang ser po /
NK029(ha)001:13941: sna tshogs khyung mgo de nyid do //
NK029(ha)001:13950: mkha' 'gro ma brgyad la sogs dang /
NK029(ha)001:13956: dum bu la sogs sna tshogs bri'o //
NK029(ha)001:13957: lnga pa rnam pa 'god pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:13958: lha yi gnas rnams su lha tshom rang rang gi mdog can gdan dang bcas pa 'god /
NK029(ha)001:13959: dkyil 'khor nang ma zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang du bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:13960: bdag nyid kun bzang yab yum du bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:13963: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer las kun bzang yab yum bton la /
NK029(ha)001:13968: a a a badz+ra sa man+ta /
NK029(ha)001:13970: de bzhin du mi bskyod pa yab yum bton la /
NK029(ha)001:13971: tsaka li la stim zhing h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig /
NK029(ha)001:13975: de bzhin du rtsibs bzhi la rigs bzhi yab yum
NK029(ha)001:13976: rtsibs mchan bzhi la nang gi sems dpa' yab yum
NK029(ha)001:13977: / gru chad bzhi la phyi'i sems dpa' yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:13978: lha snam la thub pa drug /
NK029(ha)001:13979: sgo bzhi la sgo ba yab yum bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:13980: gsang gnas nas bton tsaka li la ba stim pa 'god do //
NK029(ha)001:13982: de'i steng du khro ba'i gzhal yas khang bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:13983: bdag che mchog du bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:13985: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer las /
NK029(ha)001:13986: che mchog yab yum bton la /
NK029(ha)001:13987: tsa ka li la stim la /
NK029(ha)001:13988: a kra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13990: dbus mi skyod pa'i mdun du 'god /
NK029(ha)001:13991: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:13992: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:13993: badz+ra kro ti shwo ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:13994: dbus su che mchog yab yum gyi mdun du dgod /
NK029(ha)001:13995: rigs bzhi he ru ka yab yum rang rang gi sngags kyis phyogs bzhi'i rtsibs bzhi la 'god /
NK029(ha)001:13996: lung gi he ru ka yab yum bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:13997: rang rang gi sngags kyis mtshams kyis rtsibs bzhi la bkod /
NK029(ha)001:13998: koo ri ma la sogs gnas kyi ma mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:13999: rang rang gi sngags kyi gru chad bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:14001: phra men ma brgyad rang rang gi sngags kyis 'khyams dang po la dgod /
NK029(ha)001:14002: 'khyams gnyis pa la spor ma brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:14005: sgo bzhi dzah h+aum bam ho bzhi las /
NK029(ha)001:14007: sh+r+ai badz+ra mu ka ra ya ya na ma /
NK029(ha)001:14008: sh+r+ai badz+ra gan+d+ha pra dz+wa la ya na ma /
NK029(ha)001:14009: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ka sha ra ya ya na ma /
NK029(ha)001:14010: sh+r+ai badz+ra kha tam ga pra dz+wa la ya ya na ma /
NK029(ha)001:14013: b+h+yoo nyi shu rtsa brgyad las dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:14014: rang rang gi sngags kyis bkod /
NK029(ha)001:14015: de yan chad ni khrag mthung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya /
NK029(ha)001:14016: 'khyams bzhi pa 'phrin las myur mgyogs kyi dal la /
NK029(ha)001:14018: sum bcu rtsa gnyis las mkha' 'gro ma sum bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)001:14022: h+aum bdun las ma mo bdun /
NK029(ha)001:14023: ting bzhi las sring mo bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:14028: sgrol byed ging gi dkyil 'khor la /
NK029(ha)001:14031: ging ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu b+h+yoo bac+wa brgyad kyis 'god /
NK029(ha)001:14032: bar bar 'khyams bdun pa khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK029(ha)001:14035: kro d+ha kro d+hi h+aum drug cu 'god /
NK029(ha)001:14036: 'khyams brgyad pa mgyogs 'gro yid kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)001:14037: shar du dza drug cu las dung gi pho nya drug bcu /
NK029(ha)001:14038: b+ha na b+ha na ang gu sha dza /
NK029(ha)001:14040: lhor h+aum drug bcu las gser gyi pho nya drug bcu /
NK029(ha)001:14041: ha la ha la pa sha h+aum /
NK029(ha)001:14045: zangs kyi pho nya drug bcu /
NK029(ha)001:14046: gardza gardza spo ta bam drug bcu 'god /
NK029(ha)001:14047: byang phyogs su ho drug bcu las /
NK029(ha)001:14048: lcags kyi pho nya drug bcu /
NK029(ha)001:14049: pa tsa pa tsa gan d+he ho drug cu 'god /
NK029(ha)001:14050: 'khyams dgu pa dang lnga pa dam tshig rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK029(ha)001:14051: lnga pa gong du song nas dgu pa la ma drug bcu las /
NK029(ha)001:14052: 'og phyogs kyi ma mo drug bcu /
NK029(ha)001:14053: ma ma shwa ra h+aum drug bcu 'god /
NK029(ha)001:14054: 'khyams bcu pa la rigs 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)001:14055: rigs 'dzin brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams /
NK029(ha)001:14056: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram /
NK029(ha)001:14058: bla ma dang tsa ka li dbyer med dgod do //
NK029(ha)001:14059: de nas bum pa 'god pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:14060: khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa ste /
NK029(ha)001:14064: zhi ba'i bum pa lnga rgyal theb la sog pas 'dzin /
NK029(ha)001:14066: h+aum bum pa ma lags rgyal po lags //
NK029(ha)001:14067: rgyal po sngags kyis btab nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:14068: rgyal po chen por mnga' gsol kyis //
NK029(ha)001:14069: rgyal po'i tshul du bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:14071: sngags lta gon gyi skabs bzhin /
NK029(ha)001:14074: rdo rje dang bcas pa sngar lta gon gyi skabs ltar legs par bkod /
NK029(ha)001:14077: dbang rdzas la sogs rnams dang /
NK029(ha)001:14085: 'phan bla res la sogs mchod par 'os pa'i rgyan kun gyis legs par brgyan par bya'o //
NK029(ha)001:14086: de nas dkyil 'khor la sogs de rnams la byin phabs te /
NK029(ha)001:14087: spos dkar gyis dud pa btang nas /
NK029(ha)001:14088: rol mo'i sgra sna tshogs bsgrag cing /
NK029(ha)001:14089: rnal 'byor pa pho rnams kyis chas gos bzang po
NK029(ha)001:14090: dang bcas pas has sti g.yab cing dkyil 'khor bskor
NK029(ha)001:14091: / mo rnams chas gos bzang po dang bcas pas phreng bas g.yab cing /
NK029(ha)001:14093: h+aum nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rten nas /
NK029(ha)001:14094: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rigs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:14095: rgyas pa'i bsrung mar gyur pa'i dam tshig can //
NK029(ha)001:14096: mchod do bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi //
NK029(ha)001:14097: h+aum mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK029(ha)001:14098: bcom ldan che mchog khro rgyal 'khor dang bcas //
NK029(ha)001:14099: sngags tshig bshugs kyi brda' yis spyan 'dren gyis //
NK029(ha)001:14100: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pas g.yab dor na //
NK029(ha)001:14101: dpal chen yab yum thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK029(ha)001:14102: thugs dam brda' la dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:14103: h+aum chos nyid bde ba chen po'i sku byung ba //
NK029(ha)001:14104: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:14105: dur khrod dreg pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)001:14106: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum ye shes 'bar ma
NK029(ha)001:14107: brgyad kyi ke ri khro mo brgyad po chos nyid
NK029(ha)001:14108: mkha' ltar dag pa'i seng ha phra men brgyad po
NK029(ha)001:14109: gshegs 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod nang shod du
NK029(ha)001:14110: // spor ma gsang yum tshogs rnams tshad med bzhi
NK029(ha)001:14111: rdzogs gsang ba'i rta gdong sgo ma 'khor bcas dam
NK029(ha)001:14112: tshig lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang phyug ming sring 'khor
NK029(ha)001:14113: bcas zhe sdang 'bar ba thugs kyi khro rgyal srin
NK029(ha)001:14114: po 'khor dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor
NK029(ha)001:14115: // nas // mkha' 'gro sum bcu rtsa gnyis sgrol
NK029(ha)001:14116: byed 'bar ba las kyi rdo rje ging chen 'khor
NK029(ha)001:14117: bcas ci bgyis ba ka' nyan las kyi pho nya
NK029(ha)001:14118: sde mo 'khor bcas las rnams yongs su grub pa'i
NK029(ha)001:14119: ye shes ma mo'i tshogs rnams sdom pa sa la
NK029(ha)001:14121: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)001:14122: deng gi gnas mchog dur drod tshogs re spro /
NK029(ha)001:14123: ban+d+ha gsar snying tshogs ni rdza ltar lhag /
NK029(ha)001:14124: keng rus gsar rnying tshogs ni ri ltar spungs //
NK029(ha)001:14125: rak+ta gsar rnying tshogs ni mtsho ltar ba skyil //
NK029(ha)001:14126: mam sa gsar rnying tshogs ni thang du brdal //
NK029(ha)001:14127: zhing chen gsar snying tshogs ni rlung ltar dpungs //
NK029(ha)001:14128: byang chub sems kyi tshogs ni gangs ltar chags //
NK029(ha)001:14129: brgyan cha gsar rnying tshogs ni sprin ltar gtibs //
NK029(ha)001:14130: ta na ga na'i tshogs ni dbyings na rol //
NK029(ha)001:14131: rdo rje mched lcam lha dang lha mo ra rol //
NK029(ha)001:14132: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs ni nam mkhar 'thibs //
NK029(ha)001:14133: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la spyan 'dren na //
NK029(ha)001:14134: thugs dam brda' la dgongs ste gshegs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:14135: dkyil 'khor chen po 'di la byin phob la //
NK029(ha)001:14136: bsgrub pa'i rtags dang mtshan ma bstan nas kyang //
NK029(ha)001:14137: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi sid+d+hi stsol //
NK029(ha)001:14138: badz+ra sa ma ya sid+d+hi phem phem //
NK029(ha)001:14139: badz+ra yo gi ni sa ma ya dzah badz+ra a be sha ya a a /
NK029(ha)001:14140: ces brjod pas lha tshogs de rnams dkyil 'khor dang tsa ka li'i thog du byon te /
NK029(ha)001:14142: pra b+he shas gnyis su med par thim pas lha rnams gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo /
NK029(ha)001:14143: drug pa rab gnas la brgyad de /
NK029(ha)001:14144: sngon du bya ba'i cho ga dang /
NK029(ha)001:14145: ting nge 'dzin gyi dal ba skyed pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:14146: rang bzhin gyis dkyil 'khor spyan drangs nas bstim pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:14147: dbang po skyon gsal gyi chos bdun bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:14148: me long phul la chu bdun gyis sku khrus gsol zhing sku phyi ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:14149: che ba'i yon tan dang rgyan cha rnams kyi dbang bskur zhing mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:14150: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rdzogs par phul ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:14151: bden pa'i byin brlabs dmigs shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba te /
NK029(ha)001:14152: de la yon bdag la sogs pas bskor ba bya
NK029(ha)001:14153: zhing phyag 'tshal nas mi 'bral zhing mngon du gyur
NK029(ha)001:14154: cig / ces smon lam gdab po /
NK029(ha)001:14163: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'a tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:14164: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i zhi khro rnam pa gnyis la /
NK029(ha)001:14165: rnal 'byor pa rgan po rnams kyi don ched du lta ba dang rtogs pa gsal ba dang //
NK029(ha)001:14168: 'bras bu mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:14169: rgyud las lung du bsgyur ste /
NK029(ha)001:14170: de las rgyud ni gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor mngon du bris /
NK029(ha)001:14172: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs nas /
NK029(ha)001:14174: tshe gcig gi sangs rgyas pa ni 'gro don las kyi dkyil 'khor ro /
NK029(ha)001:14175: lung gi gzugs brnyan gyi dal dngos su mi dgos ste /
NK029(ha)001:14176: lus la lha bkod yid kyi gsal btab nas zhes byung bas /
NK029(ha)001:14177: lus la lha bkod nas snying po bzlas pa tsam gyis /
NK029(ha)001:14178: sku gsal bar bsgom pa ni las thams cad kyang
NK029(ha)001:14179: ma tshon byed kyi sangs rgyas pa ni bdag don
NK029(ha)001:14180: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro /
NK029(ha)001:14181: de la lung du gyur pas /
NK029(ha)001:14185: tshogs dang gtor ma'i lung dang /
NK029(ha)001:14189: bdag lus kyi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og gnyis te bcur nyi dkyi la bcu dang /
NK029(ha)001:14190: phyogs skyong pho mo bcu'i steng /
NK029(ha)001:14191: h'u ka ra badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)001:14192: zhes sogs rtsa ba'i sngags bcu brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:14193: khro bo chen po yab yum bcu /
NK029(ha)001:14194: stod zhal gsum phyag drug tu bsgom la /
NK029(ha)001:14195: smad lcags kyi phur pa zur gsum gyis thal phyur bar bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)001:14197: mtshams 'dir thams cad ma 'dus pa med do //
NK029(ha)001:14198: sman lung ni pad+ma ban+d+hara bdud rtsi dpa' bor sbyangs la /
NK029(ha)001:14202: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags kyis ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul du sku bskyed la /
NK029(ha)001:14203: de bdud rtsi chen por byin gyis brlabs te zhu ba la 'di brjod do //
NK029(ha)001:14205: tshogs gtogs lung rgyud chen po nas 'byung ba ltar brlabs te 'di brjod do //
NK029(ha)001:14207: b+h+rum bi sha bi shud+d+he brjod pa /
NK029(ha)001:14208: phyi snod thams cad sna tshogs dag pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK029(ha)001:14209: rang bzhin rnam par dag cing 'dus ma byas pa'i pho brang chos kyi dbyings /
NK029(ha)001:14210: dbang chen yu ma lnga'i mkha' klong nas /
NK029(ha)001:14211: dus gsum du yangs dog dang /
NK029(ha)001:14214: mtho dman med pa'i dbus na /
NK029(ha)001:14215: bdag gi lus sems kyi rgyal po chen por lhun gyis grub pa /
NK029(ha)001:14216: lha'i dkyil 'khor du ye nas yin pas bdag gi spyi gtsug /
NK029(ha)001:14217: dz+nya na tsakra dz+wa la ma d+ha la zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:14218: ye shes kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa /
NK029(ha)001:14219: 'bar ba'i zer dang bcas par gyur pa'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:14220: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas phung po lnga las grub kyang /
NK029(ha)001:14221: bzhugs gnas bdag gi da bu'i gtsug 'khor lo'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)001:14226: phyogs bzhi la glang po dang /
NK029(ha)001:14230: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar bkod pa'i /
NK029(ha)001:14231: dbus kyi seng ge'i steng du /
NK029(ha)001:14232: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika ces brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:14233: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dang phyag mtshan
NK029(ha)001:14234: rgyan dang cha lugs rgyud dang mthun par gsal zhing
NK029(ha)001:14235: bskyed / de bzhin du tshangs ma la 'khor lo'i steng du rnam par snang mdzad /
NK029(ha)001:14236: rna ba g.yas pa'i steng du rin 'byung /
NK029(ha)001:14238: rna ba g.yon par gdon mi za ba rnams rtsa sngags brjod pa tsam gyis sku gsal gyis bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:14239: yum chen mo lnga don gyis 'byung lngas grub kyang /
NK029(ha)001:14240: rdo rje sems dpa'i mdun du mum d+ha du shwa ri zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:14241: kun tu bzang mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis rgyan dang cha lugs gtso bo cha mthun par bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:14242: de bzhin du yum lnga char yang gtso bo'i mdun du thabs shes rab kyi tshul du sgom /
NK029(ha)001:14243: sems dpa' brgyad rnams shes bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:14244: dbang po bzhi las grub kyang /
NK029(ha)001:14246: mig g.yas pa la k+shi hi ra tsa ya zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:14247: sa'i snying po wal gyis bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:14248: de bzhin rna ba g.yas badz+ra pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:14255: de bzhin du sems ma brgyad kyang yul bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)001:14257: sems dpa' brgyad kyi mdun du rtsa snying brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:14258: thabs shes rab tshul du gsal bar bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:14259: phrag gong g.yas g.yon ste ke mdun rgyab du khro bo bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)001:14260: khro mo bzhi thabs dang shes rab kyi tshul du gsal bar bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:14261: dpral ba dang lce steng snying khar /
NK029(ha)001:14264: zhabs mthil drug du thub pa drug rim gyis bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:14266: sog phrag tu bzang mo la sogs pa rtsa ba'i
NK029(ha)001:14267: sngags bzlas pa tsam gyis sku gsal bar bskyed nas
NK029(ha)001:14268: / ye shes lnga dang ldan pas dbang bskur zhing /
NK029(ha)001:14269: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK029(ha)001:14271: sems gsal btab pa de rang bzhin gyi sangs rgyas pa yin kyang /
NK029(ha)001:14272: shes rab zhan pas rang bzhin dang /
NK029(ha)001:14273: ting 'dzin gnyis su med par rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:14274: spyan drangs pa yang rgyud ltar tshigs bcad kyis spyan drangs mi dgos te /
NK029(ha)001:14275: rtsa ba'i sngags kyi spyan drangs pas /
NK029(ha)001:14276: thams cad de'i ngang du ma 'dus pa med pas /
NK029(ha)001:14277: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wa na h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig mum du shwa ri /
NK029(ha)001:14278: dzahh+aum bam hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam zhes /
NK029(ha)001:14279: kun bzang yab yum yan chad brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:14280: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa byon par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)001:14281: gnyis su med pas tha mi dad cing dbyer med par phyag ba tsal ba yang h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK029(ha)001:14282: na mo mum d+ha tu shwo ri na mo //
NK029(ha)001:14285: gnyis su med pa'i 'dres pa chen por phyag tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:14286: dam tshig sems dpa' dang ye shes sems dpa' dbyer
NK029(ha)001:14287: med pas chos kyi sku rtag pa chen po 'gyur
NK029(ha)001:14288: ba med par brtan zhing mi 'gyur ba bzhugs su
NK029(ha)001:14289: gsol ba ni / d+harma k+aa ya badz+ra d+h+rika m+au d+ha tu shwa ri /
NK029(ha)001:14290: sti ra badz+ra su ra ta s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)001:14291: zhes brtan zhing mi 'gyur bar bzhugs su gsol nas /
NK029(ha)001:14292: mchod cing 'phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:14294: de nas bsgrub cing mthar phyin par bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:14295: lus kyi sgul bskyod thams cad dam tshig gi phyag
NK029(ha)001:14296: rgya yin par shes par byas la mi 'gyur bar
NK029(ha)001:14297: bsgrub pa dang / ngag gi bzlas brjod thams cad
NK029(ha)001:14298: chos nyid kyi snying po yin par rtogs par byas
NK029(ha)001:14299: bsgrub pa dang / la / mi 'da' bar bsgrub pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:14300: sems kyi dran rtog thams cad ting 'dzin gyi rang bzhin yin par yid ches par byas la /
NK029(ha)001:14302: chos thams cad lha dal gyi rang bzhin du mi 'grub pa med do //
NK029(ha)001:14303: de'i don mthar phyin par bya ba'i 'phrin las mdzad do //
NK029(ha)001:14304: zhi ba'i don thams cad ma 'dus pa med do //
NK029(ha)001:14305: zhi ba'i lung gi sgom khog rdzogs so /
NK029(ha)001:14306: he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)001:14307: khro bo'i lung du bsgyur ba la /
NK029(ha)001:14308: 'di ni ye shes lha'i lung ste /
NK029(ha)001:14309: de yang dang po las dang bya ba ci dang ci rtsam kyang /
NK029(ha)001:14310: yi dam lha ma bsgom na mi 'grub ste /
NK029(ha)001:14312: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur /
NK029(ha)001:14314: bdag nyid ma h+aa yo ga'i gzhung ltar /
NK029(ha)001:14315: ting 'dzin rnam gsum gyis shes pa'i rgyud dag par sbyangs nas /
NK029(ha)001:14316: cho ga gsum gyis lha sku phyag rgya gsal bar bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:14317: cho 'phrul chen po bzhi dang ldan par bsgom nas /
NK029(ha)001:14318: de nyid lung gi 'bras bu mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:14320: e yam rak+ta ke ram zhes pas /
NK029(ha)001:14321: rlung dang nam mkha' sha khrag gi rgya mtsho dang /
NK029(ha)001:14322: keng rus kyi ri rab dang /
NK029(ha)001:14323: dur khrod kyi me ri sna tshogs pa 'bar ba'i mkha' klong yul lnga'i dal gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)001:14325: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+nya na tsakra su raya man+dala de ba tish+tha ti ra bam zhes pas /
NK029(ha)001:14326: stong gsum khams gsum kyi srid gsum gyi gnas 'di
NK029(ha)001:14327: nyid ye nas rnam dag dur khrod kyi gzhal yas
NK029(ha)001:14328: khang rgya mtha' dbus med pa /
NK029(ha)001:14329: dur khrod kyis thod rus rnam pa sna tshogs pas
NK029(ha)001:14330: rtsigs pa lha'i rgyal po dregs pa can bdud kyi
NK029(ha)001:14331: rgyal po'i gdung byas pa ti ra chung ngu mang
NK029(ha)001:14333: ru tra dregs pa'i khog pas gzhal yas gang gi dbyibs byas pa /
NK029(ha)001:14334: dur khrod kyi brgyan gzhung du ma dang mthun pas /
NK029(ha)001:14335: ye shes kyi me ri smug nag 'bar ba'i nang du /
NK029(ha)001:14338: don snying lngas kha dog lnga'i tshon phye /
NK029(ha)001:14339: nyi ma 'khor lo lte ba la /
NK029(ha)001:14340: long ka zur bzhi 'khor lo rtsibs /
NK029(ha)001:14341: nu ma byang chub kyi 'phrin las du 'brel ba las /
NK029(ha)001:14342: he ru ka don gyi ye shes kyi rtsa dgu h+aum dgu las grub kyang /
NK029(ha)001:14343: bdag gi lus la bsgom pa ni /
NK029(ha)001:14345: ma h+aa a khra sh+ri he ru ka zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)001:14346: bdag gi lus nyid che mchog he ru ka yab yum mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug par bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:14348: yum dgu dur drod kyi klong dgu las grub kyang
NK029(ha)001:14349: lus kyi g.yon shes rab kyi rang bzhin yin pas
NK029(ha)001:14350: / a kra kro ti shwa ri sgom /
NK029(ha)001:14351: tsit+ta rtsa dgu khams gsum sa dgu rang byung ye
NK029(ha)001:14352: shes su gsal ba he ru ka yab yum bac+wa
NK029(ha)001:14354: tsi ta gu h+ya he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:14355: tsi ta'i dkyil 'khor du sa nu he ru ka yab yum sgom /
NK029(ha)001:14356: 'di rnams kyi sku mdog phyag mtshan ma ha su ka dang mthun /
NK029(ha)001:14357: 'tsher pa las badz+ra he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:14358: de bzhin du mchin pa la bud+ha he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:14359: grod pa la rat+na yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:14360: glo ba la pad ma he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:14361: mkhris pa la karma he ru ka yab yum sgom /
NK029(ha)001:14362: ma mo brgyad dang 'phra med brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:14363: dur drod kyi yul brgyad dang gnas brgyad las grub kyang /
NK029(ha)001:14364: lus la bkod na g.yas kyi rtsibs ma brgyad la ma mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:14365: g.yon gyi rtsib ma brgyad la 'phra men brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:14366: phrag g.yas su rak+sha he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:14367: phrag g.yon du sa nu he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:14368: barla g.yon du gu h+ya he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)001:14369: barla g.yas du yak+sha he ru ka yab yum bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:14370: lus kyi mdun rgyab phyogs mtshams brgyad du spor ma brgyad /
NK029(ha)001:14371: de yang brgyad las smug nag mdung dang /
NK029(ha)001:14372: ral gri thog pa bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:14373: yan lag bzhi la phata bzhi la sgo ba bzhi /
NK029(ha)001:14374: sgal tshig nyer brgyad la b+h+yo las dbang phyug nyer brgyad smug nag tri shul can bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:14375: rus mgo la h+aum mthing nag drug bcu las khro
NK029(ha)001:14376: bo khro mo thod khrag rdo rje dkrugs te gsol
NK029(ha)001:14377: ba drug bcu ru bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:14378: so sum bcu rtsa gnyis la e so gnyis las
NK029(ha)001:14379: da ki so gnyis smug nag gri thogs pa bskyed
NK029(ha)001:14380: do // rtsa sum brgya drug bcu la bum sum
NK029(ha)001:14381: brgya drug bcu las pho nya sum brgya drug bcu
NK029(ha)001:14382: thod khrag rdo rje dkrugs te gsol ba bskyed /
NK029(ha)001:14383: lte'u rtsibs bac+wo brgyad la ha las ging bac+wa brgyad
NK029(ha)001:14384: gri dang thod pa thogs pa dmar nag bskyed do
NK029(ha)001:14385: // nam tshim rtsibs ma bzhi la gsang ba'i yum bzhi bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:14386: gzugs drug mgo dang bdun la ma mo chen mo bdun bsgom /
NK029(ha)001:14387: ne'u seg bzhi la sring mo bzhi bsgo /
NK029(ha)001:14388: 'di rnams rtsa sngags bzlas pa tsam gyis bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:14389: rdzogs pa'i tshul du bskyed do //
NK029(ha)001:14390: rtsa ba'i sngags dang sku mdog phyag mtshan dbang gi skabs su gsal lo //
NK029(ha)001:14392: ba spu bye ba bzhi khri bzhi 'bum ni /
NK029(ha)001:14394: yang sprul bzhi khri bzhi 'bum yang nag mo kha shog can gyi tshogs dang /
NK029(ha)001:14397: sgrol byed la sogs pa sprul pa'i phyag nyan rnam par sna tshogs par bsgom pas /
NK029(ha)001:14398: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad bdag gi lus
NK029(ha)001:14399: dang phung po dang khams dang skye mched du 'dus
NK029(ha)001:14400: la / de thams cad dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pas /
NK029(ha)001:14401: 'di ltar bsgom na sangs rgya ba las /
NK029(ha)001:14402: 'phrin las lung gis ma zin pa phal ni /
NK029(ha)001:14403: ltung grib dang gol sa che bas /
NK029(ha)001:14404: thar pa'i gnas su mi 'gyur zhing 'gro ba'i don mi rdzogs pas /
NK029(ha)001:14405: 'di ltar bsgom na lta spyod sgrub pa dang gsum gyis don ma 'dus pa med do //
NK029(ha)001:14406: de nas gang zag gsar bu yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)001:14407: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dal rtsa ba'i sngags kyis spyan drangs la /
NK029(ha)001:14408: mtshan brjod cing phyag 'tshal bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)001:14409: mchod pa la sogs pa dang /
NK029(ha)001:14410: 'phrin las snga ma bzhin du brjod nas /
NK029(ha)001:14411: bzlas brjod kyi yan lag ni /
NK029(ha)001:14412: chos thams cad dang sangs rgyas thams cad ni rang gi lus ngag yid gsum du 'dus la /
NK029(ha)001:14413: de yang rang gi byang chub kyi sems su 'dus pas thugs kyi snying po thon tshad du bazla'o //
NK029(ha)001:14414: de nas mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu 'phrin las su 'di brjod do //
NK029(ha)001:14415: lung 'di rnams rgyud kyi gzhung goms par byas nas /
NK029(ha)001:14416: lung 'di la zhugs na ri pa 'phral skye la /
NK029(ha)001:14417: 'di mdzad pa nyid kyis sangs rgya'o //
NK029(ha)001:14419: shes rab zhan pa'i spyod yul ma yin no //
NK029(ha)001:14420: lung 'di rnams las rna bar brgyud pa las /
NK029(ha)001:14421: yi ge bris kyang mi rung ngo //
NK029(ha)001:14423: khro bo'i sgom lung bkod pa'o //
NK029(ha)001:14426: na mo h+aum gi gzi byin bskyed zhes gsung ngo /
NK029(ha)001:14427: lung gi zhi khro'i sgom khog rdzogs sahwo&a&a&a //
NK029(ha)001:14428: mdo' dbang gi lhag gtor bzhugs so /
NK029(ha)001:14429: na mo gu ru 'dus pa mdo dbang lhag ma btang ste /
NK029(ha)001:14431: der lhag ma kun bsdus la /
NK029(ha)001:14433: de nas goms pa bdun bcu 'phags par 'phrin las bzhi las gang byed man+dala bya /
NK029(ha)001:14434: rdo rje dri chu'i dal bya /
NK029(ha)001:14435: rdo rje slob dpon rtsa ba'i dal la mnyam par bzung /
NK029(ha)001:14436: las 'khan la sogs pas sgo ba yan chad sngags kyis gsal gdab /
NK029(ha)001:14437: de nas lhag ma'i 'gron snyan gsan dbab /
NK029(ha)001:14440: lhag ma kha chu dam tshig la gtogs pa rnams
NK029(ha)001:14441: sngon gyis thugs dam la ma 'da' bar bsgrub pa
NK029(ha)001:14442: po bdag gi sdong grogs la gshegs cig /
NK029(ha)001:14443: e a ra li hrim hrim hrim /
NK029(ha)001:14444: zhes thal mo lan gsum brdab po /
NK029(ha)001:14445: lhag ma 'gron byon la ma reg par bsam /
NK029(ha)001:14446: ta ki ni'i mu tras spyan drangs /
NK029(ha)001:14447: bdag gis dal gyi phyi rol du zil gyis mnan /
NK029(ha)001:14448: rta gdong gi dbang du bsdu /
NK029(ha)001:14452: h+aum bcom ldan rat+na he ru la /
NK029(ha)001:14453: koo r+ai'ii tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:14454: byang chub sem dpa' brgyad rnams kyis //
NK029(ha)001:14455: ma mo khro mo brgyad du sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14456: srin mo chen mo brgyad du brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14457: byang chub sa yi snying po yis //
NK029(ha)001:14458: khro mo chen mo koo r+air sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14459: srin mo chen mo ke thod brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14460: lhag ma byin nas dam la rtags //
NK029(ha)001:14461: rdo rje'i dam las bro skyal te //
NK029(ha)001:14462: gtan gyi bran du mched kyis 'tshal //
NK029(ha)001:14463: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bcas ste //
NK029(ha)001:14464: rdo rje'i dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK029(ha)001:14465: las kyi lhag ma 'di longs la /
NK029(ha)001:14466: bcol pa'i mkhas blang dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK029(ha)001:14467: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)001:14469: byang chub nam mkha'i snying po yis //
NK029(ha)001:14470: khro mo chen po tsoo rir sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14471: srin mo chen mo mda' 'phen brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14472: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14473: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14474: / byang chub spyan ras gzigs dbang gis //
NK029(ha)001:14475: khro mo chen mo pra mor sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14476: srin mo chen mo 'dzin byed brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14477: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14478: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi yi byang chub phyag na
NK029(ha)001:14479: rdo rje yis // khro mo chen mo be tar sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14480: srin mo chen mo za byed brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14481: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14482: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14483: / byang chub sems dpa' me tri yis //
NK029(ha)001:14484: khro mo chen mo push+kara sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14485: srin mo nang rol 'dren ma brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14486: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14487: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14488: / byang chub sgrib pa rnam sel gyis //
NK029(ha)001:14489: khro mo chen mo g+hasmara sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14490: srin mo chen mo rab 'jigs brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14491: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14492: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14493: / byang chub kun tu bzang po yis //
NK029(ha)001:14494: khro mo chen mo sme shar sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14495: srin mo chen mo srog cod brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14496: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14497: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14498: / byang chub chen po 'jam dpal gyis //
NK029(ha)001:14499: khro mo chen mo tsan dar sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14500: sme sha chen mo smyon ma brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14501: dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK029(ha)001:14502: phra men tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:14503: mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad rnams kyis //
NK029(ha)001:14504: seng ha phra men brgyad du sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14505: srin mo mgo brnyan brgyad rnams brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14506: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14507: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14508: / shar phyogs lha mo l+aa se ma //'phra men chen mo seng mgor sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14509: srin mo 'joms byed seng mgo brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14510: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14511: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14512: lho phyogs lha mo m+aa le mas //'phra men chen
NK029(ha)001:14514: srin mo za byed stag mgor brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14515: nub phyogs lha mo g+aiirti mas //'phra men chen mo wa mgor sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14516: srin mo len byed wa mgor brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14517: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14518: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14519: / byang phyogs lha mo nir ti mas //'phra men chen mo spyang mgor sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14520: srin mo ra ro khyim mgo brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14521: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14522: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14523: / shar lho lha mo d+hu pe mas //'phra men bya rgod mgo ru sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14524: srin mo bya rgod mgo can brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14525: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14526: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14527: / lho nub lha mo me tog mas //'phra men kam ka'i mgo can sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14529: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14530: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14531: / nub byang lha mo a lo ke /'phra men bya rog mgo can sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14532: srin mo 'jom byed bya rog brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14533: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14534: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14535: / byang shar lha mo dri chab mas //'phra men hu lu mu ka ra sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14536: srin mo rku byed 'ug mgo brtul //
NK029(ha)001:14537: lhag ma rdo rje gtan gyi sngon gyi rdo rje'i
NK029(ha)001:14538: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14539: / dpal chen rak+sha he ru ka sgo ma'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)001:14540: tshad med sgo ba bzhi rnams kyis //
NK029(ha)001:14541: ta krid sgo ma bzhi ru sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14542: shar phyogs byams pa lcags kyu mas //
NK029(ha)001:14543: sgo ma rta gdong dkar mo sprul //
NK029(ha)001:14544: srin mo rta'i mgo can brtul //

NK029(ha)001:14546: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14547: / lho phyogs snying rje zhags pa mas //
NK029(ha)001:14548: sgo ma phag mgo zhags par sprul //

NK029(ha)001:14550: nub phyogs dga' ba lcags sgrogs mas //
NK029(ha)001:14551: sgo ma dred mgo lcags sgrogs sprul //

NK029(ha)001:14554: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14555: / byang phyogs btang snyoms dril bu mas //
NK029(ha)001:14556: sgo ma chen mo spyang mgor sprul //

NK029(ha)001:14559: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig

NK029(ha)001:14561: spor ma'o tshogs kyis bskor ba ni /
NK029(ha)001:14562: dpal chen thugs rje'i sbyor ba las //
NK029(ha)001:14563: thub drug yid chos brgyad po yis //

NK029(ha)001:14567: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
NK029(ha)001:14568: / kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pas //

NK029(ha)001:14570: yi dwags thub pa gnas gyur pas //
NK029(ha)001:14571: spor ma glog 'phreng 'dzin mar sprul //'bar ma chen mo glog 'phreng brtul //

NK029(ha)001:14573: las kyi bcol pa'i phyi'i dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig
